\par }}\dpx5294\dpy-818\dpxsize900\dpysize360\dpfillfgcr255\dpfillfgcg255\dpfillfgcb255\dpfillbgcr255\dpfillbgcg255\dpfillbgcb255\dpfillpat1\dplinehollow}}}}{\fs18\insrsid1378858 ti\'d5n h\'b5nh kh\'b6o s\'b8t ch\'f1 ngh\'dca th\'f9c d\'a9n, \'ae\'d5 qu\'e8c 
\'eb c\'b8c n\'ad\'edc t\'ad b\'b6n ch\'f1 y\'d5u v\'b5 nhi\'d2u n\'ad\'edc thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea c\'f1a ch\'f3ng, Ch\'f1 t\'dech H\'e5 Ch\'dd Minh \'ae\'b7 s\'edm nh\'cbn th\'f8c \'ae\'ad\'eec xu h\'ad\'edng ph\'b8t tri\'d3n c\'f1a th\'eai \'ae\'b9i, t\'f5
 m\'e9t ng\'ad\'eai y\'aau n\'ad\'edc n\'e5ng nhi\'d6t, Ng\'ad\'eai \'ae\'b7 b\'bet g\'c6p ch\'f1 ngh\'dca M\'b8c - L\'aanin, tr\'eb th\'b5nh ng\'ad\'eai c\'e9ng s\'b6n. T\'f5 \'ae\'e3, Ng\'ad\'eai r\'f3t ra k\'d5t lu\'cbn: "}{\i\fs18\insrsid1378858 Mu
\'e8n c\'f8u n\'ad\'edc v\'b5 gi\'b6i ph\'e3ng d\'a9n t\'e9c kh\'abng c\'e3 con \'ae\'ad\'eang n\'b5o kh\'b8c con \'ae\'ad\'eang c\'b8ch m\'b9ng v\'ab s\'b6n}{\fs18\insrsid1378858 ". \'a7\'e3 l\'b5 con \'ae\'ad\'eang c\'b8ch m\'b9ng d\'a9n ch\'f1 t\'ad s
\'b6n ki\'d3u m\'edi do \'a7\'b6ng ti\'aan phong c\'f1a giai c\'cap c\'abng nh\'a9n l\'b7nh \'ae\'b9o nh\'bbm \'ae\'b8nh \'ae\'e6 \'ae\'d5 qu\'e8c v\'b5 phong ki\'d5n tay sai, gi\'b5nh \'ae\'e9c l\'cbp d\'a9n t\'e9c, th\'f9c hi\'d6n ng\'ad\'eai c\'b5y c
\'e3 ru\'e9ng, sau \'ae\'e3 ti\'d5n l\'aan l\'b5m c\'b8ch m\'b9ng x\'b7 h\'e9i ch\'f1 ngh\'dca, th\'f9c hi\'d6n ch\'f1 ngh\'dca x\'b7 h\'e9i v\'b5 ch\'f1 ngh\'dca c\'e9ng s\'b6n \'eb Vi\'d6t Nam. \'a7\'e3 l\'b5 \'ae\'ad\'eang l\'e8i gi\'ad\'acng cao ng
\'e4n c\'ea \'ae\'e9c l\'cbp d\'a9n t\'e9c v\'b5 ch\'f1 ngh\'dca x\'b7 h\'e9i, k\'d5t h\'eep ch\'f1 ngh\'dca y\'aau n\'ad\'edc v\'b5 ch\'f1 ngh\'dca qu\'e8c t\'d5 c\'f1a giai c\'cap c\'abng nh\'a9n, k\'d5t h\'eep s\'f8c m\'b9nh d\'a9n t\'e9c v\'b5 s\'f8
c m\'b9nh th\'eai \'ae\'b9i nh\'bbm \'aei t\'edi m\'f4c ti\'aau cao c\'b6 l\'b5 gi\'b6i ph\'e3ng d\'a9n t\'e9c, gi\'b6i ph\'e3ng x\'b7 h\'e9i v\'b5 gi\'b6i ph\'e3ng con ng\'ad\'eai. \'a7\'e3 c\'f2ng l\'b5 }{\i\fs18\insrsid1378858 n\'e9i dung t\'e6ng qu
\'b8t c\'f1a t\'ad t\'ad\'ebng H\'e5 Ch\'dd Minh.}{\fs18\insrsid1378858 
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa60\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs18\insrsid1378858 T\'ad t\'ad\'ebng }{\i\f37\fs18\insrsid1378858 "Kh\'abng c
\'e3 g\'d7 qu\'fd h\'acn \'ae\'e9c l\'cbp, t\'f9 do" }{\f37\fs18\insrsid1378858 l\'b5 \'aei\'d3m xu\'cat ph\'b8t c\'f1a t\'ad t\'ad\'ebng H\'e5 Ch\'dd Minh. T\'f5 m\'e9t thanh ni\'aan thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea, m\'cat n\'ad\'edc, ra \'aei t\'d7m \'ae\'ad\'eang c
\'f8u n\'ad\'edc, m\'f4c ti\'aau tr\'ad\'edc m\'bet c\'f1a Ng\'ad\'eai l\'b5 gi\'b6i ph\'e3ng d\'a9n t\'e9c. V\'can \'ae\'d2 \'ae\'c6t ra l\'b5 trong \'aei\'d2u ki\'d6n ch\'f1 ngh\'dca \'ae\'d5 qu\'e8c \'ae\'b7 tr\'eb th\'b5nh m\'e9t h\'d6 th\'e8ng th\'d5
 gi\'edi, c\'b8c d\'a9n t\'e9c thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea c\'e3 th\'d3 b\'bbng con \'ae\'ad\'eang n\'b5o \'ae\'d3 gi\'b5nh th\'beng l\'eei ? D\'ad\'edi \'b8nh s\'b8ng }{\i\f37\fs18\insrsid1378858 Lu\'cbn c\'ad\'acng v\'d2 v\'can \'ae\'d2 d\'a9n t\'e9c v\'b5 v\'ca
n \'ae\'d2 thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea}{\f37\fs18\insrsid1378858  c\'f1a V.I. L\'aanin v\'b5 t\'cam g\'ad\'acng C\'b8ch m\'b9ng Th\'b8ng M\'ad\'eai Nga, Ng\'ad\'eai \'ae\'b7 t\'d7m ra con \'ae\'ad\'eang gi\'b6i ph\'e3ng cho d\'a9n t\'e9c m\'d7nh v\'b5 cho t\'cat c
\'b6 c\'b8c d\'a9n t\'e9c thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea. Ng\'ad\'eai kh\'bcng \'ae\'denh: "ch\'d8 c\'e3 ch\'f1 ngh\'dca x\'b7 h\'e9i v\'b5 ch\'f1 ngh\'dca c\'e9ng s\'b6n m\'edi gi\'b6i ph\'e3ng \'ae\'ad\'eec c\'b8c d\'a9n t\'e9c b\'de \'b8p b\'f8c v\'b5 giai c\'ca
p c\'abng nh\'a9n to\'b5n th\'d5 gi\'edi"}{\cs17\f37\fs18\super\insrsid1378858 1{\footnote \pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sl-240\slmult0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {
\f37\fs16\expnd0\expndtw-4\insrsid1378858 1) T\'cat c\'b6 nh\'f7ng c\'a9u tr\'ddch kh\'abng c\'e3 ch\'f3 th\'ddch \'ae\'d2u \'ae\'ad\'eec r\'f3t ra t\'f5 trong b\'e9 }{\i\f37\fs16\expnd0\expndtw-4\insrsid1378858 H\'e5 Ch\'dd Minh To\'b5n t\'cbp.}})}{
\f37\fs18\insrsid1378858 . Ng\'ad\'eai \'ae\'ada ra h\'d7nh \'b6nh so s\'b8nh n\'e6i ti\'d5ng: Ch\'f1 ngh\'dca \'ae\'d5 qu\'e8c l\'b5 "con \'ae\'d8a hai v\'dfi", do \'ae\'e3 c\'b8ch m\'b9ng gi\'b6i ph\'e3ng d\'a9n t\'e9c mu\'e8n th\'beng l\'eei ph\'b6i th
\'f9c hi\'d6n \'ae\'ad\'eec s\'f9 li\'aan minh chi\'d5n \'ae\'cau gi\'f7a v\'ab s\'b6n \'eb thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea v\'edi v\'ab s\'b6n \'eb ch\'ddnh qu\'e8c nh\'dep nh\'b5ng nh\'ad hai c\'b8nh c\'f1a m\'e9t con chim. V\'d7 b\'e3c l\'e9t thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea l
\'b5 m\'e9t trong hai ngu\'e5n s\'e8ng c\'f1a ch\'f1 ngh\'dca t\'ad b\'b6n, cho n\'aan mu\'e8n \'ae\'b8nh \'ae\'e6 ch\'f1 ngh\'dca \'ae\'d5 qu\'e8c, tr\'ad\'edc h\'d5t ph\'b6i xo\'b8 b\'e1 thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea c\'f1a ch\'f3ng \'aei. Do \'ae\'e3, c\'b8ch m
\'b9ng thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea kh\'abng ch\'d8 tr\'abng ch\'ea v\'b5o k\'d5t qu\'b6 c\'f1a c\'b8ch m\'b9ng 
\par }\pard \qj \li0\ri0\sa60\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\lang1024\langfe1024\noproof\insrsid1378858 
