\'edi c\'b8ch m\'b9ng \'eb ch\'ddnh qu\'e8c, h\'acn n\'f7a n\'e3 c\'c7n ph\'b6i ch\'f1 \'ae\'e9ng v\'b5 c\'e3 th\'d3 gi\'b5nh th\'beng l\'eei tr\'ad\'edc, v\'b5 b\'bbng th\'beng l\'eei c\'f1a m\'d7nh n\'e3 c\'e3 th\'d3 \'ae\'e3ng g\'e3p v\'b5o s\'f9 nghi
\'d6p gi\'b6i ph\'e3ng anh em v\'ab s\'b6n \'eb ph\'ad\'acng T\'a9y. Ng\'ad\'eai vi\'d5t:
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa60\sl-272\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs18\insrsid1378858 "Ng\'b5y m\'b5 h\'b5ng tr\'a8m tri\'d6u nh\'a9n d\'a9n ch\'a9u }{\f38\fs18\insrsid1378858 \'b8}{
\f37\fs18\insrsid1378858  b\'de t\'b5n s\'b8t v\'b5 \'b8p b\'f8c th\'f8c t\'d8nh \'ae\'d3 g\'b9t b\'e1 s\'f9 b\'e3c l\'e9t \'ae\'aa ti\'d6n c\'f1a m\'e9t b\'e4n th\'f9c d\'a9n l\'dfng tham kh\'abng \'ae\'b8y, h\'e4 s\'cf h\'d7nh th\'b5nh m\'e9t l\'f9c l
\'ad\'eeng kh\'e6ng l\'e5, v\'b5 trong khi th\'f1 ti\'aau m\'e9t trong nh\'f7ng \'aei\'d2u ki\'d6n t\'e5n t\'b9i c\'f1a ch\'f1 ngh\'dca t\'ad b\'b6n l\'b5 ch\'f1 ngh\'dca \'ae\'d5 qu\'e8c, h\'e4 c\'e3 th\'d3 gi\'f3p \'ae\'ec nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai anh em m
\'d7nh \'eb ph\'ad\'acng T\'a9y trong nhi\'d6m v\'f4 gi\'b6i ph\'e3ng ho\'b5n to\'b5n".
\par }\pard\plain \s16\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa60\sl-272\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 \'a7\'e3 l\'b5 m\'e9t lu\'cbn \'aei\'d3m s\'b8ng t\'b9o m
\'b5 Ch\'f1 t\'dech H\'e5 Ch\'dd Minh \'ae\'b7 c\'e8ng hi\'d5n v\'b5o s\'f9 ph\'b8t tri\'d3n l\'fd lu\'cbn c\'f1a ch\'f1 ngh\'dca M\'b8c - L\'aanin v\'d2 c\'b8ch m\'b9ng gi\'b6i ph\'e3ng d\'a9n t\'e9c \'eb thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea. Tr\'aan n\'d2n t\'b6ng l\'fd
 lu\'cbn \'ae\'e3, Ng\'ad\'eai \'ae\'b7 c\'efng v\'edi \'a7\'b6ng ta \'ae\'d2 ra v\'b5 gi\'b6i quy\'d5t \'ae\'f3ng \'ae\'ben nhi\'d2u v\'can \'ae\'d2 v\'d2 chi\'d5n l\'ad\'eec v\'b5 s\'b8ch l\'ad\'eec, d\'c9n \'ae\'d5n th\'beng l\'eei l\'dech s\'f6 c\'f1
a cu\'e9c C\'b8ch m\'b9ng Th\'b8ng T\'b8m.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa60\sl-272\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\i\f37\fs18\insrsid1378858 T\'ad t\'ad\'ebng H\'e5 Ch\'dd Minh v\'d2 gi\'b6i ph\'e3
ng d\'a9n t\'e9c g\'ben b\'e3 th\'e8ng nh\'cat v\'edi t\'ad t\'ad\'ebng c\'f1a Ng\'ad\'eai v\'d2 ch\'f1 ngh\'dca x\'b7 h\'e9i}{\f37\fs18\insrsid1378858 . }{\f37\fs18\lang1053\langfe1033\langnp1053\insrsid1378858 V\'d7 c\'b8ch m\'b9ng gi\'b6i ph\'e3ng d
\'a9n t\'e9c 
\par }\pard \qj \li0\ri0\sa60\sl-272\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs18\lang1053\langfe1033\langnp1053\insrsid1378858 mu\'e8n th\'beng l\'eei ph\'b6i \'aei theo con \'ae\'ad\'eang c\'b8ch m\'b9ng v\'ab s\'b6n, do 
\'a7\'b6ng c\'f1a giai c\'cap c\'abng nh\'a9n l\'b7nh \'ae\'b9o, cho n\'aan con \'ae\'ad\'eang ph\'b8t tri\'d3n t\'cat y\'d5u c\'f1a c\'b8ch m\'b9ng gi\'b6i ph\'e3ng d\'a9n t\'e9c s\'cf l\'b5 ti\'d5n l\'aan c\'b8ch m\'b9ng x\'b7 h\'e9i ch\'f1 ngh\'dca. Ng
\'ad\'eai kh\'bcng \'ae\'denh: "C\'b8ch m\'b9ng gi\'b6i ph\'e3ng d\'a9n t\'e9c ph\'b6i ph\'b8t tri\'d3n th\'b5nh c\'b8ch m\'b9ng x\'b7 h\'e9i ch\'f1 ngh\'dca th\'d7 m\'edi gi\'b5nh \'ae\'ad\'eec th\'beng l\'eei ho\'b5n to\'b5n".
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa60\sl-272\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\fs18\lang1053\langfe1033\langnp1053\insrsid1378858 \'a7\'e9c l\'cbp d\'a9
n t\'e9c g\'ben li\'d2n v\'edi ch\'f1 ngh\'dca x\'b7 h\'e9i l\'b5 }{\i\fs18\lang1053\langfe1033\langnp1053\insrsid1378858 lu\'cbn \'aei\'d3m trung t\'a9m}{\fs18\lang1053\langfe1033\langnp1053\insrsid1378858  c\'f1a t\'ad t\'ad\'ebng H\'e5 Ch\'dd Minh, n
\'e3 th\'a9m nh\'cbp v\'b5 xuy\'aan su\'e8t to\'b5n b\'e9 h\'d6 th\'e8ng t\'ad t\'ad\'ebng c\'f1a Ng\'ad\'eai trong c\'b8c th\'eai k\'fa v\'b5 tr\'aan c\'b8c l\'dcnh v\'f9c.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa60\sl-272\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs18\lang1053\langfe1033\langnp1053\insrsid1378858 Ngay t\'f5 khi \'a7\'b6ng C
\'e9ng s\'b6n Vi\'d6t Nam m\'edi th\'b5nh l\'cbp, trong Ch\'ddnh c\'ad\'acng v\'ben t\'bet do Ng\'ad\'eai kh\'ebi th\'b6o, \'ae\'b7 kh\'bcng \'ae\'denh s\'f9 l\'f9a ch\'e4n con \'ae\'ad\'eang x\'b7 h\'e9i ch\'f1 ngh\'dca khi \'ae\'c6t nhi\'d6m v\'f4 gi
\'b6i ph\'e3ng d\'a9n t\'e9c trong tri\'d3n v\'e4ng ti\'d5n l\'aan ch\'f1 ngh\'dca x\'b7 h\'e9i. Th\'cbt v\'cby, t\'ad t\'ad\'ebng H\'e5 Ch\'dd Minh \'ae\'b7 l\'b5m s\'b8ng t\'e1 m\'e8i quan h\'d6 h\'f7u c\'ac gi\'f7a gi\'b6i ph\'e3ng d\'a9n t\'e9c v\'ed
i ch\'f1 ngh\'dca x\'b7 h\'e9i, \'ae\'c6t n\'d2n t\'b6ng cho b\'ad\'edc chuy\'d3n bi\'d5n t\'f5 c\'b8ch m\'b9ng d\'a9n t\'e9c d\'a9n ch\'f1 nh\'a9n d\'a9n l\'aan c\'b8ch m\'b9ng x\'b7 h\'e9i ch\'f1 ngh\'dca \'eb n\'ad\'edc ta. \'a7\'a9y l\'b5 t\'ad t\'ad
\'ebng l\'edn th\'d3 hi\'d6n t\'ddnh quy lu\'cbt c\'f1a s\'f9 ph\'b8t tri\'d3n l\'dech s\'f6 x\'b7 h\'e9i Vi\'d6t Nam: ch\'d8 c\'e3 ho\'b5n th\'b5nh c\'b8cH
\par }\pard\plain \s16\qj \li0\ri0\sa60\sl-268\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\lang1024\langfe1024\noproof\insrsid1378858 
