\'aei\'d2u ki\'d6n ti\'d5n l\'aan ch\'f1 ngh\'dca x\'b7 h\'e9i, v\'b5 ch\'d8 c\'e3 l\'b5m c\'b8ch m\'b9ng x\'b7 h\'e9i ch\'f1 ngh\'dca m\'edi gi\'f7 v\'f7ng nh\'f7ng th\'b5nh qu\'b6 do s\'f9 nghi\'d6p gi\'b6i ph\'e3ng d\'a9n t\'e9c mang l\'b9i.}{
\fs20\lang1053\langfe1033\langnp1053\insrsid1378858 
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa60\sl-272\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs18\lang1053\langfe1033\langnp1053\insrsid1378858 \'a7\'e9c l\'cbp d\'a9n t
\'e9c g\'ben li\'d2n v\'edi ch\'f1 ngh\'dca x\'b7 h\'e9i trong t\'ad t\'ad\'ebng H\'e5 Ch\'dd Minh kh\'abng ch\'d8 ph\'b8t huy t\'b8c d\'f4ng trong giai \'aeo\'b9n \'a7\'b6ng ta l\'b7nh \'ae\'b9o nh\'a9n d\'a9n ta ti\'d5n h\'b5nh cu\'e9c c\'b8ch m\'b9
ng gi\'b6i ph\'e3ng d\'a9n t\'e9c (1945-1954) m\'b5 c\'dfn xuy\'aan su\'e8t qu\'b8 tr\'d7nh ti\'d5n h\'b5nh \'ae\'e5ng th\'eai hai chi\'d5n l\'ad\'eec c\'b8ch m\'b9ng kh\'b8c nhau, nh\'adng c\'e3 quan h\'d6 kh\'a8ng kh\'ddt v\'edi nhau - c\'b8ch m\'b9ng d
\'a9n t\'e9c d\'a9n ch\'f1 nh\'a9n d\'a9n \'eb mi\'d2n Nam v\'b5 c\'b8ch m\'b9ng x\'b7 h\'e9i ch\'f1 ngh\'dca \'eb mi\'d2n B\'bec (giai \'aeo\'b9n 1954-1975) c\'f2ng nh\'ad trong nhi\'d6m v\'f4 x\'a9y d\'f9ng ch\'f1 ngh\'dca x\'b7 h\'e9i v\'b5 b\'b6o v
\'d6 T\'e6 qu\'e8c hi\'d6n nay.
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa60\sl-272\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\fs18\lang1053\langfe1033\langnp1053\insrsid1378858 T\'ad t\'ad\'ebng H\'e5
 Ch\'dd Minh v\'d2 \'ae\'e9c l\'cbp d\'a9n t\'e9c g\'ben li\'d2n v\'edi ch\'f1 ngh\'dca x\'b7 h\'e9i l\'b5 t\'e6ng h\'eep nh\'f7ng quan \'aei\'d3m chi\'d5n l\'ad\'eec c\'e3 \'fd ngh\'dca ch\'d8 \'ae\'b9o l\'edn v\'d2 ch\'ddnh tr\'de v\'b5 l\'fd lu\'cbn, v
\'d2 nh\'cbn th\'f8c v\'b5 h\'b5nh \'ae\'e9ng c\'f1a to\'b5n \'a7\'b6ng, to\'b5n d\'a9n ta trong to\'b5n b\'e9 ti\'d5n tr\'d7nh c\'b8ch m\'b9ng Vi\'d6t Nam. N\'bem \'ae\'ad\'eec n\'e9i dung t\'ad t\'ad\'ebng \'cay, qu\'b8n tri\'d6t \'ae\'f3ng nguy\'aan t
\'bec chi\'d5n l\'ad\'eec \'cay c\'f1a t\'ad t\'ad\'ebng H\'e5 Ch\'dd Minh l\'b5 c\'ac s\'eb ph\'ad\'acng ph\'b8p lu\'cbn \'ae\'d3 hi\'d3u \'ae\'ad\'eec con \'ae\'ad\'eang ph\'b8t tri\'d3n c\'f1a c\'b8ch m\'b9ng n\'ad\'edc ta, \'ae\'e5ng th\'eai gi\'f3
p hi\'d3u r\'e2 nh\'f7ng nguy\'aan nh\'a9n s\'a9u xa v\'b5 di\'d4n bi\'d5n ph\'f8c t\'b9p c\'f1a t\'d7nh h\'d7nh th\'d5 gi\'edi hi\'d6n nay. C\'f2ng tr\'aan c\'ac s\'eb \'cay hi\'d3u r\'e2 v\'d7 sao \'a7\'b6ng ta l\'b9i k\'d5t h\'eep \'ae\'ad\'eec v\'b5 k
\'d5t h\'eep t\'e8t s\'f8c m\'b9nh c\'f1a d\'a9n t\'e9c ta v\'b5 s\'f8c m\'b9nh c\'f1a th\'eai \'ae\'b9i trong qu\'b8 tr\'d7nh x\'a9y d\'f9ng v\'b5 b\'b6o v\'d6 T\'e6 qu\'e8c ta. Ch\'a9n l\'fd \'ae\'e9c l\'cbp d\'a9n t\'e9c v\'b5 ch\'f1 ngh\'dca x\'b7 h
\'e9i kh\'abng th\'d3 t\'b8ch r\'eai nhau trong t\'ad t\'ad\'ebng H\'e5 Ch\'dd Minh \'ae\'ad\'eec c\'b8ch m\'b9ng Vi\'d6t Nam v\'cbn d\'f4ng th\'b5nh c\'abng \'ae\'b7 kh\'bcng \'ae\'denh \'ae\'e3 c\'f2ng l\'b5 ch\'a9n l\'fd l\'edn c\'f1a th\'eai \'ae\'b9
i.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa60\sl-272\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs18\lang1053\langfe1033\langnp1053\insrsid1378858 Nh\'ad v\'cby, t\'ad t\'ad
\'ebng H\'e5 Ch\'dd Minh v\'d2 \'ae\'e9c l\'a9p d\'a9n t\'e9c g\'ben li\'d2n v\'edi ch\'f1 ngh\'dca x\'b7 h\'e9i, l\'b5 m\'e9t \'ae\'e3ng g\'e3p c\'f1a c\'b8ch m\'b9ng Vi\'d6t Nam v\'b5o kho t\'b5ng c\'f1a ch\'f1 ngh\'dca M\'b8c - L\'aanin, v\'b5o l\'fd
 lu\'cbn c\'b8ch m\'b9ng x\'b7 h\'e9i trong th\'eai \'ae\'b9i hi\'d6n nay.
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa60\sl-272\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\fs18\lang1053\langfe1033\langnp1053\insrsid1378858 Ng\'b5y nay, nh\'f7
ng lu\'cbn \'aei\'d3m c\'f1a Ch\'f1 t\'dech H\'e5 Ch\'dd Minh v\'d2 b\'b6n ch\'cat, \'ae\'c6c tr\'adng, v\'d2 m\'f4c ti\'aau, \'ae\'e9ng l\'f9c ... c\'f1a ch\'f1 ngh\'dca x\'b7 h\'e9i \'eb n\'ad\'edc ta... v\'c9n gi\'f7 nguy\'aan \'fd ngh\'dca \'ae\'e8i v
\'edi s\'f9 nghi\'d6p \'ae\'e6i m\'edi.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa60\sl-272\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\lang1024\langfe1024\noproof\insrsid1378858 
