\'f1 ngh\'dca x\'b7 h\'e9i l\'b5 l\'b5m sao cho d\'a9n gi\'b5u, n\'ad\'edc m\'b9nh", "m\'e4i ng\'ad\'eai \'ae\'ad\'eec \'a8n no, m\'c6c \'cam, sung s\'ad\'edng, t\'f9 do". V\'d2 b\'b6n
\par }\pard \qj \li0\ri0\sl-272\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\lang1053\langfe1033\langnp1053\insrsid1378858  }{\f37\fs18\lang1053\langfe1033\langnp1053\insrsid1378858 ch\'cat, ch\'f1 ngh\'dca x\'b7 h\'e9i l\'b5 m\'e9
t x\'b7 h\'e9i do nh\'a9n d\'a9n lao \'ae\'e9ng l\'b5m ch\'f1, "m\'e9t x\'b7 h\'e9i kh\'abng c\'e3 ch\'d5 \'ae\'e9 ng\'ad\'eai b\'e3c l\'e9t ng\'ad\'eai, m\'e9t x\'b7 h\'e9i b\'d7nh \'ae\'bcng, ai l\'b5m nhi\'d2u h\'ad\'ebng nhi\'d2u, l\'b5m \'ddt h\'ad
\'ebng \'ddt, kh\'abng l\'b5m kh\'abng h\'ad\'ebng". M\'e9t \'ae\'c6c tr\'adng c\'ac b\'b6n c\'f1a ch\'f1 ngh\'dca x\'b7 h\'e9i l\'b5 s\'f9 t\'a8ng tr\'ad\'ebng kinh t\'d5 ph\'b6i "g\'ben li\'d2n v\'edi s\'f9 ph\'b8t tri\'d3n khoa h\'e4c v\'b5 k\'fc thu
\'cbt, v\'edi s\'f9 ph\'b8t tri\'d3n v\'a8n ho\'b8 c\'f1a nh\'a9n d\'a9n", trong \'ae\'e3, con ng\'ad\'eai m\'edi x\'b7 h\'e9i ch\'f1 ngh\'dca \'ae\'ad\'eec ph\'b8t tri\'d3n c\'b6 v\'d2 th\'d3 l\'f9c, tr\'dd l\'f9c, \'ae\'b9o \'ae\'f8c v\'b5 tinh th\'c7n
. Ti\'d5n l\'aan ch\'f1 ngh\'dca x\'b7 h\'e9i "l\'b5 y\'aau c\'c7u c\'cap 
\par }\pard\plain \s16\qj \li0\ri0\sl-266\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\lang1053\langfe1033\langnp1053\insrsid1378858 b\'b8ch c\'f1a h\'b5ng ch\'f4c tri\'d6
u ng\'ad\'eai lao \'ae\'e9ng. \'a7\'e3 l\'b5 c\'abng tr\'d7nh t\'cbp th\'d3 c\'f1a qu\'c7n ch\'f3ng lao \'ae\'e9ng d\'ad\'edi s\'f9 l\'b7nh \'ae\'b9o c\'f1a \'a7\'b6ng". "Y\'aau T\'e6 qu\'e8c, y\'aau nh\'a9n d\'a9n ph\'b6i g\'ben li\'d2n v\'edi y\'aau ch
\'f1 ngh\'dca x\'b7 h\'e9i, v\'d7 c\'e3 ti\'d5n l\'aan ch\'f1 ngh\'dca x\'b7 h\'e9i th\'d7 nh\'a9n d\'a9n m\'d7nh m\'e7i ng\'b5y m\'e9t no \'cam th\'aam, T\'e6 qu\'e8c m\'e7i ng\'b5y m\'e9t gi\'b5u m\'b9nh th\'aam".
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa60\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs18\lang1053\langfe1033\langnp1053\insrsid1378858 Xu\'cat ph\'b8t t\'f5 \'ae
\'c6c \'aei\'d3m n\'ad\'edc ta qu\'b8 \'ae\'e9 l\'aan ch\'f1 ngh\'dca x\'b7 h\'e9i t\'f5 m\'e9t n\'d2n kinh t\'d5 n\'abng nghi\'d6p l\'b9c h\'cbu, \'ae\'cat n\'ad\'edc t\'b9m th\'eai b\'de chia c\'bet, l\'b9i c\'e3 chi\'d5n tranh, Ng\'ad\'eai \'ae\'d2
 ra ch\'f1 tr\'ad\'acng: v\'f5a kh\'b8ng chi\'d5n v\'f5a ki\'d5n qu\'e8c, v\'f5a ch\'e8ng M\'fc, c\'f8u n\'ad\'edc v\'f5a x\'a9y d\'f9ng ch\'f1 ngh\'dca x\'b7 h\'e9i. \'a7\'e3 l\'b5 s\'b8ng t\'b9o \'ae\'e9c \'ae\'b8o c\'f1a t\'ad t\'ad\'ebng H\'e5 Ch\'dd
 Minh.
\par \'a7\'c6c bi\'d6t, Ng\'ad\'eai th\'ad\'eang xuy\'aan nh\'bec nh\'eb ph\'b6i \'ae\'d2 ph\'dfng c\'b8ch l\'b5m r\'cbp khu\'abn, gi\'b8o \'aei\'d2u; c\'c7n xu\'cat ph\'b8t t\'f5 th\'f9c t\'d5 \'ae\'d3 t\'d7m ra con \'ae\'ad\'eang \'aei ri\'aang ph\'ef h\'ee
p v\'edi t\'d7nh h\'d7nh v\'b5 \'ae\'c6c \'aei\'d3m c\'f1a n\'ad\'edc ta. Ng\'ad\'eai n\'e3i: "Hi\'d6n nay, \'ae\'f8ng v\'d2 m\'c6t x\'a9y d\'f9ng ch\'f1 ngh\'dca x\'b7 h\'e9i, tuy ch\'f3ng ta \'ae\'b7 c\'e3 nh\'f7ng kinh nghi\'d6m d\'e5i d\'b5o c\'f1a c
\'b8c n\'ad\'edc anh em, nh\'adng ch\'f3ng ta c\'f2ng kh\'abng th\'d3 \'b8p d\'f4ng nh\'f7ng kinh nghi\'d6m \'ae\'e3 m\'e9t c\'b8ch m\'b8y m\'e3c, b\'ebi v\'d7 n\'ad\'edc ta c\'e3 nh\'f7ng \'ae\'c6c \'aei\'d3m ri\'aang c\'f1a ta".
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa60\sl-266\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs18\lang1053\langfe1033\langnp1053\insrsid1378858 T\'ad t\'ad\'ebng H\'e5 Ch\'dd Minh v\'d2 ch\'f1 ngh\'dca x\'b7 h\'e9i v\'b5 con \'ae\'ad
\'eang \'aei l\'aan ch\'f1 ngh\'dca x\'b7 h\'e9i \'eb Vi\'d6t Nam \'aeang \'ae\'ad\'eec \'a7\'b6ng ta v\'cbn d\'f4ng s\'b8ng t\'b9o v\'b5o s\'f9 nghi\'d6p \'ae\'e6i m\'edi hi\'d6n nay nh\'bbm ra s\'f8c ph\'b8t tri\'d3n kinh t\'d5, v\'a8n ho\'b8 l\'b5
m cho d\'a9n gi\'b5u n\'ad\'edc m\'b9nh, gi\'f7 v\'f7ng \'ae\'e9c l\'cbp ch\'f1 quy\'d2n v\'b5 to\'b5n v\'d1n l\'b7nh th\'e6, x\'a9y d\'f9ng th\'b5nh c\'abng ch\'f1 ngh\'dca x\'b7 h\'e9i tr\'aan \'ae\'cat n\'ad\'edc ta, g\'e3p ph\'c7n t\'ddch c\'f9c v\'b5
o cu\'e9c \'ae\'cau tranh chung c\'f1a nh\'a9n d\'a9n th\'d5 gi\'edi v\'d7 ho\'b5 b\'d7nh, \'ae\'e9c l\'cbp d\'a9n t\'e9c, d\'a9n ch\'f1 v\'b5 ti\'d5n b\'e9 x\'b7 h\'e9i.
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa60\sl-272\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs18\lang1053\langfe1033\langnp1053\insrsid1378858 C\'e3 t\'ad t\'ad\'ebng \'ae\'f3ng, \'ae\'ad\'eang l\'e8i \'ae\'f3ng, nh\'adng mu\'e8n v
\'cbn d\'f4ng c\'e3 hi\'d6u qu\'b6
\par }\pard\plain \s16\qj \li0\ri0\sa60\sl-262\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\lang1024\langfe1024\noproof\insrsid1378858 
