\'b7 n\'aau nhi\'d2u t\'cam g\'ad\'acng ti\'aau bi\'d3u c\'f1a ph\'f4 n\'f7 v\'b5 tu\'e6i tr\'ce t\'b9i c\'b8c n\'ad\'edc thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea v\'b5 ph\'f4 thu\'e9c \'ae\'d3 c\'e6 v\'f2 tinh th\'c7n \'ae\'cau tranh c\'b8ch m\'b9ng c\'f1a qu\'c7n ch\'f3ng b
\'de \'b8p b\'f8c.   
\par }{\i\f37\fs18\insrsid1378858 H\'e5 Ch\'dd Minh To\'b5n t\'cbp}{\f37\fs18\insrsid1378858 , t\'cbp 1, ngo\'b5i nh\'f7ng t\'b8c ph\'c8m l\'fd lu\'cbn s\'bec b\'d0n, ch\'f8a \'ae\'f9ng t\'ad t\'ad\'ebng ch\'ddnh tr\'de quan tr\'e4ng, c\'dfn c\'e3 nh\'f7ng t
\'b8c ph\'c8m v\'a8n h\'e4c c\'e3 gi\'b8 tr\'de, mang t\'ddnh \'ae\'b6ng s\'a9u s\'bec, t\'ddnh chi\'d5n \'ae\'cau cao v\'b5 t\'ddnh ngh\'d6 thu\'cbt \'ae\'e9c \'ae\'b8o. B\'bbng nh\'f7ng t\'b8c ph\'c8m \'ae\'e3, Ch\'f1 t\'dech H\'e5 Ch\'dd Minh \'ae\'b7 
\'ae\'c6t n\'d2n m\'e3ng cho s\'f9 ra \'ae\'eai c\'f1a n\'d2n v\'a8n h\'e4c c\'b8ch m\'b9ng mang n\'e9i dung y\'aau n\'ad\'edc v\'b5 \'ae\'cbm \'ae\'b5 b\'b6n s\'bec d\'a9n t\'e9c.   
\par }\pard \qj \li0\ri0\sl-280\slmult0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\i\f37\fs18\insrsid1378858 H\'e5 Ch\'dd Minh To\'b5n t\'cbp}{\f37\fs18\insrsid1378858 , t\'cbp 1, tr\'aan c\'ac s\'eb ti\'d5p th\'f4 th\'b5nh qu\'b6 c\'f1a l
