\f37\fs20\lang1053\langfe1033\langnp1053\insrsid1378858 
\par }\pard\plain \s20\qc \li0\ri0\sb1400\sa440\sl-380\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \b\f38\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\lang1053\langfe1033\langnp1053\insrsid1378858 V\'caN \'a7\'d2 D\'a2N B
\'b6N X\'f8
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-284\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\lang1053\langfe1033\langnp1053\insrsid1378858 B\'b8o }{
\i\f37\fs20\lang1053\langfe1033\langnp1053\insrsid1378858 L'Humanit\'d0}{\f37\fs20\lang1053\langfe1033\super\langnp1053\insrsid1378858 4}{\f37\fs20\lang1053\langfe1033\langnp1053\insrsid1378858  ng\'b5y 18-6 m\'edi \'ae\'a9y \'ae\'b7 \'ae\'a8ng v\'a8n b
\'b6n th\'d8nh c\'c7u c\'f1a nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai An Nam g\'f6i H\'e9i ngh\'de Ho\'b5 b\'d7nh}{\f37\fs20\lang1053\langfe1033\super\langnp1053\insrsid1378858 5}{\f37\fs20\lang1053\langfe1033\langnp1053\insrsid1378858  \'ae\'dfi \'a9n x\'b8 cho t\'cat c\'b6
 c\'b8c t\'ef ch\'ddnh tr\'de ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8, \'ae\'dfi c\'b6i c\'b8ch ph\'b8p ch\'d5 \'eb \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng b\'bbng ban h\'b5nh nh\'f7ng b\'b6o \'ae\'b6m cho ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8 c\'f2ng nh\'ad cho ng\'ad\'eai \'a2u, \'ae\'dfi t\'f9
 do b\'b8o ch\'dd, t\'f9 do h\'e9i h\'e4p v\'b5 l\'cbp h\'e9i, t\'f9 do d\'b9y h\'e4c, \'ae\'dfi thay th\'d5 ch\'d5 \'ae\'e9 s\'bec l\'d6nh b\'bbng ch\'d5 \'ae\'e9 ph\'b8p lu\'cbt; v\'b5 sau c\'efng, \'ae\'dfi c\'e3 m\'e9t \'aeo\'b5n \'ae\'b9i bi\'d3u th
\'ad\'eang tr\'f9c c\'f1a d\'a9n b\'b6n x\'f8, \'ae\'ad\'eec 
\par b\'c7u v\'b5o Ngh\'de vi\'d6n Ph\'b8p. Ch\'f3ng t\'abi ch\'d8 c\'e3 th\'d3 coi c\'b8c y\'aau s\'b8ch r\'cat \'ae\'f3ng \'ae\'ben \'ae\'e3 c\'f2ng l\'b5 c\'f1a ch\'ddnh m\'d7nh, trong th\'eai \'ae\'b9i m\'b5 \'fd mu\'e8n c\'f1a nh\'a9n d\'a9n l\'b5 n\'be
m quy\'d2n t\'f9 quy\'d5t.
\par }\pard \qj \li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\expnd0\expndtw-2\lang1053\langfe1033\langnp1053\insrsid1378858 N\'ad\'edc Ph\'b8p \'ae\'b7 t\'f5ng b\'bet \'ae\'c7u \'ae\'b8nh chi\'d5m \'a7
\'abng D\'ad\'acng g\'c7n nh\'ad c\'efng th\'eai gian m\'b5 n\'ad\'edc Nh\'cbt \'aei nh\'f7ng b\'ad\'edc \'ae\'c7u ti\'aan trong cu\'e9c c\'b6i c\'b8ch n\'e6i ti\'d5ng n\'a8m 1868. Nh\'adng trong kho\'b6ng m\'e9t n\'f6a th\'d5 k\'fb, n\'ad\'edc Nh\'cbt 
\'ae\'b7 bi\'d5t t\'b9o l\'cbp \'ae\'ad\'eec m\'e9t ch\'d5 \'ae\'e9 \'ae\'ada n\'e3 v\'b5o h\'b9ng nh\'f7ng c\'ad\'eang qu\'e8c \'ae\'f8ng \'ae\'c7u th\'d5 gi\'edi; c\'dfn n\'ad\'edc Ph\'b8p th\'d7 ph\'b6i n\'e3i r\'bbng v\'c9n \'aeang m\'df m\'c9
m trong ch\'ddnh s\'b8ch \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng c\'f1a m\'d7nh. Th\'cbm ch\'dd c\'e3 th\'d3 t\'f9 h\'e1i \'ae\'b7 t\'f5ng c\'e3 m\'e9t ch\'ddnh s\'b8ch \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng bao gi\'ea ch\'a8ng? - V\'d7 l\'cf t\'f5 }{
\f37\fs20\lang1053\langfe1033\langnp1053\insrsid1378858 khi b\'de Ph\'b8p chi\'d5m, \'ae\'cat n\'ad\'edc ch\'f3ng t\'abi h\'c7u nh\'ad lu\'abn lu\'abn s\'e8ng lay l\'bet ng\'b5y n\'b5y qua ng\'b5y kh\'b8c, kh\'abng h\'d2 bi\'d5t ch\'ddnh quy\'d2n mu\'e8
n d\'c9n m\'d7nh \'aei \'ae\'d5n \'ae\'a9u, - ch\'ddnh quy\'d2n n\'b5y khi th\'d7 n\'e3i v\'d2 ch\'ddnh s\'b8ch \'ae\'e5ng h\'e3a, khi th\'d7 n\'e3i v\'d2 ch\'ddnh s\'b8ch li\'aan hi\'d6p ho\'c6c g\'d7 kh\'b8c n\'f7a, nh\'adng th\'cbt ra ch\'bcng \'b8p d
\'f4ng m\'e9t ch\'ddnh s\'b8ch n\'b5o c\'b6. T\'d7nh h\'d7nh \'ae\'ddch th\'f9c l\'b5 nh\'ad sau: nay c\'f2ng nh\'ad tr\'ad\'edc kia, k\'ce chinh ph\'f4c v\'b5 nh\'a9n d\'a9n b\'de chinh ph\'f4c \'ae\'d2u s\'e8ng m\'c6t \'ae\'e8i m\'c6t, trong m\'e9t kh
\'abng kh\'dd nghi k\'fe l\'c9n nhau. B\'f8c tranh \'b6m \'ae\'b9m n\'b5y \'ae\'b8ng \'ae\'ad\'eec quan t\'a9m, \'ae\'ad\'eec x\'d0t v\'d2 m\'e9t s\'e8 m\'c6t kh\'b8c nhau.
\par }\pard\plain \s22\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-286\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f40\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\lang1053\langfe1033\langnp1053\insrsid1378858 V\'d2 t\'a9m l\'fd
, \'eb ph\'dda kia l\'b5 th\'b8i \'ae\'e9 hi\'d2m nghi v\'b5 khinh mi\'d6t; c\'dfn \'eb ph\'dda n\'b5y l\'b9i l\'b5 t\'a9m tr\'b9ng b\'f9c d\'e4c v\'b5 tuy\'d6t v\'e4ng. C\'b8c \'can ph\'c8m s\'b8ch b\'b8o th\'f9c d\'a9n \'ae\'d2u \'ae\'c7y r\'c9y nh\'f7
ng \'ae\'dfn \'ae\'b6 k\'ddch hung b\'b9o \'ae\'b8nh v\'b5o nh\'a9n d\'a9n b\'de chinh ph\'f4c, \'ae\'d2u tr\'b5n ng\'cbp nh\'f7ng l\'eai ch\'f6i r\'f1a phun th\'bcng v\'b5o m\'c6t h\'e4 v\'edi d\'f2ng kh\'dd c\'b5ng hung h\'a8ng v\'d7 t\'b8c gi\'b6 bi
\'d5t tr\'ad\'edc r\'bbng h\'e4 kh\'abng th\'d3 n\'b5o tr\'b6 mi\'d5ng l\'b9i \'ae\'ad\'eec v\'b5 h\'e4 ch\'d8 \'ae\'b5nh ph\'b6i nghi\'d5n r\'a8ng m\'b5 nu\'e8t l\'cay. Ng\'ad\'eai ta \'ae\'e4c th\'cay trong lo\'b9i \'can ph\'c8m v\'f5a n\'aau nh\'f7
ng ph\'b8n quy\'d5t nh\'ad th\'d5 n\'b5y ch\'bcng h\'b9n: " \'a7\'e8i v\'edi c\'b8i gi\'e8ng n\'dfi annam\'ddt \'cay, ch\'d8 c\'e3 m\'e9t c\'b8ch t\'e8t \'ae\'d3 cai tr\'de n\'e3, - \'ae\'e3 l\'b5 \'b8ch th\'e8ng tr\'de b\'bbng s\'f8c m\'b9nh... Truy\'d2
n h\'e4c v\'can cho b\'e4n annam\'ddt ho\'c6c cho ph\'d0p ch\'f3ng t\'f9 ch\'f3ng c\'e3 h\'e4c v\'can, t\'f8c l\'b5 m\'e9t m\'c6t cung c\'cap cho ch\'f3ng nh\'f7ng s\'f3ng b\'ben nhanh \'ae\'d3 ch\'e8ng ch\'f3ng ta, v\'b5 m\'c6t kh\'b8c \'ae\'b5o t\'b9
o nh\'f7ng con ch\'e3 th\'abng th\'b8i g\'a9y r\'bec r\'e8i h\'acn l\'b5 c\'e3 \'ddch...".
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-284\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\lang1053\langfe1033\langnp1053\insrsid1378858 V\'d2 h\'b5nh ch\'ddnh v
\'b5 ph\'b8p l\'fd: c\'b6 m\'e9t v\'f9c th\'bcm c\'b8ch bi\'d6t ng\'ad\'eai \'a2u v\'edi ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8. Ng\'ad\'eai \'a2u h\'ad\'ebng m\'e4i t\'f9 do v\'b5 ng\'f9 tr\'de nh\'ad ng\'ad\'eai ch\'f1 tuy\'d6t \'ae\'e8i; c\'dfn ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x
\'f8 th\'d7 b\'de b\'det m\'e2m v\'b5 b\'de bu\'e9c d\'a9y d\'bet \'aei, ch\'d8 c\'e3 quy\'d2n ph\'b6i ph\'f4c t\'efng, kh\'abng \'ae\'ad\'eec k\'aau ca; v\'d7 n\'d5u anh ta d\'b8m ph\'b6n \'ae\'e8i th\'d7 anh ta li\'d2n b\'de tuy\'aan b\'e8 l\'b5 k\'ce
 ph\'b6n ngh\'dech ho\'c6c l\'b5 m\'e9t t\'aan c\'b8ch m\'b9ng, v\'b5 b\'de \'ae\'e8i x\'f6 \'ae\'f3ng v\'edi t\'e9i tr\'b9ng \'cay. C\'b5ng kh\'e8n kh\'e6 h\'acn cho ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8 n\'b5o xu\'cat ngo\'b9i \'ae\'d3 tho\'b8t kh\'e1i c\'b8i ch\'d5
 \'ae\'e9 d\'deu hi\'d2n \'cay: gia quy\'d5n anh ta b\'de h\'b5nh h\'b9; b\'b6n th\'a9n anh ta, n\'d5u b\'de b\'bet, th\'d7 b\'de t\'ef kh\'e6 sai ho\'c6c b\'de \'ae\'c8y l\'aan m\'b8y ch\'d0m. Th\'cbm ch\'dd \'ae\'d3 \'aei l\'b9i trong n\'ad\'edc, t\'f5 
\'ae\'dea ph\'ad\'acng n\'b5y \'ae\'d5n \'ae\'dea ph\'ad\'acng kh\'b8c theo lu\'cbt, ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8 ph\'b6i mang theo gi\'cay ph\'d0p. C\'dfn c\'abng l\'fd, \'ae\'e8i v\'edi ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8, n\'e3 t\'e5n t\'b9i nh\'ad th\'d5 n\'b5y \'ae
\'a9y: ng\'ad\'eai \'a2u n\'b5o \'ae\'b7 gi\'d5t ch\'d5t, t\'b5n s\'b8t ho\'c6c c\'ad\'ecng d\'a9m ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8, th\'d7 trong tr\'ad\'eang h\'eep v\'f4 \'b8n kh\'abng th\'d3 \'ae\'ad\'eec \'d8m ho\'b5n to\'b5n, anh ta ch\'bec m\'c8m r\'bbng m
\'d7nh \'ae\'ad\'eec to\'b5
\par }\pard \qj \li0\ri0\sa80\sl-284\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858\charrsid5792077 \'b8n tha b\'e6ng, m\'d7nh ra to\'b5 ch\'bcng qua l\'b5 chuy\'d6n h\'d7nh th\'f8c. \'a7\'e3 l\'b5 vi\'d6c \'b8
p d\'f4ng nguy\'aan t\'bec nh\'bbm b\'b6o t\'e5n b\'bbng m\'e4i c\'b8ch uy t\'ddn c\'f1a ng\'ad\'eai da tr\'beng tr\'ad\'edc b\'e4n da v\'b5ng. Ngh\'de vi\'d6n Ph\'b8p c\'e3 bi\'d5t ch\'f3t \'ae\'d8nh v\'d2 vi\'d6c v\'f5a n\'aau, qua m\'e9t s\'e8 \'aei
\'d2u ti\'d5t l\'e9 c\'f1a \'abng ngh\'de s\'dc Vi\'abnl\'d0t trong m\'e9t b\'b6n b\'b8o c\'b8o v\'d2 ng\'a9n s\'b8ch \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng.
\par }\pard\plain \s23\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sb140\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\outlinelevel0\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \b\f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 S\'f9 ng\'f9 tr\'de c\'f1a b\'b9o ch
\'ddnh
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sl-284\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f38\fs20\cf1\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 \'eb}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  c\'b8c t\'d8nh, ng
\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8 b\'de tr\'e3i tay tr\'e3i ch\'a9n, ph\'b6i g\'b8nh ch\'deu th\'e3i tu\'fa h\'f8ng, chuy\'aan quy\'d2n c\'f1a c\'b8c quan cai tr\'de ng\'ad\'eai Ph\'b8p v\'b5 th\'e3i tham t\'b5n c\'f1a b\'e4n l\'b5m t\'abi t\'ed ngoan ngo\'b7
n cho ch\'f3ng, b\'e4n quan l\'b9i, s\'b6n ph\'c8m c\'f1a ch\'d5 \'ae\'e9 m\'edi! }{\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'ca}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 y l\'b5 c\'abng l\'fd b\'de b\'b8n \'ae\'f8t cho k\'ce n\'b5o mua \'ae\'bet nh\'cat, tr\'b6 gi\'b8 h\'eai nh\'ca
t. X\'ada kia, ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8 bao gi\'ea c\'f2ng c\'e3 th\'d3 k\'aau l\'aan \'ae\'d5n t\'cbn Tri\'d2u \'ae\'d7nh nh\'b5 vua; nh\'adng nay th\'d7 anh ch\'b5ng "annam\'ddt" kh\'e8n kh\'e6 ch\'bcng bi\'d5t c\'e3 th\'b8nh nh\'a9n n\'b5o \'ae\'d3 d
\'f9a, v\'b5 c\'dfn l\'b9i cho anh ta, ch\'d8 l\'b5 c\'abng l\'fd c\'f1a Ch\'f3a tr\'eai. Ri\'aang \'ae\'e8i v\'edi nh\'f7ng ai m\'b5 ng\'abn ng\'f7 th\'f9c d\'a9n g\'e4i l\'b5 b\'e4n qu\'cay r\'e8i, th\'d7 nh\'f7ng phi\'aan h\'e4p \'a9m u, \'ae\'ad\'ee
c t\'ab \'aei\'d3m th\'b5nh to\'b5 \'ae\'b9i h\'d7nh, b\'dd m\'cbt quy\'d5t \'ae\'denh s\'e8 ph\'cbn c\'f1a h\'e4 - nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8 ch\'ddnh tr\'f9c m\'b5 \'ae\'e5ng b\'b5o c\'f1a h\'e4 \'ae\'d2u coi tr\'e4ng v\'b5 tin y\'aau.
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858\charrsid5792077 S\'f9 t\'ad\'acng ph\'b6n c\'b5ng n\'e6i b\'cbt kh\'abng k\'d0m trong l\'dcnh v\'f9c kinh t\'d5. M\'e9t b\'aa
n l\'b5 nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8 b\'de d\'d7m trong c\'b6nh d\'e8t n\'b8t v\'b5 suy y\'d5u b\'ebi m\'e9t h\'d6 th\'e8ng tinh kh\'abn nh\'bbm nh\'e5i s\'e4, \'ae\'c7n \'ae\'e9n ho\'b8, kh\'abng l\'cap li\'d5m h\'d5t \'ae\'ad\'eec d\'ad\'edi m\'e9
t d\'b9ng gi\'b8o d\'f4c b\'dep b\'eem: h\'e4 ph\'b6i \'ae\'e6 m\'e5 h\'abi s\'abi n\'ad\'edc m\'bet trong nh\'f7ng lao t\'b8c n\'c6ng nh\'e4c nh\'cat v\'b5 b\'b9c b\'cfo nh\'cat \'ae\'d3 ki\'d5m s\'e8ng m\'e9t c\'b8ch ch\'cbt v\'cbt, v\'b5 h\'c7u nh\'ad
 ch\'d8 b\'bbng s\'f8c c\'f1a
\par }\pard \qj \li0\ri0\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858\charrsid5792077  h\'e4 th\'abi, \'ae\'d3 nu\'abi m\'e4i ng\'a9n qu\'fc c\'f1a ch\'ddnh quy\'d2n. M\'e9t b\'aan l\'b5 nh\'f7ng ng
\'ad\'eai Ph\'b8p v\'b5 ng\'ad\'eai n\'ad\'edc ngo\'b5i: h\'e4 \'ae\'d2u \'aei l\'b9i t\'f9 do, t\'f9 d\'b5nh cho m\'d7nh t\'cat c\'b6 c\'b8c t\'b5i nguy\'aan c\'f1a \'ae\'cat n\'ad\'edc, chi\'d5m \'aeo\'b9t to\'b5n b\'e9}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  }{
