NG
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-292\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Ch\'f3ng t\'abi v\'f5a nh\'cbn \'ae\'ad\'eec b\'f8c th\'ad
 sau \'ae\'a9y m\'b5 kh\'abng c\'c7n nh\'can m\'b9nh \'aei\'d2u l\'eei h\'b9i trong \'ae\'e3.
\par }{\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'eb}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  \'ae\'a9y (H\'b6i Ph\'dfng) c\'f2ng c\'e3 nh\'f7ng cu\'e9c b\'b7i c\'abng c\'f1a thu\'fb th\'f1. Ch\'bcng h\'b9n nh\'ad ng\'b5y th\'f8 n\'a8m (15-8), hai chi\'d5c t\'b5u bi\'d3n nh\'e6 neo \'ae
\'d3 ch\'eb m\'e9t s\'e8 l\'edn l\'ddnh kh\'e8 \'ae\'e1 An Nam \'aei Xyri.
\par Nh\'adng thu\'fb th\'f1 kh\'abng ch\'deu \'aei, v\'d7 ng\'ad\'eai ta kh\'abng ch\'deu ph\'b8t l\'ad\'acng cho h\'e4 b\'bbng ti\'d2n \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng. Theo gi\'b8 th\'de tr\'ad\'eang, m\'e9t \'ae\'e5ng \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng b\'bbng 10 phr\'a8ng, ch
\'f8 kh\'abng ph\'b6i 2 phr\'a8ng 50. Th\'d5 m\'b5 c\'b8c c\'abng ty h\'b5ng h\'b6i l\'b9i l\'b5m m\'e9t vi\'d6c h\'b5 l\'b9m tr\'beng tr\'een l\'b5 \'ae\'denh tr\'b6 l\'ad\'acng cho thu\'fb th\'f1 b\'bbng phr\'a8ng, ch\'f8 kh\'abng tr\'b6 b\'bbng ti\'d2
n \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng nh\'ad \'ae\'b7 tr\'b6 cho c\'abng ch\'f8c.
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-292\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 Th\'d5 l\'b5 ng\'ad\'eai ta li\'d2n xua t\'cat c\'b6 m\'e4
i ng\'ad\'eai \'eb d\'ad\'edi t\'b5u l\'aan, r\'e5i l\'cbp t\'f8c b\'bet h\'d5t c\'b8c thu\'fb th\'f1. R\'e2 r\'b5ng l\'b5 thu\'fb th\'f1 Bi\'d3n V\'b5ng ch\'bcng c\'e3 g\'d7 ph\'b6i so b\'d7 v\'edi thu\'fb th\'f1 Bi\'d3n \'a7en.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-292\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Ch\'f3ng t\'abi c\'f9c l\'f9c ph\'b6n \'ae\'e8i vi\'d6c 
\'ae\'ada l\'ddnh An Nam sang Xyri. Ph\'b6i ch\'a8ng c\'b8c nh\'b5 c\'c7m quy\'d2n c\'cap cao cho r\'bbng bao nhi\'aau anh em da v\'b5ng x\'cau s\'e8 c\'f1a ch\'f3ng t\'abi b\'de gi\'d5t h\'b9i tr\'aan c\'b8c chi\'d5n tr\'ad\'eang t\'f5 n\'a8m 1914 \'ae
\'d5n n\'a8m 1918, trong cu\'e9c chi\'d5n tranh "v\'d7 v\'a8n minh v\'b5 c\'abng l\'fd" v\'c9n ch\'ada \'ae\'f1 sao?
\par }{\f38\fs20\cf1\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 \'eb}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng, ch\'f3ng ta \'aeang s\'e8ng d\'ad\'edi s\'f9 "b\'b6o h\'e9" c\'f1a n\'ad\'edc Ph\'b8p. B\'b6o h\'e9 c\'e3 ngh\'dca l\'b5 che ch\'eb. N\'ad\'edc Ph\'b8p \'aeang 
\'ae\'d3 cho h\'b5ng
\par }\pard\plain \s25\qj \li0\ri0\sa80\sl-296\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f38\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\insrsid1378858 tri\'d6u anh em ch\'f3ng ta ch\'d5t \'ae\'e3i, trong khi \'ae
\'e3 h\'b5ng ngh\'d7n ng\'ad\'eai kh\'b8c b\'de \'ae\'ada sang Ti\'d3u }{\insrsid1378858 \'b8}{\f37\insrsid1378858  l\'b5m bia \'ae\'ec \'ae\'b9n.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\lang1053\langfe1033\langnp1053\insrsid1378858 Ng\'ad\'eai ta che ch\'eb
 cho ch\'f3ng ta nh\'ad v\'cby \'ae\'e3!
