u ng\'b5y 26-12-1920 l\'b5 \'a3min Gu\'ae\'ac.
\par 2) \'a7\'b9i bi\'d3u \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng l\'b5 Nguy\'d4n }{\f38\insrsid1378858 \'b8}{\insrsid1378858 i Qu\'e8c.}})}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 : \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng c\'e3 \'fd ki\'d5n. }{\i\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 (V\'e7 tay).}{
\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-270\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\b\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'a7\'b9i bi\'d3u \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng}{\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 2)}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 : Th\'ada c\'b8
c \'ae\'e5ng ch\'dd, l\'cf ra h\'abm nay, t\'abi \'ae\'d5n \'ae\'a9y l\'b5 \'ae\'d3 c\'efng v\'edi c\'b8c \'ae\'e5ng ch\'dd g\'e3p ph\'c7n v\'b5o s\'f9 nghi\'d6p c\'b8ch m\'b9ng th\'d5 gi\'edi, nh\'adng v\'edi m\'e9t n\'e7i \'aeau bu\'e5n s\'a9u s\'bec, t
\'abi \'ae\'d5n \'ae\'a9y v\'edi t\'ad c\'b8ch l\'b5 \'ae\'b6ng vi\'aan x\'b7 h\'e9i, \'ae\'d3 ph\'b6n kh\'b8ng nh\'f7ng t\'e9i \'b8c gh\'aa t\'ebm tr\'aan qu\'aa h\'ad\'acng t\'abi. }{\i\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 (T\'e8t l\'bem!).}{
\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  C\'b8c \'ae\'e5ng ch\'dd \'ae\'d2u bi\'d5t r\'bbng ch\'f1 ngh\'dca t\'ad b\'b6n Ph\'b8p \'ae\'b7 v\'b5o \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng t\'f5 n\'f6a th\'d5 k\'fb nay; v\'d7 l\'eei \'ddch c\'f1a n\'e3, n\'e3 \'ae\'b7 d\'efng l\'ad\'eci l
\'aa \'ae\'d3 chinh ph\'f4c \'ae\'cat n\'ad\'edc ch\'f3ng t\'abi. T\'f5 \'ae\'e3, ch\'f3ng t\'abi kh\'abng nh\'f7ng b\'de \'b8p b\'f8c v\'b5 b\'e3c l\'e9t m\'e9t c\'b8ch nh\'f4c nh\'b7, m\'b5 c\'dfn b\'de h\'b5nh h\'b9 v\'b5 \'ae\'c7u \'ae\'e9c m\'e9t c
\'b8ch th\'aa th\'b6m. T\'abi xin nh\'can m\'b9nh t\'f5 "\'ae\'c7u \'ae\'e9c" b\'bbng thu\'e8c phi\'d6n, b\'bbng r\'ad\'eeu, v.v.. Trong v\'b5i ph\'f3t, t\'abi kh\'abng th\'d3 v\'b9ch \'ae\'ad\'eec h\'d5t nh\'f7ng s\'f9 t\'b5n b\'b9o m\'b5 b\'e4n t\'ad b
\'b6n \'a8n c\'ad\'edp \'ae\'b7 g\'a9y ra \'eb \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng. Nh\'b5 t\'ef nhi\'d2u h\'acn tr\'ad\'eang h\'e4c, l\'f3c n\'b5o c\'f2ng m\'eb c\'f6a v\'b5 ch\'cbt n\'ddch ng\'ad\'eai. B\'cat k\'fa ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8 n\'b5o c\'e3 t\'ad t\'ad
\'ebng x\'b7 h\'e9i ch\'f1 ngh\'dca c\'f2ng \'ae\'d2u b\'de b\'bet v\'b5 \'ae\'abi khi b\'de gi\'d5t m\'b5 kh\'abng c\'c7n x\'d0t x\'f6. C\'b8i g\'e4i l\'b5 c\'abng l\'fd \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng l\'b5 th\'d5 \'ae\'cay! }{\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'eb }{
\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 x\'f8 \'ae\'e3, ng\'ad\'eai An Nam b\'de ph\'a9n bi\'d6t \'ae\'e8i x\'f6, h\'e4 kh\'abng c\'e3 nh\'f7ng s\'f9 b\'b6o \'ae\'b6m nh\'ad ng\'ad\'eai ch\'a9u \'a2u ho\'c6c c\'e3 qu\'e8c t\'dech ch\'a9u \'a2u. Ch\'f3ng t\'abi kh\'ab
ng c\'e3 quy\'d2n t\'f9 do b\'b8o ch\'dd v\'b5 t\'f9 do ng\'abn lu\'cbn, ngay c\'b6 quy\'d2n t\'f9 do h\'e9I
\par }\pard\plain \s25\qj \li0\ri0\sa80\sl-270\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f38\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\insrsid1378858 h\'e4p v\'b5 l\'cbp h\'e9i c\'f2ng kh\'abng c\'e3. Ch\'f3ng t
\'abi kh\'abng c\'e3 quy\'d2n c\'ad tr\'f3 v\'b5 du l\'dech ra n\'ad\'edc ngo\'b5i; ch\'f3ng t\'abi ph\'b6i s\'e8ng trong c\'b6nh ngu d\'e8t t\'e8i t\'a8m v\'d7 ch\'f3ng t\'abi kh\'abng c\'e3 quy\'d2n t\'f9 do h\'e4c t\'cbp. }{\insrsid1378858 \'eb}{
\f37\insrsid1378858  \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng, b\'e4n th\'f9c d\'a9n t\'d7m m\'e4i c\'b8ch \'ae\'d3 \'ae\'c7u \'ae\'e9c ch\'f3ng t\'abi b\'bbng thu\'e8c phi\'d6n v\'b5 l\'b5m cho ch\'f3ng t\'abi \'ae\'c7n \'ae\'e9n b\'bbng r\'ad\'eeu. Ng\'ad\'eai ta \'ae
\'b7 l\'b5m ch\'d5t h\'b5ng ngh\'d7n ng\'ad\'eai An Nam v\'b5 t\'b5n s\'b8t h\'b5ng ngh\'d7n ng\'ad\'eai kh\'b8c \'ae\'d3 b\'b6o v\'d6 nh\'f7ng l\'eei \'ddch kh\'abng ph\'b6i c\'f1a ch\'ddnh h\'e4.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-294\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Th\'ada c\'b8c \'ae\'e5ng ch\'dd, h\'acn hai m\'ad\'ac
i tri\'d6u d\'a9n An Nam, b\'bbng h\'acn n\'f6a s\'e8 d\'a9n n\'ad\'edc Ph\'b8p, \'ae\'b7 b\'de \'ae\'e8i x\'f6 nh\'ad v\'cby. }{\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'ca}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 y th\'d5 m\'b5 h\'e4 l\'b9i l\'b5 nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai \'ae\'ad\'eec n
\'ad\'edc Ph\'b8p b\'b6o h\'e9! }{\i\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 (V\'e7 tay).}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  \'a7\'b6ng X\'b7 h\'e9i c\'c7n ph\'b6i ho\'b9t \'ae\'e9ng m\'e9t c\'b8ch thi\'d5t th\'f9c \'ae\'d3 \'f1ng h\'e9 nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8 b\'de 
\'b8p b\'f8c. }{\i\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 (Hoan h\'ab).}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 
\par }{\b\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Gi\'a8ng L\'abnggh\'aa:}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  T\'abi \'ae\'b7 ph\'b8t bi\'d3u \'fd ki\'d5n \'ae\'d3 b\'b6o v\'d6 nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8.
\par }{\b\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'a7\'b9i bi\'d3u \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng:}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  Ngay khi t\'abi b\'bet \'ae\'c7u n\'e3i, t\'abi \'ae\'b7 y\'aau c\'c7u m\'e4i ng\'ad\'eai tuy\'d6t \'ae\'e8i im l\'c6ng. }{\i\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 (Nhi
\'d2u ti\'d5ng c\'ad\'eai)}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 . \'a7\'b6ng ph\'b6i tuy\'aan truy\'d2n ch\'f1 ngh\'dca x\'b7 h\'e9i trong t\'cat c\'b6 c\'b8c n\'ad\'edc thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea. Ch\'f3ng t\'abi th\'cay r\'bbng vi\'d6c \'a7\'b6ng X\'b7 h\'e9i gia nh\'cb
p Qu\'e8c t\'d5 th\'f8 ba c\'e3 ngh\'dca l\'b5 \'a7\'b6ng h\'f8a m\'e9t c\'b8ch c\'f4 th\'d3 r\'bbng t\'f5 nay \'a7\'b6ng s\'cf \'ae\'b8nh gi\'b8 \'ae\'f3ng t\'c7m quan tr\'e4ng c\'f1a v\'can \'ae\'d2 thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea. Ch\'f3ng t\'abi r\'cat sung s\'ad
\'edng khi nghe tin th\'b5nh l\'cbp m\'e9t \'aeo\'b5n \'ae\'b9i bi\'d3u th\'ad\'eang tr\'f9c nghi\'aan c\'f8u v\'d2 B\'bec Phi, v\'b5 mai \'ae\'a9y, ch\'f3ng t\'abi s\'cf vui m\'f5ng n\'d5u \'a7\'b6ng ph\'b8i m\'e9t \'ae\'e5ng ch\'dd c\'f1a \'a7\'b6ng 
\'ae\'d3 nghi\'aan c\'f8u t\'b9i ch\'e7 nh\'f7ng v\'can \'ae\'d2 \'eb \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng v\'b5 \'ae\'d2 xu\'cat nh\'f7ng ho\'b9t \'ae\'e9ng c\'c7n ph\'b6i ti\'d5n h\'b5nh.
\par }{\b\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 M\'e9t \'ae\'b9i bi\'d3u:}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  V\'edi \'ae\'e5ng ch\'dd \'a1ngve Pasa?...
\par }{\b\f37\fs20\lang1053\langfe1033\langnp1053\insrsid1378858 \'a7\'b9i bi\'d3u \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng:}{\f37\fs20\lang1053\langfe1033\langnp1053\insrsid1378858  Im \'aei! Ph\'b8i ngh\'de vi\'d6n. }{\i\f37\fs20\lang1053\langfe1033\langnp1053\insrsid1378858 
(V\'e7 tay).}{\f37\fs20\lang1053\langfe1033\langnp1053\insrsid1378858 
\par }{\b\f37\fs20\lang1053\langfe1033\langnp1053\insrsid1378858 Ch\'f1 t\'dech:}{\f37\fs20\lang1053\langfe1033\langnp1053\insrsid1378858  B\'a9y gi\'ea, t\'cat c\'b6 c\'b8c \'ae\'b9i bi\'d3u ph\'b6i im! K\'d3 c\'b6 nh\'f7ng \'ae\'b9i bi\'d3u kh\'abng thu\'e9
c ph\'b8i ngh\'de vi\'d6n!
\par }{\b\f37\fs20\lang1053\langfe1033\langnp1053\insrsid1378858 \'a7\'b9i bi\'d3u \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng:}{\f37\fs20\lang1053\langfe1033\langnp1053\insrsid1378858  Nh\'a9n danh to\'b5n th\'d3 lo\'b5i ng\'ad\'eai, nh\'a9n danh t\'cat c\'b6 c\'b8c \'ae\'b6ng vi
\'aan x\'b7 h\'e9i, c\'b6 ph\'b8i h\'f7u l\'c9n ph\'b8i t\'b6, ch\'f3ng t\'abi k\'aau g\'e4i: C\'b8c \'ae\'e5ng ch\'dd, h\'b7y c\'f8u ch\'f3ng t\'abi! }{\i\f37\fs20\lang1053\langfe1033\langnp1053\insrsid1378858 (V\'e7 tay).}{
\f37\fs20\lang1053\langfe1033\langnp1053\insrsid1378858 
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\b\f37\fs20\lang1053\langfe1033\langnp1053\insrsid1378858 Ch\'f1 t\'dech:}{\f37\fs20\lang1053\langfe1033\langnp1053\insrsid1378858  Qua nh\'f7
ng lo\'b9t v\'e7 tay t\'b8n th\'b5nh, \'ae\'b9i bi\'d3u \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng c\'e3 th\'d3 th\'cay r\'bbng to\'b5n th\'d3 \'a7\'b6ng X\'b7 h\'e9i \'ae\'d2u \'ae\'f8ng v\'d2 ph\'dda \'ae\'e5ng ch\'dd \'ae\'d3 ph\'b6n \'ae\'e8i nh\'f7ng t\'e9i \'b8c c\'f1
a giai c\'cap t\'ad s\'b6n.
\par }\pard\plain \s26\ql \li0\ri567\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin567\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\lang1053\langfe1033\langnp1053\insrsid1378858 
\par Tr\'ddch }{\i\lang1053\langfe1033\langnp1053\insrsid1378858 Bi\'aan b\'b6n t\'e8c k\'fd \'a7\'b9i h\'e9i\line to\'b5n qu\'e8c l\'c7n th\'f8 XVIII \'a7\'b6ng\line X\'b7 h\'e9i Ph\'b8p}{\lang1053\langfe1033\langnp1053\insrsid1378858 , ti\'d5ng Ph\'b8p,
\line Pari, 1921, tr.133-135.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\lang1053\langfe1033\langnp1053\insrsid1378858 
