10 TR\'a6\'eaNG H\'e4C, 1500 \'a7\'b9I L\'fd R\'a6\'eeU
\par }\pard\plain \s25\qc \li0\ri0\sb200\sa240\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f38\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\lang1053\langfe1033\langnp1053\insrsid1378858 K\'ce \'a7\'c7U \'a7\'e9
C NG\'a6\'eaI B\'b6N X\'f8
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\lang1053\langfe1033\langnp1053\insrsid1378858 \~\'a4ng Xar\'ab t\'e8t b
\'f4ng, B\'e9 tr\'ad\'ebng c\'cap ti\'d5n B\'e9 Thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea, c\'b8i ng\'ad\'eai b\'e8 th\'a9n y\'aau c\'f1a d\'a9n b\'b6n x\'f8 (\'abng ta n\'e3i th\'d5), \'a9u y\'d5m ng\'ad\'eai An Nam v\'b5 \'ae\'ad\'eec h\'e4 qu\'fd tr\'e4ng.
\par \'a7\'d3 truy\'d2n th\'f4 n\'d2n v\'a8n minh c\'f1a Ph\'b8p m\'b5 \'abng ta l\'b5 t\'b8c nh\'a9n ch\'ddnh, \'abng ta kh\'abng l\'efi b\'ad\'edc tr\'ad\'edc m\'e9t c\'b8i g\'d7 h\'d5t, k\'d3 c\'b6 nh\'f7ng h\'b5nh vi h\'ccn h\'b9 v\'b5 nh\'f7ng t\'e9i \'b8
c. \'a7\'a9y l\'b5 m\'e9t b\'bbng ch\'f8ng: m\'e9t l\'b8 th\'ad m\'b5 v\'edi c\'ad\'acng v\'de To\'b5n quy\'d2n \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng v\'b5 \'ae\'d3 cho ph\'e5ng t\'f3i c\'f1a nh\'f7ng t\'aan k\'ce c\'ad\'edp \'eb thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea v\'b5 t\'f3i \'ab
ng ta, \'abng ta g\'f6i cho c\'b8c vi\'aan ch\'f8c c\'cap d\'ad\'edi:
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\lang1053\langfe1033\langnp1053\insrsid1378858 "K\'ddnh g\'f6i \'abng c
\'abng s\'f8,
\par "T\'abi tr\'a9n tr\'e4ng y\'aau c\'c7u \'abng h\'d5t s\'f8c gi\'f3p \'ae\'ec Nha th\'ad\'acng ch\'ddnh }{\i\f37\fs20\lang1053\langfe1033\langnp1053\insrsid1378858 \'ae\'c6t th\'aam \'ae\'b9i l\'fd thu\'e8c phi\'d6n v\'b5 r\'ad\'eeu}{
\f37\fs20\lang1053\langfe1033\langnp1053\insrsid1378858 , theo ch\'d8 th\'de c\'f1a \'abng t\'e6ng gi\'b8m \'ae\'e8c Nha th\'ad\'acng ch\'ddnh \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng.
\par "\'a7\'d3 c\'abng vi\'d6c ti\'d5n h\'b5nh c\'e3 k\'d5t qu\'b6, t\'abi xin g\'f6i \'abng m\'e9t b\'b6n danh s\'b8ch nh\'f7ng \'ae\'b9i l\'fd c\'c7n \'ae\'c6t trong c\'b8c x\'b7 \'ae\'b7 k\'aa t\'aan; t\'edi nay ph\'c7n \'ae\'abng c\'b8c x\'b7 n\'b5y v\'c9
n ho\'b5n to\'b5n ch\'ada c\'e3 r\'ad\'eeu v\'b5 thu\'e8c phi\'d6n.
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\lang1053\langfe1033\langnp1053\insrsid1378858 "Th\'abng qua c\'b8c quan v
\'b5 c\'b8c x\'b7 tr\'ad\'ebng Cao Mi\'aan, \'abng c\'e3 th\'d3 d\'efng \'b6nh h\'ad\'ebng l\'edn c\'f1a \'abng \'ae\'d3 l\'b5m cho m\'e9t s\'e8 ti\'d3u th\'ad\'acng ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8 th\'cay r\'bbng bu\'abn th\'aam r\'ad\'eeu v\'b5 thu\'e8c phi
\'d6n l\'b5 r\'cat c\'e3 l\'eei.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\lang1053\langfe1033\langnp1053\insrsid1378858 "V\'d2 ph\'c7n ch\'f3ng t
\'abi th\'d7 nh\'f7ng vi\'aan ch\'f8c l\'adu \'ae\'e9ng trong l\'f3c \'aei 
\par }\pard \qj \li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\lang1053\langfe1033\langnp1053\insrsid1378858 kinh l\'fd c\'f2ng t\'d7m c\'b8ch \'ae\'c6t \'ae\'b9i l\'fd, tr\'f5 khi n\'d5u \'abng c\'abng s
\'f8 mu\'e8n h\'e4 ch\'ea \'abng v\'cbn \'ae\'e9ng c\'b8c quan ch\'f8c \'ae\'dea ph\'ad\'acng tr\'ad\'edc \'ae\'b7, th\'d7 h\'e4 ph\'b6i ch\'ea. Trong tr\'ad\'eang h\'eep \'cay, t\'abi xin \'abng vui l\'dfng b\'b8o c\'b8o cho t\'abi bi\'d5t.
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\lang1053\langfe1033\langnp1053\insrsid1378858 "Ch\'f3ng ta ch\'d8 c\'e3 th\'d3 \'ae\'b9t \'ae\'ad\'eec k\'d5t qu\'b6 m\'fc m\'b7n, n
\'d5u ch\'f3ng ta \'ae\'e5ng l\'dfng ph\'e8i h\'eep ch\'c6t ch\'cf v\'b5 li\'aan t\'f4c, v\'d7 l\'eei \'ddch t\'e8i \'aea c\'f1a c\'abng kh\'e8.
\par 
\par }\pard \qr \fi397\li0\ri567\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin567\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 K\'fd t\'aan: Anbe Xar\'ab"
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 
\par L\'f3c \'ae\'e3 c\'e3 m\'e9t ngh\'d7n n\'a8m tr\'a8m ty r\'ad\'eeu v\'b5 thu\'e8c phi\'d6n cho m\'e9t ngh\'d7n l\'b5ng trong khi ch\'d8 c\'e3 m\'ad\'eai tr\'ad\'eang h\'e4c c\'f2ng cho b\'cay nhi\'aau l\'b5ng. Ngay c\'b6 tr\'ad\'edc b\'f8c th\'ad n\'e6
i danh \'ae\'e3, ng\'ad\'eai ta \'ae\'b7 cho 12 tri\'d6u ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8 - k\'d3 c\'b6 \'ae\'b5n b\'b5 v\'b5 tr\'ce con - n\'e8c 23 \'ae\'d5n 24 tri\'d6u l\'ddt r\'ad\'eeu m\'e7i n\'a8m.
\par L\'eai b\'d7nh lu\'cbn n\'b5o c\'f2ng l\'b5 th\'f5a.
\par }\pard\plain \s24\qr \fi397\li0\ri567\sb360\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin567\lin0\itap0 \f38\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 NGUY\'d4N \'b8I QU\'e8C
\par }\pard\plain \s26\ql \li0\ri567\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin567\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 B\'b8o }{\i\insrsid1378858 La Vie Ouvri\'ccre,}{\insrsid1378858 
\line s\'e8 100, ng\'b5y 1-4-1921.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 
\par }{\b\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 
\par 
\par 
