NG
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 \~Trong th\'eai gian chi\'d5n tranh v\'f5a qua, cu\'e9
c chi\'d5n tranh v\'d7 ch\'ddnh ngh\'dca v\'b5 c\'abng l\'fd \'ae\'d3 cho c\'b8c d\'a9n t\'e9c gi\'b5nh quy\'d2n t\'f9 quy\'d5t, nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai An Nam l\'b9i bu\'e9c ph\'b6i t\'d7nh nguy\'d6n sang b\'b6o v\'d6 n\'ad\'edc M\'d1 (?). B\'cay gi\'ea ng
\'ad\'eai ta n\'e3i v\'edi h\'e4 nh\'ad \'ae\'b7 n\'e3i v\'edi ng\'ad\'eai Ph\'b8p: "B\'e4n b\'abs\'ac}{\cs17\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 1{\footnote \pard\plain \s28\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa60\sl-240\slmult0
\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 1) }{\i\insrsid1378858 Boches:}{\insrsid1378858  t\'aan g\'e4i ch\'d5 gi\'d4u v\'b5 khinh b\'d8 c\'f1a ng\'ad\'ea
i Ph\'b8p \'ae\'e8i v\'edi l\'ddnh \'a7\'f8c.}})}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  s\'cf tr\'b6 c\'abng!".
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-276\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 Tuy nhi\'aan, gi\'ea \'ae\'a9y hai n\'a8m sau chi\'d5
n tranh, n\'ad\'edc M\'d1 b\'de m\'bec n\'ee m\'e9t c\'b8ch th\'beng l\'eei, nh\'f7ng khu nh\'b5 ngh\'d8 m\'b8t \'ae\'bet ti\'d2n c\'f1a c\'b8c quan ch\'f8c cao c\'cap c\'f1a Nh\'b5 n\'ad\'edc kh\'abng \'aeem l\'b9i \'ae\'ad\'eec b\'e6ng l\'e9c bao nhi
\'aau, v\'b5 b\'e4n b\'abs\'ac v\'c9n kh\'abng tr\'b6 g\'d7. B\'cay gi\'ea, n\'ad\'edc M\'d1 b\'b6o h\'e9 \'a9u y\'d5m quay v\'d2 nh\'f7ng \'ae\'f8a con nu\'abi c\'f1a m\'d7nh v\'b5 n\'e3i m\'e9t c\'b8ch \'a9u y\'d5m h\'acn n\'f7a: "V\'d7 b\'e4n \'a7\'f8
c l\'cbt l\'e4ng kh\'abng mu\'e8n tr\'b6, v\'cby th\'d7 c\'b8c con, nh\'f7ng k\'ce lao \'ae\'e9ng An Nam, h\'b7y tr\'b6 thay cho ch\'f3ng".
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-276\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Nh\'adng h\'b7y nghe l\'eai n\'e3i c\'f1a \'abng Xar\'ab t
\'e8t b\'f4ng, trong m\'e9t cu\'e9c tranh lu\'cbn v\'d2 ng\'a9n s\'b8ch thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea, v\'de u\'fb vi\'aan nh\'a9n d\'a9n thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea \'ae\'e3 \'ae\'b7 tuy\'aan b\'e8: "Ch\'f5ng n\'b5o m\'b5 x\'f8 \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng c\'dfn c\'e3 th\'d3 t
\'f9 \'ae\'b6m \'ae\'ad\'acng m\'e9t s\'e8 g\'b8nh n\'c6ng t\'b5i ch\'ddnh m\'b5 ch\'ddnh qu\'e8c kh\'abng g\'b8nh v\'b8c n\'e6i, x\'f8 \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng s\'cf g\'b8nh v\'b8c, v\'d7 d\'ef sao n\'ad\'edc Ph\'b8p, ch\'ddnh qu\'e8c, \'ae\'b7 c\'f8u \'a7
\'abng D\'ad\'acng tho\'b8t kh\'e1i s\'f9 tham lam c\'f1a n\'ad\'edc \'a7\'f8c".
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-276\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 Nh\'a9n danh h\'b5ng ngh\'d7n ng\'ad\'eai An Nam \'ae\'b7 b
\'e1 th\'a9y \'eb n\'ad\'edc Ph\'b8p trong chi\'d5n tranh, t\'abi xin c\'b8m \'acn \'abng, \'abng Xar\'ab. H\'b7y tin ch\'bec r\'bbng ch\'f3ng t\'abi bi\'d5t r\'cat r\'e2 ch\'ddnh chi\'d5n th\'beng tr\'aan s\'abng M\'b8cn\'ac \'ae\'b7 ng\'a8n c\'b6n qu
\'a9n xung k\'ddch \'a7\'f8c ti\'d5n v\'d2 s\'abng M\'aa K\'abng, \'ae\'d3 truy\'d2n b\'b8 tr\'aan ru\'e9ng \'ae\'e5ng ch\'f3ng t\'abi ch\'d5 \'ae\'e9 d\'b7 man c\'f1a ch\'f1 ngh\'dca t\'ad b\'b6n v\'b5 ch\'f1 ngh\'dca \'ae\'d5 qu\'e8c Ph\'e6. N\'d5u kh
\'abng c\'e3 ng\'b5i v\'b5 ng\'ad\'eai thay m\'c6t \'ae\'b8ng k\'ddnh c\'f1a ch\'f3ng t\'abi, \'abng Ut\'acr\'a9y, ch\'f3ng t\'abi s\'cf m\'cat c\'b8i t\'f9 do th\'a9n y\'aau \'ae\'ad\'eec say s\'ada b\'bbng r\'ad\'eeu c\'e5n v\'b5 c\'b8i b\'d7nh \'ae\'bc
ng qu\'fd gi\'b8 \'ae\'ad\'eec \'ae\'c7u \'ae\'e9c b\'bbng thu\'e8c phi\'d6n; kh\'abng c\'e3 ng\'b5i, giai c\'cap v\'ab s\'b6n b\'b6n x\'f8 kh\'abng c\'dfn \'ae\'ad\'eec nh\'e5i nh\'d0t v\'b5o tai nh\'f7ng b\'b5i di\'d4n v\'a8n hay ho v\'b5 nh\'f7ng l\'ea
i h\'f8a t\'e8t \'ae\'d1p \'ae\'ad\'eec ng\'b5i ban cho m\'e9t c\'b8ch h\'f7u \'b8i; kh\'abng c\'e3 ng\'b5i.... Nh\'adng h\'b7y cho qua v\'b5 quay tr\'eb l\'b9i b\'b5i di\'d4n v\'a8n c\'f1a ng\'b5i.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Ng\'b5i c\'dfn n\'e3i: "T\'abi tin r\'bbng trong m\'e9t th
\'eai gian kh\'abng xa n\'f7a, x\'f8 \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng s\'cf kh\'abng ti\'aau m\'cat m\'e9t \'ae\'e5ng xu n\'b5o n\'f7a c\'f1a ch\'ddnh qu\'e8c v\'b5 n\'e3 s\'cf t\'f9 h\'b5o v\'b5 h\'b9nh ph\'f3c \'ae\'ad\'eec \'aeem l\'b9i s\'f9 \'ae\'e3ng g\'e3p c
\'f1a m\'d7nh".
\par Nh\'cat \'ae\'denh th\'d5, \'ae\'d5n th\'eai k\'fa \'ae\'e3, kh\'abng c\'dfn xa l\'bem, nh\'ad ng\'b5i n\'e3i, giai c\'cap v\'ab s\'b6n ch\'ddnh qu\'e8c s\'cf l\'b5m nhi\'d6m v\'f4 c\'f1a m\'d7nh: h\'e4 s\'cf t\'e8ng c\'e6 t\'cat c\'b6 b\'e4n \'a8n b\'b8
m ra kh\'e1i c\'f6a; sau khi \'ae\'b7 gi\'b6i ph\'e3ng m\'d7nh, h\'e4 s\'cf gi\'b6i ph\'e3ng nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai anh em \'eb \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng; \'ae\'ad\'eec gi\'b6i ph\'e3ng kh\'e1i \'b8ch \'ae\'d5 qu\'e8c ch\'f1 ngh\'dca, nh\'a9n d\'a9n \'a7\'ab
ng D\'ad\'acng nh\'cat \'ae\'denh s\'cf t\'f9 h\'b5o v\'b5 h\'b9nh ph\'f3c, t\'f9 h\'b5o v\'b5 h\'b9nh ph\'f3c h\'acn l\'b5 \'abng t\'ad\'ebng, \'aeem l\'b9i s\'f9 \'ae\'e3ng g\'e3p c\'f1a m\'d7nh, c\'efng v\'edi nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai lao \'ae\'e9ng Ph\'b8
p x\'a9y d\'f9ng T\'e6 qu\'e8c chung. Trong khi ch\'ea \'ae\'eei, h\'b7y c\'f8 b\'bet nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai b\'b9i tr\'cbn \'eb \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng tr\'b6 ti\'d2n. Ng\'b5i h\'b7y kh\'d0o xoay x\'eb theo ph\'ad\'acng ph\'b8p D}{
\cs17\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 1{\footnote \pard\plain \s28\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa60\sl-240\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 1) D. Vi\'d5
t t\'bet t\'f5 ch\'f7 }{\i\insrsid1378858 d\'d0brouillard}{\insrsid1378858 , c\'e3 ngh\'dca l\'b5 th\'b8o v\'b8t, linh ho\'b9t.}})}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 . N\'d5u h\'dfm ti\'d2n c\'f1a nh\'a9n d\'a9n r\'e7ng, th\'d7 c\'dfn c\'e3 c\'b8c l\'a8ng m\'e9 c
\'f1a vua ch\'f3a.
\par }\pard\plain \s24\qr \fi397\li0\ri567\sb360\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin567\lin0\itap0 \f38\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 NGUY\'d4N \'b8I QU\'e8C
\par }\pard\plain \s26\ql \li0\ri567\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin567\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 B\'b8o }{\i\insrsid1378858 La Vie Ouvri\'ccre,}{\insrsid1378858 
\line s\'e8 101, ng\'b5y 8-4-1921.
\par }\pard\plain \s21\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \b\f39\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 
\par }\pard\plain \s20\qc \li0\ri0\sb1400\sa440\sl-380\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \b\f38\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 \line \line \line \line \line QUY\'d2N C\'f1A NH\'f7
NG NG\'a6\'eaI L\'ddNH CHI\'d5N}{\cs17\super\insrsid1378858 1{\footnote \pard\plain \s28\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa60\sl-240\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {
\insrsid1378858 1) }{\i\insrsid1378858 Les poilus:}{\insrsid1378858  T\'aan g\'e4i h\'b5i h\'ad\'edc  d\'efng \'ae\'d3 ch\'d8 l\'ddnh Ph\'b8p trong Chi\'d5n tranh th\'d5 gi\'edi th\'f8 nh\'cat, c\'e3 ngh\'dca l\'b5 "nh\'f7ng k\'ce l\'abng l\'b8".}})}{
\b0\insrsid1378858 
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 \~"Nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai l\'ddnh chi\'d5n c\'e3 quy\'d2n 
\'ae\'e8i v\'edi ch\'f3ng ta", \'abng Cl\'aam\'a8ngx\'ab, ng\'ad\'eai cha c\'f1a chi\'d5n th\'beng \'ae\'b7 n\'e3i nh\'ad v\'cby. "Nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai l\'ddnh chi\'d5n c\'e3 quy\'d2n \'ae\'e8i v\'edi ch\'f3ng ta", nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai con, nh\'f7ng n\'b9
n nh\'a9n An Nam nh\'bec l\'b9i nh\'ad v\'cby. \'a7\'e8i v\'edi \'abng Cl\'aam\'a8ngx\'ab, nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai l\'ddnh chi\'d5n c\'e3 quy\'d2n thi\'aang li\'aang l\'b5 ch\'d5t \'aei \'ae\'d3 b\'b6o v\'d6 k\'d0t s\'bet, nh\'f7ng chi\'d5c k\'d0t s\'bet l
\'b5m b\'bbng m\'e5 h\'abi th\'ee thuy\'d2n c\'f1a h\'e4 v\'b5 nh\'d0t \'ae\'c7y b\'bbng m\'b8u binh l\'ddnh c\'f1a h\'e4. \'a7\'e8i v\'edi ng\'ad\'eai An Nam, th\'d7 nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai l\'ddnh chi\'d5n - hay nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai c\'dfn l\'b9i trong s
\'e8 l\'ddnh chi\'d5n tr\'ad\'edc kia - c\'e3 quy\'d2n thi\'aang li\'aang \'ae\'ad\'eec b\'e4n t\'ad b\'b6n thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea ban cho, l\'b5 duy tr\'d7 n\'d2n v\'a8n minh t\'ad s\'b6n, ngh\'dca l\'b5 \'ae\'c7u \'ae\'e9c ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8 sau khi 
\'ae\'b7 gi\'d5t h\'b9i m\'e9t s\'e8 l\'edn v\'d7 quy\'d2n l\'eei c\'f1a t\'ad b\'b6n.
\par Theo b\'b8o ch\'dd \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng, c\'b8c m\'abn b\'b5i b\'b8n l\'ce thu\'e8c phi\'d6n s\'cf \'ae\'ad\'eec c\'cap cho nh\'f7ng qu\'b6 ph\'f4 c\'f1a binh l\'ddnh Ph\'b8p ch\'d5t tr\'cbn v\'b5 th\'ad\'acng binh Ph\'b8p.
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 Nh\'ad v\'cby, ch\'ddnh ph\'f1 thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea \'ae\'b7
 l\'b5m m\'e9t vi\'d6c m\'b5 ph\'b9m hai t\'e9i \'b8c ph\'b6n nh\'a9n lo\'b9i. M\'e9t m\'c6t, h\'e4 th\'cay t\'f9 m\'d7nh l\'b5m c\'abng vi\'d6c \'ae\'c7u \'ae\'e9c b\'c8n th\'d8u \'ae\'e3 ch\'ada \'ae\'f1, h\'e4 mu\'e8n l\'abi k\'d0o th\'aam nh\'f7ng n
\'b9n nh\'a9n kh\'e8n kh\'e6 c\'f1a h\'e4 trong cu\'e9c ch\'d0m gi\'d5t huynh \'ae\'d6 t\'ad\'acng t\'b5n tham gia v\'b5o. M\'c6t kh\'b8c, h\'e4 \'ae\'b8nh gi\'b8 qu\'b8 th\'cap t\'ddnh m\'d6nh v\'b5 x\'ad\'acng m\'b8u c\'f1a nh\'f7ng k\'ce b\'de h\'e4 l
\'f5a b\'dep, m\'b5 h\'e4 t\'ad\'ebng r\'bbng v\'f8t cho m\'c8u x\'ad\'acng th\'f5a \'ae\'e3 l\'b5 c\'e3 th\'d3 \'ae\'f1 \'ae\'d2n b\'ef s\'f9 m\'cat m\'b8t m\'e9t c\'bcng tay c\'bcng ch\'a9n hay c\'b8i tang c\'f1a m\'e9t ng\'ad\'eai ch\'e5ng.
\par Ch\'f3ng t\'abi tin r\'bbng nh\'f7ng th\'ad\'acng binh v\'b5 nh\'f7ng qu\'b6 ph\'f4 s\'cf \'ae\'b8 tung m\'e3n qu\'b5 h\'abi h\'b8m \'ae\'e3 v\'b5 s\'cf c\'abng ph\'c9n nh\'e6 v\'b5o m\'c6t nh\'f7ng k\'ce \'ae\'b7 \'ae\'d2 x\'ad\'edng vi\'d6c \'ae\'e3; v
\'b5 ch\'f3ng t\'abi ch\'bec ch\'ben r\'bbng c\'b6 th\'d5 gi\'edi v\'a8n minh v\'b5 nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai Ph\'b8p l\'ad\'acng thi\'d6n s\'cf c\'efng v\'edi ch\'f3ng t\'abi l\'aan \'b8n b\'e4n c\'b8 m\'cbp \'eb c\'b8c thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea \'ae\'b7 kh\'abng ng
\'c7n ng\'b9i \'ae\'c7u \'ae\'e9c c\'b6 m\'e9t ch\'f1ng t\'e9c \'ae\'d3 l\'b5m \'ae\'c7y t\'f3i ti\'d2n c\'f1a m\'d7nh.
\par }\pard\plain \s24\qr \fi397\li0\ri567\sb360\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin567\lin0\itap0 \f38\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 NGUY\'d4N \'b8I QU\'e8C
\par }\pard\plain \s26\ql \li0\ri567\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin567\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 B\'b8o }{\i\insrsid1378858 La Vie Ouvri\'ccre,}{\insrsid1378858 
