\'b6N QU\'e8C T\'d5
\par }\pard\plain \s25\qc \li0\ri0\sb360\sa320\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f38\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 \'a7\'a4NG D\'a6\'a5NG
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 \~Ch\'d5 \'ae\'e9 c\'e9ng s\'b6n c\'e3 \'b8p d\'f4ng \'ae
\'ad\'eec \'eb ch\'a9u }{\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'b8}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  n\'e3i chung v\'b5 \'eb \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng n\'e3i ri\'aang kh\'abng? \'a7\'cay l\'b5 v\'can \'ae\'d2 m\'b5 ch\'f3ng ta \'aeang quan t\'a9m hi\'d6n nay.
\par Mu\'e8n hi\'d3u v\'can \'ae\'d2 \'ae\'e3, ch\'f3ng ta ph\'b6i xem x\'d0t t\'d7nh h\'d7nh hi\'d6n nay \'eb l\'f4c \'ae\'dea ch\'a9u }{\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'b8}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  v\'d2 m\'c6t l\'dech s\'f6 v\'b5 \'ae\'dea l\'fd.
\par L\'f4c \'ae\'dea r\'e9ng l\'edn \'ae\'e3 c\'e3 di\'d6n t\'ddch 80 l\'c7n l\'edn h\'acn n\'ad\'edc Ph\'b8p (45.000.000 km}{\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 2}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 ), v\'edi d\'a9n s\'e8 g\'c7n 800 tri\'d6u ng\'ad\'eai, c\'e3 m\'e9t c\'ac
 c\'cau ch\'ddnh tr\'de t\'ad\'acng \'ae\'e8i ph\'f8c t\'b9p.
\par Trong t\'cat c\'b6 c\'b8c n\'ad\'edc ch\'a9u }{\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'b8}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 , Nh\'cbt B\'b6n l\'b5 n\'ad\'edc duy nh\'cat m\'bec ph\'b6i m\'e9t c\'b8ch tr\'c7m tr\'e4ng nh\'cat ch\'f8ng b\'d6nh truy\'d2n nhi\'d4m l\'b5 ch\'f1
 ngh\'dca t\'ad b\'b6n \'ae\'d5 qu\'e8c. T\'f5 chi\'d5n tranh Nga - Nh\'cbt, ch\'f8ng b\'d6nh \'ae\'e3 di\'d4n bi\'d5n ng\'b5y c\'b5ng nguy k\'dech, l\'f3c \'ae\'c7u b\'bbng s\'f9 th\'abn t\'ddnh Tri\'d2u Ti\'aan, ti\'d5p \'ae\'cay l\'b5 s\'f9 tham gia v
\'b5o cu\'e9c chi\'d5n tranh "v\'d7 ch\'ddnh ngh\'dca".
\par \'a7\'d3 ng\'a8n c\'b6n n\'ad\'edc Nh\'cbt tr\'ad\'eet d\'b5i \'ae\'d5n v\'f9c th\'bcm c\'f1a hi\'d6n t\'ad\'eeng ph\'ad\'acng T\'a9y ho\'b8 kh\'abng th\'d3 c\'f8u v\'b7n n\'e6i, ngh\'dca l\'b5 \'ae\'d3 ph\'b8 tan ch\'f1 ngh\'dca t\'ad b\'b6n tr\'ad\'ed
c khi n\'e3 c\'e3 th\'d3 b\'bet r\'d4 s\'a9u v\'b5o qu\'c7n \'ae\'b6o Nh\'cbt B\'b6n, m\'e9t \'ae\'b6ng x\'b7 h\'e9i v\'f5a \'ae\'ad\'eec th\'b5nh l\'cbp. C\'f2ng nh\'ad t\'cat c\'b6 c\'b8c ch\'ddnh ph\'f1 t\'ad s\'b6n, ch\'ddnh ph\'f1 Thi\'aan ho\'b5ng 
\'ae\'b7 d\'efng m\'e4i c\'b8ch m\'b5 ch\'f3ng c\'e3 th\'d3 \'ae\'d3 ch\'e8ng l\'b9i phong tr\'b5o \'ae\'e3. C\'f2ng nh\'ad t\'cat c\'b6 c\'b8c l\'f9c l\'ad\'eeng c\'abng nh\'a9n \'eb ch\'a9u \'a2u v\'b5 ch\'a9u M\'fc, phong tr\'b5o c\'abng nh\'a9n Nh\'cb
t B\'b6n c\'f2ng v\'f5a th\'f8c t\'d8nh. M\'c6c d\'ef s\'f9 \'ae\'b5n \'b8p c\'f1a ch\'ddnh ph\'f1, phong tr\'b5o do \'a7\'b6ng X\'b7 h\'e9i Nh\'cbt B\'b6n l\'b7nh \'ae\'b9o v\'c9n ph\'b8t tri\'d3n kh\'b8 nhanh.
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-262\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 C\'b8c \'ae\'b9i h\'e9i \'ae\'b6ng b\'de c\'cam \'eb c\'b8c th\'b5nh ph\'e8 Nh\'cbt B\'b6n, nh\'f7ng cu\'e9c \'ae\'d7
nh c\'abng, nh\'f7ng cu\'e9c bi\'d3u t\'d7nh c\'f1a d\'a9n ch\'f3ng v\'c9n n\'e6 ra.
\par Trung Qu\'e8c, tr\'ad\'edc kia v\'b5 hi\'d6n nay v\'c9n l\'b5 con b\'df s\'f7a c\'f1a t\'ad b\'b6n \'a2u, M\'fc. Nh\'adng s\'f9 th\'b5nh l\'cbp ch\'ddnh quy\'d2n c\'f1a nh\'b5 c\'b8ch m\'b9ng T\'abn D\'cbt Ti\'aan \'eb ph\'dda Nam, \'ae\'b7 h\'f8a h\'d1
n v\'edi ch\'f3ng ta m\'e9t n\'ad\'edc Trung Hoa \'ae\'ad\'eec t\'e6 ch\'f8c l\'b9i v\'b5 v\'ab s\'b6n ho\'b8. C\'e3 th\'d3 hy v\'e4ng m\'e9t c\'b8ch kh\'abng qu\'b8 \'ae\'b8ng r\'bbng, trong m\'e9t t\'ad\'acng lai g\'c7n \'ae\'a9y, hai ch\'de em - n\'ad
\'edc Trung Hoa m\'edi v\'b5 n\'ad\'edc Nga c\'abng nh\'a9n - s\'cf n\'bem tay nhau trong t\'d7nh h\'f7u ngh\'de \'ae\'d3 ti\'d5n l\'aan v\'d7 l\'eei \'ddch c\'f1a n\'d2n d\'a9n ch\'f1 v\'b5 nh\'a9n \'ae\'b9o.
\par B\'a9y gi\'ea, ch\'f3ng ta h\'b7y \'aei \'ae\'d5n ch\'a9u }{\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'b8 }{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'aeau kh\'e6.
\par N\'ad\'edc Tri\'d2u Ti\'aan ngh\'cco \'ae\'e3i \'aeang \'eb trong tay ch\'f1 ngh\'dca t\'ad b\'b6n Nh\'cbt. }{\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'ca}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 n \'a7\'e9 - x\'f8 }{\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'ca}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 n \'a7\'e9 
\'ae\'abng d\'a9n v\'b5 gi\'b5u c\'e3 - b\'de \'ae\'cc n\'c6ng d\'ad\'edi \'b8ch b\'e4n b\'e3c l\'e9t ng\'ad\'eai Anh. May sao, \'fd ch\'dd gi\'b6i ph\'e3ng \'aeang l\'b5m s\'abi s\'f4c t\'cat c\'b6 nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai b\'de \'b8p b\'f8c \'ae\'e3, v\'b5
 m\'e9t cu\'e9c c\'e6 \'ae\'e9ng c\'b8ch m\'b9ng s\'abi n\'e6i \'aeang lay chuy\'d3n tinh th\'c7n }{\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'ca}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 n \'a7\'e9 v\'b5 Tri\'d2u Ti\'aan. T\'cat c\'b6 m\'e4i ng\'ad\'eai \'ae\'d2u chu\'c8n b\'de m\'e9
t c\'b8ch t\'f5 t\'f5 nh\'adng kh\'abn kh\'d0o cho cu\'e9c \'ae\'cau tranh t\'e8i cao v\'b5 gi\'b6i ph\'e3ng.
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-262\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 V\'b5 \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng! X\'f8 \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'ac
ng b\'de ch\'f1 ngh\'dca t\'ad b\'b6n Ph\'b8p b\'e3c l\'e9t, \'ae\'d3 l\'b5m gi\'b5u cho m\'e9t s\'e8 c\'b8 m\'cbp! Ng\'ad\'eai ta \'ae\'ada ng\'ad\'eai \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng v\'b5o ch\'e7 ch\'d5t trong cu\'e9c ch\'d0m gi\'d5t c\'f1a b\'e4n t\'ad b\'b6n 
\'ae\'d3 b\'b6o v\'d6 nh\'f7ng c\'b8i g\'d7 m\'b5 ch\'ddnh h\'e4 kh\'abng h\'d2 bi\'d5t. Ng\'ad\'eai ta \'ae\'c7u \'ae\'e9c h\'e4 b\'bbng r\'ad\'eeu c\'e5n v\'b5 thu\'e8c phi\'d6n. Ng\'ad\'eai ta k\'d7m h\'e4 trong ngu d\'e8t (c\'f8 10 tr\'ad\'eang h\'e4
c th\'d7 c\'e3 1.000 \'ae\'b9i l\'fd thu\'e8c phi\'d6n ch\'ddnh th\'f8c). Ng\'ad\'eai ta b\'dea \'ae\'c6t ra nh\'f7ng v\'f4 \'a9m m\'adu \'ae\'d3 cho h\'e4 n\'d5m nh\'f7ng \'a9n hu\'d6 c\'f1a n\'d2n v\'a8n minh t\'ad s\'b6n \'eb tr\'aan m\'b8y ch\'d0
m, trong nh\'b5 t\'ef hay \'ae\'b5y bi\'d6t x\'f8!
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-262\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 75 ngh\'d7n kil\'abm\'d0t vu\'abng \'ae\'cat \'aeai}{
\cs17\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 1{\footnote \pard\plain \s28\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa60\sl-240\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 1) S\'e8 li
\'d6u n\'b5y c\'e3 th\'d3 do b\'b8o in nh\'c7m. Di\'d6n t\'ddch \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng 745.000km}{\super\insrsid1378858 2}{\insrsid1378858 .}})}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 , 20 tri\'d6u d\'a9n b\'de b\'e3c l\'e9t t\'b5n nh\'c9n trong tay m\'e9t nh\'f3m k
\'ce c\'ad\'edp th\'f9c d\'a9n, \'ae\'cay l\'b5 x\'f8 \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng hi\'d6n nay.
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \li0\ri0\sa80\sl-274\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 B\'a9y gi\'ea h\'b7y x\'d0t nh\'f7ng l\'fd do l\'dech s\'f6
 cho ph\'d0p ch\'f1 ngh\'dca c\'e9ng s\'b6n th\'a9m nh\'cbp d\'d4 d\'b5ng v\'b5o ch\'a9u }{\f38\insrsid1378858 \'b8}{\insrsid1378858 , d\'d4 d\'b5ng h\'acn l\'b5 \'eb ch\'a9u \'a2u.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-274\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Ng\'ad\'eai ch\'a9u }{\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'b8}{
\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  - tuy b\'de ng\'ad\'eai ph\'ad\'acng T\'a9y coi l\'b5 l\'b9c h\'cbu - v\'c9n hi\'d3u r\'e2 h\'acn h\'d5t s\'f9 c\'c7n thi\'d5t ph\'b6i c\'b6i c\'b8ch to\'b5n b\'e9 x\'b7 h\'e9i hi\'d6n t\'b9i. V\'b5 \'ae\'a9y l\'b5 l\'fd do t\'b9
i sao:
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-274\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\expnd0\expndtw-2\insrsid1378858 G\'c7n 5.000 n\'a8m tr\'ad\'edc \'ae\'a9
y, Ho\'b5ng \'ae\'d5 (2.679 tr\'ad\'edc C.N) \'ae\'b7 \'b8p d\'f4ng ch\'d5 \'ae\'e9 t\'d8nh \'aei\'d2n: \'abng chia \'ae\'cat \'aeai tr\'e5ng tr\'e4t theo hai \'ae\'ad\'eang d\'e4c v\'b5 hai \'ae\'ad\'eang ngang. Nh\'ad v\'cby s\'cf c\'e3 ch\'ddn ph\'c7
n b\'bbng nhau. Ng\'ad\'eai c\'b5y ru\'e9ng \'ae\'ad\'eec l\'dcnh m\'e7i ng\'ad\'eai m\'e9t ph\'c7n trong 8 mi\'d5ng, mi\'d5ng \'eb gi\'f7a t\'cat c\'b6 \'ae\'d2u c\'efng l\'b5m v\'b5 s\'b6n ph\'c8m \'ae\'ad\'eec s\'f6 d\'f4ng v\'b5o vi\'d6c c\'abng \'dd
ch. Nh\'f7ng \'ae\'ad\'eang ph\'a9n gi\'edi \'ae\'ad\'eec d\'efng l\'b5m m\'ad\'acng d\'c9n n\'ad\'edc.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-274\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Tri\'d2u \'ae\'b9i nh\'b5 H\'b9 (2.205 tr\'ad\'edc C.N) 
\'ae\'c6t ra ch\'d5 \'ae\'e9 lao \'ae\'e9ng b\'bet bu\'e9c.
\par Kh\'e6ng T\'f6 v\'dc \'ae\'b9i (551 tr\'ad\'edc C.N) kh\'ebi x\'ad\'edng thuy\'d5t \'ae\'b9i \'ae\'e5ng v\'b5 truy\'d2n b\'b8 s\'f9 b\'d7nh \'ae\'bcng v\'d2 t\'b5i s\'b6n}{\cs17\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 1{\footnote \pard\plain 
\s28\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa60\sl-240\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 1) B\'b6n ch\'cat h\'e4c thuy\'d5t c\'f1a Kh\'e6ng T\'f6 l\'b5 n\'c6ng v
\'d2 \'a7\'bcng c\'cap, \'ae\'d2 cao t\'c7ng l\'edp th\'e8ng tr\'de}{\f38\insrsid1378858 . \'eb}{\insrsid1378858  \'ae\'a9y n\'aau l\'b9i thuy\'d5t \'ae\'b9i \'ae\'e5ng c\'f1a Kh\'e6ng T\'f6  l\'b5 Nguy\'d4n }{\f38\insrsid1378858 \'b8}{\insrsid1378858 
i Qu\'e8c mu\'e8n g\'ben v\'edi cu\'e9c \'ae\'cau tranh v\'d7 s\'f9 c\'abng b\'bbng v\'b5 b\'d7nh \'ae\'bcng trong x\'b7 h\'e9i thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea (B.T.).}})}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 . \'a4ng t\'f5ng n\'e3i: thi\'aan h\'b9 s\'cf th\'b8i b\'d7nh khi th
\'d5 gi\'edi \'ae\'b9i \'ae\'e5ng. Ng\'ad\'eai ta kh\'abng s\'ee thi\'d5u, ch\'d8 s\'ee c\'e3 kh\'abng \'ae\'d2u. B\'d7nh \'ae\'bcng s\'cf xo\'b8 b\'e1 ngh\'cco n\'b5n, v.v..
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-274\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 H\'e4c tr\'df c\'f1a Kh\'e6ng T\'f6 l\'b5 M\'b9nh T\'f6, ti
\'d5p t\'f4c t\'ad t\'ad\'ebng c\'f1a th\'c7y v\'b5 v\'b9ch ra m\'e9t k\'d5 ho\'b9ch chi ti\'d5t \'ae\'d3 t\'e6 ch\'f8c s\'f9 s\'b6n xu\'cat v\'b5 ti\'aau th\'f4. S\'f9 b\'b6o v\'d6 v\'b5 ph\'b8t tri\'d3n l\'b5nh m\'b9nh c\'f1a tr\'ce em, s\'f9 gi\'b8o d
\'f4c v\'b5 lao \'ae\'e9ng c\'ad\'ecng b\'f8c \'ae\'e8i v\'edi ng\'ad\'eai l\'edn, s\'f9 l\'aan \'b8n nghi\'aam kh\'bec th\'e3i \'a8n b\'b8m, s\'f9 ngh\'d8 ng\'aci c\'f1a ng\'ad\'eai gi\'b5, kh\'abng c\'e3 \'aei\'d2u g\'d7 \'ae\'d2 \'b8n c\'f1a \'abng kh
\'abng \'ae\'d2 c\'cbp \'ae\'d5n. Vi\'d6c th\'f1 ti\'aau b\'cat b\'d7nh \'ae\'bcng v\'d2 h\'ad\'ebng th\'f4, h\'b9nh ph\'f3c kh\'abng ph\'b6i cho m\'e9t s\'e8 \'ae\'abng m\'b5 cho t\'cat c\'b6 m\'e4i ng\'ad\'eai, \'ae\'cay l\'b5 \'ae\'ad\'eang l\'e8
i kinh t\'d5 c\'f1a v\'de hi\'d2n tri\'d5t.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-274\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Tr\'b6 l\'eai m\'e9t c\'a9u h\'e1i c\'f1a vua, \'abng \'ae
\'b7 n\'e3i th\'bcng th\'ben: d\'a9n vi qu\'fd, x\'b7 t\'bec th\'f8 chi, qu\'a9n vi khinh.
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 V\'d2 c\'f1a c\'b6i t\'ad h\'f7u, lu\'cbt ph\'b8p An Nam c\'cam mua b\'b8n to\'b5n b\'e9 \'ae\'cat \'aeai. H\'acn n\'f7
a, m\'e9t ph\'c7n t\'ad \'ae\'cat tr\'e5ng tr\'e4t b\'bet bu\'e9c ph\'b6i \'ae\'d3 l\'b5m c\'f1a chung. C\'f8 ba n\'a8m ng\'ad\'eai ta chia l\'b9i ru\'e9ng \'ae\'cat \'ae\'e3. M\'e7i ng\'ad\'eai d\'a9n trong x\'b7 th\'abn \'ae\'ad\'eec nh\'cbn m\'e9t ph
\'c7n. \'a7i\'d2u \'ae\'e3 kh\'abng h\'d2 ng\'a8n c\'b6n m\'e9t s\'e8 ng\'ad\'eai tr\'eb n\'aan gi\'b5u c\'e3, v\'d7 c\'dfn ba ph\'c7n t\'ad \'ae\'cat \'aeai kh\'b8c c\'e3 th\'d3 mua b\'b8n, nh\'adng n\'e3 c\'e3 th\'d3 c\'f8u nhi\'d2u ng\'ad\'eai kh\'b8
c tho\'b8t kh\'e1i c\'b6nh b\'c7n c\'efng.
\par C\'b8i thi\'d5u \'ae\'e8i v\'edi ch\'f3ng t\'abi, m\'b5 tr\'b8ch nhi\'d6m c\'f1a ch\'f3ng t\'abi ph\'b6i n\'e3i l\'aan \'eb \'ae\'a9y \'ae\'d3 nh\'f7ng \'ae\'e5ng ch\'dd c\'f1a ch\'f3ng ta c\'e3 nhi\'d6t t\'d7nh truy\'d2n b\'b8 ch\'f1 ngh\'dca c\'e9ng s
\'b6n v\'b5 th\'f9c t\'a9m mu\'e8n gi\'f3p \'ae\'ec nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai lao \'ae\'e9ng l\'cbt \'ae\'e6 \'b8ch c\'f1a nh\'f7ng k\'ce b\'e3c l\'e9t v\'b5 \'aei v\'b5o gia \'ae\'d7nh chung c\'f1a giai c\'cap v\'ab s\'b6n qu\'e8c t\'d5, \'ae\'d3 cho nh\'f7
ng \'ae\'e5ng ch\'dd \'ae\'e3 c\'e3 th\'d3 gi\'f3p \'ae\'ec ch\'f3ng t\'abi m\'e9t c\'b8ch c\'e3 hi\'d6u qu\'b6. C\'b8i m\'b5 ch\'f3ng t\'abi thi\'d5u \'ae\'d3 tr\'eb th\'b5nh c\'e9ng s\'b6n, l\'b5 nh\'f7ng \'aei\'d2u ki\'d6n c\'ac b\'b6n nh\'cat \'ae\'d3
 h\'b5nh \'ae\'e9ng:
\par }\pard \qj \fi2268\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 T\'f9 do b\'b8o ch\'dd 
\par T\'f9 do du l\'dech 
\par T\'f9 do d\'b9y v\'b5 h\'e4c
\par }\pard\plain \s18\qj \fi2268\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\fs20\expnd0\expndtw-4\insrsid1378858 T\'f9 do h\'e9i h\'e4p (t\'cat c\'b6
 nh\'f7ng c\'b8i n\'b5y \'ae\'d2u b\'de nh\'f7ng k\'ce khai ho\'b8 thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea ng\'a8n c\'cam ch\'f3ng t\'abi m\'e9t c\'b8ch d\'b7 man).
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Ng\'b5y m\'b5 h\'b5ng tr\'a8m tri\'d6u nh\'a9n d\'a9n ch
\'a9u }{\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'b8 }{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 b\'de t\'b5n s\'b8t v\'b5 \'b8p b\'f8c th\'f8c t\'d8nh \'ae\'d3 g\'b9t b\'e1 s\'f9 b\'e3c l\'e9t \'ae\'aa ti\'d6n c\'f1a m\'e9t b\'e4n th\'f9c d\'a9n l\'dfng tham kh\'abng \'ae\'b8y, h\'e4 s
\'cf h\'d7nh th\'b5nh m\'e9t l\'f9c l\'ad\'eeng kh\'e6ng l\'e5, v\'b5 trong khi th\'f1 ti\'aau m\'e9t trong nh\'f7ng \'aei\'d2u ki\'d6n t\'e5n t\'b9i c\'f1a ch\'f1 ngh\'dca t\'ad b\'b6n l\'b5 ch\'f1 ngh\'dca \'ae\'d5 qu\'e8c, h\'e4 c\'e3 th\'d3 gi\'f3p 
\'ae\'ec nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai anh em m\'d7nh \'eb ph\'ad\'acng T\'a9y trong nhi\'d6m v\'f4 gi\'b6i ph\'e3ng ho\'b5n to\'b5n.
\par }\pard\plain \s24\qr \fi397\li0\ri567\sb360\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin567\lin0\itap0 \f38\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 \~NGUY\'d4N \'b8I QU\'e8C
\par }\pard\plain \ql \li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 T}{\f37\insrsid1378858\charrsid30160 \'b9p ch\'dd }{
\i\f37\insrsid1378858\charrsid30160 La Revue Communiste,}{\f37\insrsid1378858\charrsid30160 \line s\'e8 15, th\'b8ng 5-1921}{\insrsid1378858 .}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 
\par }\pard \qj \fi2268\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 
\par }\pard\plain \s20\qc \li0\ri0\sb1400\sa440\sl-380\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \b\f38\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 \line \line \line \line V\'f4 \'a2M M\'a6U \'eb \'a7
\'a4NG D\'a6\'a5NG}{\cs17\super\insrsid1378858 1{\footnote \pard\plain \s28\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa60\sl-240\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 
1) B\'b5i n\'b5y d\'dech t\'f5 b\'b6n ti\'d5ng Ph\'b8p r\'f3t trong Kho h\'e5 s\'ac c\'f1a m\'cbt th\'b8m Ph\'b8p, \'ae\'d2 ng\'b5y 17-8-1921. V\'d2 sau, h\'c7u h\'d5t b\'b5i n\'b5y \'ae\'ad\'eec Nguy\'d4n }{\f38\insrsid1378858 \'b8}{\insrsid1378858 i Qu
\'e8c \'ae\'ada v\'b5o "}{\i\insrsid1378858 B\'b6n \'b8n ch\'d5 \'ae\'e9 th\'f9c d\'a9n Ph\'b8p}{\insrsid1378858 ", ch\'ad\'acng VIII C\'abng l\'fd, tr\'f5 m\'e9t s\'e8 c\'a9u \'eb cu\'e8i b\'b5i.
\par 2) Phong tr\'b5o ch\'e8ng thu\'d5 \'eb Trung K\'fa, n\'a8m 1908 v\'b5 v\'f4 m\'adu kh\'ebi ngh\'dca \'eb Hu\'d5, n\'a8m 1916.}})}{\insrsid1378858 
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-268\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 \~\'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng l\'b5 m\'e9t c\'ab g\'b8i c\'ad
ng. C\'ab r\'cat m\'f9c x\'f8ng \'ae\'b8ng v\'edi b\'b5 m\'d1 Ph\'b8p qu\'e8c. }{\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'eb }{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 b\'b5 m\'d1 c\'e3 c\'b8i g\'d7 th\'d7 c\'ab ta c\'f2ng c\'e3 c\'b8i n\'cay: n\'b5o ch\'ddnh ph\'f1, n\'b5o nh\'f7ng b
\'b6o \'ae\'b6m, n\'b5o c\'abng l\'fd v\'b5 c\'f2ng c\'e3 c\'b6 \'a9m m\'adu phi\'d5n lo\'b9n nho nh\'e1 n\'f7a. Nh\'adng \'eb \'ae\'a9y, ch\'f3ng t\'abi ch\'d8 n\'e3i v\'d2 hai v\'can \'ae\'d2 sau th\'abi.
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-268\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 C\'abng l\'fd \'ae\'ad\'eec t\'ad\'eeng tr\'adng qua h\'d7
nh \'b6nh m\'e9t n\'f7 th\'c7n tay c\'c7m c\'a9n v\'b5 tay c\'c7m ki\'d5m. Nh\'adng \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng l\'b9i \'eb qu\'b8 xa n\'ad\'edc Ph\'b8p, mu\'abn tr\'efng c\'b8ch tr\'eb, n\'aan khi n\'f7 th\'c7n t\'edi x\'f8 n\'b5y th\'d7 c\'b8n c\'a9n \'ae
\'b7 m\'cat th\'a8ng b\'bbng, \'ae\'dca c\'a9n \'ae\'b7 ch\'b6y l\'e1ng v\'b5 bi\'d5n th\'b5nh nh\'f7ng t\'c8u thu\'e8c phi\'d6n v\'b5 nh\'f7ng chai r\'ad\'eeu ty. Tr\'aan tay n\'f7 th\'c7n t\'e9i nghi\'d6p \'cay ch\'d8 c\'dfn \'ae\'e9c c\'b8i ki\'d5m 
\'ae\'d3 ch\'d0m gi\'d5t. B\'b5 \'ae\'b7 ch\'d0m nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai v\'ab t\'e9i v\'b5 c\'f2ng ch\'d8 ch\'d0m c\'e3 h\'e4 m\'b5 th\'abi!
\par C\'dfn v\'d2 v\'f4 \'a9m m\'adu th\'d7 l\'b9i l\'b5 m\'e9t c\'a9u chuy\'d6n kh\'b8c.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-268\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'eb }{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'ae\'a9y, ch\'f3ng t\'ab
i kh\'abng n\'e3i v\'d2 nh\'f7ng v\'f4 \'a9m m\'adu n\'e6i ti\'d5ng trong n\'a8m 1908 hay 1916}{\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 2)}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 . L\'f3c \'ae\'e3, nhi\'d2u th\'c7n d\'a9n b\'b6o h\'e9 s\'e8 \'ae\'e1 c\'f1a n\'ad\'edc Ph\'b8p 
\'ae\'b7 \'ae\'ad\'eec may m\'ben n\'d5m \'ae\'f1 m\'efi \'a9n hu\'d6 c\'f1a n\'d2n v\'a8n minh th\'f9c d\'a9n hi\'d2n ho\'b5 tr\'aan m\'b8y ch\'d0m, trong nh\'b5 t\'ef hay \'eb nh\'f7ng 
\par }\pard \qj \li0\ri0\sa80\sl-268\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 n\'aci b\'de \'ae\'ada \'aei \'ae\'c7y. Nh\'f7ng v\'f4 \'a9m m\'adu \'cay \'ae\'b7 qua l\'a9u r\'e5i, v\'b5 b\'a9y gi\'ea ch
\'d8 c\'dfn l\'b9i nh\'f7ng n\'d0t \'b6m \'ae\'b9m trong tr\'dd nh\'ed c\'f1a ng\'ad\'eai d\'a9n b\'b6n x\'f8 \'ae\'b7 h\'d0o m\'dfn v\'d7 \'aeau kh\'e6.
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-266\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 H\'b7y n\'e3i \'ae\'d5n v\'f4 \'a9m m\'adu g\'c7n \'ae\'a9y nh\'cat. Trong khi \'eb M\'c9u qu\'e8c c\'e3 m\'e9t v\'f4 
\'a9m m\'adu b\'abns\'aav\'ddch n\'e6i ti\'d5ng th\'d7 \'eb \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng c\'b8c ng\'b5i th\'f9c d\'a9n c\'f2ng mu\'e8n c\'e3 m\'e9t v\'f4 \'a9m m\'adu t\'ad\'acng t\'f9 v\'b5 ... cu\'e8i c\'efng c\'b8c ng\'b5i \'cay c\'f2ng n\'c6n ra m\'e9t v
\'f4 \'a9m m\'adu th\'cbt s\'f9, ch\'bcng kh\'b8c n\'b5o nh\'ad trong c\'a9u chuy\'d6n ng\'f4 ng\'abn con nh\'b8i mu\'e8n ph\'d7nh to b\'f4ng nh\'ad con b\'df}{\cs17\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 1{\footnote \pard\plain 
\s28\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa60\sl-240\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 1) Truy\'d6n ng\'f4 ng\'abn c\'f1a La Ph\'abngten: c\'e3 m\'e9t con nh
\'b8i th\'cay con b\'df to h\'acn m\'d7nh, li\'d2n c\'e8 ph\'d7nh b\'f4ng ra cho b\'bbng con b\'df, cu\'e8i c\'efng v\'ec b\'f4ng m\'b5 ch\'d5t.}})}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 .
\par C\'a9u chuy\'d6n \'cay \'ae\'b7 \'ae\'ad\'eec d\'f9ng l\'aan nh\'ad th\'d5 n\'b5y: M\'e9t ng\'b5i quan Ph\'b8p (quan c\'abng s\'f8), m\'e9t quan huy\'d6n v\'b5 m\'e9t th\'c7y l\'fd tr\'ad\'ebng \'ae\'ad\'eec giao tr\'b8ch nhi\'d6m d\'f9ng l\'aan m\'e9t v
\'f4 \'a9m m\'adu \'ae\'f3ng quy c\'b8ch. \'a7\'d3 chu\'c8n b\'de ra bi\'d3u di\'d4n, b\'e9 ba t\'ed th\'c7y \'cay b\'ccn tung ra c\'b8i tin: C\'e3 m\'e9t \'a9m m\'adu phi\'d5n lo\'b9n \'ae\'denh l\'b5m n\'e6 tan x\'f8 B\'bec K\'fa b\'bbng 250 qu\'b6
 bom. C\'abng vi\'d6c chu\'c8n b\'de xong xu\'abi. M\'b5n k\'dech k\'d0o l\'aan. C\'abng ch\'f3ng x\'f3c c\'b6m m\'b9nh m\'cf v\'b5 d\'ad lu\'cbn x\'abn xao. B\'bet b\'ed v\'a9y l\'efng d\'e5n d\'cbp nh\'ad m\'ada. Hi\'d6n nay, ch\'f3ng ta ch\'ada bi\'d5
t c\'b8c ng\'b5i c\'abng s\'f8, quan huy\'d6n v\'b5 th\'c7y l\'fd, m\'e9t c\'f9u ph\'b9m \'ae\'b7 \'ae\'ad\'eec th\'a8ng ch\'f8c v\'b5 ban b\'e6ng l\'e9c g\'d7 ch\'ada, nh\'adng n\'d5u b\'a9y gi\'ea ch\'ada \'ae\'ad\'eec th\'d7 r\'e5i t\'cat nhi\'aan h
\'e4 c\'f2ng s\'cf \'ae\'ad\'eec. Gi\'ea \'ae\'a9y, ch\'f3ng t\'abi n\'e3i ti\'d5p \'ae\'d5n chuy\'d6n C\'abng l\'fd. Ng\'b5y 16 th\'b8ng 2, To\'b5 \'a7\'b9i h\'d7nh H\'b5 N\'e9i \'ae\'b7 m\'eb phi\'aan to\'b5 cu\'e8i c\'efng x\'f6 v\'f4 \'b8n n\'b5
y. Trong qu\'b8 tr\'d7nh to\'b5 lu\'cbn t\'e9i, ng\'ad\'eai ta \'ae\'ad\'eec bi\'d5t r\'bbng kh\'abng h\'d2 c\'e3 m\'e9t t\'e6 ch\'f8c c\'b8ch m\'b9ng n\'b5o \'ae\'b7 chu\'c8n b\'de nh\'f7ng bom ph\'b8 \'ae\'e3, v\'b5 v\'f4 \'a9m m\'adu \'cay ch\'d8 l\'b5
 m\'e9t th\'f1 \'aeo\'b9n x\'b6o quy\'d6t c\'f1a b\'e4n quan l\'b9i mong \'ae\'ad\'eec ch\'ddnh ph\'f1 ban th\'ad\'ebng b\'e6ng l\'e9c v\'b5 ch\'f8c t\'ad\'edc. Nh\'ad v\'cby, li\'d6u ch\'f3ng ta c\'e3 th\'d3 tin t\'ad\'ebng r\'bbng sau v\'f4 x\'d0t x\'f6
 \'cay, ng\'ad\'eai ta s\'cf tha b\'e6ng cho nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai An Nam ch\'bcng may \'ae\'b7 b\'de b\'e1 t\'ef, b\'de t\'e8 gi\'b8c tham gia v\'f4 phi\'d5n lo\'b9n b\'dea \'ae\'c6t \'cay kh\'abng? Kh\'abng \'ae\'a9u! B\'cat c\'f8 b\'bbng gi\'b8 n\'b5
o, ng\'ad\'eai ta c\'f2ng ph\'b6i b\'b6o v\'d6 uy t\'ddn cho c\'b8c quan cai tr\'de ch\'f8! V\'d7 th\'d5, m\'b5 l\'cf ra ch\'d8 c\'c7n phong th\'ad\'ebng m\'e9t c\'b8ch b\'d7nh th\'ad\'eang cho nh\'f7ng 
\par }\pard \qj \li0\ri0\sa80\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 con ng\'ad\'eai s\'b8ng t\'b9o ra \'a9m m\'adu \'cay, th\'d7 ng\'ad\'eai ta l\'b9i k\'d5t t\'e9i t\'ef t\'f5 2 \'ae\'d5n 5 n
\'a8m 12 ng\'ad\'eai An Nam ph\'c7n l\'edn l\'b5 nh\'b5 nho, v\'b5 tr\'aan t\'cam c\'e6ng l\'edn c\'f1a nh\'b5 t\'ef kia, ng\'ad\'eai ta th\'cay \'ae\'d2 r\'b5nh r\'b5nh m\'cay ch\'f7 \'ae\'b9i t\'f9, c\'e8 nhi\'aan l\'b5 b\'bbng ti\'d5ng Ph\'b8p: T\'f9
 do, B\'d7nh \'ae\'bcng, B\'b8c \'b8i. Chao \'abi! N\'f9c c\'ad\'eai thay. V\'b5 c\'b8c b\'b8o ch\'dd x\'ada nay v\'c9n t\'f9 x\'adng l\'b5 b\'aanh v\'f9c cho ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8 v\'e9i v\'b5ng l\'aan ti\'d5ng ca ng\'eei c\'b8i ch\'dd c\'abng v\'ab t
\'ad c\'f1a n\'d2n C\'abng l\'fd n\'f9c c\'ad\'eai n\'b5y. Ch\'f3ng ta h\'b7y nghe t\'ea }{\i\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 La D\'d0p\'aache Coloniale}{\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 11}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  l\'b5 t\'ea b\'b8o gi\'f7 vai tr\'df v\'ab \'ae
\'dech v\'d2 b\'b5i x\'ddch ng\'ad\'eai An Nam, n\'e3i: "To\'b5 \'b8n n\'ad\'edc Ph\'b8p v\'f5a m\'edi x\'d0t x\'f6 xong m\'e9t v\'f4 \'b8n. To\'b5 tha b\'e6ng cho m\'e9t n\'f6a s\'e8 b\'de can, c\'dfn m\'e9t n\'f6a s\'e8 th\'d7 \'ae\'ad\'eec h\'ad\'ebng 
\'b8n nh\'d1. Trong v\'f4 \'b8n n\'b5y, \'ae\'d3 c\'e3 l\'fd bu\'e9c t\'e9i, ng\'ad\'eai ta \'ae\'b7 tung d\'ad lu\'cbn r\'c7m l\'aan m\'e9t c\'b8ch thi\'aan t\'ad tr\'ad\'edc khi x\'f6, v\'b5 sau \'ae\'e3, ng\'ad\'eai ta \'ae\'b7 k\'d5t \'b8n c\'b8c nh
\'b5 nho l\'b5m nh\'f7ng b\'b5i th\'ac t\'e5i ca t\'f4ng c\'abng \'ae\'f8c c\'f1a n\'d2n T\'f9 do".
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\expnd0\expndtw-4\insrsid1378858 \'a7\'e3 th\'cbt l\'b5 tai v\'b9 cho nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai An Nam n\'b5o ca ng\'eei c\'abng \'ae\'f8c c
\'f1a n\'d2n T\'f9 do. Ng\'ad\'eai ta ph\'b9t h\'e4 5 n\'a8m t\'ef ch\'d8 v\'d7 c\'e3 th\'d5 th\'abi! T\'ea b\'b8o \'cay vi\'d5t ti\'d5p: "\'a7\'f3ng, ta ph\'b6i b\'bbng l\'dfng v\'edi c\'b8i b\'b6n \'b8n ch\'dd c\'abng v\'ab t\'ad c\'f1a c\'b8c v\'de
 quan to\'b5 v\'b5 th\'c8m ph\'b8n c\'f1a ch\'f3ng ta ch\'f8!". V\'b5 t\'ea }{\i\f37\fs20\expnd0\expndtw-4\insrsid1378858 La D\'d0p\'aache Coloniale}{\f37\fs20\expnd0\expndtw-4\insrsid1378858  \'ae\'b7 vui v\'ce \'ae\'a8ng tin b\'b6n \'b8n ch\'dd c\'ab
ng v\'ab t\'ad v\'d2 v\'f4 \'a9m m\'adu n\'e6i ti\'d5ng \'cay \'eb V\'dcnh Y\'aan. Nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai An Nam \'eb Pari, c\'f2ng nh\'ad \'ae\'e5ng b\'b5o ph\'ad\'acng xa c\'f1a h\'e4 tin t\'ad\'ebng c\'b8c v\'de quan to\'b5, h\'e4 \'ae\'b7 tuy\'aan b\'e8
 c\'b8c v\'de \'cay x\'d0t x\'f6 r\'cat c\'abng minh v\'b5 v\'f4 \'b8n \'ae\'ad\'eec k\'d5t th\'f3c m\'fc m\'b7n. Kh\'abng ph\'b6i nh\'ad th\'d5 \'ae\'a9u, th\'ada \'abng Puvu\'e8cvin, \'abng \'ae\'b7 th\'e6i ph\'e5ng m\'e9t c\'b8ch qu\'b8 \'ae\'b8ng \'ae
\'cay! \'a7\'d3 tr\'b6 l\'eai, ch\'f3ng t\'abi ch\'d8 xin nh\'bec l\'b9i \'aei\'d2u m\'b5 \'abng \'ae\'b7 vi\'d5t trong ph\'c7n \'ae\'c7u b\'b5i b\'b8o c\'f1a \'abng: "Nh\'f7ng con ch\'e3 s\'f1a, v.v. th\'abi \'aei, h\'eci nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai anh em b
\'cat h\'b9nh, c\'b8c anh em \'ae\'b7 l\'c7m to r\'e5i, c\'b8c anh em c\'f2ng th\'f5a hi\'d3u r\'bbng l\'b5m g\'d7 c\'e3 t\'f9 do cho ch\'f3ng ta m\'b5 l\'b9i \'aei hoan ngh\'aanh v\'edi ca ng\'eei n\'e3. Nh\'adng, ng\'ad\'eai An Nam ch\'f3ng t\'abi \'eb
 kh\'bep m\'e4i n\'aci, ch\'f3ng t\'abi s\'cf ki\'aan quy\'d5t \'ae\'ada s\'f9 b\'cat c\'abng gh\'aa t\'ebm v\'b5 phi l\'fd \'cay ra ph\'b6n \'ae\'e8i tr\'ad\'edc t\'cat c\'b6 m\'e4i ng\'ad\'eai Ph\'b8p ch\'a9n ch\'ddnh. Ch\'f3ng t\'abi mong r\'bbng d\'ad
 lu\'cbn n\'ad\'edc Ph\'b8p th\'abng c\'b6m v\'edi nh\'f7ng n\'e7i \'aeau kh\'e6 c\'f1a c\'b8c anh em v\'b5 s\'cf \'ae\'cau tranh \'ae\'dfi cho C\'abng l\'fd \'ae\'ad\'eec th\'f9c hi\'d6n".
\par }\pard\plain \s24\qr \fi397\li0\ri567\sb200\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin567\lin0\itap0 \f38\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 \~NGUY\'d4N \'b8I QU\'e8C
\par }\pard\plain \s26\ql \li0\ri567\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin567\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 T\'b5i li\'d6u ti\'d5ng Ph\'b8p, l\'adu t\'b9i\line Vi\'d6n l\'de
ch s\'f6 \'a7\'b6ng.
\par }\pard\plain \s21\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \b\f39\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 
\par }\pard\plain \s20\qc \li0\ri0\sb1400\sa440\sl-380\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \b\f38\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 PHONG TR\'b5O C\'b8CH M\'b9NG \'eb \'caN \'a7\'e9

\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-276\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 \~Cu\'e9c xung \'ae\'e9t Hy L\'b9p - K\'aaman}{
\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 12}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  hay \'ae\'f3ng h\'acn l\'b5 cu\'e9c xung \'ae\'e9t Anh - Th\'e6 \'aeang di\'d4n ra. C\'b8c cu\'e9c kh\'ebi ngh\'dca \'eb Malaba}{\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 13}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  \'ae
ang \'ae\'ad\'eec d\'ad lu\'cbn h\'d5t s\'f8c ch\'f3 \'fd. \'a7\'d5 qu\'e8c Anh \'aeang ph\'b6i ch\'e8ng \'ae\'ec kh\'bep n\'aci. Nh\'bec l\'b9i l\'dech s\'f6 phong tr\'b5o c\'b8ch m\'b9ng }{\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'ca}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 n \'a7
\'e9 l\'f3c n\'b5y l\'b5 m\'e9t vi\'d6c l\'fd th\'f3.
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa40\sl-276\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 T\'f5 cu\'e9c kh\'ebi ngh\'dca n\'a8m 1857, \'ae\'d5 qu\'e8c Anh t\'ad\'ebng \'ae\'b7 d\'d7m \'ae\'ad\'eec tinh th\'c7
n c\'b8ch m\'b9ng c\'f1a nh\'a9n d\'a9n }{\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'ca}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 n \'a7\'e9 trong cu\'e9c \'ae\'b5n \'b8p \'ae\'c9m m\'b8u v\'b5 thi\'d5t l\'cbp v\'dcnh vi\'d4n s\'f9 b\'e3c l\'e9t \'b8p b\'f8c d\'b7 man c\'f1a ph\'ad\'ac
ng 
\par T\'a9y l\'aan hai b\'ea s\'abng H\'bbng. Ch\'f3ng \'ae\'b7 l\'c7m to.
\par N\'a8m 1880, nh\'b5 tri\'d5t h\'e4c Rama K\'acris\'acna d\'efng t\'abn gi\'b8o \'ae\'d3 truy\'d2n b\'b8 c\'b8ch m\'b9ng. \'a4ng t\'abn th\'ea n\'f7 th\'c7n Kali v\'b5 khuy\'aan \'ae\'e5ng b\'b5o m\'d7nh t\'abn th\'ea n\'f7 th\'c7n, ng\'ad\'eai m\'d1 c\'f1
a l\'f9c l\'ad\'eeng ph\'b8 ho\'b9i v\'b5 x\'a9y d\'f9ng.
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-276\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 \'a7am\'ab\'aea v\'b5 Bank\'acris\'acna k\'d5 t\'f4c s\'f9
 nghi\'d6p c\'f1a Rama v\'b5 gi\'b8o d\'f4c ch\'f1 tr\'ad\'acng c\'b8ch m\'b9ng m\'e9t c\'b8ch d\'f2ng c\'b6m, c\'abng khai. T\'cat nhi\'aan c\'b6 hai \'ae\'d2u b\'de b\'bet gi\'f7 v\'b5 \'ae\'b5y bi\'d6t x\'f8.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sl-276\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'a7\'d5n n\'a8m 1897 t\'ea b\'b8o }{
\i\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 K\'aaxari}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  m\'edi ra \'ae\'eai, ng\'ad\'eai ch\'f1 tr\'ad\'acng l\'b5 Til\'bec. B\'b5i b\'b8o \'ae\'c7u ti\'aan c\'f1a \'abng l\'b5 b\'b5i v\'a8n xu\'cat s\'bec "L\'eai than c\'f1a Xi\'abgi". N\'e9
i dung k\'d3 chuy\'d6n m\'e9t \'abng vua c\'f2 t\'d8nh d\'cby t\'f5 d\'ad\'edi m\'e5 s\'a9u, tr\'eb l\'b9i th\'a8m v\'ad\'acng qu\'e8c th\'a9n y\'aau. \'a4ng r\'cat bu\'e5n khi th\'cay th\'c7n d\'a9n c\'f1a m\'d7nh ph\'b6i ch\'deu ki\'d5p n\'ab l\'d6 kh
\'e6 nh\'f4c. \'a4ng k\'aau g\'e4i t\'cat c\'b6
\par }\pard \qj \li0\ri0\sl-276\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai }{\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'ca}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 n \'a7\'e9 h\'b7y th\'f8c t\'d8nh v\'b5 h\'eep l\'f9
c \'ae\'d3 l\'cbt \'ae\'e6 \'b8ch ngo\'b9i bang v\'b5 gi\'b5nh l\'b9i n\'d2n \'ae\'e9c l\'cbp m\'b5 \'abng \'ae\'b7 truy\'d2n l\'b9i cho h\'e4.
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-284\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 T\'ea b\'b8o th\'ad\'eang xuy\'aan ph\'e6 bi\'d5n cho \'ae\'e9c gi\'b6 t\'d7m hi\'d3u ph\'ad\'acng ph\'b8p c\'b8ch m\'b9
ng Nga.
\par M\'e9t phong tr\'b5o gi\'b6i ph\'e3ng \'ae\'ad\'eec l\'b7nh \'ae\'b9o d\'f2ng c\'b6m, cho \'ae\'d5n khi t\'ea b\'b8o b\'de \'ae\'d7nh b\'b6n v\'b5 ch\'f1 nhi\'d6m b\'de \'aei \'ae\'b5y.
\par }\pard\plain \s22\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-284\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f40\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Nh\'a9n ti\'d6n xin n\'e3i r\'bbng \'eb ch\'a9u }{
\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'b8}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 , ng\'ad\'eai ta quan ni\'d6m s\'f9 ch\'a9n th\'cbt v\'b5 l\'ad\'acng t\'a9m nh\'b5 b\'b8o kh\'b8c v\'edi ch\'a9u \'a2u. Nh\'f7ng nh\'b5 b\'b8o t\'ad s\'b6n ph\'ad\'acng T\'a9y s\'cf c\'ad\'eai n\'d5
u ch\'f3ng ta n\'e3i v\'edi h\'e4 r\'bbng ph\'c7n l\'edn c\'b8c b\'b5i \'eb c\'b8c b\'b8o x\'b7 h\'e9i ch\'f1 ngh\'dca nh\'ad t\'ea }{\i\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 K\'aaxari, Vihari}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 , v.v. \'ae\'d2u vi\'d5t kh\'abng l\'cay ti\'d2n v
\'b5 \'ae\'abi khi c\'b6 bi\'aan t\'cbp vi\'aan c\'dfn \'ae\'ad\'eec tr\'b6 c\'abng b\'bbng nh\'f7ng th\'b8ng, th\'cbm ch\'dd b\'bbng nh\'f7ng n\'a8m t\'ef. \'a7\'cay l\'b5 tr\'ad\'eang h\'eep c\'f1a t\'ea }{\i\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Vihari}{
\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 , ba bi\'aan t\'cbp vi\'aan \'ae\'d2u b\'de b\'bet v\'b5 l\'c7n l\'ad\'eet b\'de k\'d5t \'b8n. Nh\'adng \'aei\'d2u \'ae\'e3 kh\'abng l\'b5m thay \'ae\'e6i th\'b8i \'ae\'e9 l\'c9n c\'b8ch suy ngh\'dc c\'f1a h\'e4. Trong s\'e8 "ng
\'ad\'eai l\'b5m c\'abng", nh\'f7ng ai c\'e3 th\'d3 t\'f9 cho m\'d7nh nh\'ad th\'d5?
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-284\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Cu\'e9c v\'cbn \'ae\'e9ng \'ae\'c6c bi\'d6t l\'aan cao t
\'f5 sau chi\'d5n tranh Nga - Nh\'cbt. Hai s\'f9 ki\'d6n ti\'aau bi\'d3u sau \'ae\'a9y \'ae\'b8nh d\'cau t\'d7nh h\'d7nh t\'ad t\'ad\'ebng c\'f1a ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8. T\'ad\'eeng n\'f7 ho\'b5ng V\'ddcht\'abria b\'de b\'abi nh\'e4 v\'b5o \'ae\'aam tr
\'ad\'edc l\'d4 k\'fb ni\'d6m ng\'b5y sinh c\'f1a n\'f7 ho\'b5ng. B\'b5i h\'b8t Ban\'ae\'aamataran - b\'b5i M\'b8cx\'a9ye c\'f1a ng\'ad\'eai }{\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'ca}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 n \'a7\'e9 - \'ae\'ad\'eec ph\'e6 bi\'d5n nhanh ch\'e3
ng v\'b5 \'ae\'ad\'eec h\'b8t b\'bbng t\'cat c\'b6 c\'b8c th\'e6 ng\'f7 c\'f1a }{\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'ca}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 n \'a7\'e9.
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-284\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 Nh\'f7ng h\'e9i Amxilam Xanit\'ac - t\'e6 ch\'f8c r\'cc
n luy\'d6n tinh th\'c7n v\'b5 th\'d3 l\'f9c - \'ae\'ad\'eec th\'b5nh l\'cbp kh\'bep n\'aci nh\'ad c\'e3 ph\'d0p l\'b9. Vi\'d6c t\'c8y chay h\'b5ng ho\'b8 Anh v\'b5 l\'b5m tan r\'b7 tinh th\'c7n c\'b8c \'ae\'acn v\'de l\'ddnh b\'b6n x\'f8 \'ae\'ad\'ee
c nghi\'aan c\'f8u r\'cat c\'abng phu.
\par }\pard\plain \s22\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-284\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f40\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Nh\'f7ng n\'e7 l\'f9c kh\'abng ng\'f5ng \'ae\'e3 
\'ae\'b7 \'aeem l\'b9i k\'d5t qu\'b6. Th\'b8ng 1 n\'a8m 1915, nhi\'d2u trung \'aeo\'b5n n\'e6i l\'aan b\'b9o \'ae\'e9ng v\'b5 do s\'f9 gi\'b8n \'aeo\'b9n c\'f1a m\'cbu d\'dech Anh - }{\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'ca}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 n, c\'b8c ng
\'a9n h\'b5ng thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea \'eb khu Xiti \'ae\'b7 b\'de thua thi\'d6t m\'e9t tri\'d6u phr\'a8ng do nh\'f7ng c\'e6 phi\'d5u kh\'abng \'ae\'ad\'eec thanh to\'b8n trong n\'a8m 1920.
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-284\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 Th\'b6m ho\'b9 c\'f1a \'ae\'cat n\'ad\'edc \'ae\'b7 xo\'b8
 b\'e1 s\'f9 ph\'a9n bi\'d6t \'ae\'bcng c\'cap v\'b5 t\'abn gi\'b8o. Ng\'ad\'eai gi\'b5u ng\'ad\'eai ngh\'cco, qu\'fd t\'e9c v\'b5 n\'abng d\'a9n, H\'e5i gi\'b8o v\'b5 Ph\'cbt gi\'b8o, \'ae\'d2u h\'eep s\'f8c \'aeo\'b5n k\'d5t.
\par }\pard \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-294\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\insrsid1378858 Nhi\'d2u nh\'a9n v\'cbt ti\'aan ti\'d5n, nhi\'d2u gi\'b8o s\'ad \'ae\'b9i h\'e4c nh\'ad H\'b8c\'aeayan v\'b5 nh\'f7ng ng\'ad
\'eai kh\'b8c \'ae\'b7 hy sinh t\'b5i s\'b6n, \'ae\'b7 t\'f5 ch\'e8i nh\'f7ng ch\'f8c v\'f4 cao m\'b5 ch\'ddnh ph\'f1 thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea mu\'e8n ban cho h\'e4 \'ae\'d3 d\'d4 b\'d2 khu\'cat ph\'f4c. H\'e4 \'aei t\'f5 l\'b5ng n\'b5y qua l\'b5ng kh\'b8c, k
\'aau g\'e4i \'ae\'cau tranh cho \'ae\'e9c l\'cbp. Sinh vi\'aan, h\'e4c sinh c\'f2ng tham gia c\'abng t\'b8c tuy\'aan truy\'d2n.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-294\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 V\'d2 ph\'dda m\'d7nh, nh\'f7ng chi\'d5n s\'dc ch\'f1 tr
\'ad\'acng h\'b5nh \'ae\'e9ng tr\'f9c ti\'d5p c\'f2ng kh\'abng ng\'e5i y\'aan. H\'e4 ch\'deu tr\'b8ch nhi\'d6m th\'f1 ti\'aau nh\'f7ng quan ch\'f8c thi\'aan v\'de, nh\'f7ng k\'ce ph\'b6n b\'e9i v\'b5 nh\'f7ng t\'aan \'b8c \'abn c\'b6nh s\'b8t ch\'ddnh tr
\'de. V\'edi nh\'f7ng ch\'f8c v\'de r\'cat k\'aau, c\'b8c ph\'e3 v\'ad\'acng v\'b5 th\'e8ng \'ae\'e8c c\'f2ng kh\'abng l\'b5m cho h\'e4 s\'ee, nh\'f7ng s\'f9 ki\'d6n n\'a8m 1907, 1908 v\'b5 1909}{\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 14}{
\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  \'ae\'b7 ch\'f8ng minh \'aei\'d2u \'ae\'e3. N\'a8m 1916, m\'e9t c\'cbu b\'d0 16 tu\'e6i \'ae\'b7 n\'d0m bom ngay gi\'f7a \'ae\'ad\'eang v\'b5 gi\'f7a ban ng\'b5y v\'b5o xe c\'f1a t\'aan c\'c7m \'ae\'c7u n\'e6i ti\'d5ng c\'f1a c
\'f4c \'aei\'d2u tra. L\'dfng d\'f2ng c\'b6m kh\'abng tr\'f5 gi\'b5 hay tr\'ce.
\par Danh s\'b8ch nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai b\'de hy sinh k\'d0o d\'b5i r\'cat \'aeau x\'e3t. Trong m\'ad\'eai n\'a8m, kh\'abng k\'d3 nh\'f7ng v\'f4 th\'b6m s\'b8t t\'cbp th\'d3, \'ae\'b7 c\'e3 h\'acn 200 ng\'ad\'eai l\'cay m\'b8u \'ae\'b5o t\'ad\'edi g\'e8c c\'a9
y c\'b8ch m\'b9ng v\'b5 l\'fd t\'ad\'ebng. Trong s\'e8 nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai tu\'c9n ti\'d5t, c\'e3 70 sinh vi\'aan, 16 th\'c7y gi\'b8o, 20 \'aei\'d2n ch\'f1, 23 hay 25 nh\'b5 bu\'abn, 7 th\'c7y thu\'e8c, 20 c\'abng ch\'f8c. Trong s\'e8 nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'ea
i hy sinh c\'e3 50 ng\'ad\'eai tu\'e6i ch\'d8 t\'f5 16 \'ae\'d5n 20!
\par V\'d7 v\'cby m\'b5 b\'e4n ch\'f1 h\'e8t ho\'b6ng, g\'c7n nh\'ad kinh ho\'b5ng. M\'e9t nh\'a9n v\'cbt th\'ad\'eeng l\'adu \'ae\'b7 th\'e8t l\'aan: "N\'d5u s\'f9 vi\'d6c \'ae\'e3 c\'dfn ti\'d5p di\'d4n, th\'d7 nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai \'ae\'b8ng k\'ddnh c\'f1
a ch\'f3ng ta bu\'e9c ph\'b6i cu\'e8n g\'e3i kh\'e1i n\'aci n\'b5y".
\par L\'f3c \'ae\'e3, song song v\'edi b\'e9 m\'b8y \'ae\'b5n \'b8p th\'bcng tay, ng\'ad\'eai ta thi h\'b5nh m\'e9t ch\'ddnh s\'b8ch ngu d\'a9n ho\'b5n to\'b5n.
\par C\'b8c h\'e9i "Xamiti" b\'de gi\'b6i t\'b8n, h\'e9i vi\'aan b\'de b\'bet giam, m\'e4i cu\'e9c h\'e9i h\'e4p v\'b5 c\'b8c t\'e6 ch\'f8c ch\'ddnh tr\'de \'ae\'d2u b\'de ng\'a8n c\'cam. C\'b8c bi\'d6n ph\'b8p "c\'cap c\'f8u" m\'e4c l\'aan nh\'ad n\'cam. Tr
\'cbn m\'ada \'ae\'b5n \'b8p \'ae\'e3 ch\'d8 l\'b5m cho hoa c\'b8ch m\'b9ng th\'aam n\'eb r\'e9.
\par }\pard\plain \s22\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f40\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 M\'e9t cu\'e9c t\'e6ng kh\'ebi ngh\'dca \'aeang 
\'ae\'ad\'eec chu\'c8n b\'de trong n\'a8m 1914 v\'b5 1915. Kh\'abng may cu\'e9c kh\'ebi ngh\'dca b\'de th\'cat b\'b9i. H\'b5ng tr\'a8m ng\'ad\'eai l\'adu vong tr\'eb v\'d2 n\'ad\'edc v\'edi quy\'d5t t\'a9m gi\'b8ng m\'e9t \'ae\'dfn \'ae\'cbp tan \'b8ch th
\'e8ng tr\'de \'aeang \'ae\'cc n\'c6ng \'ae\'cat n\'ad\'edc. H\'e4 b\'de ph\'b8t hi\'d6n v\'b5 \'ae\'d2u b\'de b\'bet gi\'f7 tr\'ad\'edc khi \'ae\'c6t \'ae\'ad\'eec ch\'a9n l\'aan qu\'aa h\'ad\'acng m\'b5 h\'e4 \'ae\'b7 h\'f8a h\'d1n s\'cf gi\'b6i ph\'e3
ng ho\'c6c hy sinh. M\'e9t l\'c7n n\'f7a, b\'e4n k\'ce c\'bep l\'b9i g\'c6p may!
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Nh\'adng l\'df l\'f6a \'ae\'b7 nh\'e3m l\'aan, kh\'abng g
\'d7 c\'e3 th\'d3 d\'cbp t\'bet n\'e6i. C\'b8c kh\'c8u hi\'d6u \'ae\'ad\'eec truy\'d2n t\'f5 ng\'ad\'eai n\'b5y qua ng\'ad\'eai kh\'b8c. C\'b8c h\'e9i "Xamiti" b\'dd m\'cbt h\'e9i h\'e4p. Nh\'f7ng cu\'e9c l\'b9c quy\'aan v\'d7 \'ae\'e9c l\'cbp \'ae\'ad
\'eec ti\'d5n h\'b5nh nhanh ch\'e3ng, ho\'c6c l\'b5 do t\'f9 nguy\'d6n \'ae\'e3ng g\'e3p, \'ae\'abi khi b\'bbng h\'d7nh th\'f8c "\'aeaic\'e8t".
\par Ch\'f3ng t\'abi th\'cay c\'c7n ph\'b6i gi\'b6i th\'ddch m\'e9t t\'dd v\'d2 ch\'f7 "\'aeaic\'e8t", m\'b5 t\'f5 tr\'ad\'edc \'ae\'d5n nay nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai ph\'ad\'acng T\'a9y th\'ad\'eang hi\'d3u sai. Ng\'ad\'eai Anh g\'e4i l\'b5 "\'aeaic\'e8t" c\'f2
ng nh\'ad ng\'ad\'eai Ph\'b8p g\'e4i c\'ad\'edp b\'e3c. C\'b6 hai \'ae\'d2u kh\'abng h\'d2 ph\'a9n bi\'d6t gi\'f7a s\'f9 c\'ad\'edp b\'e3c v\'edi s\'f9 \'ae\'e3ng g\'e3p \'ae\'abi khi b\'bet bu\'e9c cho s\'f9 nghi\'d6p chung, c\'f2ng nh\'ad h\'e4 kh\'ab
ng h\'d2 ph\'a9n bi\'d6t gi\'f7a nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai y\'aau n\'ad\'edc \'ae\'cau tranh cho \'ae\'cat n\'ad\'edc m\'d7nh v\'edi b\'e4n c\'c6n b\'b7 \'eb th\'b5nh th\'de.
\par Mu\'e8n l\'b5m m\'e9t vi\'d6c g\'d7, t\'cat nhi\'aan ph\'b6i c\'e3 ti\'d2n v\'e8n, v\'b5 mu\'e8n c\'e3 v\'e8n, ph\'b6i bi\'d5t n\'aci n\'b5o c\'e3 \'ae\'d3 t\'d7m.
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 \'a7\'d3 ch\'f8ng minh s\'f9 c\'ad\'acng tr\'f9c c\'f1a nh
\'f7ng h\'e9i vi\'aan "Xamiti" ph\'f4 tr\'b8ch t\'b5i ch\'ddnh c\'f1a U\'fb ban c\'b8ch m\'b9ng, ch\'d8 c\'c7n k\'d3 nh\'f7ng th\'dd d\'f4 sau \'ae\'a9y:
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 M\'e9t trong nh\'f7ng \'aei\'d2u c\'f1a \'aei\'d2u l\'d6 h
\'e9i "Xamiti" n\'aau r\'bbng nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai gia nh\'cbp h\'e9i ph\'b6i lu\'abn nh\'ed r\'bbng h\'e4 \'aeang ho\'b9t \'ae\'e9ng cho c\'b8ch m\'b9ng nh\'bbm thi\'d5t l\'cbp l\'b9i nh\'f7ng quy\'d2n \'ae\'b7 b\'de ch\'b5 \'ae\'b9p ch\'f8 kh\'abng ph
\'b6i v\'d7 s\'f9 h\'ad\'ebng th\'f4 c\'b8 nh\'a9n c\'f1a m\'e9t s\'e8 ng\'ad\'eai. R\'bbng t\'cat c\'b6 c\'b8c h\'e9i vi\'aan ph\'b6i t\'f5 b\'e1 vi\'d6c u\'e8ng r\'ad\'eeu, t\'f5 b\'e1 m\'e4i th\'f8 xa hoa ph\'ef phi\'d5m.
\par M\'e7i l\'c7n \'ae\'e3ng g\'e3p b\'bet bu\'e9c hay \'aeaic\'e8t, ng\'ad\'eai \'ae\'e3ng \'ae\'ad\'eec g\'f6i \'ae\'d5n m\'e9t bi\'aan lai. Sau \'ae\'a9y l\'b5 m\'e9t \'aeo\'b9n tr\'ddch trong bi\'aan lai:
\par "\'a7\'e5ng b\'b5o th\'a9n m\'d5n, b\'b9n ph\'b6i bi\'d5t r\'bbng mu\'e8n gi\'b6i ph\'e3ng \'ae\'cat n\'ad\'edc th\'a9n y\'aau c\'f1a ch\'f3ng ta tho\'b8t v\'dfng n\'ab l\'d6, th\'d7 c\'c7n ph\'b6i c\'e3 s\'f9 hy sinh, l\'dfng tin c\'cby v\'b5 c\'b6m t
\'d7nh c\'f1a t\'cat c\'b6 \'ae\'e5ng b\'b5o ch\'f3ng ta. N\'d5u t\'cat c\'b6 nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai c\'e3 kh\'b6 n\'a8ng nh\'ad b\'b9n \'ae\'d2u hi\'d3u nh\'f7ng kh\'e3 kh\'a8n c\'f1a c\'abng vi\'d6c ch\'f3ng t\'abi v\'b5 t\'f9 nguy\'d6n \'ae\'e3ng g\'e3
p v\'b5o s\'f9 nghi\'d6p c\'f1a ch\'f3ng t\'abi, th\'d7 ch\'f3ng t\'abi kh\'abng b\'de bu\'e9c ph\'b6i qu\'cay r\'c7y b\'b9n nh\'ad th\'d5 n\'b5y; n\'ad\'edc Nh\'cbt \'ae\'ad\'eec t\'f9 do v\'b5 h\'efng c\'ad\'eang l\'b5 nh\'ea c\'e3 l\'dfng hy sinh v\'b5
 s\'f9 th\'bet l\'adng bu\'e9c b\'f4ng c\'f1a to\'b5n d\'a9n Nh\'cbt. Anh linh c\'f1a T\'e6 qu\'e8c h\'b7y hun \'ae\'f3c tr\'b8i tim v\'b5 soi s\'b8ng t\'a9m th\'c7n c\'f1a anh em ch\'f3ng ta! v.v.. K\'fd t\'aan: I.B. Th\'ad k\'fd t\'b5i ch\'ddnh c\'f1
a ph\'a9n c\'f4c B. c\'f1a H\'e9i \'a7\'e9c l\'cbp }{\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'ca}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 n \'a7\'e9".
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-292\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 Phong tr\'b5o c\'b5ng lan r\'e9ng c\'b5ng \'ae\'ad\'eec c
\'f1ng c\'e8. Khi th\'cay \'ae\'b7 t\'ad\'acng \'ae\'e8i m\'b9nh, phong tr\'b5o r\'eai kh\'e1i b\'e3ng t\'e8i \'ae\'d3 ra gi\'f7a \'b8nh s\'b8ng, d\'ad\'edi nh\'f7ng con m\'bet kinh ng\'b9c c\'f1a nh\'b5 c\'c7m quy\'d2n. M\'e9t \'ae\'b9i h\'e9i \'ae\'ad
\'eec tri\'d6u t\'cbp v\'edi hai v\'b9n \'ae\'b9i bi\'d3u c\'e3 m\'c6t. M\'e9t v\'b5i \'ae\'b6ng vi\'aan "x\'b7 h\'e9i" Anh c\'f2ng tham d\'f9, h\'e4 \'ae\'ad\'eec ti\'d5p \'ae\'e3n kh\'abng l\'cay g\'d7 l\'b5m n\'e5ng nhi\'d6t l\'bem v\'d7 nh\'f7ng l\'fd
 lu\'cbn m\'b5u h\'e5ng nh\'b9t c\'f1a h\'e4.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-292\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Mahatma G\'a8ng\'aei \'ae\'b7 \'ae\'c6t vi\'aan \'ae\'b8 
\'ae\'c7u ti\'aan \'ae\'d3 d\'f9ng l\'aan thuy\'d5t b\'cat h\'eep t\'b8c v\'b5 b\'cat b\'b9o \'ae\'e9ng. \'a7\'ad\'eang l\'e8i \'ae\'e3 \'ae\'ad\'eec theo \'aeu\'e6i m\'e9t c\'b8ch 
\par }\pard \qj \li0\ri0\sa80\sl-292\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 th\'beng l\'eei. Tr\'ce em r\'eai b\'e1 tr\'ad\'eang h\'e4c c\'f1a ng\'ad\'eai Anh. C\'b8c lu\'cbt s\'ad r\'eai kh\'e1i to\'b5
 \'b8n c\'f1a ng\'ad\'eai Anh. C\'b8c vi\'aan ch\'f8c v\'b5 th\'ee thuy\'d2n kh\'abng l\'b5m vi\'d6c trong c\'b8c c\'abng s\'eb v\'b5 nh\'b5 m\'b8y m\'b5 ch\'f1 l\'b5 ng\'ad\'eai Anh. Kh\'abng c\'dfn quan h\'d6, kh\'abng c\'dfn bu\'abn b\'b8n gi\'f7a ng
\'ad\'eai Anh v\'b5 ng\'ad\'eai }{\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'ca}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 n. \'a7\'d3 gi\'f7 v\'f7ng phong tr\'b5o, c\'c7n ph\'b6i c\'e3 nh\'f7ng qu\'fc c\'f8u t\'d5. Trong th\'eai gian ba th\'b8ng, ng\'ad\'eai ta \'ae\'b7 quy\'aan \'ae
\'ad\'eec h\'acn s\'b8u m\'ad\'aci tri\'d6u phr\'a8ng. Nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai }{\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'ca}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 n \'a7\'e9 gi\'b5u c\'e3 l\'cay nh\'b5 m\'d7nh l\'b5m tr\'ad\'eang h\'e4c. Nh\'f7ng v\'f4 ki\'d6n \'ae\'ad\'eec \'ae\'ad
a ra x\'f6 tr\'ad\'edc c\'b8c to\'b5 \'b8n b\'b6n x\'f8 m\'edi th\'b5nh l\'cbp. M\'e9t s\'e8 ng\'ad\'eai }{\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'ca}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 n \'a7\'e9 t\'f9 nguy\'d6n g\'e3p \'ae\'d5n ba m\'ad\'aci tri\'d6u \'ae\'e5ng m\'e9t n\'a8
m "cho \'ae\'d5n khi \'ae\'e9c l\'cbp ho\'b5n to\'b5n".
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-292\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Tr\'ad\'edc l\'b5n s\'e3ng nh\'ad v\'cby, l\'b8 c\'ea kh\'abng bao gi\'ea th\'cay m\'c6t tr\'eai l\'c6n c\'e3 nguy c\'ac
 r\'aci xu\'e8ng m\'c6t tr\'a8ng. \'a7\'d5 qu\'e8c Anh kh\'abng bi\'d5t xoay x\'eb c\'b8ch n\'b5o. Ch\'f3ng t\'ad\'ebng r\'bbng k\'fd m\'e9t hi\'d6p \'ae\'denh th\'ad\'acng m\'b9i v\'edi n\'ad\'edc C\'e9ng ho\'b5 Nga l\'b5 c\'e3 th\'d3 ng\'a8n ch\'c6n t
\'ad t\'ad\'ebng c\'b8ch m\'b9ng th\'a9m nh\'cbp }{\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'ca}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 n \'a7\'e9, nh\'ad m\'e9t t\'ea gi\'cay th\'cam h\'f3t m\'e9t gi\'e4t m\'f9c!
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 Ch\'f3ng d\'efng C\'abngxt\'a8ngtin l\'b5m c\'b8i ch\'f4p 
\'ae\'d3 d\'cbp t\'bet l\'df l\'f6a c\'f1a phong tr\'b5o Li\'aan H\'e5i gi\'b8o. Ch\'f3ng nh\'c6t Phayxan l\'aan \'ae\'d3 ch\'e8ng \'ae\'ec to\'b5 nh\'b5 \'ae\'d5 qu\'e8c \'aeang s\'f4p \'ae\'e6 \'eb ph\'ad\'acng \'a7\'abng. V\'b5 sau n\'f7a th\'d7 sao? 
\'ddt ra ch\'f3ng c\'e3 th\'d3 t\'f9 an \'f1i khi th\'eai h\'b9n r\'eai kh\'e1i }{\f38\insrsid1378858 \'ca}{\insrsid1378858 n \'a7\'e9 c\'f1a ch\'f3ng \'ae\'b7 \'ae\'d5n, b\'bbng c\'b8ch t\'f9 nh\'f1 r\'bbng ch\'f3ng \'ae\'b7 t\'b5n nh\'c9n k\'d0o theo s
\'f9 s\'f4p \'ae\'e6 c\'f1a \'ae\'d5 qu\'e8c Ph\'b8p, \'aeang ho\'b9t \'ae\'e9ng \'eb \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng m\'e9t c\'b8ch x\'cau xa.
\par }\pard\plain \s24\qr \fi397\li0\ri567\sb360\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin567\lin0\itap0 \f38\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 \~nGUY\'d4N \'b8I QU\'e8C
\par }\pard\plain \s26\ql \li0\ri567\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin567\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 T\'b9p ch\'dd }{\i\insrsid1378858 La Revue Communiste,}{
\insrsid1378858 \line s\'e8 18-19, th\'b8ng 8, 9-1921.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-292\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 
