\f37\fs20\expnd0\expndtw-2\super\insrsid1378858 2}{\f37\fs20\expnd0\expndtw-2\insrsid1378858  . T\'e6ng c\'e9ng: 4.120.000 km}{\f37\fs20\expnd0\expndtw-2\super\insrsid1378858 2}{\f37\fs20\expnd0\expndtw-2\insrsid1378858  (g\'c7n g\'cap t\'b8m l\'c7n di
\'d6n t\'ddch n\'ad\'edc Ph\'b8p) v\'edi m\'e9t d\'a9n s\'e8 l\'b5 47.000.000 ng\'ad\'eai. S\'e8 d\'a9n \'ae\'e3 n\'e3i h\'acn 20 th\'f8 ti\'d5ng kh\'b8c nhau. T\'d7nh tr\'b9ng c\'e3 nhi\'d2u ti\'d5ng n\'e3i kh\'b8c nhau nh\'ad v\'cby l\'b5m kh\'e3 kh\'a8
n cho c\'abng t\'b8c tuy\'aan truy\'d2n, b\'ebi v\'d7 tr\'f5 m\'cay thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea c\'f2 ra, th\'d7 m\'e9t tuy\'aan 
\par }\pard \qj \li0\ri0\sl-278\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\expnd0\expndtw-2\insrsid1378858 truy\'d2n vi\'aan ng\'ad\'eai Ph\'b8p ch\'d8 c\'e3 th\'d3 n\'e3i chuy\'d6n v\'edi qu\'c7n ch\'f3ng b\'b6n x\'f8
 qua ng\'ad\'eai phi\'aan d\'dech m\'b5 th\'abi. M\'b5 phi\'aan d\'dech th\'d7 kh\'e3 n\'e3i l\'aan \'ae\'ad\'eec h\'d5t \'fd, v\'b6 l\'b9i trong nh\'f7ng x\'f8 b\'de cai tr\'de m\'e9t c\'b8ch \'ae\'e9c \'aeo\'b8n \'cay, th\'cbt kh\'e3 m\'b5 t\'d7m ra 
\'ae\'ad\'eec m\'e9t ng\'ad\'eai phi\'aan d\'dech nh\'f7ng l\'eai l\'cf c\'b8ch m\'b9ng.
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-278\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 L\'b9i c\'dfn nh\'f7ng tr\'eb ng\'b9i kh\'b8c n\'f7a. Tuy ng\'ad\'eai d\'a9n b\'b6n x\'f8 \'eb t\'cat
\par }\pard\plain \s25\qj \li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f38\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\insrsid1378858 c\'b6 c\'b8c thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea \'ae\'d2u l\'b5 nh\'f7ng ng
\'ad\'eai b\'de \'b8p b\'f8c v\'b5 b\'e3c l\'e9t nh\'ad nhau, nh\'adng tr\'d7nh \'ae\'e9 v\'a8n ho\'b8, kinh t\'d5 v\'b5 ch\'ddnh tr\'de gi\'f7a x\'f8 n\'b5y v\'edi x\'f8 kh\'b8c l\'b9i r\'cat kh\'b8c nhau. Gi\'f7a An Nam v\'edi C\'abngg\'ab, M\'b8ctin
\'ddch hay T\'a9n \'a7\'b6o, ho\'b5n to\'b5n kh\'abng gi\'e8ng nhau ch\'f3t n\'b5o, tr\'f5 s\'f9 c\'efng kh\'e6.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\b\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 2.}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  }{
\b\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 T\'d7nh tr\'b9ng th\'ea \'ac c\'f1a giai c\'cap v\'ab s\'b6n ch\'ddnh qu\'e8c \'ae\'e8i v\'edi c\'b8c thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 . - Trong nh\'f7ng lu\'cbn c\'ad\'acng v\'d2 v\'can \'ae\'d2 thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea}{
\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 22}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 , L\'aanin \'ae\'b7 tuy\'aan b\'e8 r\'e2 r\'d6t r\'bbng "nhi\'d6m v\'f4 c\'f1a c\'abng nh\'a9n \'eb c\'b8c n\'ad\'edc \'aei chi\'d5m thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea l\'b5 ph\'b6i gi\'f3p \'ae\'ec m\'e9t c\'b8
ch t\'ddch c\'f9c nh\'cat phong tr\'b5o gi\'b6i ph\'e3ng c\'f1a c\'b8c n\'ad\'edc ph\'f4 thu\'e9c". Mu\'e8n th\'d5, c\'abng nh\'a9n \'eb ch\'ddnh qu\'e8c c\'c7n ph\'b6i bi\'d5t r\'e2 thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea l\'b5 c\'b8i g\'d7, ph\'b6i bi\'d5t nh\'f7ng vi\'d6
c g\'d7 \'ae\'b7 x\'b6y ra \'eb thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea, bi\'d5t r\'e2 n\'e7i \'aeau kh\'e6 - h\'b5ng ngh\'d7n l\'c7n \'aeau kh\'e6 h\'acn c\'abng nh\'a9n \'eb ch\'ddnh qu\'e8c - nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai anh em c\'f1a h\'e4, nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai v\'ab s\'b6n thu
\'e9c \'ae\'dea ph\'b6i ch\'deu \'ae\'f9ng. T\'e3m l\'b9i l\'b5 c\'abng nh\'a9n \'eb ch\'ddnh qu\'e8c ph\'b6i quan t\'a9m \'ae\'d5n v\'can \'ae\'d2 thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea.
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 Ti\'d5c thay, m\'e9t s\'e8 \'ae\'abng chi\'d5n s\'dc v\'c9
n c\'dfn t\'ad\'ebng r\'bbng, m\'e9t thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea ch\'bcng qua ch\'d8 l\'b5 m\'e9t x\'f8 d\'ad\'edi \'ae\'c7y c\'b8t v\'b5 tr\'aan l\'b5 m\'c6t tr\'eai, v\'b5i c\'a9y d\'f5a xanh v\'edi m\'cay ng\'ad\'eai kh\'b8c m\'b5u da, th\'d5 th\'abi. V\'b5 h
\'e4 ho\'b5n to\'b5n kh\'abng \'ae\'d3 \'fd g\'d7 \'ae\'d5n.
\par }\pard\plain \s22\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f40\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\b\f37\fs20\expnd0\expndtw2\insrsid1378858 3. T\'d7nh tr\'b9ng d\'e8t n\'b8
t c\'f1a ng\'ad\'eai d\'a9n b\'b6n x\'f8}{\f37\fs20\expnd0\expndtw2\insrsid1378858 . - Trong t\'cat c\'b6 c\'b8c n\'ad\'edc thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea, \'eb c\'b8i x\'f8 \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng gi\'b5 c\'e7i kia c\'f2ng nh\'ad \'eb x\'f8 \'a7ah\'abm\'a9y tr\'ce
 trung n\'b5y, ng\'ad\'eai ta kh\'abng hi\'d3u \'ae\'cau tranh giai c\'cap l\'b5 g\'d7, l\'f9c l\'ad\'eeng giai c\'cap v\'ab s\'b6n l\'b5 g\'d7 c\'b6, v\'d7 m\'e9t l\'cf \'ae\'acn gi\'b6n l\'b5 \'eb \'ae\'e3 kh\'abng c\'e3 n\'d2n kinh doanh l\'edn v\'d2
 th\'ad\'acng nghi\'d6p hay c\'abng nghi\'d6p, c\'f2ng kh\'abng c\'e3 t\'e6 ch\'f8c c\'abng nh\'a9n. Tr\'ad\'edc con m\'bet ng\'ad\'eai d\'a9n b\'b6n x\'f8, ch\'f1 ngh\'dca b\'abns\'aav\'ddch - danh t\'f5 n\'b5y v\'d7 th\'ad\'eang \'ae\'ad\'eec giai c\'ca
p t\'ad s\'b6n d\'efng \'ae\'d5n lu\'abn, n\'aan \'ae\'c6c s\'bec h\'acn v\'b5 m\'b9nh ngh\'dca h\'acn - c\'e3 ngh\'dca l\'b5: ho\'c6c s\'f9 ph\'b8 ho\'b9i t\'cat c\'b6, ho\'c6c s\'f9 gi\'b6i ph\'e3ng kh\'e1i \'b8ch n\'ad\'edc ngo\'b5i. Ngh\'dca th\'f8 nh
\'cat g\'b8n cho danh t\'f5 \'cay l\'b5m cho qu\'c7n ch\'f3ng v\'ab h\'e4c v\'b5 nh\'f3t nh\'b8t xa l\'b8nh ch\'f3ng ta; ngh\'dca th\'f8 hai th\'d7 d\'c9n h\'e4 \'ae\'d5n ch\'f1 ngh\'dca qu\'e8c gia. C\'b6 hai \'aei\'d2u \'ae\'e3 \'ae\'d2u nguy hi\'d3m c
\'b6. Ch\'d8 c\'e3 m\'e9t s\'e8 \'ddt ng\'ad\'eai trong nh\'a9n d\'a9n hi\'d3u \'ae\'ad\'eec th\'d5 n\'b5o l\'b5 ch\'f1 ngh\'dca c\'e9ng s\'b6n. Nh\'adng s\'e8 ng\'ad\'eai th\'ad\'eeng l\'adu \'cay,- thu\'e9c giai c\'cap t\'ad s\'b6n b\'b6n x\'f8}{
\cs17\f37\fs20\expnd0\expndtw2\super\insrsid1378858 1{\footnote \pard\plain \s28\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sl-240\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 
1) }{\i\insrsid1378858 La bourgeoisie autochtone.}})}{\f37\fs20\expnd0\expndtw2\insrsid1378858  v\'b5}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  l\'b5 c\'e9t tr\'f4 c\'f1a giai c\'cap t\'ad s\'b6n th\'f9c d\'a9n, - c\'f2ng kh\'abng th\'ddch th\'f3 g\'d7 vi\'d6c ch\'f1
 ngh\'dca c\'e9ng s\'b6n \'ae\'ad\'eec ng\'ad\'eai ta hi\'d3u v\'b5 \'ae\'ad\'eec truy\'d2n b\'b8 r\'e9ng r\'b7i c\'b6. Tr\'b8i l\'b9i, gi\'e8ng nh\'ad con ch\'e3 trong chuy\'d6n ng\'f4 ng\'abn, h\'e4 l\'b9i th\'ddch \'aeeo c\'b8i v\'dfng c\'e6 \'ae\'d3
 ki\'d5m mi\'d5ng x\'ad\'acng c\'f1a ch\'f1. N\'e3i chung, qu\'c7n ch\'f3ng c\'a8n b\'b6n l\'b5 c\'e3 tinh th\'c7n n\'e6i d\'cby, nh\'adng c\'dfn r\'cat d\'e8t n\'b8t. H\'e4 mu\'e8n gi\'b6i ph\'e3ng, nh\'adng h\'e4 ch\'ada bi\'d5t l\'b5m c\'b8ch n\'b5o 
\'ae\'d3 \'ae\'b9t \'ae\'ad\'eec m\'f4c \'ae\'ddch \'cay.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-250\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\b\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 4. Nh\'f7ng th\'b5nh ki\'d5n}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 
. - V\'d7 giai c\'cap v\'ab s\'b6n \'eb c\'b6 hai \'ae\'bbng \'ae\'d2u kh\'abng hi\'d3u bi\'d5t l\'c9n nhau, n\'aan \'ae\'b7 n\'b6y ra nh\'f7ng th\'b5nh ki\'d5n. \'a7\'e8i v\'edi c\'abng nh\'a9n Ph\'b8p, th\'d7 ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8 l\'b5 m\'e9t h\'b9
ng ng\'ad\'eai th\'cap k\'d0m, kh\'abng \'ae\'b8ng k\'d3, kh\'abng c\'e3 kh\'b6 n\'a8ng \'ae\'d3 hi\'d3u bi\'d5t \'ae\'ad\'eec v\'b5 l\'b9i c\'b5ng kh\'abng c\'e3 kh\'b6 n\'a8ng ho\'b9t \'ae\'e9ng. \'a7\'e8i v\'edi ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8, nh\'f7ng ng
\'ad\'eai Ph\'b8p - m\'c6c d\'c7u h\'e4 l\'b5 h\'b9ng ng\'ad\'eai n\'b5o c\'f2ng \'ae\'d2u l\'b5 nh\'f7ng k\'ce b\'e3c l\'e9t \'ae\'e9c \'b8c. Ch\'f1 ngh\'dca \'ae\'d5 qu\'e8c v\'b5 ch\'f1 ngh\'dca t\'ad b\'b6n kh\'abng b\'e1 l\'ec d\'dep l\'eei d\'f4ng s
\'f9 nghi k\'fe l\'c9n nhau \'ae\'e3 v\'b5 s\'f9 ph\'a9n bi\'d6t \'ae\'bcng h\'b9ng gi\'b6 t\'b9o v\'d2 n\'dfi gi\'e8ng \'ae\'e3 \'ae\'d3 ng\'a8n c\'b6n vi\'d6c tuy\'aan truy\'d2n v\'b5 \'ae\'d3 chia r\'cf nh\'f7ng l\'f9c l\'ad\'eeng \'ae\'b8ng ph\'b6i 
\'aeo\'b5n k\'d5t l\'b9i.
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-242\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\b\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 5. \'a7\'b5n \'b8p d\'b7 man}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 . - N\'d5u b\'e4n th\'f9c d\'a9n Ph\'b8p r\'cat v\'f4ng v\'d2
 trong vi\'d6c ph\'b8t tri\'d3n n\'d2n kinh t\'d5 \'eb thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea, th\'d7 h\'e4 l\'b9i l\'b5 nh\'f7ng tay l\'b7o luy\'d6n trong ngh\'d2 \'ae\'b5n \'b8p d\'b7 man v\'b5 trong vi\'d6c ch\'d5 t\'b9o ra c\'b8i l\'dfng trung th\'b5nh b\'bet bu\'e9c. Nh
\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai nh\'ad \'abng G\'a8ng\'aei v\'b5 \'abng \'a7\'ea Val\'acra c\'e3 l\'cf \'ae\'b7 l\'aan thi\'aan \'ae\'b5ng t\'f5 l\'a9u r\'e5i n\'d5u c\'b8c \'abng \'cay sinh \'eb m\'e9t trong nh\'f7ng thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea c\'f1a Ph\'b8p. B\'de t\'cat c
\'b6 m\'e4i th\'f8 th\'f1 \'aeo\'b9n th\'a9m hi\'d3m c\'f1a c\'b8c to\'b5 \'b8n qu\'a9n s\'f9 v\'b5 to\'b5 \'b8n \'ae\'c6c bi\'d6t v\'a9y xung quanh, m\'e9t ng\'ad\'eai chi\'d5n s\'dc \'eb b\'b6n x\'f8 kh\'e3 l\'dfng ti\'d5n h\'b5nh vi\'d6c gi\'b8o d\'f4
c \'ae\'e5ng b\'b5o b\'de \'b8p b\'f8c v\'b5 d\'e8t n\'b8t c\'f1a m\'d7nh m\'b5 kh\'abng sa v\'b5o nanh vu\'e8t c\'f1a c\'b8c nh\'b5 \'aei khai ho\'b8 cho h\'e4.
\par Tr\'ad\'edc nh\'f7ng kh\'e3 kh\'a8n \'cay, \'a7\'b6ng ph\'b6i l\'b5m g\'d7?
\par T\'a8ng c\'ad\'eang c\'abng t\'b8c tuy\'aan truy\'d2n c\'f1a \'a7\'b6ng \'ae\'d3 kh\'bec ph\'f4c.
\par }\pard\plain \s24\qr \fi397\li0\ri567\sb120\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin567\lin0\itap0 \f38\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 NGUY\'d4N \'b8I QU\'e8C
\par }\pard\plain \qj \li0\ri0\sl-240\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs18\insrsid1378858 B\'b8o }{\i\f37\fs18\insrsid1378858 L'Humanit\'d0,}{
