a mai th\'d5, c\'ab nh\'d8! Ng\'ad\'eai ta \'aeem thu l\'b9i \'ae\'d3 c\'efng m\'e9t ch\'e7 c\'b6 c\'b8i h\'ad vinh c\'f1a t\'b8c gi\'b6 bao cu\'e9c gi\'d5t ch\'e3c kinh kh\'f1ng \'eb ch\'a9u \'a2u v\'b5 c\'b6 n\'bem di h\'b5i c\'f1a n\'b9n nh\'a9n cu\'e9
c t\'b5n s\'b8t th\'d5 gi\'edi!
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-268\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 C\'b8i \'ae\'b5i n\'b5y l\'b5 n\'aci l\'adu t\'e5n t\'ad
\'eeng tr\'adng nh\'f7ng nguy\'aan nh\'a9n c\'f1a m\'e4i cu\'e9c chi\'d5n tranh tr\'ad\'edc kia v\'b5 sau n\'b5y; c\'f2ng nh\'ad ng\'ad\'eai l\'ddnh kh\'abng t\'aan tu\'e6i n\'b5y l\'b5 hi\'d6n th\'a9n t\'ad\'eeng tr\'adng c\'f1a t\'cat c\'b6 nh\'f7ng 
ai b\'de gi\'d5t h\'b9i \'ae\'d3 tho\'b6 m\'b7n c\'b8i tham v\'e4ng v\'b5 c\'b8i ki\'aau k\'fa c\'f1a b\'e4n t\'ad\'edng l\'b7nh. B\'ebi v\'d7 ai m\'b5 \'ae\'b7 \'ae\'e4c t\'aan nh\'f7ng chi\'d5n tr\'cbn \'ae\'c7y tr\'b5n l\'dech s\'f6 t\'f5 \'ae\'c7u 
\'ae\'d5n cu\'e8i, ai m\'b5 \'ae\'b7 \'ae\'e4c b\'cay nhi\'aau t\'aan kh\'bec l\'aan ri\'aang m\'e9t \'ae\'b5i k\'fb ni\'d6m n\'b5y th\'abi}{\cs17\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 1{\footnote \pard\plain \s28\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa60\sl-240\slmult0
\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 1) Kh\'b6i ho\'b5n m\'abn \'a3toan c\'e3 kh\'bec \'ae\'c7y v\'b5o \'ae\'b8 t\'aan c\'b8c chi\'d5n tr\'cbn v\'b5 c
\'b8c t\'ad\'edng l\'dcnh th\'eai Nap\'abl\'aa\'abng.
\par 2) }{\i\insrsid1378858 Fatty:}{\insrsid1378858  T\'f5 l\'e3ng \'ae\'d3 ch\'d8 b\'e4n tai to m\'c6t l\'edn. G\'e8c ti\'d5ng Anh c\'e3 ngh\'dca l\'b5 ng\'ad\'eai b\'d0o.
\par 3) N\'e3i chuy\'d6n nu\'abi \'ae\'dc \'aei\'d5m.}})}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 , th\'d7 ph\'b6i kinh ho\'b5ng th\'cay, bi\'d5t bao nhi\'aau l\'b5 n\'abng d\'a9n, bao nhi\'aau l\'b5 c\'abng nh\'a9n \'ae\'b8ng th\'ad\'acng \'ae\'b7 ng\'b7 xu\'e8ng kh\'abng t
\'aan tu\'e6i, nh\'ad k\'ce \'aeang n\'bbm \'ae\'a9y!
\par \'a7\'d3 m\'e9t chuy\'d5n th\'ad sau, t\'abi s\'cf k\'d3 cho c\'ab nghe v\'d2 anh l\'ddnh t\'e9i nghi\'d6p n\'b5y, khi c\'dfn s\'e8ng \'ae\'b7 ph\'b6i \'ae\'ad\'acng \'ae\'c7u v\'edi nh\'f7ng tr\'b5ng s\'f3ng \'ae\'b9i b\'b8c li\'aan thanh nh\'ad th\'d5 n
\'b5o, nay v\'c9n ph\'b6i \'ae\'ad\'acng \'ae\'c7u nh\'ad th\'d5 n\'b5o v\'edi nh\'f7ng tr\'b5ng di\'d4n v\'a8n ngo\'b9i giao v\'b5 t\'e1 t\'d7nh th\'a9n thi\'d5t v\'ea v\'det c\'f1a c\'b8c v\'de s\'f8 th\'c7n v\'b5 c\'f1a c\'b8c c\'f4 Ph\'de}{
\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 2)}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 . H\'abm nay, h\'b7y tr\'eb l\'b9i c\'a9u chuy\'d6n v\'efng n\'b5y \'ae\'b7.
\par V\'cby, t\'abi \'aeang n\'e3i v\'edi c\'ab r\'bbng \'a3toan l\'b5 x\'e3m c\'b8c ph\'f1 \'ae\'d6 th\'aanh thang, c\'b8c v\'ad\'ean c\'a9y hoa n\'eb sum su\'aa, c\'b8c c\'e7 ng\'f9a xe v\'ad\'acng gi\'b6. \'a7\'e3 l\'b5 m\'e9t \'e6 xa hoa, t\'f8 x\'f8, th
\'f5a th\'b7i tr\'b5n tr\'d2 v\'b5 bi\'d5ng l\'ad\'eai lo\'cc lo\'d1t. \'a7\'e3 l\'b5 thi\'aan \'ae\'ad\'eang b\'e4n \'a8n b\'b8m \'ae\'f1 c\'b8c c\'ec v\'b5 \'ae\'f1 c\'b8c x\'f8. Sang tr\'e4ng l\'b5 sang tr\'e4ng cho \'ae\'d5n c\'b6 con v\'cbt. Ch\'b6 n
\'e3i l\'b5m g\'d7 \'ae\'d5n c\'b8i gi\'b8 ng\'abng cu\'e5ng th\'b6 ra bao m\'e9t con m\'cco h\'b6o h\'b9ng hay m\'e9t con ng\'f9a lo\'b9i kho\'b8i}{\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 3)}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 , n\'e3 \'ae\'f1 \'ae\'d3 nu\'abi s\'e8ng to
\'b5n b\'e9 d\'a9n c\'ad m\'e9t t\'d8nh n\'ad\'edc ta, c\'f8 c\'b8i 
\par }\pard\plain \s25\qj \li0\ri0\sa80\sl-268\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f38\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\insrsid1378858 con khuy\'d3n x\'e3m n\'b5y l\'b5 c\'f2ng \'ae\'ad\'eec s\'e8
ng l\'e9ng l\'c9y v\'b5 t\'e8n k\'d0m h\'acn ng\'ad\'eai \'aei l\'b5m th\'ee nhi\'d2u.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 R\'eai ch\'ddnh l\'e9 Vag\'acram v\'b5 \'ae\'b9i l\'e9 Cu
\'e8cxen, l\'b5 v\'b5o x\'e3m Batinhon. X\'e3m n\'b5y l\'b5 x\'e3m ki\'d3u con d\'aci, ngh\'dca l\'b5 d\'a9n b\'b6n \'ae\'dea n\'aci n\'b5y thu\'e9c m\'e9t giai c\'cap trung gian. H\'e4 kh\'abng gi\'b5u s\'f4 \'ae\'d3 bay nh\'b6y nh\'ad b\'e4n c\'f5 kh
\'abi trong gi\'edi t\'ad b\'b6n, m\'b5 c\'f2ng ch\'bcng \'ae\'f1 ngh\'cco \'ae\'d3 ph\'b6i v\'cat v\'b6 gi\'e8ng \'ae\'b8m th\'ee thuy\'d2n. Phong v\'f2 bi\'d3u \'aeo m\'f8c gi\'b5u c\'e3 c\'f1a h\'e4 c\'f8 l\'b5 theo s\'f9 th\'a8ng tr\'c7m kinh t\'d5 h
\'bbng ng\'b5y m\'b5 l\'aan xu\'e8ng; h\'e4 c\'e3 th\'d3 h\'abm nay th\'d7 th\'ad th\'b8i tr\'e5ng b\'bep c\'b6i, \'ae\'d3 r\'e5i h\'abm sau l\'b5 ph\'b6i b\'b8n \'ae\'f8t v\'ad\'ean t\'ad\'eec \'aei. D\'a9n \'ae\'a9y l\'b5 ti\'d3u th\'ad\'acng, l\'b5 
\'abng x\'d5p ph\'dfng gi\'cay, l\'b5 \'abng c\'df v\'d2 h\'adu. B\'b5 \'aei \'ae\'a9u l\'b5 c\'e3 m\'e9t con ch\'e5n}{\cs17\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 1{\footnote \pard\plain \s28\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa60\sl-240\slmult0
\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 1) }{\i\insrsid1378858 Zibeline:}{\insrsid1378858  Gi\'e8ng ch\'e5n B\'bec c\'f9c, t\'f8c m\'e9t lo\'b9i th\'f3 l
\'abng d\'b5i v\'b5 m\'ad\'eet, m\'d7nh d\'b5i, \'aeu\'abi d\'b5i n\'aan \'ae\'b7 \'ae\'ad\'eec x\'f6 l\'fd gi\'f7 nguy\'aan l\'abng d\'efng l\'b5m kh\'a8n qu\'b5ng c\'e6 ph\'f4 n\'f7 sang tr\'e4ng.
\par 2) Nh\'f7ng lo\'b9i hu\'a9n ch\'ad\'acng, huy ch\'ad\'acng c\'f1a Ph\'b8p; m\'e7i lo\'b9i c\'e3 h\'d7nh d\'b8ng, m\'b5u s\'bec ri\'aang.
\par 3) Nh\'b5 \'eb Pari th\'ad\'eang t\'f5 n\'a8m \'ae\'d5n t\'b8m t\'c7ng. Nh\'f7ng h\'e9 sang tr\'e4ng nh\'cat hay \'eb t\'c7ng g\'b8c cho \'ae\'d5n g\'b8c ba. G\'b8c cao h\'acn, th\'d7 nh\'f7ng h\'e9 gia t\'ad t\'c7m th\'ad\'eang h\'acn \'eb.}})}{
\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  to qu\'can quanh c\'e6 v\'b5 m\'e9t con ch\'e3 con b\'e5ng tr\'aan tay. \'a4ng th\'d7 bao gi\'ea c\'f2ng c\'e3 c\'b8i g\'d7 ch\'d3nh m\'b6ng c\'b5i khuy\'d5t ve \'b8o, m\'e9t c\'f1 ki\'d6u C\'abng hu\'a9n N\'abng nghi\'d6p ho\'c6
c l\'b5 b\'abng hoa t\'ddm c\'f1a v\'de ch\'f8c s\'bec H\'e4c ch\'ddnh}{\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 2)}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 . B\'b5 canh c\'f6a th\'d7 s\'b8ng s\'b8ng ch\'a8m ch\'f3t t\'ad\'edi nh\'f7ng ch\'cbu hoa thu h\'b6i \'ae\'ad\'eang c\'e6
 truy\'d2n c\'f1a b\'b5 b\'b5y tr\'aan c\'f6a s\'e6, s\'b8ng s\'b8ng gi\'f2 c\'b8i th\'b6m tr\'b6i c\'c7u thang ch\'ddnh - t\'cam th\'b6m n\'b5y b\'ad\'edng b\'d8nh nh\'cat \'ae\'denh kh\'abng ch\'deu leo cao h\'acn t\'c7ng g\'b8c ba}{
\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 3)}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 . C\'f8 suy quy lu\'cbt v\'cbn h\'b5nh c\'f1a v\'b9n v\'cbt th\'d7 d\'a9n c\'ad x\'e3m n\'b5y c\'e3 nhi\'d2u kh\'b6 n\'a8ng v\'ab s\'b6n ho\'b8 h\'acn l\'b5 s\'b6n sinh ra nh\'f7ng \'ae\'f8c ng
\'b5i t\'ad b\'b6n ch\'f1 ngh\'dca.
\par X\'e3m \'a3pin\'d0t l\'b5 ph\'dda ch\'a9n c\'f1a c\'b8i thang. N\'e3 l\'b5 ng\'ad\'eai b\'b5 con kh\'e8n kh\'e3, k\'ce th\'f5a k\'d5 b\'de g\'b9t b\'e1 c\'f1a hai x\'e3m kia. N\'e3 g\'c7n nh\'ad l\'b5 thu\'e9c m\'e9t gi\'e8ng ng\'ad\'eai kh\'b8c, ra v\'ce
 b\'cfn l\'cfn, khi\'aam nh\'ad\'eang, b\'de c\'b8i kh\'e8n c\'efng n\'e3 \'ae\'cc b\'d1p. N\'b5y c\'ab, h\'b7y xem \'abng b\'b8c m\'d7nh \'d0p m\'dda l\'cay \'ae\'ad\'eang theo c\'b8i ki\'d3u ngh\'d7n n\'a8m x\'ada c\'f2 c\'f1a d\'a9n ta, th\'d7 c\'ab
 ngh\'dc ra \'ae\'ad\'eec c\'b8i c\'b6nh x\'b7 h\'e9i \'eb \'ae\'a9y n\'e3 th\'d5 n\'b5o. C\'e3 bao nhi\'aau n\'ad\'edc \'d0p ngon ng\'e4t th\'d7 c\'f8 tu\'abn c\'b6 ra m\'e9t b\'aan c\'e8i, c\'dfn b\'aan kia th\'d7 ch\'d8 c\'e3 b\'b7, b\'d1t ra, qu\'be
t l\'b9i. \'a7\'a9y c\'f2ng th\'d5. M\'e9t b\'aan l\'b5 gi\'b5u sang v\'b5 nh\'b5n r\'e7i, m\'e9t b\'aan l\'b5 c\'c7n c\'ef v\'b5 thi\'d5u th\'e8n. L\'abi th\'abi v\'b5 g\'c7y gu\'e9c nh\'ad ng\'e3n tay kho\'bbm kho\'bbm c\'f1a con m\'f4 ph\'ef thu\'fb gi
\'b5, \'e8ng l\'df s\'ad\'ebi \'eb \'a3pin\'d0t m\'efa h\'cc th\'d7 um kh\'e3i v\'b5 m\'efa \'ae\'abng th\'d7 l\'b9i nh\'ad t\'bet ng\'cam. Tr\'abng xa, nh\'b5 c\'f6a kh\'bcng khiu trong x\'e3m gi\'e8ng y m\'c6t ng\'ad\'eai v\'cby, nh\'f7ng b\'e9 m\'c6
t ng\'ad\'eai ng\'ac ng\'b8c m\'b5 c\'b8i b\'d2 m\'c6t ti\'d6m c\'f1a m\'e9t b\'b8c bu\'abn gi\'ce r\'b8ch hay c\'f1a m\'e9t hi\'d6u th\'det \'ad\'edp l\'b9nh th\'d7 l\'b5m ra d\'b8ng c\'b8i mi\'d6ng m\'e3m, c\'dfn c\'f6a s\'e6 \'ae\'b7 to\'b8c to\'b9c th
\'d7 d\'efng l\'b5m nh\'f7ng con m\'bet nh\'cem nh\'f7ng d\'f6 l\'b9i c\'cbn th\'de. X\'e3m nh\'f7ng con ng\'ad\'eai l\'b5m l\'f4ng, s\'b6n xu\'cat v\'b5 \'ae\'e3i meo. X\'e3m ng\'ad\'eai l\'b5m th\'ee, x\'e3m ng\'ad\'eai ngh\'cco, x\'e3m ng\'ad\'eai c
\'efng kh\'e8n.
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-290\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 Gi\'f7a x\'e3m, c\'e3 m\'e9t m\'c8u ph\'e8 d\'b5i ch\'f5
ng d\'a8m ch\'f4c m\'d0t. Quanh ph\'e8 th\'cay t\'d2 t\'f9u m\'e9t ng\'abi tr\'ad\'eang ti\'d3u h\'e4c, m\'e9t nh\'b5 m\'b8y v\'b5 m\'e9t qu\'b8n ch\'b8o b\'d7nh d\'a9n. C\'e3 ph\'b6i th\'d5 kh\'abng n\'b5o, c\'ab em h\'e4 th\'a9n m\'d5n, c\'b6 c\'b8i b
\'e9 s\'cbu \'cay th\'d5 l\'b5 r\'cat m\'f9c ti\'aau bi\'d3u? Khi c\'dfn b\'d0, th\'d7 tr\'ce con \'aei h\'e4c \'ae\'d3 m\'b5 bi\'d5t t\'abn tr\'e4ng quy\'d2n thi\'aang li\'aang c\'f1a c\'b8c \'abng ch\'f1. L\'edn l\'aan, anh th\'ee r\'eai nh\'b5 tr\'ad
\'eang \'aei g\'e3p ph\'c7n l\'b5m gi\'b5u cho gi\'edi ch\'f1 nh\'a9n \'abng m\'b5 m\'d7nh \'ae\'b7 \'ae\'ad\'eec h\'e4c t\'cbp s\'efng b\'b8i c\'b8i uy nghi. Gi\'b5 r\'e5i y\'d5u \'aei, th\'d7 \'abng l\'b7o \'ae\'ad\'eec, v\'c9n gi\'edi ch\'f1 nh\'a9n 
\'abng \'ae\'e3, m\'b5 c\'f4 \'ae\'b7 l\'b5m gi\'b5u cho, t\'e8ng c\'f4 ra ngo\'b5i \'ae\'ad\'eang \'ae\'d3 nh\'ea ch\'c8n b\'c7n m\'b5 s\'e8ng n\'e8t cu\'e9c \'ae\'eai hay lam hay l\'b5m c\'f1a m\'d7nh!
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 M\'e7i s\'b8ng, t\'abi ph\'b6i \'aei ngang qu\'b8n ch\'b8
o b\'d7nh d\'a9n \'ae\'d3 \'ae\'d5n x\'ad\'ebng l\'b5m vi\'d6c c\'f1a t\'abi. Tr\'eai \'ae\'d1p hay x\'cau, n\'beng \'cam hay tuy\'d5t r\'aci, th\'d7 t\'abi c\'f2ng c\'f8 th\'cay t\'f4m l\'b9i tr\'ad\'edc c\'f6a ng\'abi nh\'b5 c\'abng n\'b5y l\'e8i ba ch
\'f4c c\'b8c c\'f4. C\'b8c c\'f4 \'a8n b\'cbn th\'cbt kh\'abng t\'ad\'ebng t\'ad\'eeng \'ae\'ad\'eec. Ng\'ad\'eai th\'d7 kho\'b8c c\'b8i ch\'a8n tr\'aan l\'adng, ng\'ad\'eai th\'d7 l\'b9i m\'c6c c\'b8i \'b8o d\'b5i b\'e3 c\'f1a h\'c7u b\'b5n tr\'ad\'eb
ng - \'ae\'c7u \'ae\'e9i c\'b8i m\'f2 r\'acm \'ae\'b7 v\'b5ng \'f3a, ng\'ad\'eai kh\'b8c n\'f7a t\'b6 t\'aci \'ae\'f4p v\'b8 mu\'abn m\'b5u s\'bec. Gi\'b5y c\'b8c c\'f4, m\'e2m h\'b8 ra nh\'ad h\'e9p th\'ad c\'b6, c\'ad\'eai nh\'b9o v\'edi m\'e4i kh\'b8
ch qua \'ae\'ad\'eang. Trong l\'f3c \'ae\'eei c\'f6a m\'eb v\'b5 \'ae\'d3 gi\'d5t th\'eai 
\par }\pard \qj \li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 gi\'ea, c\'b8c c\'f4 xem m\'cay m\'c8u b\'b8o }{\i\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Le Matin}{\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 24}{
\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  hay t\'ea }{\i\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Le Petit Parisien}{\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 25}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  nh\'c6t \'ae\'ad\'eec ch\'bcng bi\'d5t \'eb \'ae\'a9u n\'f7a. Tr\'eai c\'e3 l\'b9nh qu\'b8 th\'d7 c\'b8c c\'f4
 th\'e6i th\'e6i l\'aan ng\'e3n tay ho\'c6c l\'b5 gi\'eb \'aei\'d6u nh\'cat b\'e9 ra nh\'b6y}{\cs17\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 1{\footnote \pard\plain \s28\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa60\sl-240\slmult0
\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 1) }{\i\insrsid1378858 One-step}{\insrsid1378858  "M\'e9t b\'ad\'edc", t\'aan m\'e9t \'aei\'d6u v\'f2 g\'e8c M\'fc
, nhanh v\'b5 m\'b9nh. }{\f38\insrsid1378858 \'eb}{\insrsid1378858  \'ae\'a9y \'fd n\'e3i c\'b8c c\'f4 gi\'b5 khoa ch\'a9n m\'f3a tay cho \'ae\'ec r\'d0t.
\par 2) L\'e8i s\'ad\'ebi sang, s\'ad\'ebi c\'b6 nh\'b5 nh\'adng ch\'d8 \'ae\'e8t l\'df \'eb m\'e9t n\'aci th\'abi, c\'e3 \'e8ng d\'c9n h\'aci n\'ad\'edc n\'e3ng \'ae\'d5n t\'f5ng ph\'dfng.}})}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  \'ae\'d3 t\'f9 s\'ad\'ebi \'cam. M\'e9
t c\'f4 nh\'d7n t\'abi c\'b6 c\'ad\'eai: "Ch\'f3 xem, s\'ad\'ebi ki\'d3u trung t\'a9m}{\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 2)}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  c\'f1a b\'e4n n\'b5y \'ae\'cay!".
\par }\pard\plain \s27\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-272\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f40\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 D\'b8ng c\'b8c c\'f4 t\'e5i t\'b5n th\'d5, nh\'ad
ng ai n\'cay \'ae\'d2u th\'cbt d\'d4 th\'ad\'acng, v\'b5 c\'b8c c\'f4 tr\'abng th\'cay t\'abi m\'b7i r\'e5i, th\'d7 cu\'e8i c\'efng \'cay c\'f2ng l\'b5 c\'e3 quen bi\'d5t. M\'e9t th\'f8 t\'d7nh b\'bbng h\'f7u th\'d5 l\'b5 n\'b6y ra gi\'f7a ch\'f3ng t\'ab
i v\'b5 hai b\'aan ch\'b5o nhau khi \'aei qua.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-272\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 T\'abi \'ae\'c6c bi\'d6t \'ae\'d3 \'fd m\'e9t c\'f4 gi\'b5
 trong s\'e8 \'ae\'e3. \'a4ng c\'f4 s\'b9ch s\'cf, t\'ad\'acm t\'cat, v\'b5 b\'e9 d\'b9ng bi\'d3u l\'e9 m\'e9t n\'e7i bu\'e5n phi\'d2n \'ae\'ad\'eec n\'d0n xu\'e8ng, m\'e9t ni\'d2m t\'f9 tr\'e4ng ch\'bcng ch\'deu \'ae\'d3 ng\'b7 khu\'feu, ngay trong c\'ac
n qu\'c9n b\'b8ch. C\'f4 c\'e3 \'aeeo m\'e9t d\'b6i huy ch\'ad\'acng th\'ad\'ebng c\'abng c\'f8u n\'b9n. C\'f4 bao gi\'ea c\'f2ng c\'f8 \'ae\'f8ng \'ae\'bbng sau ng\'ad\'eai kh\'b8c.
\par M\'e9t h\'abm, t\'abi \'ae\'d5n b\'bet tay c\'f4 v\'b5 n\'e3i v\'edi c\'f4: "C\'e8 \'aci, c\'e8 c\'e3 vui l\'dfng cho ph\'d0p \'ae\'ad\'eec m\'eai c\'efng d\'efng m\'e9t b\'f7a l\'e3t d\'b9, ch\'f1 nh\'cbt t\'edi, \'ae\'ad\'eec kh\'abng?". C\'f4 \'ae\'b8
p: "\'a4ng t\'f6 t\'d5 qu\'b8, th\'ada \'abng, th\'d5 cho n\'aan t\'abi t\'f5 ch\'e8i th\'d7 ho\'b8 ra ph\'f4 l\'dfng t\'e8t c\'f1a \'abng, v\'cby xin nh\'cbn".
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-290\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Ch\'f3ng t\'abi c\'efng \'ae\'d5n m\'e9t qu\'b8n \'a8n nh\'e1. \'a7\'c6t xong m\'e3n \'a8n, ch\'f3ng t\'abi chuy\'d6n tr
\'df, v\'b5 \'abng c\'f4 b\'b6o t\'abi: "T\'abi kh\'abng d\'b8m t\'f9 ti\'d6n ng\'e1 l\'eai tr\'ad\'edc v\'edi \'abng, b\'ebi v\'d7 tr\'ad\'edc h\'d5t \'abng l\'b5 ng\'ad\'eai n\'ad\'edc ngo\'b5i, th\'d5 r\'e5i t\'abi l\'b9i ng\'b9i l\'b5m ph\'cbt l\'df
ng \'abng, thanh ni\'aan d\'d4 t\'f9 \'b8i th\'cay c\'e3 ng\'ad\'eai \'ae\'d5n b\'bet chuy\'d6n l\'b9i nh\'ad t\'abi, m\'e9t l\'b7o gi\'b5 ngh\'cco kh\'e6, ch\'bcng kh\'b8c \'ae\'f8a \'a8n m\'b5y v\'cby. Nh\'adng m\'b5 c\'f8 m\'e7i l\'c7n \'abng \'ae
i qua tr\'ad\'edc m\'c6t t\'abi, l\'b5 l\'dfng t\'abi l\'b9i tr\'b5n ng\'cbp m\'e9t ni\'d2m \'aeau \'ae\'edn kh\'abn c\'efng, t\'abi ch\'d8 mu\'e8n kh\'e3c. T\'abi r\'cat hi\'d3u \'abng l\'cay th\'d5 l\'b5m l\'b9, nh\'adng \'cay l\'b5 t\'b9i th\'d5 n\'b5
y: th\'cay \'abng, l\'b5 t\'abi l\'b9i nh\'ed th\'bbng con th\'f8 c\'f1a t\'abi, t\'abi \'ae\'b7 m\'cat n\'e3 trong tr\'cbn gi\'c6c. N\'e3 c\'f2ng kho\'b6ng tu\'e6i \'abng \'ae\'cay. Ch\'bec \'abng h\'a8m nh\'a8m, h\'a8m s\'b8u ch\'f8 g\'d7? - H\'a8m s
\'b8u, c\'e8 \'b9, t\'abi tr\'b6 l\'eai. - \'a7\'f3ng r\'e5i, n\'e3 k\'d0m \'abng m\'e9t tu\'e6i. \'a4ng kh\'abng ch\'b8n tai th\'d7 \'ae\'d3 t\'abi k\'d3 chuy\'d6n n\'e3 \'abng nghe, chuy\'d6n n\'e3 m\'b5 th\'cbt ra l\'b5 chuy\'d6n t\'abi. - Xin m\'eai c
\'e8, nghe chuy\'d6n c\'e8 s\'cf th\'ddch th\'f3 l\'bem. - Th\'eai t\'abi c\'dfn \'ddt tu\'e6i, \'abng b\'b9n c\'efng b\'b5n \'ae\'b8ng k\'ddnh c\'f1a t\'abi k\'d3, t\'abi l\'b5m ngh\'d2 h\'b5ng h\'b6i \'ae\'a8ng b\'b9}{
\cs17\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 1{\footnote \pard\plain \s28\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa60\sl-240\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 1) T\'f8
c thu\'fb th\'f1 d\'a9n s\'f9. Do y\'aau c\'c7u c\'f1a s\'f9 ki\'d3m so\'b8t qu\'e8c gia v\'b5 qu\'e8c t\'d5, ng\'ad\'eai \'aei bi\'d3n ph\'b6i theo lu\'cbt h\'b5ng h\'b6i qu\'e8c t\'d5, \'ae\'ad\'eec \'ae\'a8ng k\'fd v\'b5o m\'e9t danh b\'b9 nh\'b5 n\'ad
\'edc. C\'e3 \'ae\'a8ng b\'b9 m\'edi l\'b5 c\'abng nh\'a9n h\'b5ng h\'b6i ch\'ddnh th\'f8c.}})}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 . T\'abi \'ae\'b7 c\'e3 \'aei v\'dfng quanh th\'d5 gi\'edi nhi\'d2u l\'c7n. T\'abi c\'f2ng c\'e3 l\'c7n \'ae\'d5n x\'f8 \'abng, \'ae
\'d5n S\'b5i G\'dfn, \'ae\'d5n H\'b6i Ph\'dfng. Sau t\'abi t\'bbn ti\'d6n c\'ad\'edi m\'e9t c\'ab g\'b8i n\'abng th\'abn hi\'d2n l\'b5nh. V\'ee ch\'e5ng \'ae\'d5n l\'cbp nghi\'d6p \'eb v\'efng B\'bec. Nh\'b5 t\'abi m\'eb m\'e9t c\'f6a h\'b5ng nh\'e1 b\'b8
n gia v\'de v\'c6t v\'b7nh, c\'dfn t\'abi th\'d7 v\'b5o l\'b5m m\'e9t nh\'b5 m\'b8y. V\'ee ch\'e5ng t\'abi c\'e3 hai trai, m\'e9t g\'b8i, ba ch\'b8u th\'cbt l\'b5 c\'f1a tr\'eai cho \'abng \'b9! Nh\'b5 t\'abi v\'edi t\'abi, b\'e4n t\'abi ch\'deu kh\'e3
 kham kh\'e6 c\'f2ng nhi\'d2u, nu\'abi \'ae\'ad\'eec c\'b8c ch\'b8u \'a8n h\'e4c, n\'e3 gi\'e1i giang l\'bem. B\'b5 con l\'e8i x\'e3m \'ae\'d2u l\'cay l\'b5m th\'ccm thu\'e5ng, v\'d7 c\'b8c ch\'b8u n\'d5t na, th\'cbt l\'b5 ngoan ngo\'b7n, ch\'a8m l\'b5
m, l\'b9i c\'e3 h\'e4c. Ch\'b8u M\'abrix\'ac l\'b5 ch\'b8u l\'edn, l\'b5m ngh\'d2 th\'ee v\'cf. Ch\'b8u Anbe th\'d7 l\'b5m th\'ee m\'b8y. Em g\'b8i c\'b8c ch\'b8u, l\'b5 ch\'b8u Yvon, n\'e3 l\'b5 m\'e9t b\'abng hoa xinh xinh m\'ad\'eai t\'b8m c\'b8i xu
\'a9n xanh- nh\'ad \'eb x\'f8 t\'abi ng\'ad\'eai ta hay n\'e3i v\'a8n hoa th\'d5 - hoa l\'b5m si ng\'a9y l\'f8a trai kh\'bep v\'efng, ch\'b8u n\'e3 \'ae\'b8nh m\'b8y ch\'f7. M\'e7i \'ae\'f8a ki\'d5m \'ae\'ad\'eec \'ae\'e5ng ti\'d2n c\'f2ng kha kh\'b8, 
\'ae\'f1 cho m\'d7nh v\'b5 cho v\'ee ch\'e5ng ch\'f3ng t\'abi. Ban ng\'b5y th\'d7 c\'b8c ch\'b8u \'aei l\'b5m, t\'e8i \'ae\'d5n c\'b6 m\'cay ch\'b8u m\'b6i m\'aa h\'e4c h\'b5nh. Ch\'f1 nh\'cbt n\'b5o c\'f2ng c\'b6 ng\'b5y b\'b5n lu\'cbn v\'edi nhau nh\'f7
ng c\'b8i h\'e4c \'ae\'ad\'eec trong tu\'c7n. N\'e3i th\'cbt t\'d7nh \'ae\'d3 \'abng hay, c\'f8 nghe c\'b8c ch\'b8u n\'e3 b\'b5n n\'e3 n\'e3i l\'b5 s\'ad\'edng l\'b9 s\'ad\'edng l\'efng; \'cay ch\'ddnh c\'b8c ch\'b8u \'ae\'b7 d\'b9y ch\'f3ng t\'abi, m\'d1
 c\'b8c ch\'b8u v\'edi t\'abi, bi\'d5t \'ae\'ad\'eec kh\'abng bi\'d5t bao nhi\'aau th\'f8. V\'cby l\'b5 v\'ee ch\'e5ng ch\'f3ng t\'abi th\'cbt l\'b5 \'ae\'abi b\'e8 m\'d1 s\'ad\'edng nh\'cat tr\'c7n \'ae\'eai.
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 "Chi\'d5n tranh b\'efng n\'e6. Ch\'b8u M\'abrix\'ac b\'de th\'ad\'acng n\'c6ng t\'f5 \'ae\'c7u, \'ddt l\'a9u sau th\'d7
 ch\'d5t. Ch\'b8u Anbe th\'d7 b\'de ghi l\'b5 m\'cat t\'ddch, sau ba th\'b8ng chi\'d5n tr\'cbn. C\'f8 th\'d5 l\'b5 nh\'b5 t\'abi v\'b5 ch\'b8u g\'b8i ho\'b8 \'aei\'aan l\'aan, \'aei\'aan v\'d7 \'aeau \'ae\'edn. L\'b5ng t\'abi l\'b5 c\'b8i \'ae\'dd
ch cho ph\'b8o n\'b7, \'ae\'b9n Ph\'b8p \'ae\'d5n v\'edi ch\'f3ng t\'abi c\'f2ng nhi\'d2u ngang \'ae\'b9n \'a7\'f8c; \'ae\'b9n n\'e3 kh\'abng c\'e3 qu\'e8c t\'dech, n\'aan \'ae\'b9n b\'aan n\'b5y hay b\'aan kia th\'d7 c\'f2ng \'ae\'d2u ph\'b8 ph\'b8ch 
\'ae\'e5 \'ae\'b9c, c\'f2ng \'ae\'d2u gi\'d5t h\'b9i ng\'ad\'eai ta, d\'f6ng d\'adng nh\'ad nhau, t\'b5n kh\'e8c nh\'ad nhau.
\par "M\'e9t h\'abm n\'e4, trong gian nh\'b5 ch\'f3ng t\'abi \'eb \'ae\'b7 \'ae\'e6 v\'ec \'ae\'d5n n\'f6a, v\'ee t\'abi c\'efng ch\'b8u g\'b8i t\'abi \'aeang n\'cau n\'ad\'edng, th\'d7 m\'e9t c\'b8i n\'e5i}{\cs17\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 1{\footnote 
\pard\plain \s28\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa60\sl-240\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 1) T\'f5 l\'e3ng ch\'d8 \'ae\'b9n ph\'b8o c\'ec l\'edn.}})}{
\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  - ch\'bcng ph\'b6i lo\'b9i n\'e5i Na Uy n\'e6i ti\'d5ng c\'f1a Lui Phorext\'ac \'ae\'a9u, m\'b5 l\'b5 c\'b8i lo\'b9i n\'e5i n\'e3 gi\'cbp be gi\'cbp b\'d0t tu\'e8t - n\'e3 b\'e6 xu\'e8ng.
\par "M\'e9t ti\'d5ng n\'e6 kinh h\'e5n, r\'e5i t\'cat c\'b6 h\'cat tung l\'aan. T\'abi tho\'b8t th\'a9n v\'d7 \'aeang xu\'e8ng t\'c7ng h\'c7m l\'cay c\'b8i g\'d7 \'ae\'e3. \'a7\'d5n khi l\'b9i ng\'ad\'eai, t\'f5 d\'ad\'edi h\'c7m l\'aan, th\'d7 l\'aan h\'d5
t c\'c7u thang, t\'abi ch\'bcng c\'dfn th\'cay nh\'b5, th\'cay c\'f6a, th\'cay v\'ee, th\'cay con \'ae\'a9u c\'b6 n\'f7a, m\'b5 ch\'d8 th\'cay m\'e9t kho\'b6ng tr\'e8ng kh\'abng, m\'e9t kho\'b6ng tr\'e8ng kh\'abng kh\'f1ng khi\'d5p, h\'b7i h\'efng, m\'e9
t kho\'b6ng tr\'e8ng kh\'abng n\'e3 l\'cap \'ae\'c6c kh\'abng trung b\'bbng c\'b8i n\'b7o nu\'e9t, c\'b8i t\'cbn c\'efng, c\'b8i ch\'d5t ch\'e3c, c\'b8i tan hoang. T\'abi qu\'b8 s\'f7ng s\'ea \'ae\'d3 c\'dfn ho\'b6ng h\'e8t... Nh\'adng h\'b7y ch\'ea \'ae
\'cay, \'ae\'b7 h\'d5t \'ae\'a9u! C\'b8i l\'f3c gh\'aa g\'edm nh\'cat trong c\'b6 \'ae\'eai t\'abi, l\'b5 l\'f3c m\'b5 t\'abi nh\'cbn ra trong \'ae\'e8ng nh\'b5 c\'f6a v\'f4n n\'b8t, m\'e9t c\'b8i b\'b5n tay m\'b8u me c\'f1a ch\'b8u Yvon t\'e9i nghi\'d6
p c\'f1a t\'abi, r\'e5i c\'b8ch m\'cay b\'ad\'edc, l\'b5 m\'e9t c\'b8i ch\'a9n c\'dfn gi\'b5y t\'cat y nguy\'aan c\'f1a ng\'ad\'eai v\'ee \'ae\'b8ng th\'ad\'acng c\'f1a t\'abi. }{\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'ca}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 y b\'cay gi\'ea, 
\'cay b\'cay gi\'ea...".
\par }\pard\plain \s27\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f40\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'a7\'d5n \'ae\'a9y, \'abng gi\'b5 t\'b8i nh\'ee
t. T\'abi \'ae\'e4c th\'cay trong \'ae\'abi m\'bet c\'f4, b\'e7ng d\'b9i \'aei, m\'e9t n\'e7i ni\'d2m \'aeau x\'e3t v\'b5 c\'a8m h\'ean kh\'abng sao t\'b6 xi\'d5t. M\'e9t c\'acn co gi\'cbt l\'b5m c\'f4 to\'b5n th\'a9n run r\'c8y. C\'f4 t\'fa hai b\'b5
n tay \'aeang qu\'bep l\'b9i l\'aan m\'d0p b\'b5n. Hai ch\'a9n c\'f4 di di \'ae\'d2u nh\'dep, nh\'ad ph\'b8t s\'e8t, tr\'aan s\'b5n nh\'b5, m\'b5 c\'a8ng g\'a9n c\'e8t ra nh\'ad v\'cby, th\'d7 l\'b5 khi n\'b5o con ng\'ad\'eai ta \'aeang c\'e8 k\'d7m l\'b9
i m\'e9t ni\'d2m x\'f3c \'ae\'e9ng \'aeang mu\'e8n b\'efng ra. T\'abi nh\'e1 nh\'d1 b\'b6o c\'f4: "Th\'abi v\'f5a r\'e5i, c\'e8 \'aci! Xin \'ae\'d3 h\'abm kh\'b8c c\'e8 k\'d3 cho nghe. C\'e8 x\'aci c\'f1 khoai r\'b8n, c\'e8 nh\'d0!". \'a4ng c\'f4 nh\'ad
 kh\'abng nghe th\'cay t\'abi n\'e3i; c\'f4 th\'eb d\'b5i m\'e9t h\'aci, n\'e3i ti\'d5p: "\'a7\'cay \'abng xem, \'abng th\'a9n m\'d5n, chi\'d5n tranh, cu\'e9c chi\'d5n tranh tr\'eai tru \'ae\'cat di\'d6t n\'b5y t\'abi c\'e3 c\'b8i g\'d7 th\'d7 n\'e3 \'ae
\'b7 gi\'d5t s\'b9ch c\'b6, n\'b5o l\'b5 h\'b9nh ph\'f3c, n\'b5o l\'b5 nh\'b5 c\'f6a, n\'b5o ng\'ad\'eai v\'ee qu\'fd, n\'b5o b\'c7y con y\'aau. C\'dfn t\'abi, th\'d7 b\'a9y gi\'ea t\'abi nh\'ea thi\'aan h\'b9 b\'e8 th\'dd \'ae\'d3 s\'e8ng qua ng\'b5
y, sau b\'cay nhi\'aau n\'a8m tr\'eai l\'b5m \'a8n, c\'f9c nh\'e4c. Bi\'d5t \'ae\'a9u, v\'a9ng, bi\'d5t \'ae\'a9u ch\'bcng ph\'b6i ch\'ddnh ch\'b8u Anbe \'ae\'b8ng th\'ad\'acng c\'f1a t\'abi l\'b5 ng\'ad\'eai b\'a9y gi\'ea \'ae\'a9y \'aeang n\'bbm \'ae
\'e3 d\'ad\'edi Kh\'b6i ho\'b5n m\'abn!".
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 C\'f4 g\'b9t m\'e9t gi\'e4t n\'ad\'edc m\'bet th\'cb
t to, tay run run n\'a9ng c\'b8i c\'e8c m\'b5 t\'abi v\'f5a r\'e3t r\'ad\'eeu v\'b5o, mi\'d6ng n\'e3i: "N\'b5o, ch\'f3c s\'f8c kho\'ce \'abng!".
\par 
\par }\pard\plain \s26\ql \li0\ri567\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin567\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 B\'b8o }{\i\insrsid1378858 L'Humanit\'d0,}{\insrsid1378858 \line 
ng\'b5y 30 v\'b5 31-5-1922.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 
\par 
\par 
\par 
\par }\pard\plain \s21\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \b\f39\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 
\par 
