\par }\pard\plain \qj \li1134\ri0\sb120\sa360\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin1134\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 \~}{\b\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Qu\'e8c v\'ad\'ac
ng n\'ad\'edc Nam s\'bep l\'b5m "kh\'b8ch c\'f1a n\'ad\'edc Ph\'b8p". G\'e4i l\'b5 c\'e3 l\'eai ch\'b5o m\'f5ng t\'dd ti, ch\'f3ng t\'abi k\'ddnh d\'a9ng ng\'b5i gi\'cac m\'e9ng n\'b5y c\'f1a \'ae\'e5ng ch\'dd Nguy\'d4n }{\b\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'b8}{
\b\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 i Qu\'e8c c\'f1a ch\'f3ng t\'abi, ng\'ad\'eai b\'c7y t\'abi trung th\'b5nh c\'f1a ng\'b5i.
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-286\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 \'a7\'aam t\'e8i qu\'bbn qu\'b9i d\'ad\'edi l\'b5n m\'ad
a nh\'e1 h\'b9t d\'c7m d\'d2. M\'b6nh tr\'a8ng v\'b5ng v\'e4t c\'e8 b\'ddu tr\'aan nh\'f7ng m\'b8i l\'d2u tranh. C\'a9y \'ae\'c9m \'ad\'edt \'ae\'c7m \'ae\'d7a n\'ad\'edc m\'bet tu\'abn r\'aci. Gi\'e3 th\'e6i qua nh\'f7ng c\'f4m l\'b8 m\'d6t m\'e1
i va nhau th\'b5nh ti\'d5ng kinh r\'een. C\'b5nh c\'a9y v\'c6n v\'d1o nh\'ad nh\'f7ng c\'b8nh tay ma qu\'b8i, v\'b5 nh\'f7ng \'ae\'b8m n\'ad\'edc b\'de t\'f5ng c\'acn gi\'e3 \'ae\'e9t ng\'e9t qu\'cat, c\'f8 n\'f8c n\'eb. C\'b6nh v\'cbt n\'ad\'edc Nam, l
\'e5ng trong c\'a9y c\'e1 um t\'efm, v\'e8n t\'ad\'aci vui v\'b5 th\'ac m\'e9ng th\'d5 d\'ad\'edi \'b8nh tr\'a8ng, nay bu\'e5n th\'b6m l\'b9 l\'efng. C\'acn h\'cap h\'e8i \'aeang ch\'aci v\'aci kh\'bep. Tai \'ad\'acng l\'b6ng v\'b6ng \'ae\'a9u \'ae\'a9y.

\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-286\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'b8}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 nh s\'b8ng l\'f5 \'ae\'f5 c
\'f1a nh\'f7ng c\'a9y n\'d5n th\'acm ch\'cap ch\'edi \'ae\'c7u ng\'e4n b\'cac cong queo, h\'bet l\'aan nh\'f7ng c\'a9y c\'e9t s\'acn m\'b5i nh\'bdn b\'e3ng trong cung \'aei\'d6n nh\'f7ng b\'e3ng \'aeen lung lay v\'b5 nh\'f7ng con m\'bet h\'cap h\'b8y. B
\'e4n quan ho\'b9n lim dim u\'d3 o\'b6i tr\'aan chi\'d5c chi\'d5u tr\'b6i d\'ad\'edi \'ae\'cat \'eb m\'e9t g\'e3c nh\'b5. Nh\'ad c\'b6m th\'cay \'ae\'ad\'eec c\'e3 im l\'c6ng \'aeang b\'df l\'aa.
\par Tr\'e8ng canh v\'f5a \'aei\'d3m ba ti\'d5ng. T\'efng, t\'efng, t\'efng! C\'b8c anh l\'b5 ng\'ad\'eai ph\'ad\'acng T\'a9y, c\'b8c anh ch\'bcng hi\'d3u th\'d5 l\'b5 th\'d5 n\'b5o c\'b6, h\'f6? T\'efng, t\'efng, t\'efng! Nh\'a9n n\'e3 l\'aan n\'a8m th\'d5 l
\'b5 ba gi\'ea c\'f1a c\'b8c anh \'ae\'cay. \'a7\'a9y l\'b5 th\'eai kh\'bec ban \'ae\'aam l\'f3c l\'ad\'acng tri c\'cat cao ti\'d5ng. L\'f3c c\'b8c \'ae\'e8ng m\'b6 kh\'b9c ra nh\'f7ng k\'ce n\'bbm b\'aan trong, h\'e4 l\'d7a kh\'e1i nh\'f7ng t\'cam li\'d6
m he h\'d0 m\'eb, \'ae\'d3 ra ngo\'b5i \'aei d\'df \'aei d\'c9m, c\'cat l\'aan ti\'d5ng r\'f3 hoan l\'b9c. L\'f3c \'ae\'c7u \'e3c con ng\'ad\'eai \'ae\'c7y r\'c9y nh\'f7ng b\'e3ng h\'d7nh, m\'e9ng m\'de. T\'efng, t\'efng, t\'efng! Nh\'a9n n\'e3 l\'aa
n ba, th\'d7 \'cay l\'b5 con s\'e8 ch\'ddn, con s\'e8 t\'cbn c\'efng trong nh\'f7ng con s\'e8 ch\'bcng th\'d3 chia c\'f2ng ch\'bcng th\'d3 nh\'a9n, m\'b5 theo vua Ph\'f4c Hi th\'d7 n\'e3 bi\'d3u hi\'d6n s\'f9 suy \'ae\'e8n c\'f1a m\'e9t sinh linh \'ae\'ad
\'eec coi nh\'ad c\'efng t\'e9t }{\i\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 (d\'ad\'acng c\'f6u)}{\cs17\i\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 1{\footnote \pard\plain \s28\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa60\sl-240\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 
\f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 1) Nguy\'aan b\'b6n vi\'d5t }{\i\insrsid1378858 gi\'ad\'acng c\'f6u}{\insrsid1378858 , v\'d7 t\'b8c gi\'b6 mu\'e8n b\'b9n \'ae\'e4c Ph\'b8p \'ae\'e4c \'ae\'ad\'eec g\'c7n \'a9
m Vi\'d6t h\'acn.
\par D\'ad\'acng c\'f6u, m\'e9t qu\'ce trong Kinh D\'dech, bi\'d3u hi\'d6n m\'f8c cao nh\'cat m\'b5 m\'e9t con ng\'ad\'eai ho\'c6c m\'e9t s\'f9 v\'cbt c\'e3 th\'d3 ti\'d5n t\'edi \'ae\'ad\'eec v\'b5 t\'f5 \'aei\'d3m n\'b5y tr\'eb \'aei n\'e3 s\'cf xu\'e8ng d
\'e8c (kh\'b8i ni\'d6m thu\'e9c v\'f2 tr\'f4 quan si\'aau h\'d7nh huy\'d2n b\'dd Trung Qu\'e8c c\'e6, sau th\'ad\'eang g\'ben v\'edi m\'aa t\'ddn v\'d2 t\'ad\'edng s\'e8).
\par Ph\'f4c Hi, vua th\'c7n tho\'b9i Trung Qu\'e8c c\'e6 s\'ac, \'ae\'ad\'eec coi l\'b5 thu\'fb t\'e6 c\'f1a v\'f2 tr\'f4 quan n\'e3i tr\'aan.
\par 2) }{\i\insrsid1378858 Ph\'f4ng ho\'b5ng}{\insrsid1378858  trong nguy\'aan b\'b6n vi\'d5t b\'bbng ti\'d5ng Vi\'d6t.
\par 3) H\'a8ml\'d0t: Nh\'a9n v\'cbt ch\'ddnh trong v\'eb k\'dech c\'efng t\'aan c\'f1a v\'a8n h\'b5o Anh S\'d5chxpia. Trong \'aeo\'b9n \'ae\'c7u c\'f1a v\'eb k\'dech H\'a8ml\'d0t, ho\'b5ng t\'f6 n\'ad\'edc \'a7an M\'b9ch, ti\'d5p x\'f3c v\'edi b\'e3
ng ma vua cha hi\'d6n v\'d2 \'ae\'dfi \'ae\'ad\'eec con b\'b8o th\'ef.}})}{\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858  }{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 .
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'a7\'e3 ch\'ddnh l\'b5 l\'f3c Thi\'aan t\'f6 n\'bbm m\'ac. Ng\'b5i m\'ac th\'cay nh\'f7ng con r\'e5ng ch\'b9m tr\'aan t\'f1
, b\'b5n b\'e7ng bi\'d5n \'ae\'e9ng, ho\'b8 th\'b5nh nh\'f7ng con r\'ben g\'edm ghi\'d5c, m\'eb thao l\'b8o nh\'f7ng con m\'bet \'ae\'e1 ng\'c7u tia m\'b8u. C\'dfn nh\'f7ng con }{\i\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 ph\'f4ng ho\'b5ng}{
\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 2)}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 , gi\'e8ng chim t\'ad\'eeng tr\'adng cho uy quy\'d2n vua ch\'f3a, th\'d7 v\'ad\'acn chi\'d5c c\'e6 d\'b5i ngo\'bdng tua t\'f1a l\'abng, qu\'d6t m\'e1 xo\'cc c\'b8nh, y h\'d6t \'ae\'b8m g\'b5 tr
\'e8ng c\'b8u k\'d8nh, \'ae\'b8ng gh\'d0t. M\'e4i v\'cbt b\'bbng ng\'e4c th\'b9ch, b\'bbng ch\'a9u b\'b8u, \'ae\'d2u x\'d8n \'aei, x\'b8m x\'det l\'b9i. T\'cat c\'b6 c\'f8 t\'f5 t\'f5 quay tr\'dfn, v\'b5 tan d\'c7n, tan d\'c7n. R\'e5i m\'e9t b\'e3ng ma tr
\'efm kh\'a8n, tr\'a8ng tr\'beng hi\'d6n l\'aan. Nh\'b5 vua kinh ho\'b5ng run l\'aan l\'cbp c\'cbp, v\'d7 kh\'abng ph\'b6i vua ch\'f3a n\'b5o c\'f2ng \'ae\'d2u can \'ae\'b6m nh\'ad H\'a8ml\'d0t}{\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 3)}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 
, v\'b5 th\'abng minh nh\'ad th\'d5 th\'d7 l\'b9i c\'b5ng kh\'abng. Ng\'b5i mu\'e8n k\'d0o chi\'d5u che m\'c6t m\'b5 kh\'abng \'ae\'ad\'eec. 
\par }\pard \qj \li0\ri0\sa80\sl-270\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'a7\'ad\'eang b\'d6 v\'b5 gi\'cbn d\'f7, b\'e3ng ma n\'e3i v\'edi v\'de ch\'f1 ho\'b5ng cung th\'d5 n\'b5y:
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-270\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 - Mi c\'e3 nh\'cbn ra ta kh\'abng, \'ae\'f8a con kh\'e8n kh\'e6 kia \'aci! Ta l\'b5 m\'e9t trong nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'ea
i khai s\'b8ng n\'ad\'edc Nam t\'ad\'aci \'ae\'d1p n\'b5y \'ae\'a9y. Ta l\'b5 Tr\'adng Tr\'bec, n\'a8m 39}{\cs17\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 1{\footnote \pard\plain \s28\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa60\sl-240\slmult0
\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 1) Hai B\'b5 Tr\'adng kh\'ebi ngh\'dca n\'a8m 40.
\par 2) L\'fd B\'abn, t\'f8c L\'fd B\'dd, kh\'ebi ngh\'dca n\'a8m 542.
\par 3) L\'aa \'a7\'b9i H\'b5nh ph\'b8 gi\'c6c n\'a8m 981.
\par 4) Nh\'b5 Tr\'c7n b\'bet \'ae\'c7u t\'f5 n\'a8m 1226.}})}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  \'ae\'b7 c\'efng em g\'b8i ta l\'b5 Tr\'adng Nh\'de v\'b5 \'ae\'e5ng b\'b5o \'ae\'b8nh \'aeu\'e6i b\'e4n x\'a9m l\'a8ng, tr\'b6 th\'ef ch\'e5ng, gi\'b6i tho\'b8t qu\'aa h
\'ad\'acng. \'a7\'f5ng c\'e3 run l\'aan nh\'ad th\'d5, con \'aci! M\'b5 ph\'b6i l\'beng nghe l\'cay l\'eai m\'d1 b\'b6o! Ch\'bcng hay mi c\'e3 bi\'d5t r\'bbng, theo t\'cbp t\'f4c ngh\'d7n n\'a8m c\'f1a n\'ad\'edc Nam ta x\'ada c\'f2 th\'d7 Ho\'b5ng \'ae
\'d5 l\'b5 ch\'deu m\'d6nh tr\'eai \'ae\'d3 tr\'de d\'a9n, v\'d7 th\'d5 m\'b5 \'ae\'ad\'eec coi l\'b5 con c\'f1a tr\'eai, cha m\'d1 c\'f1a d\'a9n?
\par "Vua mu\'e8n x\'f8ng v\'edi l\'dfng tr\'eai v\'b5 l\'b5m tr\'dfn nhi\'d6m v\'f4 ch\'dd t\'abn c\'f1a m\'d7nh th\'d7 ph\'b6i ch\'deu kh\'e6 tr\'ad\'edc d\'a9n v\'b5 chia s\'ad\'edng sau d\'a9n. Vua ph\'b6i tu\'a9n l\'d6nh tr\'eai, m\'b5 ti\'d5ng d\'a9n ch
\'ddnh l\'b5 truy\'d2n l\'b9i \'fd tr\'eai. B\'bbng kh\'abng th\'d7 \'cay l\'b5 tr\'eai \'aeo\'b9n tuy\'d6t, t\'e6 ti\'aan t\'f5 b\'e1, nh\'a9n d\'a9n ru\'e5ng r\'c9y.
\par "Gi\'eb s\'f6 \'ae\'cat n\'ad\'edc ra m\'b5 xem, mi s\'cf th\'cay t\'e6 ti\'aan \'ae\'b7 treo bao t\'cam g\'ad\'acng \'ae\'b9o \'ae\'f8c v\'b5 d\'f2ng c\'b6m, ch\'dd kh\'dd v\'b5 t\'f9 t\'abn. L\'fd B\'abn (544)}{\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 2)}{
\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  , v\'edi m\'e9t nh\'f3m ngh\'dca s\'dc, \'ae\'b7 n\'e6i d\'cby v\'b5 b\'ce g\'b7y \'b8ch \'ae\'ab h\'e9 c\'f1a H\'b8n t\'e9c. Ng\'ab Quy\'d2n (938) \'ae\'b7 ph\'b8 tan \'ae\'b9o qu\'a9n n\'ad\'edc ngo\'b5i k\'d0o v\'b5o \'ae\'b8
nh chi\'d5m \'ae\'cat \'aeai T\'e6 qu\'e8c ta.
\par "D\'a9n ta s\'e8ng trong h\'b9nh ph\'f3c v\'b5 th\'denh v\'ad\'eeng d\'ad\'edi tri\'d2u nh\'b5 \'a7inh. N\'a8m 980}{\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 3)}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 , L\'aa \'a7\'b9i H\'b5nh \'ae\'b7 d\'f2ng c\'b6m kh\'abng ch\'deu khu\'cat ph
\'f4c tr\'ad\'edc y\'aau s\'b8ch c\'f1a l\'b8ng gi\'d2ng h\'efng m\'b9nh h\'acn m\'d7nh g\'cap b\'e9i, \'abng \'ae\'b7 \'ae\'b8nh th\'beng \'ae\'dech, gi\'d5t ch\'d5t t\'ad\'edng \'ae\'dech. Do \'ae\'e3 \'ae\'b7 gi\'b6i tho\'b8t \'ae\'ad\'eec \'ae\'e5ng b
\'b5o kh\'e1i n\'b9n n\'ab d\'dech.
\par }\pard\plain \s22\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-270\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f40\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 "Qu\'a9n M\'abng C\'e6 \'aei \'ae\'d5n \'ae\'a9
u ph\'b8 s\'b9ch \'ae\'cay, \'ae\'b7 b\'de nh\'b5 Tr\'c7n v\'ce vang c\'f1a ch\'f3ng ta \'ae\'b8nh b\'b9i (1225)}{\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 4)}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 . L\'aa L\'eei \'ae\'b7 h\'efng d\'f2ng \'ae\'f8ng ra l\'b7nh \'ae\'b9o cu\'e9c c
\'b8ch m\'b9ng n\'ad\'edc Nam, \'ae\'cbp tan ch\'d5 \'ae\'e9 t\'b5n b\'b9o v\'b5 
\par 
\par }\pard \s22\qj \li0\ri0\sa80\sl-270\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 h\'b9ch s\'b8ch m\'b5 nh\'f7ng k\'ce t\'f9 x\'adng l\'b5 b\'b6o h\'e9 ta b\'bet ta ch\'deu.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 .....
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-274\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 "Th\'cbt l\'b5 nh\'f4c nh\'b7 th\'cbm t\'d6, th\'cbt l\'b5 ch\'b8n ng\'b8n gh\'aa g\'edm, th\'cbt l\'b5 cay \'ae\'beng 
\'aa ch\'d2 xi\'d5t bao cho c\'b8c v\'de, n\'d5u t\'f5 nh\'f7ng t\'c7ng m\'a9y, t\'e6 ti\'aan mi ph\'b6i tr\'abng th\'cay d\'a9n t\'e9c m\'b5 c\'b8c v\'de \'ae\'b7 gi\'b5nh \'ae\'ad\'eec t\'f9 do nay ch\'deu ph\'cbn n\'ab l\'d6, \'ae\'cat n\'ad\'edc \'ae
\'b7 \'ae\'ad\'eec c\'b8c v\'de gi\'b6i tho\'b8t nay l\'a9m v\'b5o c\'b6nh n\'ab d\'dech, k\'ce k\'d5 t\'f4c ngai v\'b5ng c\'f1a c\'b8c v\'de nay s\'e8ng trong \'ad\'acn h\'ccn.
\par "M\'c6c d\'c7u l\'d4 nghi kh\'abng cho ph\'d0p c\'b8c v\'de nguy\'aan th\'f1 n\'ad\'edc ta r\'eai kh\'e1i cung c\'cam, th\'d5 nh\'adng ch\'f3ng ta v\'c9n ph\'b6i \'aeau bu\'e5n nh\'cbn th\'cay r\'bbng v\'c9n c\'e3 nh\'f7ng b\'cbc qu\'a9n tr\'ad\'ebng ph
\'b6i l\'adu vong.
\par "N\'a8m 1407}{\cs17\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 1{\footnote \pard\plain \s28\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa60\sl-240\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {
\insrsid1378858 1) Cu\'e9c x\'a9m l\'ad\'eec c\'f1a nh\'b5 Minh b\'bet \'ae\'c7u n\'a8m 1406.}})}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 , T\'c7u (phong ki\'d5n) \'ae\'b8nh nhau v\'edi ta; nh\'ea \'fd ch\'dd \'ae\'e9c l\'cbp v\'b5 l\'dfng kh\'b8t khao t\'f9 do h\'acn l
\'b5 nh\'ea qu\'a9n \'ae\'abng s\'f8c m\'b9nh, n\'ad\'edc Nam \'ae\'b7 th\'beng. Chinh chi\'d5n l\'f3c \'ae\'e3 th\'d5 l\'b5 l\'b9i b\'bet \'ae\'c7u. Gi\'c6c bi\'d5t r\'bbng kh\'abng khu\'cat ph\'f4c \'ae\'ad\'eec ta b\'bbng uy l\'f9c, \'ae\'b7 d\'ef
ng chi\'d5n tranh hao m\'dfn. Tr\'c7n \'a7\'d5 Qu\'fc \'ae\'b7 l\'b7nh \'ae\'b9o d\'a9n Nam \'aeo\'b9t \'ae\'ad\'eec th\'beng l\'eei, sau th\'cay d\'a9n c\'efng ki\'d6t, \'ae\'e3i kh\'b8t, m\'b8u \'ae\'e6 x\'ad\'acng r\'aci. \'a4ng bi\'d5t r\'bbng gi\'c6
c ch\'d8 mu\'e8n h\'b9i m\'d7nh \'abng, v\'b5 ch\'f3ng b\'bet \'ae\'ad\'eec \'abng r\'e5i th\'d7 d\'a9n Nam s\'cf \'ae\'ad\'eec y\'aan \'e6n. V\'d7 v\'cby \'abng ra n\'e9p m\'d7nh; \'abng n\'e9p m\'d7nh \'ae\'d3 d\'a9n \'abng \'ae\'ec hao t\'e6
n sinh linh, x\'ad\'acng m\'b8u. B\'de c\'c7m t\'ef gi\'b6i \'aei, \'abng nh\'b6y xu\'e8ng s\'abng t\'f9 t\'f6. \'a4ng th\'b5 ch\'d5t vinh ch\'f8 kh\'abng s\'e8ng nh\'f4c. Ng\'b5y nay, m\'e7i bu\'e6i m\'c6t tr\'eai m\'e4c l\'aan l\'c6n xu\'e8ng, mu\'ab
n ngh\'d7n \'b8nh h\'b5o quang v\'b5ng \'e3ng qu\'a9y tr\'aan d\'dfng s\'abng trong n\'ad\'edc b\'b9c long lanh, t\'b9o n\'aan \'ae\'b5i k\'fb ni\'d6m v\'dcnh c\'f6u cho linh h\'e5n b\'cat di\'d6t c\'f1a con ng\'ad\'eai chi\'d5n b\'b9i v\'dc \'ae\'b9i 
\'ae\'e3...
\par "Ti\'d5p \'ae\'e3 l\'b5 H\'b5m Nghi, Th\'b5nh Th\'b8i v\'b5 Duy T\'a9n - ng\'ad\'eai \'eb ng\'abi ngay tr\'ad\'edc mi. Ch\'ddnh nh\'f7ng k\'ce x\'adng x\'adng l\'b5 t\'abn tr\'e4ng phong t\'f4c, lu\'cbt l\'d6 n\'ad\'edc ta \'ae\'b7 \'ae\'b5y \'b6i ba v
\'de v\'b5 mai \'ae\'a9y s\'cf d\'efng mi l\'b5m m\'e3n \'ae\'e5 rao h\'b5ng thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea, c\'e6 \'ae\'e9ng \'ae\'d5 qu\'e8c. C\'e3 th\'cay kh\'abng, con! Ch\'bcng th\'d3 bao gi\'ea trong ni\'aan gi\'b8m n\'ad\'edc mi l\'b9i c\'e3 m\'e9t vua Nam n
\'b5o ch\'deu l\'b5m t\'abi t\'ed \'ae\'d5n nh\'ad mi, l\'b9i c\'e3 m\'e9t cu\'e9c ng\'f9 gi\'b8 tu\'c7n du n\'b5o th\'b6m h\'b9i \'ae\'d5n m\'f8c n\'b5y. Tr\'ad\'edc \'ae\'a9y, mi \'ae\'b7 t\'f5ng ph\'b9m t\'e9i b\'b8ng b\'e6 l\'b5 b\'d6 l\'aan b\'b5n th
\'ea linh thi\'aang c\'f1a \'abng v\'b6i h\'d7nh \'b6nh gh\'aa t\'ebm c\'f1a th\'bbng da tr\'beng ng\'b8i ng\'f1 v\'b5 b\'f4ng ph\'d6 n\'e4, n\'e3 s\'c6c l\'aan m\'efi t\'e1i, \'edn m\'efi th\'a9y ma. T\'b9i sao, \'f5, t\'b9i sao mi l\'b9i l\'b5m th\'d5
? Nay mi l\'b9i s\'bep l\'c8n xa t\'abn mi\'d5u. Tay mi s\'cf kh\'abng th\'bep h\'ad\'acng v\'b5o nh\'f7ng ti\'d5t \'ae\'c7u xu\'a9n, \'ae\'c7u thu n\'f7a. Mi s\'cf kh\'abng t\'f9 tay m\'eb h\'ad\'acng \'b8n d\'a9ng hoa qu\'b6 \'ae\'c7u m\'efa v\'b5 c\'f3
ng c\'acm m\'edi n\'f7a. V\'c9n hay, con \'b9! r\'bbng t\'cat c\'b6 nh\'f7ng c\'b8i \'cay ch\'bcng qua \'ae\'d2u l\'b5 nghi l\'d4 c\'e6 h\'f1 ! nh\'adng mi c\'f2ng th\'f5a bi\'d5t r\'bbng ch\'d8 c\'dfn \'ae\'e9c ngh\'dca v\'f4 \'ae\'e3 l\'b5 mi c\'dfn l
\'b5m \'ae\'ad\'eec v\'edi t\'e6 ti\'aan v\'b5 mi c\'f2ng ch\'d8 c\'dfn \'ae\'e9c c\'b8i uy t\'ddn \'ae\'e3 m\'b5 th\'abi tr\'ad\'edc m\'bet th\'c7n d\'a9n.
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 "Gi\'ea th\'d7 mi l\'b9i s\'bep l\'b5m t\'d6 h\'b9i h\'acn n\'f7a. Mi s\'bep ca ng\'eei c\'abng \'ae\'f8c c\'f1a nh\'f7
ng \'ae\'f8a b\'e3c l\'e9t v\'b5 hi\'d5p \'ae\'b8p d\'a9n mi. Mi s\'bep ph\'ab tr\'ad\'acng s\'f9 th\'denh v\'ad\'eeng c\'f1a \'ae\'cat n\'ad\'edc mi, c\'b8i th\'denh v\'ad\'eeng \'ae\'ad\'eec s\'bep \'ae\'c6t \'ae\'a9u ra \'ae\'cay trong tr\'dd t\'ad\'eb
ng t\'ad\'eeng qu\'b8 gi\'b5u c\'f1a b\'e4n b\'e3c l\'e9t. Mi s\'bep t\'a9ng b\'e8c c\'abng \'acn v\'ab ng\'c7n v\'b5 t\'ad\'ebng t\'ad\'eeng c\'f1a n\'d2n v\'a8n minh \'ae\'b7 th\'a9m nh\'cbp s\'acn h\'b5 x\'b7 t\'bec c\'f1a mi b\'bbng m\'f2i nh\'e4n c
\'f1a l\'ad\'eci l\'aa v\'b5 b\'bbng h\'e4ng s\'f3ng ca-n\'abng.
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-276\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 "\'a4i, nh\'d7n, h\'b7y nh\'d7n n\'b5o, \'ae\'f8a con th\'b6m th\'ad\'acng kia \'aci! H\'b7y nh\'d7n quanh mi! Th\'ca
y ch\'a8ng Trung Hoa \'aeang th\'f8c t\'d8nh, Nh\'cbt B\'b6n \'aeang duy t\'a9n...? Th\'cay ch\'a8ng to\'b5n c\'c7u \'aeang ti\'d5n, ch\'d8 c\'e3 d\'a9n mi l\'b5, nh\'ea mi v\'b5 l\'f2 quan th\'ad\'eeng c\'f1a mi, c\'f8 ph\'b6i ch\'d7m ng\'cbp m\'b7
i trong v\'f2ng l\'c7y d\'e8t n\'b8t v\'b5 t\'abi \'ae\'dfi kh\'e8n n\'b9n?
\par "H\'b7y nh\'d7n Tri\'d2u Ti\'aan, Ai C\'cbp v\'b5 }{\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'ca}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 n \'a7\'e9, t\'cat c\'b6 c\'b8c n\'ad\'edc \'ae\'e3 \'ae\'d2u \'aeang \'ae\'f8ng l\'aan \'ae\'dfi h\'e1i quy\'d2n l\'eei, c\'abng l\'fd v\'b5 t\'f9
 do!
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-276\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 "Ch\'ddnh gi\'f7a l\'f3c \'ae\'e3 th\'d7 mi... Im... Nghe k
\'d7a! Nghe th\'cay ch\'a8ng... Nghe th\'cay ch\'a8ng nh\'f7ng ti\'d5ng k\'aau g\'b5o...? A! Ng\'ad\'eai ta \'ae\'d5n kia k\'d7a, \'ae\'abng qu\'b8, t\'cat c\'b6 nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai d\'a9n n\'ad\'edc Nam \'ae\'b7 b\'de thi\'d6t m\'b9ng cho cu\'e9c chi
\'d5n tranh \'eb ch\'a9u \'a2u. Ng\'ad\'eai ta \'ae\'d5n \'ae\'dfi nh\'f7ng g\'d7 m\'b5 b\'e4n quan th\'c7y mi \'ae\'b7 c\'efng mi h\'f8a h\'d1n v\'edi ng\'ad\'eai ta, anh em ng\'ad\'eai ta. Tr\'b6 l\'eai ng\'ad\'eai ta \'aei n\'b5o! A! Ng\'ad\'eai ta gi
\'cbn d\'f7, ng\'ad\'eai ta b\'e1 \'aei.
\par }\pard \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\insrsid1378858 "B\'a9y gi\'ea th\'d7 ng\'ad\'eai ta quay l\'adng \'aei r\'e5i, ng\'ad\'eai ta \'aeang \'aei \'ae\'d5n ph\'dda \'ae\'bb
ng kia. C\'e3 th\'cay ng\'ad\'eai ta kh\'abng? \'a7\'bbng kia \'cay, n\'aci m\'c6t tr\'eai \'aeang m\'e4c huy ho\'b5ng kh\'abn xi\'d5t, n\'aci tung bay ki\'aau h\'b7nh l\'b8 c\'ea Nh\'a9n \'ae\'b9o v\'b5 Lao \'ae\'e9ng. \'a7\'cay! Ch\'ddnh \'ae\'cay l\'b5
 n\'aci y\'aan ngh\'d8 t\'a9m linh nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai \'ae\'b7 khu\'cat, l\'b5 t\'ad\'acng lai c\'f1a d\'a9n t\'e9c m\'b5 mi \'ae\'b7 ph\'f4ng s\'f9 ch\'bcng ra g\'d7!
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 "G\'b5 s\'bep g\'b8y s\'b8ng. Sao B\'bec \'ae\'c8u ti\'d5
n ngang tr\'eai. Nh\'b9c ti\'aan \'aeang gi\'f4c gi\'b7 ta. Th\'abi, ch\'b5o!".
\par M\'e5 h\'abi nh\'edp nh\'b8p \'ae\'c9m tr\'b8n v\'de ch\'f3a th\'ad\'eeng \'aeang ng\'f1. Ng\'b5i mu\'e8n k\'aau l\'aan. Nh\'adng kh\'abng k\'aau \'ae\'ad\'eec. L\'ad\'eci ng\'b5i l\'ddu l\'b9i v\'d7 s\'ee.
\par M\'e9t quan ho\'b9n b\'ad\'edc v\'b5o, khom khom c\'b8i l\'adng ba l\'c7n, r\'e5i the th\'d0 c\'b8i gi\'e4ng \'ae\'b5n b\'b5:
\par - Ngai d\'ad\'edi}{\cs17\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 1{\footnote \pard\plain \s28\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa60\sl-240\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {
\insrsid1378858 1) }{\i\insrsid1378858 Tr\'abne sous}{\insrsid1378858 : Ch\'aci ch\'f7, do d\'dech s\'b8t t\'f5ng ch\'f7 t\'f5 "B\'d6 h\'b9" sang ti\'d5ng Ph\'b8p. H\'b9: d\'ad\'edi l\'b5 "sous", m\'b5 "sous" th\'d7 l\'b9i c\'f2ng c\'e3 ngh\'dca l\'b5
 xu. V\'cby \'eb \'ae\'a9y c\'e3 th\'d3 hi\'d3u }{\i\insrsid1378858 Ngai d\'ad\'edi}{\insrsid1378858 , c\'f2ng c\'e3 th\'d3 hi\'d3u Ngai xu... Ch\'d8 chuy\'d3n \'ae\'ad\'eec ph\'c7n n\'b5o \'fd \'ae\'efa v\'b5 ch\'a9m ch\'e4c nhi\'d2u m\'c6t sang b\'b6n d
\'dech ti\'d5ng Vi\'d6t.}})}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 ! \'a7\'b7 c\'e3 l\'d6nh l\'aan \'ae\'ad\'eang c\'f1a T\'dfa Kh\'a9m truy\'d2n sang r\'e5i \'ae\'cay \'b9!
\par }\pard\plain \s24\qr \fi397\li0\ri567\sb360\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin567\lin0\itap0 \f38\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 \~NGUY\'d4N \'b8I QU\'e8C
\par }\pard\plain \s26\ql \li0\ri567\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin567\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 B\'b8o }{\i\insrsid1378858 L'Humanit\'d0,}{\insrsid1378858 
\par ng\'b5y 24-6-1922.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 
