c K\'fa), v\'d7 m\'f4c \'ae\'ddch t\'e8ng ti\'d2n, \'a7\'b8cl\'ac \'ae\'b7 b\'bet b\'ed, giam c\'c7m v\'b5 k\'d5t \'b8n v\'ab c\'ed ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8. H\'ben \'ae\'b7 gi\'b8ng nh\'f7ng c\'f3 \'ae\'cam v\'b5 nh\'f7ng tr\'cbn \'ae\'dfn roi v\'b5o nh
\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8 b\'de g\'e4i \'aei l\'ddnh "t\'d7nh nguy\'d6n". H\'ben \'ae\'e8i x\'f6 t\'b5n \'b8c v\'edi nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai l\'ddnh l\'d6 b\'b6n x\'f8, n\'bem t\'e3c h\'e4 l\'abi x\'d2nh x\'d6ch, \'ae\'cbp \'ae\'c7u h\'e4 v\'b5o t\'ad
\'eang nh\'b5 c\'f1a h\'ben.   
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 H\'ben \'ae\'a9m l\'ad\'eci ki\'d5m v\'b5o nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'ea
i t\'ef khi\'d5n h\'e4 b\'cat t\'d8nh nh\'a9n 
\par }\pard \qj \li0\ri0\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 s\'f9.   
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-284\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Vi\'aan c\'abng s\'f8 \'a7\'b8cl\'ac \'ae\'b8nh m\'e9t ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8 b\'bbng roi s\'bet v\'b5 l\'b5m g\'b7
y hai ng\'e3n tay c\'f1a ng\'ad\'eai n\'b5y. H\'ben d\'efng roi \'ae\'b8nh t\'f3i b\'f4i m\'e9t vi\'aan \'ae\'e9i ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8. H\'ben ch\'abn \'ae\'d5n t\'cbn c\'e6 nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai l\'ddnh l\'d6 b\'b6n x\'f8 n\'b5o kh\'abng l\'b5m v\'f5
a l\'dfng v\'b5 ch\'d8 cho \'ae\'b5o h\'e4 l\'aan khi h\'e4 \'ae\'b7 g\'c7n ch\'d5t. H\'ben d\'efng g\'cby \'ae\'a9m l\'dfi m\'bet m\'e9t vi\'aan \'ae\'e9i ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8 kh\'b8c.   
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-284\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 Cu\'e8i c\'efng cu\'e9c kh\'ebi ngh\'dca Th\'b8i Nguy\'aan 
\'ae\'b7 b\'efng n\'e6 ch\'e8ng l\'b9i s\'f9 t\'b5n \'b8c c\'f1a h\'ben v\'b5 m\'b8u ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8 l\'c9n m\'b8u ng\'ad\'eai Ph\'b8p \'ae\'b7 \'ae\'e6. Bao nhi\'aau m\'b8u \'ae\'b7 ch\'b6y, bao nhi\'aau nh\'b5 \'ae\'b7 b\'de ph\'b8, v\'b5
 bao nhi\'aau ng\'ad\'eai v\'ab t\'e9i \'ae\'b7 b\'de ch\'c6t \'ae\'c7u.   
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-284\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'a7\'d3 th\'ad\'ebng nh\'f7ng c\'abng tr\'b9ng \'ae\'b8
ng khen \'cay c\'f1a vi\'aan c\'abng s\'f8 \'a7\'b8cl\'ac, ng\'ad\'eai ta phong h\'ben ch\'f8c ch\'b8nh gi\'b8m kh\'b6o c\'b8c tr\'ad\'eang l\'edn \'eb H\'b5 N\'e9i v\'b5 b\'e6 nhi\'d6m h\'ben l\'b5m \'ae\'e6ng l\'fd v\'a8n ph\'dfng c\'f1a vi\'aan th\'e8
ng s\'f8 B\'bec K\'fa.   
\par }\pard \qj \li0\ri0\sa80\sl-284\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\expnd0\expndtw-4\insrsid1378858 B\'b8o }{\i\f37\fs20\expnd0\expndtw-4\insrsid1378858 L'Humanit\'d0 }{
