\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-284\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 N\'d5u vi\'aan s\'dc quan \'a7\'f8c Ph\'abn Sephen b\'de t\'ef 20 n\'a8m kh\'e6 sai v\'d7 \'ae\'b7 t\'b5n s\'b8t ng\'ad
\'eai \'eb R\'abngc\'ac th\'d7 vi\'aan c\'abng s\'f8 \'a7\'b8cl\'ac \'ae\'b8ng ph\'b6i t\'ef \'ddt nh\'cat l\'b5 g\'cap ba l\'c7n 20 n\'a8m kh\'e6 sai v\'d7 t\'e9i \'b8c c\'f1a h\'ben.   
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Nh\'adng c\'b8c b\'b9n c\'e3 bi\'d5t s\'e8 ph\'cbn c\'f1a h\'ben ta nh\'ad th\'d5 n\'b5o kh\'abng?   
\par H\'ben \'ae\'b7 tr\'eb th\'b5nh u\'fb vi\'aan H\'e9i \'ae\'e5ng th\'b5nh ph\'e8 S\'b5i G\'dfn, ngh\'dca l\'b5 ng\'ad\'eai c\'e9ng t\'b8c tr\'f9c ti\'d5p c\'f1a c\'b8c ng\'b5i Xar\'ab v\'b5 Ut\'acr\'a9y v\'b5 l\'b5m ch\'f1 v\'cbn m\'d6nh nh\'f7ng ng\'ad
