\'b6N\line V\'b5 THANH NI\'a3N TRUNG QU\'e8C
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Phong tr\'b5o thanh ni\'aan x\'b7 h\'e9i ch\'f1 ngh\'dca m\'ed
i b\'bet \'ae\'c7u \'eb Trung Qu\'e8c t\'f5 n\'a8m 1920. Nh\'adng t\'f5 \'ae\'e3 v\'b5 ch\'d8 c\'e3 t\'f5 \'ae\'e3 th\'d7 nh\'f7ng thanh ni\'aan m\'b8cx\'ddt, nh\'f7ng thanh ni\'aan v\'ab ch\'ddnh ph\'f1 ch\'f1 ngh\'dca, nh\'f7ng nghi\'d6p \'aeo\'b5n x
\'b7 h\'e9i ch\'f1 ngh\'dca v\'b5 nh\'f7ng c\'abng \'aeo\'b5n m\'edi gia nh\'cbp c\'b8c h\'e9i li\'aan hi\'d6p. V\'b5 ch\'d8 t\'f5 th\'b8ng 11 n\'a8m 1921, nh\'f7ng thanh ni\'aan c\'e9ng s\'b6n m\'edi th\'b5nh l\'cbp \'ae\'ad\'eec c\'b8c t\'e6 ch\'f8c 
\'ae\'e9c l\'cbp c\'f1a h\'e4. 5 ngh\'d7n thanh ni\'aan \'ae\'b7 t\'cbp h\'eep d\'ad\'edi ng\'e4n c\'ea b\'f3a li\'d2m. H\'e5i th\'b8ng 5 n\'a8m 1922, h\'e4 tri\'d6u t\'cbp \'a7\'b9i h\'e9i to\'b5n Trung Qu\'e8c. 16 di\'d4n gi\'b6 \'ae\'b7 l\'aan ph\'b8
t bi\'d3u 
\par }\pard \qj \li0\ri0\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 tr\'aan di\'d4n \'ae\'b5n \'a7\'b9i h\'e9i. H\'e4 \'ae\'b7 b\'c7u ra m\'e9t Ban ch\'cap h\'b5nh g\'e5m 25 \'ae\'b9i bi\'d3u, thay m
\'c6t cho 15 t\'e6 ch\'f8c, v\'b5 2 \'ae\'b9i bi\'d3u thay m\'c6t cho c\'b8c thanh ni\'aan \'eb ngo\'b5i n\'ad\'edc. H\'e4 th\'abng qua m\'e9t b\'b6n \'aei\'d2u l\'d6 g\'e5m 35 \'aei\'d3m.  
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'a7\'b9i h\'e9i k\'aau g\'e4i c\'b8c c\'abng nh\'a9n v\'b5 lao \'ae\'e9ng to\'b5n Trung Qu\'e8c, c\'b8c sinh vi\'aan, c
\'b8c thanh ni\'aan nam n\'f7, t\'cat c\'b6 nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai c\'e3 t\'ad t\'ad\'ebng \'ae\'e9c l\'cbp, c\'b8c binh l\'ddnh c\'f2ng nh\'ad c\'b6nh s\'b8t.   
\par C\'ad\'acng l\'dcnh c\'f1a t\'e6 ch\'f8c \'ae\'e3 g\'e5m c\'e3 4 ph\'c7n sau \'ae\'a9y:   
\par }\pard\plain \s4\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-260\slmult0\keepn\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\outlinelevel3\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \b\f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 A. V\'d2 ch\'ddnh tr\'de   
