\'aan 18 tu\'e6i tr\'eb
\par }\pard\plain \s25\qj \li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f38\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\insrsid1378858 xu\'e8ng, 8 gi\'ea cho nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai \'ae\'b7 \'ae\'f1
 tu\'e6i thanh ni\'aan). 2. Tu\'c7n l\'d4 ngh\'d8 m\'e9t ng\'b5y. 3. B\'e1 ch\'d5 \'ae\'e9 h\'eep \'ae\'e5ng c\'b8 nh\'a9n k\'fd gi\'f7a ch\'f1 v\'b5 th\'ee. 4. B\'b6o h\'e9 lao \'ae\'e9ng cho c\'abng nh\'a9n. 5. Lao \'ae\'e9ng ngang nhau th\'d7 tr\'b6 l
\'ad\'acng ngang nhau.   
\par }\pard\plain \s4\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\keepn\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\outlinelevel3\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \b\f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 C. V\'d2 gi\'b8o d\'f4c   
