\'b8c cu\'e9c th\'b6o lu\'cbn v\'d2 \'ae\'cau tranh giai c\'cap.   
\par }\pard\plain \s4\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\keepn\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\outlinelevel3\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \b\f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 D. V\'d2 vi\'d6c gi\'b8o d\'f4c \'eb
 nh\'b5 tr\'ad\'eang   
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\expnd0\expndtw-4\insrsid1378858 S\'f6a \'ae\'e6i ch\'ad\'acng tr\'d7nh gi
\'b8o d\'f4c, gi\'b8o d\'f4c ph\'e6 th\'abng b\'bet bu\'e9c, v.v..   
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'a7\'b9i h\'e9i k\'d5t th\'f3c b\'bbng b\'b5i "Qu\'e8c t
\'d5 ca". 
\par }\pard\plain \s24\qr \fi397\li0\ri567\sb360\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin567\lin0\itap0 \f38\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 Nguy\'d4n \'b8i qu\'e8c  
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 
\par T.B. M\'b7i khi t\'edi Pari, ch\'f3ng t\'abi m\'edi nh\'cbn \'ae\'ad\'eec s\'e8 b\'b8o }{\i\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Ti\'d2n phong }{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'ae\'c7u ti\'aan, vi\'d5t b\'bbng ch\'f7 Trung Qu\'e8c.   
\par 
\par }\pard\plain \s26\ql \li0\ri567\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin567\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 B\'b8o }{\i\insrsid1378858 L'Humanit\'d0,}{\insrsid1378858   

\par ng\'b5y 19-8-1922.            
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 
\par }\pard\plain \s21\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \b\f39\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 \column 
\par }\pard\plain \s20\qc \li0\ri0\sb1400\sa440\sl-380\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \b\f38\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 "CH\'f1 NGH\'dcA VI\'a7A"\line C\'dfN \'a7ANG TI\'d5
P DI\'d4N
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-296\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 \~H\'b5ng ngh\'d7n d\'a9n b\'b6n x\'f8 b\'de c\'ad\'ecng b
\'f8c \'ae\'c8y v\'b5o qu\'a9n \'ae\'e9i \'ae\'d3 b\'b6o v\'d6 nh\'f7ng k\'d0t b\'b9c cho nh\'f7ng k\'ce b\'e3c l\'e9t m\'d7nh.
\par Ch\'f3ng ta nh\'ed r\'bbng, \'ae\'d3 bu\'e9c nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai ch\'a9u Phi th\'f9c hi\'d6n "ngh\'dca v\'f4 c\'f1a m\'d7nh", ng\'ad\'eai ta \'ae\'b7 \'ae\'e8t nh\'b5 c\'ad\'edp c\'f1a c\'f1a h\'e4 v\'b5 sau \'ae\'e3, nh\'f7ng n\'b9n nh\'a9n \'cay b\'de
 b\'bet \'aei l\'ddnh cho \'ae\'e9i qu\'a9n ti\'aan phong c\'f1a }{\i\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 n\'d2n v\'a8n minh.
\par }{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 "Vi\'d6c d\'b9y d\'e7" ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8 b\'bbng nh\'f7ng c\'f3 \'ae\'b8 \'ae\'ddt v\'b5 \'ae\'b8nh \'ae\'cbp \'ae\'b7 tr\'eb th\'b5nh th\'e3i quen c\'f1a nh\'f7ng v\'de tr\'f8 danh c\'f1a ch\'f3ng ta.
\par Anh Nah\'abng b\'cat h\'b9nh, "ng\'ad\'eai b\'de gi\'d5t hai l\'c7n" - l\'c7n \'ae\'c7u do \'ae\'b9i u\'fd Vi\'aea v\'b5 sau \'ae\'e3, l\'b5 do b\'b8c s\'dc, ng\'ad\'eai \'ae\'ad\'eec l\'d6nh m\'e6 x\'b8c v\'b5 x\'b8c \'ae\'denh nguy\'aan nh\'a9n c\'b8
i ch\'d5t c\'f1a anh, ng\'ad\'eai \'ae\'b7 kh\'abng ng\'c7n ng\'b9i \'ae\'b8nh c\'bep v\'b5 gi\'cau di h\'b5i c\'f1a ng\'ad\'eai ch\'d5t \'ae\'e3 \'ae\'d3 l\'cap li\'d5m cho k\'ce gi\'d5t ng\'ad\'eai, - than \'abi, kh\'abng ph\'b6i l\'b5 n\'b9n nh\'a9n 
\'ae\'c7u ti\'aan c\'f1a ch\'f1 ngh\'dca qu\'a9n phi\'d6t th\'f9c d\'a9n! M\'e9t b\'b9n \'ae\'e5ng nghi\'d6p c\'f1a ch\'f3ng t\'abi \'eb thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea cho bi\'d5t v\'d2 m\'e9t tr\'ad\'eang h\'eep bi th\'b6m kh\'b8c.
\par }{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858\charrsid8535090 "L\'c7n n\'b5y, - anh \'cay n\'e3i, - s\'f9 vi\'d6c x\'b6y ra \'eb Med\'abng Car\'aa, trong trung \'aeo\'b5n b\'e9 binh th\'f8 5. N\'b9n nh\'a9n l\'b5 m\'e9t ng\'ad\'eai l\'ddnh tr\'ce t\'aan l\'b5 Terie, sinh qu
\'b8n \'eb T\'aan\'d0t, b\'de g\'e4i ra l\'ddnh n\'a8m 1921. C\'b8i ch\'d5t c\'f1a anh ta th\'cbt l\'b5 \'ae\'c6c bi\'d6t bi \'ae\'b8t. Ng\'b5y m\'e5ng 5 th\'b8ng 8, Terie \'ae\'d5n qu\'a9n y trung \'aeo\'b5n xin thu\'e8c t\'c8y. Anh nh\'cbn thu\'e8
c, hay n\'e3i cho \'ae\'f3ng h\'acn,}{\i\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858\charrsid8535090 
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \li0\ri0\sa80\sl-296\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 anh \'ae\'b7 nh\'cbn c\'b8i m\'b5 anh cho l\'b5 thu\'e8c t\'c8
y. Ng\'ad\'eai l\'ddnh u\'e8ng thu\'e8c v\'b5 sau v\'b5i gi\'ea th\'d7 ch\'d5t m\'e9t c\'b8ch \'aeau \'ae\'edn kh\'f1ng khi\'d5p. \'a4ng Terie, cha c\'f1a anh \'cay nh\'cbn \'ae\'ad\'eec m\'e9t b\'f8c \'aei\'d6n ng\'ben ng\'f1i v\'d2 c\'b8i ch\'d5t c\'f1
a con trai b\'b8o r\'bbng l\'d4 an t\'b8ng s\'cf \'ae\'ad\'eec t\'e6 ch\'f8c v\'b5o ng\'b5y h\'abm sau. \'a7i\'aan d\'b9i v\'d7 \'aeau \'ae\'edn, ng\'ad\'eai cha \'ae\'b8ng th\'ad\'acng v\'e9i v\'b7 \'ae\'d5n Angi\'aa, \'ae\'d5n trung \'aeo\'b5n b\'e9
 binh th\'f8 5 \'ae\'e3ng \'eb Med\'abng Car\'aa, v\'b5 t\'b9i \'ae\'a9y, \'abng bi\'d5t x\'b8c \'ae\'f8a con trai duy nh\'cat c\'f1a \'abng \'aeang \'eb trong qu\'a9n y vi\'d6n Mai\'ab. L\'b5m th\'d5 n\'b5o m\'b5 n\'e3 l\'b9i r\'aci v\'b5o \'ae\'cay? T
\'b9i sao ng\'ad\'eai ta l\'b9i \'ae\'ada n\'e3 v\'d2 Mai\'ab? Ph\'b6i ch\'a8ng l\'b5 v\'d7 c\'c7n ph\'b6i t\'d7m ra nguy\'aan nh\'a9n th\'f9c s\'f9 c\'f1a c\'b8i ch\'d5t v\'b5 m\'ab t\'b6 n\'e3 nh\'ad m\'e9t c\'b8i ch\'d5t \'ae\'e9t ng\'e9t tr\'aan \'ae
\'ad\'eang h\'b5nh qu\'a9n?
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 T\'b9i qu\'a9n y vi\'d6n, khi ng\'ad\'eai cha b\'cat h\'b9
nh \'ae\'d2 ngh\'de \'ae\'ad\'eec ph\'d0p nh\'d7n x\'b8c con trai th\'d7 ng\'ad\'eai ta b\'b6o \'abng ta }{\i\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 h\'b7y \'ae\'eei}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 . Sau \'ae\'e3, m\'e9t v\'de thi\'d5u t\'b8 xu\'cat hi\'d6n v\'b5 n\'e3i r\'bb
ng vi\'d6c ph\'c9u nghi\'d6m \'ae\'b7 \'ae\'ad\'eec ti\'d5n h\'b5nh, nh\'adng nguy\'aan nh\'a9n c\'f1a c\'b8i ch\'d5t kh\'abng r\'e2 v\'b5 \'abng ta kh\'abng th\'d3 cho ph\'d0p ng\'ad\'eai cha nh\'d7n th\'cay x\'b8c ng\'ad\'eai con trai c\'f1a \'abng.

\par Theo nh\'f7ng tin t\'f8c cu\'e8i c\'efng th\'d7 ng\'ad\'eai ta bi\'d5t r\'bbng khi \'abng Terie y\'aau c\'c7u vi\'aan ch\'d8 huy trung \'aeo\'b5n b\'e9 binh th\'f8 5 gi\'b6i th\'ddch, \'abng ta \'ae\'ad\'eec tr\'b6 l\'eai nh\'ad sau: "Con trai c\'f1a \'ab
ng ch\'d5t v\'d7 b\'de ng\'e9 \'ae\'e9c".
\par }\pard\plain \s24\qr \fi397\li0\ri567\sb360\sa240\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin567\lin0\itap0 \f38\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 NGuy\'d4n \'b8i qu\'e8c
\par }\trowd \lastrow \ts11\trgaph108\trleft-108\trftsWidth1\trpaddl108\trpaddr108\trpaddfl3\trpaddfr3 \clvertalt\clbrdrt\brdrtbl \clbrdrl\brdrtbl \clbrdrb\brdrtbl \clbrdrr\brdrtbl \cltxlrtb\clftsWidth3\clwWidth3652\clshdrawnil \cellx3544\clvertalt\clbrdrt
\brdrtbl \clbrdrl\brdrtbl \clbrdrb\brdrtbl \clbrdrr\brdrtbl \cltxlrtb\clftsWidth3\clwWidth3544\clshdrawnil \cellx7088\pard\plain \s26\ql \li0\ri317\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin317\lin0 
\f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 B\'b8o }{\i\insrsid1378858 L'Humanit\'d0,}{\insrsid1378858  ng\'b5y 7-9-1922.
\par In trong s\'b8ch: H\'e5 Ch\'dd Minh,\~
\par }{\i\insrsid1378858 Nh\'f7ng b\'b5i vi\'d5t v\'b5 n\'e3i ch\'e4n l\'e4c,
\par }{\insrsid1378858 ti\'d5ng Nga, Nxb. Ch\'ddnh tr\'de qu\'e8c gia,
\par M\'b8txc\'acva, 1959, tr. 28-29.}{\b\insrsid1378858 \cell }\pard \s26\ql \li0\ri567\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin567\lin0 {\insrsid1378858 D\'dech theo b\'b5i in trong s\'b8ch
\par }{\i\insrsid1378858 Nh\'f7ng b\'b5i vi\'d5t v\'b5 n\'e3i ch\'e4n l\'e4c.\cell }\pard\plain \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 \trowd \lastrow 
\ts11\trgaph108\trleft-108\trftsWidth1\trpaddl108\trpaddr108\trpaddfl3\trpaddfr3 \clvertalt\clbrdrt\brdrtbl \clbrdrl\brdrtbl \clbrdrb\brdrtbl \clbrdrr\brdrtbl \cltxlrtb\clftsWidth3\clwWidth3652\clshdrawnil \cellx3544\clvertalt\clbrdrt\brdrtbl \clbrdrl
\brdrtbl \clbrdrb\brdrtbl \clbrdrr\brdrtbl \cltxlrtb\clftsWidth3\clwWidth3544\clshdrawnil \cellx7088\row }\pard\plain \s26\ql \li0\ri567\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin567\lin0\itap0 
\f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 
\par 
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 
\par }\pard \qc \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\b\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 \column \line \line \line }{\f38\insrsid1378858\charrsid8535090 PH\'dfNG KI\'d3M DUY\'d6T \'eb \'a7\'a4NG D\'a6\'a5NG}
{\f38\insrsid1378858 \line }{\f38\insrsid1378858\charrsid8535090 
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 \~B\'b8o }{\i\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 L'Humanit\'d0}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 , s\'e8 ra ng\'b5y 13 th\'b8ng 9 c\'e3
 cho bi\'d5t \'eb Ma\'aeag\'b8txca v\'c9n c\'dfn ch\'d5 \'ae\'e9 ki\'d3m duy\'d6t th\'ad t\'f5 nghi\'aam kh\'bec, m\'c6c d\'ef b\'e8n n\'a8m \'ae\'b7 qua sau "cu\'e9c chi\'d5n tranh v\'d7 c\'abng l\'fd".
\par \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng d\'ad\'edi quy\'d2n cai tr\'de c\'f1a vi\'aan to\'b5n quy\'d2n L\'abng c\'f2ng ch\'bcng kh\'b8c g\'d7 Ma\'aeag\'b8txca d\'ad\'edi s\'f9 th\'e8ng tr\'de c\'f1a vi\'aan to\'b5n quy\'d2n G\'b8cbi: c\'f2ng nh\'f7ng b\'cat c\'abng, nh
\'f7ng vi\'d6c l\'e9ng quy\'d2n, nh\'f7ng v\'f4 tai ti\'d5ng, nh\'f7ng \'aei\'d2u \'ab nh\'f4c nh\'ad th\'d5.
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 Ch\'f3ng t\'abi \'ae\'ad\'eec bi\'d5t \'eb S\'eb B\'adu ch
\'ddnh v\'b5 S\'eb M\'cbt th\'b8m \'a7\'abng 
\par D\'ad\'acng \'ae\'ad\'eec l\'d6nh gi\'f7 nh\'f7ng g\'e3i v\'b5 th\'ad g\'f6i cho b\'b8o }{\i\insrsid1378858 Le Paria}{\insrsid1378858 , xu\'cat b\'b6n \'eb Pari, c\'f2ng nh\'ad nh\'f7ng th\'ad t\'ddn do b\'b8o n\'b5y g\'f6i v\'d2 \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng.

\par }{\expnd0\expndtw-4\insrsid1378858 Kh\'abng ph\'b6i l\'b5 ng\'c9u nhi\'aan m\'b5 h\'b5nh vi l\'b9m quy\'d2n n\'b5y l\'b9i x\'b6y ra \'ae\'f3ng l\'f3c vi\'aan quan cai tr\'de x\'b6o tr\'b8 B\'ab\'aeoanh v\'b5 ng\'ad\'eai tr\'ee l\'fd xu\'cat s\'bec c\'f1
a h\'ben, con r\'d3 vi\'aan B\'e9 tr\'ad\'ebng B\'e9 Thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea Anbe Xar\'ab, \'ae\'d5n S\'b5i G\'dfn.
\par Ngo\'b5i ra, ch\'f3ng ta v\'cap ph\'b6i lu\'cbt x\'a9m ph\'b9m quy\'d2n b\'cat kh\'b6 x\'a9m ph\'b9m th\'ad ri\'aang, v\'b5 c\'b8c vi\'aan cai tr\'de ti\'d5p t\'f4c gi\'f7 v\'b5 l\'f4c so\'b8t th\'ad ri\'aang.
\par }{\insrsid1378858 Nh\'ad th\'d5 l\'b5 ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8 b\'de gi\'d5t ch\'e3c, c\'ad\'edp ph\'b8 v\'b5 kh\'abng \'ae\'ad\'eec h\'ad\'ebng nh\'f7ng quy\'d2n s\'ac \'ae\'bcng nh\'cat: c\'b6 \'ae\'d5n quy\'d2n th\'ad t\'ddn! S\'f9 vi ph\'b9m t\'f9
 do c\'b8 nh\'a9n n\'b5y ch\'f8ng minh th\'aam ch\'ddnh s\'b8ch \'ae\'aa ti\'d6n c\'f1a 
\par b\'e4n m\'cbt th\'b8m v\'b5 ch\'ddnh s\'b8ch l\'b9m quy\'d2n \'aeang th\'e8ng tr\'de \'eb nh\'f7ng thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea ch\'f3ng ta.
\par }\pard\plain \s24\qr \fi397\li0\ri567\sb120\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin567\lin0\itap0 \f38\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 nguy\'d4n \'b8i qu\'e8c
\par }\pard\plain \ql \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\insrsid1378858\charrsid8535090 B\'b8o }{\i\f37\insrsid1378858\charrsid8535090 
L'Humanit\'d0,}{\f37\insrsid1378858\charrsid8535090 \line ng\'b5y 28-9-1922.}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858\charrsid8535090 
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \li0\ri0\sa80\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 
\par 
\par }\pard\plain \s20\qc \li0\ri0\sb1400\sa440\sl-380\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \b\f38\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 \line \line \line \line \line \'a7\'e5NG T\'a2M NH\'ca
T TR\'dd
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-292\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 - \'a7i ch\'ee n\'b5o \'ae\'cay, anh Hai?
\par - \'a7i ch\'ee \'a7\'abng. Th\'d5 c\'dfn anh, anh Ba?
\par - T\'abi c\'f2ng v\'cby. Th\'d5 c\'e3 m\'e3n h\'b5ng g\'d7 qu\'fd trong \'ae\'abi th\'f3ng b\'b6nh \'cay th\'d5?
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-292\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 - V\'b5ng m\'b7 c\'f3ng \'abng v\'b6i \'b9. C\'df
n anh, anh c\'e3 c\'b8i g\'d7 hay hay cho kh\'b8ch h\'b5ng n\'b5o?
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-292\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 - Tr\'c7u non \'ae\'d3 l\'b5m th\'acm v\'b5 \'ae\'d3 nhu
\'e9m h\'e5ng mi\'d6ng xinh c\'f1a c\'b8c ch\'de ch\'b5ng \'ae\'d1p \'ae\'cay.
\par Th\'d5 r\'e5i hai anh b\'b8n h\'b5ng b\'c6t im. M\'c6t tr\'eai \'ae\'f8ng b\'e3ng chi\'d5u \'ad\'edt \'ae\'c9m nh\'f7ng b\'bep tay b\'bep ch\'a9n l\'f9c l\'ad\'ecng g\'c7n nh\'ad \'ae\'d3 tr\'c7n c\'f1a hai anh. B\'e8n chi\'d5c th\'f3ng n\'c6ng n\'d2 \'ae
ung \'ae\'ada \'eb \'ae\'c7u hai \'ae\'dfn g\'b8nh tre \'ae\'c6t ngang tr\'aan vai ch\'b8y n\'beng. B\'f4i cu\'e8n l\'aan quanh b\'ad\'edc ch\'a9n tho\'a8n tho\'bet th\'b5nh m\'e9t th\'f8 m\'b5n s\'ad\'acng, l\'b5m cho m\'e4i c\'f6 \'ae\'e9ng c\'f1
a hai anh m\'ea \'b6o v\'b5 nh\'d7n xa l\'b9i c\'dfn c\'e3 v\'ce m\'fc thu\'cbt l\'b5 kh\'b8c.
\par - Nghe n\'b5y, ng\'ad\'eai anh em! - Ba n\'e3i.
\par - Tai t\'abi \'aeang l\'beng nghe l\'eai anh d\'b9y - Hai \'ae\'b8p.
\par - Hai ta c\'efng \'aei m\'e9t ch\'ee n\'b5y, theo c\'efng m\'e9t con \'ae\'ad\'eang n\'b5y, l\'b9i c\'e3 c\'efng m\'e9t m\'f4c \'ae\'ddch - l\'b5 b\'b8n h\'d5t h\'b5ng, c\'efng m\'e9t ch\'dd h\'ad\'edng - l\'b5 l\'b5m \'a8n l\'ad\'acng thi\'d6n ki\'d5m mi
\'d5ng c\'acm. Ph\'b6i th\'d5 kh\'abng n\'b5o?
\par - Anh n\'e3i mu\'abn ngh\'d7n l\'c7n \'ae\'f3ng.
