\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-286\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 \~Trong cu\'e9c chi\'d5n tranh v\'d7 c\'abng l\'fd}{
\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 28}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  \'ae\'d3 b\'b6o v\'d6 ch\'ddnh ngh\'dca, v\'a8n minh, v.v., ng\'ad\'eai ta \'ae\'b7 \'ae\'e9ng vi\'aan 10 v\'b9n ng\'ad\'eai Tuynidi \'aei l\'ddnh, v\'b5 60% trong s\'e8 \'ae\'e3 \'ae\'b7 kh\'ab
ng tr\'eb v\'d2 n\'f7a. Th\'eai \'ae\'e3, ng\'ad\'eai Tuynidi \'ae\'ad\'eec vu\'e8t ve v\'b5 tr\'d7u m\'d5n. Ng\'ad\'eai ta \'ae\'b7 ca ng\'eei r\'cat l\'b5 th\'bem thi\'d5t t\'d7nh anh em ru\'e9t th\'det gi\'f7a Ph\'b8p v\'b5 Tuynidi, "m\'e8i t\'d7nh ru
\'e9t th\'det \'ae\'b7 \'ae\'eai \'ae\'eai g\'ben ch\'c6t v\'b5o trong x\'ad\'acng m\'b8u v\'b5 quang vinh". Ng\'ad\'eai ta \'ae\'b7 th\'f9c h\'b5nh c\'b6 m\'e9t ch\'d5 \'ae\'e9 ki\'d3m duy\'d6t \'ae\'d3 c\'cam b\'b8o ch\'dd d\'ef th\'d5 n\'b5o c\'f2ng kh
\'abng \'ae\'ad\'eec l\'b5m ph\'cbt \'fd ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8.
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-286\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 Ng\'b5y nay, t\'d7nh anh em \'ae\'e3 \'ae\'b7 thay h\'d7nh 
\'ae\'e6i d\'b9ng. N\'e3 kh\'abng ph\'b6i ch\'d8 th\'d3 hi\'d6n b\'bbng nh\'f7ng c\'b8i vu\'e8t ve ho\'c6c nh\'f7ng c\'f6 ch\'d8 tr\'d7u m\'d5n m\'b5 th\'abi, n\'e3 c\'dfn th\'d3 hi\'d6n m\'e9t c\'b8ch h\'efng h\'e5n h\'acn b\'bbng nh\'f7ng ph\'b8t s\'f3
ng l\'f4c ho\'c6c nh\'f7ng tr\'cbn roi da kia. B\'bbng ch\'f8ng l\'b5 nh\'f7ng vi\'d6c sau \'ae\'a9y. Khi tr\'abng th\'cay ba ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8 cho c\'f5u v\'b5o \'a8n c\'e1 \'eb v\'ad\'ean c\'a9y \'abliu c\'f1a m\'d7nh, m\'e9t v\'de th\'f9c d\'a9
n Ph\'b8p li\'d2n b\'b6o v\'ee \'aei l\'cay s\'f3ng v\'b5 \'ae\'b9n ra. Khi v\'ee mang s\'f3ng \'ae\'b9n ra, th\'d7 v\'de \'aei khai ho\'b8 c\'f1a ch\'f3ng ta n\'cap v\'b5o m\'e9t b\'f4i c\'a9y, r\'e5i \'aeo\'b5ng! \'aeo\'b5ng! \'aeo\'b5ng! Ba ph\'b8t b
\'ben ra, th\'d5 l\'b5 ba ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8 ng\'b7 xu\'e8ng, b\'de th\'ad\'acng g\'c7n ch\'d5t.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-286\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 M\'e9t v\'de th\'f9c d\'a9n Ph\'b8p kh\'b8c c\'e3
 hai anh c\'abng nh\'a9n b\'b6n x\'f8 gi\'f3p vi\'d6c, t\'aan l\'b5 Am\'aeuni v\'b5 Ben Benkhia; hai anh n\'b5y h\'d7nh nh\'ad \'ae\'b7 c\'e3 l\'cay tr\'e9m v\'b5i ch\'efm nho. V\'de th\'f9c d\'a9n kia li\'d2n cho g\'e4i hai ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8 \'ae
\'d5n, r\'e5i d\'efng roi g\'a9n b\'df m\'b5 v\'f4t h\'e4 lia l\'dea cho \'ae\'d5n l\'f3c h\'e4 ch\'d5t ng\'cat. Khi hai ng\'ad\'eai n\'b5y t\'d8nh l\'b9i, quan l\'edn b\'b6o h\'e9 c\'f1a ch\'f3ng ta li\'d2n sai tr\'e3i gi\'cbt c\'b8nh khu\'fbu l\'b9i v
\'b5 treo h\'e4 l\'aan. D\'ef hai ng\'ad\'eai kh\'e8n kh\'e6 kia \'ae\'b7 b\'cat t\'d8nh nh\'a9n s\'f9, th\'d5 m\'b5 cu\'e9c h\'b5nh h\'b9 b\'d8 \'e6i \'ae\'e3 v\'c9n c\'f8 k\'d0o d\'b5i \'ae\'d5n b\'e8n ti\'d5ng \'ae\'e5ng h\'e5, m\'b7i \'ae\'d5n khi c
\'e3 m\'e9t ng\'ad\'eai \'eb c\'b9nh nh\'b5 ph\'b6n \'ae\'e8i m\'edi th\'abi.
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Hai ng\'ad\'eai \'ae\'b8ng th\'ad\'acng \'ae\'e3 \'ae\'ad\'eec khi\'aang \'ae\'d5n nh\'b5 th\'ad\'acng v\'b5 m\'e7i ng
\'ad\'eai b\'de c\'bet m\'cat m\'e9t b\'b5n tay, c\'dfn b\'b5n tay n\'f7a ch\'bcng bi\'d5t c\'e3 th\'d3 c\'f8u kh\'e1i \'ae\'ad\'eec kh\'abng.
\par T\'d7nh r...u...\'e9t th\'det nh\'ad th\'d5 \'ae\'cay!
\par Ch\'b6 l\'b5 \'abng Luyxi\'aang Xanh \'ae\'b8ng t\'abn k\'ddnh, v\'d7 \'ae\'b7 qu\'b8 b\'cbn v\'d2 vi\'d6c tr\'f4c xu\'cat nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai c\'e9ng s\'b6n v\'b5 c\'b8c nh\'b5 b\'b8o, n\'aan kh\'abng c\'e3 th\'d7 gi\'ea ngh\'dc \'ae\'d5n \'ae\'eai s
\'e8ng c\'f1a ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8 "\'ae\'ad\'eec b\'b6o h\'e9" c\'f1a \'abng \'ae\'cay m\'b5.
\par }\pard\plain \s24\qr \fi397\li0\ri567\sb360\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin567\lin0\itap0 \f38\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 nguy\'d4n \'b8i qu\'e8c
\par }\pard\plain \s26\ql \li0\ri567\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin567\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 B\'b8o }{\i\insrsid1378858 Le Paria,}{\insrsid1378858  s\'e8 8,

\par ng\'b5y 1-11-1922.
