\par }\pard\plain \s20\qc \li0\ri0\sb1400\sa440\sl-380\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \b\f38\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 S\'f9 TH\'deNH V\'a6\'eeNG C\'f1A \'a7\'a4NG D\'a6\'a5
NG\line D\'a6\'edI TRI\'d2U \'a7\'b9I M. L\'a4NG
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-294\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 \~Ng\'b5i A. Xar\'ab, v\'de B\'e9 tr\'ad\'ebng thu\'e9c 
\'ae\'dea v\'dc \'ae\'b9i c\'f1a ch\'f3ng ta, kh\'abng bao gi\'ea b\'e1 s\'e3t m\'e9t d\'dep n\'b5o \'ae\'d3 say s\'ada t\'b8n t\'f4ng v\'d2 s\'f9 th\'denh v\'ad\'eeng c\'f1a x\'f8 \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng, x\'f8 \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng "c\'f1a Ng\'b5i", v
\'b5 v\'d2 nh\'f7ng s\'f9 nghi\'d6p v\'dc \'ae\'b9i m\'b5 ng\'b5i c\'efng b\'e9 h\'b9 c\'f1a ng\'b5i \'ae\'b7 l\'b5m ho\'c6c \'aeang l\'b5m t\'b9i \'ae\'cay. \'a7\'d3 ch\'f8ng minh r\'bbng ng\'b5i ch\'d8 n\'e3i \'ae\'f3ng s\'f9 th\'cbt, ch\'d8 n\'e3i \'ae
\'e9c c\'e3 s\'f9 th\'cbt th\'abi, ch\'f3ng t\'abi c\'c7n \'ae\'ada ra cho ng\'b5i v\'b5 cho c\'b8c
\par  b\'b9n ch\'f3ng ta \'ae\'e4c nh\'f7ng \'aeo\'b9n sau \'ae\'a9y, tr\'ddch \'eb m\'e9t b\'f8c th\'ad c\'f1a \'ae\'b9i t\'b8 B\'d0cna g\'f6i cho b\'b8o }{\i\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 La R\'d0publique Fran}{\i\f41\fs18\charscalex97\insrsid1378858 \'e7}{
\i\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 aise}{\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 29}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 , ng\'b5y 6-12-1922 v\'b5, th\'ada ng\'b5i B\'e9 tr\'ad\'ebng, xin ng\'b5i c\'f8 y\'aan t\'a9m, \'ae\'b9i t\'b8 \'ae\'e3 kh\'abng ph\'b6i l\'b5 m\'e9t ng\'ad\'ea
i c\'e9ng s\'b6n \'ae\'a9u. B\'f8c th\'ad n\'e3i nh\'ad sau:
\par "S\'e8 h\'b5ng xu\'cat kh\'c8u c\'f1a \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng hi\'d6n \'aeang c\'c7m ch\'f5ng hay c\'dfn gi\'b6m xu\'e8ng n\'f7a. N\'a8m 1914, \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng \'ae\'b7 xu\'cat kh\'c8u 45.000kg t\'ac l\'f4a; 99.000 t\'can ng\'ab; 400 t\'can ch\'cc; n
\'a8m ngo\'b8i ch\'d8 xu\'cat kh\'c8u c\'e3 15.000 kg t\'ac l\'f4a; 32.000 t\'can ng\'ab; 156 t\'can ch\'cc.
\par }\pard \qj \li0\ri0\sa80\sl-294\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 "Ng\'ad\'eai ta c\'f2ng t\'ad\'ebng r\'bbng hi\'d6n nay ch\'ddnh ph\'f1 \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng \'aeang t\'ddch c\'f9c ti\'d5
n h\'b5nh nh\'f7ng c\'abng tr\'d7nh l\'edn c\'c7n thi\'d5t cho vi\'d6c khai th\'b8c thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea n\'b5y. Th\'d5 nh\'adng, t\'f5 n\'a8m 1914 \'ae\'d5n nay, ng\'ad\'eai ta kh\'abng h\'d2 \'ae\'c6t th\'aam \'ae\'ad\'eec }{\i\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 m
\'e9t kil\'abm\'d0t \'ae\'ad\'eang s\'bet n\'b5o, c\'f2ng kh\'abng khai th\'b8c th\'aam \'ae\'ad\'eec m\'e9t h\'d0cta ru\'e9ng \'ae\'cat n\'b5o}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 . C\'b8ch \'ae\'a9y m\'ad\'eai n\'a8m, \'abng Xar\'ab c\'e3 \'ae\'ada th\'abng qua m
\'e9t ch\'ad\'acng tr\'d7nh ki\'d5n thi\'d5t bao g\'e5m vi\'d6c x\'a9y d\'f9ng con \'ae\'ad\'eang s\'bet t\'f5 Vinh \'ae\'d5n \'a7\'abng H\'b5 v\'b5 b\'e8n h\'d6 th\'e8ng
\par \'ae\'b9i }{\f37\fs20\expnd0\expndtw-2\insrsid1378858 thu\'fb n\'abng; t\'cat c\'b6 nh\'f7ng c\'abng tr\'d7nh \'ae\'e3 \'ae\'d2u \'ae\'b7 ng\'f5ng t\'f5 h\'acn n\'a8m n\'a8m nay, l\'cay c\'ed l\'b5 kh\'abng c\'e3 kinh ph\'dd. Nh\'adng c\'f2ng trong th\'ea
i gian \'ae\'e3, x\'f8 \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng \'ae\'b7 d\'b5nh ra 65 tri\'d6u \'ae\'e5ng, 450 tri\'d6u phr\'a8ng \'ae\'d3 x\'a9y d\'f9ng \'ae\'ad\'eang s\'b8 v\'b5 dinh th\'f9. M\'eai \'abng Phagi\'aa h\'b7y suy ngh\'dc v\'d2 nh\'f7ng con s\'e8 \'ae\'e3
 xem! G\'c7n m\'e9t n\'f6a t\'fb \'ae\'b7 chi ph\'dd \'ae\'d3 x\'a9y d\'f9ng nh\'f7ng \'ae\'ad\'eang \'abt\'ab ch\'b9y m\'b5 tr\'aan \'ae\'e3 kh\'abng h\'d2 l\'adu th\'abng \'ae\'ad\'eec l\'cay m\'e9t t\'can h\'b5ng ho\'b8 n\'b5o; \'ae\'d3 d\'f9ng nh\'f7
ng dinh th\'f9 v\'b5 c\'abng s\'eb cho h\'bbng h\'b5 sa s\'e8 c\'abng ch\'f8c \'aeang sinh s\'abi n\'b6y n\'eb nh\'ad c\'a9y c\'e8i sum xu\'aa v\'efng nhi\'d6t \'ae\'edi; trong khi \'cay th\'d7 nh\'f7ng c\'abng tr\'d7nh \'ae\'b7 \'ae\'ad\'eec th\'f5a nh
\'cbn l\'b5 t\'e8i c\'c7n thi\'d5t v\'b5 \'ae\'b7 \'ae\'ad\'eec Ngh\'de vi\'d6n th\'abng qua r\'e5i, l\'b9i b\'de b\'e1 r\'aci}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 .
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 "Nh\'adng xin \'ae\'f5ng t\'ad\'ebng r\'bbng ng\'ad\'ea
i ta c\'e3 \'fd mu\'e8n thay \'ae\'e6i ph\'ad\'acng ph\'b8p \'eb \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng \'ae\'a9u. \'a7\'d3 ho\'b5n th\'b5nh ch\'ad\'acng tr\'d7nh 1912, \'a4ng L\'abng \'ae\'b7 xin ph\'d0p Ngh\'de vi\'d6n \'ae\'ad\'eec ph\'b8t h\'b5nh c\'abng tr\'b8i. Hi
\'d6n nay, \'abng ta l\'b9i c\'dfn xin ph\'d0p ph\'b8t h\'b5nh m\'e9t c\'abng tr\'b8i th\'f8 hai n\'f7a. Nh\'f7ng k\'ce hi\'d6n nay \'aeang l\'b7nh \'ae\'b9o vi\'d6c khai th\'b8c x\'f8 \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng xem ch\'f5ng \'ae\'b7 \'ae\'denh t\'a9m kh\'ab
ng mu\'e8n l\'b5m c\'b8i g\'d7 th\'cbt s\'f9 c\'e3 \'ddch l\'eei c\'b6, n\'d5u tr\'ad\'edc h\'d5t ng\'ad\'eai ta kh\'abng cho ph\'d0p h\'e4 \'ae\'ad\'eec vay n\'ee. C\'dfn \'ae\'e8i v\'edi ng\'a9n qu\'fc, \'ae\'e8i v\'edi nh\'f7ng d\'f9 tr\'f7 gom g\'e3p 
\'ae\'ad\'eec trong v\'b5 sau th\'eai k\'fa chi\'d5n tranh, th\'d7 h\'e4 s\'bdn s\'b5ng vung tay n\'d0m qua c\'f6a s\'e6, n\'d5u Ngh\'de vi\'d6n kh\'abng \'ae\'ada h\'e4 v\'b5o n\'d2n n\'d5p".
\par }\pard\plain \s24\qr \fi397\li0\ri567\sb360\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin567\lin0\itap0 \f38\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 Nguy\'d4n \'b8i qu\'e8c
\par }\pard\plain \s26\ql \li0\ri567\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin567\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 B\'b8o }{\i\insrsid1378858 La Vie Ouvri\'ccre,}{\insrsid1378858 

\par ng\'b5y 22-12-1922.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 
\par }\pard\plain \s21\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \b\f39\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 \column 
\par }\pard\plain \s20\qc \li0\ri0\sb1400\sa440\sl-380\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \b\f38\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 V\'f9C TH\'bcM THU\'e9C \'a7\'deA
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-284\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 \~N\'ad\'edc Ph\'b8p c\'e3 m\'e9t h\'d6 th\'e8ng thu\'e9c 
\'ae\'dea r\'e9ng m\'ad\'eai tri\'d6u kil\'abm\'d0t vu\'abng v\'edi d\'a9n s\'e8 l\'b5 56 tri\'d6u ng\'ad\'eai da v\'b5ng v\'b5 da \'aeen. \'a7\'d3 "khai th\'b8c" t\'cat c\'b6 nh\'f7ng c\'b8i \'ae\'e3, \'abng Anbe Xar\'ab, B\'e9 tr\'ad\'ebng B\'e9 Thu\'e9
c \'ae\'dea c\'c7n c\'e3 ba hay b\'e8n t\'fb phr\'a8ng. Mu\'e8n th\'d5, \'abng \'ae\'b7 "t\'e6 ch\'f8c" m\'e9t chi\'d5n d\'dech b\'b8o ch\'dd r\'e9ng r\'b7i v\'b5 \'ae\'b7 \'ae\'e4c kh\'abng bi\'d5t bao nhi\'aau l\'b5 di\'d4n v\'a8n. Ng\'b5i B\'e9 tr\'ad
\'ebng l\'b9i c\'dfn vi\'d5t c\'b6 m\'e9t pho s\'b8ch d\'b5y 656 trang (gi\'b8 20 phr\'a8ng m\'e9t cu\'e8n). Trong khi ch\'ea \'ae\'eei thu \'ae\'ad\'eec nh\'f7ng t\'fb \'ae\'e3, xin ph\'d0p Ng\'b5i B\'e9 tr\'ad\'ebng h\'b7y cho ch\'f3ng t\'abi b\'e6
 sung \'ae\'abi ch\'f3t v\'b5o nh\'f7ng 
\par l\'fd l\'cf c\'f1a Ng\'b5i.
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sl-284\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Ng\'a9n s\'b8ch Nam K\'fa ch\'bcng h\'b9n, n\'a8m 1911, l\'b5 5.561.680 \'ae\'e5ng (12.791.000 phr\'a8ng); n\'a8m 1912 l\'b5
 7.321.817 \'ae\'e5ng (16.840.000 phr\'a8ng). N\'a8m 1922, ng\'a9n s\'b8ch \'ae\'e3 l\'aan t\'edi 12.821.325 \'ae\'e5ng (96.169.000 phr\'a8ng). M\'e9t con t\'ddnh \'ae\'acn gi\'b6n ch\'d8 cho ch\'f3ng ta th\'cay r\'bbng gi\'f7a hai n\'a8m 1911 v\'b5 1922
, trong ng\'a9n s\'b8ch c\'f1a thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea n\'b5y c\'e3 m\'e9t s\'f9 ch\'aanh l\'d6ch l\'b5 83.378.000 phr\'a8ng (t\'fb su\'cat h\'e8i \'aeo\'b8i c\'f1a \'ae\'e5ng b\'b9c hai n\'a8m \'ae\'e3 l\'b5 2 phr\'a8ng 25 v\'b5 7 phr\'a8ng 50). S\'e8 ti\'d2
n \'ae\'e3 ch\'b9y \'aei \'ae\'a9u? Ch\'b9y v\'b5o c\'b8c kho\'b6n chi v\'d2 nh\'a9n vi\'aan m\'b5 th\'abi, v\'d7 c\'b8c kho\'b6n n\'b5y \'ae\'b7 nu\'e8t g\'c7n h\'d5t 100 ph\'c7n 100 t\'e6ng s\'e8 thu.
\par }\pard \qj \li0\ri0\sa80\sl-284\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 R\'e5i h\'d5t nh\'f7ng \'aei\'aan r\'e5 n\'b5y \'ae\'d5n nh\'f7ng s\'f9 \'aei\'aan r\'e5 kh\'b8c \'ae\'b7 l\'b5m vung ph\'dd 
\'ae\'e5ng ti\'d2n m\'b5 ng\'ad\'eai d\'a9n An Nam \'ae\'b8ng th\'ad\'acng h\'b9i \'ae\'b7 ph\'b6i \'ae\'e6 m\'e5 h\'abi n\'ad\'edc m\'bet m\'edi ki\'d5m ra \'ae\'ad\'eec. Hi\'d6n ch\'f3ng t\'abi ch\'ada bi\'d5t r\'e2 s\'e8 ti\'d2n m\'b5 \'ae\'f8
c vua An Nam \'ae\'b7 chi ti\'aau v\'d2 vi\'d6c sang du ngo\'b9n b\'aan Ph\'b8p \'ae\'f3ng l\'b5 bao nhi\'aau \'ae\'e5ng, nh\'adng ch\'f3ng t\'abi bi\'d5t r\'bbng, \'ae\'d3 \'ae\'eei
\par }\pard \qj \li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'ae\'ad\'eec }{\f37\fs20\expnd0\expndtw-4\insrsid1378858 ng\'b5y t\'e8t cho con R\'e5ng nan}{
\cs17\f37\fs20\expnd0\expndtw-4\super\insrsid1378858 1{\footnote \pard\plain \s28\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa60\sl-240\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {
\insrsid1378858 1) }{\f38\insrsid1378858 \'b8}{\insrsid1378858 m ch\'d8 Kh\'b6i \'a7\'denh.}})}{\f37\fs20\expnd0\expndtw-4\insrsid1378858  c\'e3 th\'d3 ng\'f9 gi\'b8 xu\'e8ng t\'b5u, ng\'ad\'eai ta \'ae\'b7 ph\'b6i b\'e5i th\'ad\'eang ph\'dd t\'e6n cho t
\'b5u Po\'e3ct\'e8tx\'ac v\'d2 b\'e8n ng\'b5y ch\'ea \'ae\'eei, m\'e7i ng\'b5y 100.000 phr\'a8ng (t\'f8c l\'b5 400.000 phr\'a8ng). Ti\'d2n t\'b5u h\'d5t 400.000 phr\'a8ng. Ti\'d2n chi\'aau \'ae\'b7i h\'d5t 240.000 phr\'a8ng (kh\'abng k\'d3 ti\'d2n l\'ad
\'acng tr\'b6 cho b\'e4n c\'b6nh s\'b8t \'ae\'d3 canh g\'b8c nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai An Nam \'eb Ph\'b8p). 77.600 phr\'a8ng \'ae\'d3 tr\'b6 ti\'d2n \'a8n \'eb t\'b9i M\'b8cx\'a9y cho s\'e8 l\'ddnh kh\'e8 xanh An Nam d\'efng \'ae\'d3 b\'e5ng s\'f3ng ch\'b5o C
\'f4 l\'edn B\'e9 tr\'ad\'ebng v\'b5 Ho\'b5ng th\'ad\'eeng.
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-274\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 V\'d7 n\'e3i \'ae\'d5n M\'b8cx\'a9y, n\'aan nh\'a9n ti\'d6
n ch\'f3ng ta h\'b7y xem th\'f6 cu\'e9c tri\'d3n l\'b7m thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea \'eb \'ae\'a9y \'ae\'b7 t\'e6n ph\'dd cho ch\'f3ng ta bi\'d5t bao nhi\'aau. Tr\'ad\'edc h\'d5t, v\'b5 ngo\'b5i nh\'f7ng k\'ce th\'c7n th\'d5 \'eb ch\'ddnh qu\'e8c ra, ng\'ad\'ea
i ta c\'dfn cho m\'eai ba ch\'f4c vi\'aan ch\'f8c cao c\'cap \'eb c\'b8c thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea v\'d2, - b\'e4n n\'b5y h\'bbng ng\'b5y ph\'cc ph\'ecn \'eb Cann\'acbie m\'b5 v\'c9n \'ae\'ad\'eec l\'dcnh ph\'f4 c\'cap c\'b6 \'eb Tri\'d3n l\'b7m l\'c9n \'eb thu
\'e9c \'ae\'dea. Ri\'aang \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng ph\'b6i b\'e1 ra 12 tri\'d6u cho cu\'e9c tri\'d3n l\'b7m \'ae\'e3. V\'b5 c\'b8c b\'b9n c\'e3 bi\'d5t ng\'ad\'eai ta \'ae\'b7 chi ti\'aau s\'e8 ti\'d2n \'ae\'e3 nh\'ad th\'d5 n\'b5o kh\'abng? \'a7\'a9y l\'b5
 m\'e9t th\'dd d\'f4: C\'b8i vi\'d6c g\'e4i l\'b5 d\'f9ng l\'aan m\'ab h\'d7nh c\'b8c cung \'aei\'d6n \'a1ngco \'ae\'b7 l\'b5m t\'e8n m\'cat 3000 m\'d0t kh\'e8i g\'e7 x\'a9y d\'f9ng, gi\'b8 m\'e7i m\'d0t l\'b5 400 hay 500 phr\'a8ng. T\'e6ng c\'e9ng: 1 tri
\'d6u 200 ngh\'d7n \'ae\'d5n 1 tri\'d6u 500 ngh\'d7n phr\'a8ng.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-274\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 C\'dfn nh\'f7ng vi\'d6c vung ph\'dd kh\'b8c n\'f7a. \'a7
\'d3 chuy\'aan ch\'eb quan To\'b5n quy\'d2n, m\'b5 ch\'d8 d\'efng c\'b8c xe h\'aci v\'b5 nh\'f7ng c\'e7 xe ng\'f9a th\'d7 c\'f2ng ch\'ada \'ae\'f1. Ng\'b5i c\'c7n ph\'b6i c\'e3 m\'e9t toa xe \'ae\'c6c bi\'d6t n\'f7a kia, vi\'d6c s\'bep x\'d5p toa xe \'ae
\'e3 t\'e6n ph\'dd cho c\'abng kh\'e8 125.350 phr\'a8ng.
\par Trong v\'dfng m\'ad\'eai m\'e9t th\'b8ng ho\'b9t \'ae\'e9ng, C\'f4c kinh t\'d5 \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng \'ae\'b7 l\'b5m cho ng\'a9n s\'b8ch \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng hao h\'f4t m\'e9t s\'e8 ti\'d2n l\'b5 464.000 phr\'a8ng.
\par T\'b9i Tr\'ad\'eang thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea, n\'aci \'ae\'b5o t\'b9o nh\'f7ng "nh\'b5 \'aei khai ho\'b8" sau n\'b5y, 44 gi\'b8o s\'ad \'ae\'b7 \'ae\'ad\'eec \'ae\'b5i th\'e4 \'ae\'d3 d\'b9y t\'f5 30 \'ae\'d5n 35 h\'e4c vi\'aan, l\'b9i bao nhi\'aau l\'b5 ngh
\'d7n phr\'a8ng n\'f7a.
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 S\'eb thanh tra th\'ad\'eang tr\'f9c c\'b8c c\'abng tr\'d7nh ph\'dfng th\'f1 thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea h\'bbng n\'a8m t\'e8
n cho ng\'a9n s\'b8ch h\'d5t 758.168 phr\'a8ng. Th\'d5 m\'b5 c\'b8c ng\'b5i thanh tra th\'d7 kh\'abng bao gi\'ea r\'eai kh\'e1i Pari, v\'b5 \'ae\'e8i v\'edi c\'b8c thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea th\'d7 c\'b8c ng\'b5i c\'f2ng kh\'abng hi\'d3u bi\'d5t g\'d7 h\'acn l
\'b5 hi\'d3u bi\'d5t vi\'d6c tr\'aan m\'c6t tr\'a8ng.
\par N\'d5u \'ae\'d5n c\'b8c thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea kh\'b8c, th\'d7 \'eb \'ae\'a9u, ch\'f3ng ta c\'f2ng th\'cay m\'e9t t\'d7nh tr\'b9ng t\'d6 h\'b9i nh\'ad v\'cby. \'a7\'d3 \'ae\'e3n ti\'d5p m\'e9t ph\'b8i \'aeo\'b5n "kinh t\'d5" b\'b8n ch\'ddnh th\'f8c, kho b\'b9
c M\'b8ctin\'ddch "v\'eei \'aei" m\'cat 400.000 phr\'a8ng. Trong v\'dfng m\'ad\'eai n\'a8m, ng\'a9n s\'b8ch Mar\'e8c \'ae\'b7 t\'f5 17 tri\'d6u t\'a8ng l\'aan t\'edi 290 tri\'d6u phr\'a8ng, m\'c6c d\'c7u ng\'ad\'eai ta \'ae\'b7 gi\'b6m \'aei 30% c\'b8
c kho\'b6n chi ti\'aau cho b\'b6n x\'f8, t\'f8c l\'b5 nh\'f7ng kho\'b6n chi ti\'aau c\'e3 th\'d3 \'aeem l\'b9i l\'eei \'ddch cho d\'a9n b\'b6n x\'f8.
\par \'a7\'e3 l\'b5 s\'e8 ti\'d2n h\'b5ng tri\'d6u v\'b5 th\'cbm ch\'dd h\'b5ng t\'fb m\'b5 n\'d5u ng\'ad\'eai ta bi\'d5t c\'b8ch t\'d7m th\'d7 c\'e3 l\'cf ng\'ad\'eai ta s\'cf ki\'d5m ra \'ae\'ad\'eec m\'e9t c\'b8ch d\'d4 d\'b5ng. Nh\'adng Ng\'b5i B\'e9 tr
\'ad\'ebng l\'b9i c\'f8 mu\'e8n g\'e2 v\'b5o d\'a9n b\'b6n x\'f8.
\par }\pard\plain \s24\qr \fi397\li0\ri567\sb360\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin567\lin0\itap0 \f38\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 \~NGUY\'d4N \'b8I QU\'e8C
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\b\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 
\par Xin h\'e1i
\par }{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 C\'e3 ph\'b6i v\'d7 qu\'b8 nhi\'d2u t\'ddnh nh\'a9n \'ae\'b9o, nh\'ad \'abng Xar\'ab \'ae\'b7 nhi\'d2u l\'c7n tuy\'aan b\'e8, m\'b5 ng\'ad\'eai ta \'ae\'b7 b\'bet c\'b8c ph\'b9m nh\'a9n \'eb nh\'b5 t\'ef Nha Trang (Trung K\'fa
) ph\'b6i \'a8n khan, ngh\'dca l\'b5 \'a8n c\'acm m\'b5 kh\'abng \'ae\'ad\'eec u\'e8ng n\'ad\'edc kh\'abng? C\'e3 ph\'b6i ng\'ad\'eai ta \'ae\'b7 qu\'d0t tanhtuya\'aei\'e8t l\'aan m\'f2i c\'b8c ph\'b9m nh\'a9n \'ae\'d3 d\'d4 nh\'cbn ra h\'e4 khi h\'e4 v
\'ad\'eet ng\'f4c kh\'abng?
\par }\pard\plain \s24\qr \fi397\li0\ri567\sb360\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin567\lin0\itap0 \f38\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 N.A.Q.
\par }\pard\plain \s26\ql \li0\ri567\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin567\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 B\'b8o }{\i\insrsid1378858 L'Humanit\'d0,}{\insrsid1378858 
\par ng\'b5y 9-1-1923.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 
\par 
\par }\pard\plain \s20\qc \li0\ri0\sb1400\sa440\sl-380\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \b\f38\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 \line \line \line \line NH\'f7NG NG\'a6\'eaI B\'b6N X
\'f8\line \'a7\'a6\'eeC \'a6A CHU\'e9NG}{\cs17\super\insrsid1378858 1{\footnote \pard\plain \s28\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa60\sl-240\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 
\f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 1) }{\i\insrsid1378858 Indig\'ccnes \'b5 la mode.}})}{\insrsid1378858 
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-268\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 \~N\'a8m 1604, m\'e9t ng\'ad\'eai Anh t\'aan l\'b5 S\'d5
chxpia v\'e8n l\'b5 m\'e9t nh\'b5 v\'a8n chuy\'aan nghi\'d6p, \'abng ta c\'e3 nh\'b7 \'fd \'ae\'ada ra m\'e9t v\'eb k\'dech m\'b5 vai ch\'ddnh l\'b5 m\'e9t ng\'ad\'eai da \'aeen. Ng\'ad\'eai da \'aeen n\'b5y t\'aan g\'e4i \'a4tenl\'ab, qu\'b6 l\'b5 m\'e9
t anh h\'efng, m\'e9t anh h\'efng th\'cbt s\'f9 anh h\'efng. \'a4tenl\'ab \'ae\'b7 t\'f5ng chinh chi\'d5n nhi\'d2u, nh\'adng kh\'abng ph\'b6i l\'b5 \'ae\'b8nh C\'b8cp\'a8ngchi\'aa, c\'f2ng kh\'abng ph\'b6i v\'d7 anh l\'b5 ng\'ad\'eai \'ae\'ad\'eec \'abng 
\'a7ianh\'ac tuy\'d3n m\'e9, c\'f2ng kh\'abng ph\'b6i v\'d7 anh l\'b5 ng\'ad\'eai d\'ad\'edi tr\'ad\'edng c\'f1a t\'ad\'edng M\'a8nggianh, v\'b6 l\'b9i h\'e5i \'ae\'e3 v\'c9n ch\'ada n\'e6 ra cu\'e9c chi\'d5n tranh v\'d7 c\'abng l\'fd - m\'b5 l\'b5 \'ae
\'b8nh nh\'f7ng c\'ad\'eang qu\'e8c hi\'d5u chi\'d5n \'eb ch\'a9u \'a2u v\'b5 ch\'a9u Phi. \'a4tenl\'ab l\'b5m th\'e8ng so\'b8i c\'f1a qu\'cbn c\'abng x\'f8 V\'aan\'aaxi. C\'f8 theo l\'eai \'abng Viviani n\'e3i th\'d7 tr\'aan m\'b8i t\'e3c xo\'a8n c\'f1a 
\'a4tenl\'ab \'ae\'b7 c\'e3 bi\'d5t bao nhi\'aau v\'dfng hoa chi\'d5n th\'beng. Nh\'adng chi\'d5n c\'abng l\'edn nh\'cat c\'f1a \'a4tenl\'ab l\'b5 \'ae\'b7 th\'beng \'ae\'ad\'eec \'a7\'aax\'ae\'aam\'abnia.
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-268\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 \'a7\'aax\'ae\'aam\'abnia kh\'abng ph\'b6i l\'b5 m\'e9t th
\'b5nh ph\'e8 c\'f1a b\'e4n b\'abs\'ac, c\'f2ng kh\'abng ph\'b6i l\'b5 m\'e9t thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea. \'a7\'e3 ch\'d8 l\'b5 t\'aan m\'e9t c\'ab g\'b8i d\'deu d\'b5ng, xinh x\'ben, \'ae\'c7y h\'b9nh ph\'f3c, con c\'f1a nguy\'aan l\'b7o ngh\'de vi\'d6n Brabanti
\'ab. \'a4tenl\'ab \'ae\'b7 chi\'d5m \'ae\'ad\'eec tr\'b8i tim n\'b5ng b\'bbng c\'b8ch k\'d3 l\'b9i cho n\'b5ng nghe l\'dech s\'f6 c\'b6m \'ae\'e9ng c\'f1a \'ae\'eai m\'d7nh, nh\'f7ng tr\'cbn \'ae\'b8nh v\'dc \'ae\'b9i, nh\'f7ng tr\'cbn v\'a9y th\'b5nh d
\'b5i \'ae\'bbng \'ae\'bdng, nh\'f7ng chi\'d5n c\'abng r\'f9c r\'ec, t\'e3m l\'b9i l\'b5 nh\'f7ng chuy\'d6n t\'b8n t\'d8nh hay ho g\'d7 \'ae\'e3! Bi\'d5t cha m\'d7nh v\'e8n ch\'f8c t\'ad\'edc nh\'ad th\'d5 th\'d7 s\'bdn c\'e3 nhi\'d2u th\'b5nh ki\'d5n, nh
\'cat l\'b5 th\'b5nh ki\'d5n ch\'f1ng t\'e9c, n\'aan n\'b5ng \'a7\'aax\'ae\'aam\'abnia hi\'d2n h\'cbu ch\'d8 m\'e9t l\'dfng nghe theo ti\'d5ng g\'e4i 
\par }\pard \s15\qj \li0\ri0\sa80\sl-268\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\insrsid1378858 c\'f1a t\'d7nh y\'aau, n\'b5ng quy\'d5t l\'cay ch\'b5ng da \'aeen l\'b5m ch\'e5ng m\'b5 kh\'abng c\'c7n \'ae\'d5n \'fd ki\'d5n c
\'f1a cha.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-258\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Trong v\'eb k\'dech n\'b5y, nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai da tr\'be
ng nh\'ad tay th\'b8m t\'f6 Iag\'ab v\'b5 anh ch\'b5ng R\'ab\'aerig\'ab b\'de khinh b\'d8, \'ae\'d2u kh\'abng \'ae\'e3ng m\'e9t vai g\'d7 cho\'b8ng l\'bem; ch\'ddnh h\'e4 l\'b9i l\'b5 nh\'f7ng vai \'aeen t\'e8i nh\'cat. Song c\'b8i \'ae\'e3 ch\'bcng can g
\'d7 \'ae\'d5n ch\'f3ng ta.
\par }{\f37\fs20\expnd0\expndtw-2\insrsid1378858 310 n\'a8m \'ae\'b7 tr\'abi qua. Ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8 l\'b9i \'ae\'ad\'eec \'ae\'ada l\'aan s\'a9n kh\'cau: nh\'adng \'ae\'a9y l\'b5 s\'a9n kh\'cau chi\'d5n tranh}{
\cs17\f37\fs20\expnd0\expndtw-2\super\insrsid1378858 1{\footnote \pard\plain \s28\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa60\sl-240\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {
\insrsid1378858 1) Ch\'d8 Chi\'d5n tranh th\'d5 gi\'edi th\'f8 nh\'cat (1914-1918).
\par 2) }{\i\insrsid1378858 Adapt\'d0s ou adopt\'d0s.}})}{\f37\fs20\expnd0\expndtw-2\insrsid1378858 . T\'b8c gi\'b6 l\'c7n n\'b5y gi\'cau bi\'d6t t\'aan tu\'e6i, t\'d7m c\'f2ng ch\'bcng th\'cay, song c\'b8c vai di\'d4n,- anh h\'efng hay kh\'abng- nh\'adng v
\'d7 qu\'b8 nh\'cbp vai c\'f1a m\'d7nh n\'aan ph\'c7n \'ae\'abng \'ae\'b7 n\'bbm l\'b9i tr\'aan s\'a9n kh\'cau. Th\'cbt l\'b5 m\'e9t t\'can bi k\'dech! N\'a8m 1922, l\'b9i th\'cay xu\'cat hi\'d6n nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8 \'ae\'ad\'eec \'ada chu
\'e9ng. Ta kh\'abng n\'e3i \'ae\'d5n Batuala, con ng\'ad\'eai \'ae\'ad\'eec phong t\'c6ng v\'b5 Xiki, k\'ce \'a9n nh\'a9n c\'f1a khoa h\'e4c l\'b5m g\'d7. Ta ch\'d8 n\'e3i \'ae\'d5n nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8 \'ae\'b7 th\'ddch \'f8ng \'ae\'ad\'ee
c, ho\'c6c \'ae\'ad\'eec th\'ddch th\'f3}{\f37\fs20\expnd0\expndtw-2\super\insrsid1378858 2)}{\f37\fs20\expnd0\expndtw-2\insrsid1378858 .
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-258\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 B\'de tr\'e3i g\'ab v\'b5o c\'e9t bu\'e5m t\'b5u v\'b5 \'ae
\'ad\'eec \'ae\'ada \'aei l\'b5m qu\'a9n t\'d7nh nguy\'d6n \'eb ch\'a9u \'a2u, \'ae\'b8nh ph\'ad\'eang man r\'ee \'ae\'d3 b\'b6o v\'d6 v\'a8n minh, nh\'adng m\'e9t khi \'ae\'d5n x\'f8 v\'a8n minh r\'e5i th\'d7 nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8 c\'f1a \'ab
ng T\'aary l\'b9i \'ae\'ad\'eec c\'b8i th\'f3 tha h\'e5 n\'d5m "tr\'b8i c\'a9y trong v\'ad\'ean c\'cam". Nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8 c\'dfn s\'e8ng s\'e3t sau cu\'e9c t\'b5n s\'b8t n\'a8m 1914 c\'f2ng nh\'ad nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8 c\'df
n s\'e8ng s\'e3t sau \'ae\'b9i chi\'d5n 1914-1918 \'ae\'d2u c\'e3 th\'d3 t\'f9 h\'b5o r\'bbng v\'d7 c\'abng l\'fd v\'b5 n\'d2n d\'a9n ch\'f1 c\'f1a ch\'f1ng t\'e9c cao \'ae\'bcng, h\'e4 kh\'abng nh\'f7ng \'ae\'b7 hi\'d5n \'ae\'eai m\'d7nh, x\'ad\'acng m
\'b8u m\'d7nh, m\'b5 c\'dfn hi\'d5n c\'b6 ni\'d2m t... in c\'f1a m\'d7nh n\'f7a.
\par }{\expnd0\expndtw-4\insrsid1378858 \'a4ng S\'d5chxpia tr\'ad\'edc kia l\'cay l\'b5m h\'b5i l\'dfng th\'cay ng\'ad\'eai d\'a9n b\'b6n x\'f8 trong v\'eb k\'dech c\'f1a m\'d7nh \'ae\'b7 \'ae\'b5ng ho\'b5ng l\'cay \'ae\'ad\'eec c\'ab g\'b8i m\'c9u qu\'e8c. C
\'dfn \'abng T\'aary ng\'b5y nay th\'d7 ch\'d8 nh\'cbn th\'cay c\'e3 m\'e9t \'aei\'d2u l\'b5 ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8 c\'f1a \'abng r\'cat \'ae\'bec l\'f9c \'ae\'d3 g\'e3p ph\'c7n l\'b5m cho d\'a9n s\'e8 ph\'d7nh l\'aan b\'bbng c\'b8ch l\'b5m ph\'d7nh b
\'f4ng c\'b8c c\'ab n\'b5ng da tr\'beng. \'a4ng Xasa Ghit\'acry c\'dfn \'aei xa h\'acn n\'f7a. \'a4ng mu\'e8n ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8 ph\'b6i \'ae\'ad\'eec v\'a8n minh ho\'b5n to\'b5n. \'a4ng mu\'e8n h\'e4 ph\'b6i c...\'bem s\'f5ng c\'b8c \'abng ch\'e5
ng da tr\'beng c\'ac! \'a4ng \'ae\'b7 \'ae\'ad\'eec ho\'b5n to\'b5n to\'b9i nguy\'d6n, v\'d7 ch\'ddn th\'b8ng sau cu\'e9c "chinh ph\'f4c" b\'b5 
\par }\pard \s15\qj \li0\ri0\sa80\sl-258\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\expnd0\expndtw-4\insrsid1378858 M\'b8cgr\'ddt \'a7\'aanoay\'aa \'ae\'b7 sinh h\'b9 \'ae\'ad\'eec m\'e9t c\'cbu b\'d0 b\'b6n x\'f8. Nh\'adng ch\'f3
ng ta l\'cay l\'b5m ti\'d5c r\'bbng \'a7\'aanoay\'aa \'ae\'b7 kh\'abng hoan ngh\'aanh ch\'f3 b\'d0 b\'b6n x\'f8 \'ae\'e3 cho l\'bem. V\'e8n l\'b5 m\'e9t nh\'b5 y\'aau n\'ad\'edc t\'f5 \'ae\'c7u \'ae\'d5n ch\'a9n, n\'aan \'abng ta mu\'e8n r\'bbng ch\'f3 b
\'d0 m\'b5u da "s\'abc\'abla" kia ra \'ae\'eai gi\'b8 \'ae\'f5ng c\'e3 nh\'bdn nh\'f4i v\'b5 b\'d0 nh\'e1 nh\'ad th\'d5, m\'b5 l\'b9i l\'b5 m\'e9t ng\'ad\'eai r\'a9u ria x\'e5m xo\'b5m, ba l\'ab tr\'aan l\'adng, s\'f3ng tr\'aan vai \'ae\'d3 b\'b6o v\'d6 
\'ae\'cat n\'ad\'edc, th\'d7 qu\'fd bi\'d5t ch\'f5ng n\'b5o.}{\insrsid1378858 
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-250\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Ngay c\'b6 trong c\'b8c trang ti\'d3u thuy\'d5t \'ae\'a8
ng tr\'aan b\'b8o, ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8 c\'f2ng \'ae\'b7 gi\'b5nh \'ae\'ad\'eec \'ae\'dea v\'de c\'f1a m\'d7nh. \'a4ng Angiabe - \'cay xin l\'e7i, \'abng Anbe Gi\'a8ng ch\'f8 - \'ae\'b7 ch\'bcng k\'d3 chuy\'d6n r\'bbng \'eb H\'e9i ch\'ee M\'b8cx\'a9
y c\'e3 m\'e9t ch\'b5ng An Nam kia l\'b5m ngh\'d2 k\'d0o xe \'ae\'b7 l\'e4t \'ae\'ad\'eec v\'b5o m\'bet xanh c\'f1a m\'e9t b\'b5 \'ae\'c7m xinh \'ae\'d1p n\'e4. Sau khi \'aei th\'a8m H\'e9i ch\'ee v\'d2, b\'b5 b\'ccn cho g\'e4i anh xe \'ae\'d5n ph\'df
ng ng\'f1 l\'e9ng l\'c9y c\'f1a b\'b5. V\'b5 v\'a9n v\'a9n ... Ng\'ad\'eai y\'aau b\'de c\'bem s\'f5ng c\'f1a b\'b5 b\'e7ng nhi\'aan t\'edi. B\'e8i r\'e8i, l\'c8n n\'f3p, v.v.. Nh\'adng c\'b8i ch\'ddnh c\'f1a c\'a9u chuy\'d6n l\'b9i \'eb ch\'e7 kh\'b8
c kia. Nguy\'aan l\'b5 ch\'b5ng c\'abng t\'f6 kia \'ae\'b7 \'ae\'b8nh c\'bep \'ae\'ad\'eec m\'e9t vi\'aan ng\'e4c b\'ddch b\'b5y \'eb gian th\'ea c\'f1a \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng v\'b5 \'ae\'d5n \'ae\'d3 khoe v\'edi ng\'ad\'eai ng\'e4c c\'f1a m\'d7nh. (\'a4
i! l\'ad\'acng thi\'d6n v\'cby thay!). Ng\'ad\'eai An Nam kia \'ae\'f8ng n\'cap \'ae\'bbng sau tr\'abng th\'cay qu\'b6 tang h\'b5nh vi \'ae\'c7y t\'e9i l\'e7i \'cay, li\'d2n nh\'b6y ra \'ae\'b8nh cho anh ch\'b5ng \'a8n c\'bep ng\'b7 g\'f4c, r\'e5i mang l
\'d4 v\'cbt qu\'fd \'ae\'e3 v\'d2 b\'b5n th\'ea.
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-250\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\expnd0\expndtw-4\insrsid1378858 Kh\'abng k\'d3 c\'b8c \'aei\'d6u nh\'b9c k
