c danh vang d\'e9i. Ng\'b5y nay, x\'f8 Nam K\'fa v\'edi l\'dfng hi\'d5u th\'b6o v\'b5 mong mu\'e8n t\'e1 l\'dfng trung th\'b5nh kh\'abng b\'ea b\'d5n \'ae\'e8i v\'edi n\'ad\'edc khai ho\'b8 v\'a8n minh cho m\'d7nh - v\'f5a r\'e5i c\'f2ng c\'e3 c\'b8i v
\'f4 th\'ad n\'c6c danh "c\'f1a n\'e3". Nh\'adng x\'f8 thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea n\'b5y \'ae\'b7 "b\'bet ch\'ad\'edc" v\'f4ng v\'d2 v\'d7 kh\'abng ph\'b6i l\'b5 v\'f4 m\'e9t n\'b5ng Lavan di\'d4m l\'d6 m\'b5 l\'b5 v\'f4 m\'e9t h\'ad\'acng ch\'f8c An Nam gi\'b5
 nua v\'f5a b\'de b\'bet b\'e1 t\'ef, kh\'abng ph\'b6i v\'d7 \'ae\'b7 l\'b9m d\'f4ng th\'ad n\'c6c danh m\'b5 v\'d7 \'ae\'b7 b\'de th\'ad n\'c6c danh t\'e8 c\'b8o. Vi\'d6c \'cay th\'f9c ch\'cat nh\'ad th\'d5 n\'b5y:
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 M\'e9t \'ae\'aam th\'b8ng 12 n\'a8m 1922, c\'f4 h\'ad\'ac
ng c\'b6 An Nam \'aeang m\'ac m\'b5ng th\'d7 b\'e7ng nghe ti\'d5ng m\'e2 huy\'aan n\'b8o b\'b8o cho d\'a9n l\'b5ng bi\'d5t c\'e3 c\'ad\'edp \'eb tr\'aan s\'abng c\'b8i, ngay tr\'ad\'edc m\'c6t Ch\'ee L\'b8ch! (\'a4! v\'cby th\'d7 c\'b8i n\'d2n an ninh m
\'b5 c\'b8c nh\'b5 ch\'f8c tr\'b8ch t\'f5ng ca t\'f4ng \'eb \'ae\'a9u nh\'d8?). C\'f4 h\'ad\'acng c\'b6 nh\'b5 ta v\'efng d\'cby v\'ed l\'cay kh\'c8u s\'f3ng - nguy\'aan c\'f4 h\'ad\'acng c\'b6 c\'f2ng \'ae\'e5ng th\'eai l\'b5 tr\'ad\'acng tu\'c7n c\'f1
a m\'e9t tr\'b9i \'cap l\'edn - v\'b5 l\'cbp t\'f8c c\'efng v\'edi hai gia nh\'a9n xu\'e8ng thuy\'d2n b\'aci ra s\'abng.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 V\'f5a \'ae\'d5n n\'aci, c\'f4 h\'ad\'acng c\'b6 v\'b5
 hai gia nh\'a9n li\'d2n b\'de b\'e4n c\'ad\'edp n\'e6 s\'f3ng b\'ben; m\'e9t trong hai gia nh\'a9n b\'de tr\'f3ng \'ae\'b9n gi\'f7a ng\'f9c v\'b5 v\'b5i ph\'f3t sau th\'d7 t\'bet th\'eb. C\'f4 h\'ad\'acng c\'b6 b\'ben tr\'b6 l\'b9i b\'e4n c\'ad\'edp m
\'e9t ph\'b8t kh\'abng tr\'f3ng, tr\'b8i l\'b9i b\'de b\'e4n c\'ad\'edp b\'ben b\'de th\'ad\'acng v\'b5o tay ph\'b6i.
\par R\'e5i ch\'d8 v\'d7 th\'ad n\'c6c danh t\'e8 c\'b8o, m\'b5 c\'f4 h\'ad\'acng c\'b6 n\'e4 \'ae\'b7 b\'de b\'bet giam v\'d2 t\'e9i l\'b5 \'ae\'b7 gi\'d5t gia nh\'a9n c\'f1a m\'d7nh.
\par M\'c6c d\'ef cha ng\'ad\'eai x\'cau s\'e8 v\'b5 ng\'ad\'eai gia nh\'a9n c\'dfn s\'e8ng \'ae\'b7 \'ae\'d6 \'ae\'acn minh oan cho b\'de c\'b8o, nh\'adng c\'f4 h\'ad\'acng n\'e4 v\'c9n c\'dfn n\'bbm trong "bu\'e5ng t\'e8i" "\'ae\'d3 ch\'ea \'b8nh s\'b8ng c
\'f1a c\'abng l\'fd".
\par }\pard\plain \s24\qr \fi397\li0\ri567\sb360\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin567\lin0\itap0 \f38\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 N.A.Q.
\par }\pard\plain \s26\ql \li0\ri567\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin567\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 B\'b8o }{\i\insrsid1378858 Le Paria}{\insrsid1378858 , s\'e8 11,

\par ng\'b5y 1-2-1923.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 
