\'a3 B\'e8I KH\'b8C
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 \~M\'c6c d\'ef c\'e3 s\'f9 r\'efm beng xung quanh cu\'e9
c tri\'d3n l\'b7m \'eb M\'b8cx\'a9y, nh\'f7ng b\'b5i di\'d4n v\'a8n long tr\'e4ng, nh\'f7ng cu\'e9c du ngo\'b9n c\'f1a ho\'b5ng gia v\'b5 nh\'f7ng b\'b5i khoa tr\'ad\'acng tr\'aan c\'b8c b\'b8o, t\'d7nh h\'d7nh \'eb \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng v\'c9n t\'e5i t
\'d6.
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 Chi\'d5c gh\'d5 b\'de c\'b8o m\'b5 vi\'aan quan cai tr\'de 
"thanh li\'aam" Lan\'ab v\'f5a r\'eai kh\'e1i ch\'ada k\'dep ngu\'e9i th\'d7 \'ae\'b7 c\'e3 tin v\'d2 nh\'f7ng v\'f4 b\'aa b\'e8i m\'edi.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Tr\'ad\'edc h\'d5t, \'ae\'e3 l\'b5 v\'f4 Bu\'aein\'ab. 
\'a4ng Bu\'aein\'ab l\'b5 m\'e9t "nh\'b5 khai ho\'b8" 
\par \'aei\'d3n h\'d7nh; m\'e9t quan cai tr\'de chuy\'aan \'a8n h\'e8i l\'e9. Kho\'b6n c\'ac b\'b6n c\'f1a l\'eai bu\'e9c t\'e9i \'abng ta l\'b5 nh\'ad sau:
\par "L\'b5ng T\'a9n An \'ae\'b7 l\'cay qu\'fc l\'b5ng v\'b5 vay ti\'d2n \'ae\'d3 x\'a9y d\'f9ng m\'e9t tr\'b9m \'aei\'d6n. Vi\'d6c \'cay t\'e1 ra th\'b5nh c\'abng, v\'d7 thu nh\'cbp do tr\'b9m \'aeem l\'b9i trang tr\'b6i c\'e3 d\'ad t\'cat c\'b6 m\'e4i kho
\'b6n chi ti\'aau. Ngo\'b5i ra, c\'b8c nh\'b5 c\'abng c\'e9ng v\'b5 \'ae\'ad\'eang l\'b5ng \'ae\'ad\'eec b\'b6o \'ae\'b6m \'aei\'d6n \'ae\'ccn kh\'abng m\'cat ti\'d2n.
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Th\'d5 m\'b5 m\'e9t vi\'aan quan cai tr\'de kh\'abn kh\'d0o (\'abng Bu\'aein\'ab) \'ae\'b7 th\'f9c hi\'d6n m\'e9t s\'f9 s\'be
p \'ae\'c6t nh\'ad sau: l\'b5ng T\'a9n An nh\'ad\'eeng kh\'abng tr\'b9m \'aei\'d6n cho m\'e9t anh th\'c7u kho\'b8n, \'ae\'d3 \'ae\'ad\'eec h\'ad\'ebng c\'b8i th\'f3 ph\'b6i tr\'b6 ti\'d2n \'aei\'d6n th\'bep s\'b8ng c\'b8c nh\'b5 c\'abng c\'e9ng v\'b5 \'ae
\'ad\'eang l\'b5ng. R\'e5i ng\'ad\'eai ta b\'e7ng nh\'cbn th\'cay n\'aan chu\'e9c l\'b9i \'ae\'c6c quy\'d2n \'ae\'b7 nh\'ad\'eeng kh\'abng v\'b5 mu\'e8n th\'d5 l\'b5ng ph\'b6i x\'d5p ra m\'cay ch\'f4c ngh\'d7n \'ae\'e5ng. To\'b5n b\'e9 chuy\'d6n n\'b5y gi
\'e8ng m\'e9t cu\'e8n ti\'d3u thuy\'d5t th\'f9c s\'f9, trong \'ae\'e3, vi\'aan c\'f9u c\'abng s\'f8 \'ae\'b7 b\'e9c l\'e9 tr\'dd t\'ad\'ebng t\'ad\'eeng c\'f1a m\'d7nh v\'edi m\'e9t s\'f9 v\'ab s\'d8 kh\'abng th\'d3 t\'ad\'ebng n\'e6i.
\par }\pard \qj \li0\ri0\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 V\'f4 b\'aa b\'e8i th\'f8 hai l\'b5 v\'f4 T\'aaa. \'a7\'a9y l\'b5 \'aei\'d2u b\'b9n \'ae\'e5ng nghi\'d6p c\'f1a ch\'f3ng t\'abi 
\'eb \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng k\'d3 l\'b9i:
\par }\pard \qj \li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 "Ch\'f3ng t\'abi s\'e8ng trong m\'e9t b\'c7u kh\'abng kh\'dd... th\'f9c s\'f9 phi th\'ad\'eang: v\'f4 Bu\'aein\'ab, v\'f4 Lan
\'ab v\'b5 \'ddt l\'a9u sau l\'b5 v\'f4 T\'aaa.
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'a4ng T\'aaa, m\'e9t k\'fc s\'ad c\'e3 r\'cat nhi\'d2u c\'abng lao, gi\'b8m \'ae\'e8c m\'e9t h\'b7ng l\'edn c\'f1a Ph
\'b8p \'eb H\'b6i Ph\'dfng, \'abng \'ae\'d5n nh\'b5 \'abng Xcala, gi\'b8m \'ae\'e8c S\'eb \'aeoan v\'b5 mu\'e8n ngo\'c6c v\'edi ch\'ddnh quy\'d2n \'ae\'d3 b\'b8n thu\'e8c phi\'d6n, \'abng \'ae\'b7 \'ae\'ada cho \'abng ta s\'e8 ti\'d2n m\'e9t v\'b9n \'ae
\'abla, l\'cay c\'ed l\'b5 tr\'b6 ti\'d2n tr\'ad\'edc h\'b9n, kh\'abng c\'c7n l\'cay b\'cat c\'f8 bi\'aan lai, gi\'cay t\'ea g\'d7 c\'b6. \'a7\'d3 d\'b8m \'aei m\'e9t b\'ad\'edc nh\'ad v\'cby, c\'c7n ph\'b6i \'ae\'ben \'aeo suy ngh\'dc k\'fc v\'b5 ph\'b6
i tin ch\'bec r\'bbng ng\'ad\'eai ta s\'cf kh\'abng t\'d7m th\'cay trong h\'b5nh vi \'ae\'e3 m\'e9t \'aei\'d2u g\'d7 kh\'abng b\'d7nh th\'ad\'eang. \'a7i\'d2u \'ae\'e3 c\'e3 ngh\'dca l\'b5 trong gi\'edi kinh doanh \'eb \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng, nh\'f7ng vi
\'d6c giao d\'dech nh\'ad v\'cby l\'b5 chuy\'d6n b\'d7nh th\'ad\'eang.
\par T\'cat c\'b6 nh\'f7ng k\'ce c\'e3 quy\'d2n h\'b5nh nh\'ad v\'cby c\'f2ng \'ae\'d2u s\'cf l\'eei d\'f4ng \'ae\'d3 v\'ac v\'d0t c\'f1a c\'b6i cho b\'b6n th\'a9n m\'d7nh v\'b5 b\'bbng c\'b8ch \'ae\'e3 s\'cf mang l\'b9i t\'e6n th\'cat l\'edn cho x\'b7 h\'e9
i".
\par N\'d5u t\'aan \'aeao ph\'f1 \'a7\'b8cl\'ac, c\'abng s\'f8 t\'d8nh Th\'b8i Nguy\'aan, \'ae\'ad\'eec c\'f6 l\'b5m U\'fb vi\'aan H\'e9i \'ae\'e5ng th\'b5nh ph\'e8 S\'b5i G\'dfn, c\'dfn \'abng B\'ab\'aeoanh, ng\'ad\'eai \'aeang \'ae\'ad\'eec quan to\'b5
 Oaren n\'e3ng l\'dfng mong \'ae\'eei \'ae\'b7 tr\'eb th\'b5nh quy\'d2n To\'b5n quy\'d2n \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng, th\'d7 c\'b8c \'abng T\'aaa v\'b5 Bu\'aein\'ab \'ddt ra c\'f2ng n\'aan \'ae\'ad\'eec g\'ben b\'e9i tinh m\'edi ph\'b6i.
\par }\pard\plain \s24\qr \fi397\li0\ri567\sb360\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin567\lin0\itap0 \f38\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 nguy\'d4n \'b8i qu\'e8c
\par }\pard\plain \s26\ql \li0\ri567\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin567\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 B\'b8o }{\i\insrsid1378858 L'Humanit\'d0,}{\insrsid1378858 
\par ng\'b5y 5-2-1923.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 
\par }{\b\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 \column 
\par }\pard\plain \s20\qc \li0\ri0\sb1400\sa440\sl-380\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \b\f38\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 N\'b9N THI\'d5U TR\'a6\'eaNG H\'e4C
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-300\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 \~D\'a9n ch\'f3ng \'aeang \'ae\'dfi h\'e1i ph\'b6i c\'e3
 tr\'ad\'eang h\'e4c, m\'b5 hi\'d6n nay, tr\'ad\'eang h\'e4c \'aeang thi\'d5u m\'e9t c\'b8ch t\'d6 h\'b9i. M\'e7i n\'a8m, c\'f8 \'ae\'d5n ng\'b5y khai tr\'ad\'eang, c\'b8c b\'cbc cha m\'d1 d\'ef c\'e3 \'aei g\'e2 c\'f6a kh\'bep n\'aci, c\'c7u xin m\'e4i s
\'f9 gi\'f3p \'ae\'ec, th\'cbm ch\'dd xin n\'e9p g\'cap \'ae\'abi ti\'d2n \'a8n h\'e4c m\'b5 h\'e4 v\'c9n kh\'abng g\'f6i \'ae\'ad\'eec con c\'b8i \'ae\'d5n tr\'ad\'eang. V\'b5 nh\'f7ng \'ae\'f8a tr\'ce n\'b5y, c\'e3 \'ae\'d5n h\'b5ng ngh\'d7n, b\'de \'ae
\'b5y v\'b5o c\'b6nh ngu d\'e8t ch\'d8 v\'d7 kh\'abng c\'e3 \'ae\'f1 tr\'ad\'eang s\'eb cho ch\'f3ng \'aei h\'e4c.
\par Ng\'ad\'eai ta s\'cf n\'e3i r\'bbng, v\'d7 ng\'a9n s\'b8ch kh\'abng \'ae\'f1 cho ch\'ddnh ph\'f1 x\'a9y th\'aam tr\'ad\'eang m\'edi. Kh\'abng h\'bcn th\'d5 \'ae\'a9u. Trong s\'e8 12 tri\'d6u \'ae\'e5ng c\'f1a ng\'a9n s\'b8ch Nam K\'fa, th\'d7 10 tri\'d6u 
\'ae\'e5ng \'ae\'b7 t\'d7m \'ae\'ad\'eec c\'b8ch l\'e4t v\'b5o t\'f3i c\'b8c c\'abng ch\'f8c.
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-300\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 M\'c6t kh\'b8c, s\'ee r\'bbng thanh ni\'aan An Nam b\'de ti
\'aam nhi\'d4m ch\'f1 ngh\'dca b\'abns\'aav\'ddch, Ch\'ddnh ph\'f1 thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea l\'b5m m\'e4i c\'b8ch c\'e3 th\'d3 l\'b5m \'ae\'d3 ng\'a8n c\'b6n h\'e4 sang h\'e4c \'eb ch\'ddnh qu\'e8c. \'a7i\'d2u 500 (Bis) c\'f1a ngh\'de \'ae\'denh ng\'b5y 20 th
\'b8ng 6 n\'a8m 1921 v\'d2 h\'e4c ch\'ddnh \'eb \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng n\'e3i nh\'ad sau:
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-300\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 "M\'e4i ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8, v\'ab lu\'cbn l\'b5 d
\'a9n thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea Ph\'b8p hay d\'a9n do Ph\'b8p b\'b6o h\'e9, mu\'e8n sang ch\'ddnh qu\'e8c ti\'d5p t\'f4c h\'e4c t\'cbp, \'ae\'d2u }{\i\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 ph\'b6i \'ae\'ad\'eec ph\'d0p c\'f1a quan to\'b5n quy\'d2n}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 
. Quan to\'b5n quy\'d2n s\'cf quy\'d5t \'ae\'denh sau khi h\'e1i \'fd ki\'d5n quan th\'f1 hi\'d5n v\'b5 quan gi\'b8m \'ae\'e8c Nha h\'e4c ch\'ddnh.
\par Tr\'ad\'edc khi \'aei, \'ae\'ad\'acng s\'f9 ph\'b6i c\'e3 m\'e9t h\'e4c b\'b9 \'ae\'b9i h\'e4c do Nha h\'e4c ch\'ddnh c\'cap, c\'e3 d\'b8n \'b6nh v\'b5 ghi r\'e2 l\'fd l\'dech, \'ae\'dea ch\'d8 cha m\'d1, nh\'f7ng
\par }\pard\plain \s25\qj \li0\ri0\sa80\sl-300\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f38\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\insrsid1378858 tr\'ad\'eang \'ae\'b7 h\'e4c, c\'b8c h\'e4c b\'e6ng ho\'c6
c tr\'ee c\'cap \'ae\'b7 \'ae\'ad\'eec h\'ad\'ebng, c\'b8c b\'bbng c\'cap \'ae\'b7 c\'e3 v\'b5 \'ae\'dea ch\'d8 c\'f1a ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6o l\'b7nh \'eb Ph\'b8p. H\'e4c b\'b9 \'ae\'e3 ph\'b6i \'ae\'ad\'eec quan to\'b5n quy\'d2n ph\'aa chu\'c8n.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-300\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 H\'e5 s\'ac c\'f1a nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8 du h
