\'ben \'eb tr\'ad\'eang \'aeua, tr\'abng h\'ben c\'e3 v\'ce nh\'f3t nh\'b8t h\'acn, l\'f3ng ta l\'f3ng t\'f3ng h\'acn c\'ac, c\'e3 c\'b6 c\'b8i ch\'f4p \'ae\'ccn ch\'f4p l\'aan c\'b8i \'ae\'c7u qu\'can kh\'a8n, c\'b8c ng\'e3n tay th\'d7 \'aeeo \'ae\'c7
y nh\'f7ng nh\'c9n.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 - Th\'d5 hay l\'b5 h\'ben \'ae\'b7 \'aeem t\'cat c\'b6 c
\'b8c th\'f8 \'ae\'e3 \'ae\'d5n ti\'d6m c\'c7m \'ae\'e5 r\'e5i? Nh\'adng m\'b5 nh\'d7n k\'fc xem k\'d7a! Ch\'bcng ph\'b6i v\'c9n c\'b8i m\'f2i t\'d1t \'cay, v\'c9n \'ae\'abi m\'bet x\'d5ch \'cay, v\'c9n c\'b8i m\'c6t b\'f1ng nh\'ad v\'e1 chanh \'cay \'ae
\'cay \'b5}{\cs17\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 1{\footnote \pard\plain \s28\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa60\sl-240\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 
1) Qu\'b6 chanh \'eb ch\'a9u \'a2u v\'e1 m\'b5u v\'b5ng b\'f1ng.
\par 2) }{\i\insrsid1378858 Ses mandarins et mandarines}{\insrsid1378858 . Ch\'aci ch\'f7, do trong ti\'d5ng Ph\'b8p, }{\i\insrsid1378858 Mandarin}{\insrsid1378858  c\'e3 ngh\'dca l\'b5 \'abng quan v\'b5 }{\i\insrsid1378858 mandarine}{\insrsid1378858  c\'e3
 ngh\'dca l\'b5 qu\'b6 qu\'fdt; theo quy t\'bec t\'f5 v\'f9ng h\'e4c th\'d7, b\'d7nh th\'ad\'eang ra, mu\'e8n chuy\'d3n gi\'e8ng \'ae\'f9c sang gi\'e8ng c\'b8i ph\'b6i th\'aam "e" sau t\'f5 ch\'d8 gi\'e8ng \'ae\'f9c. }{\f38\cf1\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 \'eb}
{\f38\insrsid1378858  }{\insrsid1378858 \'ae\'a9y, ch\'d8 chuy\'d3n \'ae\'ad\'eec ph\'c7n n\'b5o \'fd \'ae\'efa sang b\'b6n d\'dech ti\'d5ng Vi\'d6t. C\'e3 th\'d3 d\'dech: \'abng quan b\'b5 ki\'d5c.}})}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 ?
\par - }{\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'f5}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  nh\'d8, th\'d7 c\'f2ng c\'e3 th\'d3 l\'b5 anh \'ae\'f3ng. Nh\'adng h\'ben \'ae\'d5n \'ae\'a9y l\'b5m g\'d7 nh\'d8 trong \'ae\'ad\'eang xe \'aei\'d6n ng\'c7m n\'b5y, v\'b5 t\'f4i c\'b8c \'ab
ng quan b\'b5 ki\'d5c}{\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 2)}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  \'aei theo th\'d7 \'ae\'a9u c\'b6 ?
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 - C\'e3 khi \'ae\'b7 g\'f6i tu\'e8t \'eb kho h\'b5nh l\'fd
 nh\'b5 ga \'ae\'d3 \'aei ch\'aci vi h\'b5nh \'ae\'cay.
\par }\pard \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\insrsid1378858 \'a7\'cay, c\'ab em h\'e4 th\'a9n m\'d5n c\'f1a t\'abi! T\'abi \'ae\'b7 thu\'cbt l\'b9i y nguy\'aan c\'a9u chuy\'d6n gi\'f7
a m\'e9t \'ae\'abi b\'b9n tr\'ce ng\'e5i c\'efng toa xe v\'edi t\'abi. H\'e4 ng\'cau nghi\'d5n tr\'abng t\'abi v\'edi c\'c6p m\'bet ma m\'b7nh, t\'df m\'df, nh\'adng l\'b9i ra b\'e9 kh\'abng nh\'d7n t\'abi g\'d7 c\'b6.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Cu\'e9c \'ae\'e8i tho\'b9i ti\'d5p di\'d4n nh\'ad sau:

\par - Th\'d5 em ngh\'dc th\'d5 n\'b5o v\'d2 ng\'ad\'eai kh\'b8ch c\'f1a ch\'f3ng ta ? ng\'ad\'eai con trai h\'e1i, ng\'ec t\'abi l\'b5 m\'e9t \'ae\'cang Ho\'b5ng th\'ad\'eeng v\'b5 t\'ad\'ebng r\'bbng t\'abi kh\'abng hi\'d3u h\'e4 n\'e3i g\'d7 v\'edi nhau.

\par - H\'ben c\'dfn l\'b5m m\'d7nh b\'cbt c\'ad\'eai h\'acn n\'f7a c\'ac l\'f3c h\'ben \'aeeo l\'aan ng\'ad\'eai h\'ben \'ae\'f1 c\'b6 b\'e9 l\'f4a l\'b5, \'ae\'f1 c\'b6 b\'e9 h\'b9t c\'ad\'eam, ng\'ad\'eai b\'b9n g\'b8i anh ta tr\'b6 l\'eai.
\par - H\'b9t ch\'a9u b\'b8u \'ae\'cay ch\'f8! Em th\'ddch c\'e3 ch\'e7 ch\'a9u b\'b8u \'cay qu\'b8 \'aei, ch\'f8 c\'dfn g\'d7!
\par - Em m\'b5 c\'e3 \'cay \'b5, th\'d7 em c\'e8 t\'d7nh \'ae\'b8nh m\'cat \'aei, \'ae\'d3 \'ae\'ad\'eec b\'b8o ch\'dd n\'e3i \'ae\'d5n, v\'b5 th\'d5 l\'b5 \'ae\'ad\'eec tr\'eb th\'b5nh m\'e9t ng\'abi sao. Th\'d5 c\'dfn anh, anh ngh\'dc g\'d7 v\'d2 ng\'ad\'ea
i d\'a9n b\'b6o h\'e9 c\'f1a ch\'f3ng ta n\'b5o ?
\par - }{\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'dd}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 ch cho ch\'f3ng ta l\'bem \'ae\'cay. C\'b8i l\'df \'eb G\'a8ngbe \'ae\'b7 b\'b8n r\'e5i. C\'b8i r\'ad\'acng c\'f1a H\'aara Mi\'d5cten c\'f2ng \'ae\'b7 thanh to\'b8n r\'e5i. V\'f4 \'b8n ng\'ad\'ea
i b\'de ch\'c6t ra t\'f5ng kh\'f3c th\'d7 kh\'abng thu h\'f3t \'ae\'ad\'eec c\'abng ch\'f3ng l\'bem v\'d7 kh\'abng thu\'e9c gi\'edi th\'ad\'eeng l\'adu. V\'b5 th\'d5 l\'b5 c\'b8i kho gi\'b6i tr\'dd c\'f1a ch\'f3ng ta}{\cs17\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 1
{\footnote \pard\plain \s28\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa60\sl-240\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 1) Nh\'b5 c\'c7m quy\'d2n c\'b8c n\'ad\'edc t\'ad
 b\'b6n th\'ad\'eang d\'efng nh\'f7ng tin "th\'eai s\'f9" gi\'cbt g\'a9n \'ae\'d3 d\'c9n d\'bet qu\'c7n ch\'f3ng sao l\'b7ng \'ae\'cau tranh ch\'ddnh tr\'de. M\'cay c\'a9u chuy\'d6n v\'f5a nh\'bec \'ae\'d5n l\'b5 m\'e9t s\'e8 v\'f4 gi\'d5t ng\'ad\'eai l
\'cay c\'f1a \'ddt nhi\'d2u "ly k\'fa", c\'e3 th\'cbt, x\'b6y ra \'eb Ph\'b8p l\'f3c b\'cay gi\'ea.
\par 2) Nguy\'aan b\'b6n: B.I.C. }{\i\insrsid1378858 (Banque d'Indochine).}{\insrsid1378858  Ng\'a9n h\'b5ng \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng. 
\par 3) Ti\'d5ng Ph\'b8p ch\'d8 n\'e3i "\'ae\'e6i"; th\'ad\'eang n\'e3i "\'ae\'e6i xe" nh\'adng th\'cbt ra l\'b5 "\'ae\'e6i tuy\'d5n xe". H\'d6 th\'e8ng xe \'aei\'d6n ng\'c7m Pari g\'e5m nhi\'d2u tuy\'d5n g\'c6p nhau \'eb m\'e9t s\'e8 tr\'b9m nh\'cat \'ae\'de
nh, \'eb \'ae\'e3, c\'e3 th\'d3 chuy\'d3n t\'f5 tuy\'d5n n\'b5y sang tuy\'d5n kh\'b8c.}})}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  s\'bep c\'b9n r\'b8o nh\'ad B.\'a7.D}{\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 2)}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  v\'cby. Nh\'cbt b\'b8o ch\'bcng c\'df
n c\'b8i g\'d7 \'ae\'d3 b\'abi b\'b8c l\'aan gi\'cay c\'b6. \'a7\'f3ng l\'f3c \'ae\'e3 th\'d7 ...
\par - \'a7\'e6i xe \'eb \'ae\'a9y ch\'f8}{\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 3)}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  anh y\'aau \'aci ?
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 - Kh\'abng, ga sau. \'a7\'f3ng l\'f3c \'ae\'e3 th\'d7 c\'e3
 m\'e9t anh vua \'ae\'d5n v\'edi ch\'f3ng ta 
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 - Em th\'d7 em th\'ddch S\'b8cl\'ab}{
\cs17\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 1{\footnote \pard\plain \s28\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa60\sl-240\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 1) }{
\i\insrsid1378858 Charlot}{\insrsid1378858 : Vai h\'d2 n\'e6i ti\'d5ng c\'f1a \'aei\'d6n \'b6nh do di\'d4n vi\'aan ki\'aam \'ae\'b9o di\'d4n n\'e6i ti\'d5ng Anh S\'b8cli Saplin s\'b8ng t\'b9o.}})}{\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858  }{
\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 h\'acn. V\'edi l\'b9i, vua, th\'d7 t\'e8n l\'bem.
\par - \'a7\'a9u c\'e3! Th\'d5 em c\'dfn nh\'ed bu\'e6i d\'b9 h\'e9i thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea \'eb nh\'b5 h\'b8t ca v\'f2 \'ae\'cay ch\'f8 ? Ph\'b6i tr\'b6 nh\'f7ng ngh\'d7n r\'ad\'ebi phr\'a8ng \'ae\'d3 xem v\'ee l\'cf n\'b5ng h\'c7u vua Cao Mi\'aan, xem t\'f4i l
\'b5m tr\'df leo tr\'cco nh\'b5o l\'e9n c\'f1a s\'ad th\'b8nh x\'f8 C\'abngg\'ab}{\cs17\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 2{\footnote \pard\plain \s28\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa60\sl-240\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 
\f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 2) }{\i\insrsid1378858 Les aerobates du marabout de Congo.}{\insrsid1378858  C\'b6 danh hi\'d6u s\'ad th\'b8nh \'ae\'b9o H\'e5i ("marabu"), c\'b6 t\'aan n\'ad\'edc C\'abngg\'ab 
\'eb \'ae\'a9y \'ae\'d2u l\'b5 phi\'d5m ch\'d8.}})}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 ; h\'abm nay th\'d7 ch\'f3ng m\'d7nh c\'e3 m\'cat t\'dd ti\'d2n n\'b5o \'ae\'a9u m\'b5 \'ae\'ad\'eec xem vua \'aeang ngay c\'b9nh ? Nghe n\'e3i \'abng b\'c7u Nh\'b5 h\'b8t M\'f3
a r\'e8i}{\cs17\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 3{\footnote \pard\plain \s28\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa60\sl-240\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 
3) }{\i\insrsid1378858 Le manager du Guignol}{\insrsid1378858 . (Guignol l\'b5 t\'aan vai ch\'ddnh trong tr\'df r\'e8i, sau d\'efng r\'e9ng ra \'ae\'d3 ch\'d8 con ng\'ad\'eai ng\'a9y ng\'ab ho\'c6c c\'a9u chuy\'d6n l\'e8 l\'a8ng).}})}{
\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  c\'e3 \'ae\'denh k\'fd giao k\'cco thu\'aa \'ae\'cay....
\par T\'b5u \'ae\'e7, c\'c6p trai g\'b8i b\'ad\'edc xu\'e8ng, m\'bet c\'f8 li\'d5c nh\'d7n tr\'e9m t\'abi, v\'b5 t\'abi th\'d7 bu\'e5n c\'ad\'eai qu\'b8, b\'e7ng \'ae\'a9m ra ngh\'dc, v\'b5 ngh\'dc \'ae\'d5n c\'ab. T\'abi nh\'ad c\'dfn tr\'abng th\'cay c\'b8
i ng\'b5y m\'b5 c\'ab v\'edi t\'abi, \'ae\'abi ch\'f3ng ta, nh\'ad \'ae\'abi chim \'cay th\'abi, \'ae\'cbu v\'bet v\'ceo tr\'aan \'ae\'c7u g\'e8i \'abng b\'b8c th\'a9n y\'aau, nghe b\'b8c k\'d3 chuy\'d6n c\'e6 t\'ddch. T\'abi nh\'ed chuy\'d6n vua Thu\'ca
n, v\'d7 mu\'e8n \'ae\'ddch th\'a9n tai nghe m\'bet th\'cay d\'a9n c\'e3 b\'bbng l\'dfng m\'d7nh kh\'abng, n\'aan c\'b6i trang l\'b5m d\'a9n c\'b5y \'aei d\'df la kh\'bep x\'f8. L\'b9i nh\'ed chuy\'d6n vua Pie n\'ad\'edc Nga \'aei l\'b5m th\'ee v\'b5 \'ae
\'d5n l\'b5m vi\'d6c \'eb c\'b8c c\'abng tr\'ad\'eang n\'ad\'edc Anh. B\'aan nh\'f7ng b\'cbc c\'b6i trang v\'dc \'ae\'b9i \'cay mu\'e8n \'aei s\'a9u v\'b5o cu\'e9c s\'e8ng c\'f1a nh\'a9n d\'a9n, ng\'b5y nay, c\'dfn c\'e3 nh\'f7ng \'abng ho\'b5ng, \'ab
ng ch\'f3a, \'ae\'d3 ti\'d6n vi\'d6c ri\'aang v\'b5 v\'d7 nh\'f7ng l\'fd do kh\'abng cao th\'ad\'eeng b\'bbng, c\'f2ng "vi h\'b5nh" \'ae\'cay.
\par T\'abi kh\'abng \'ae\'ad\'eec r\'e2 \'fd \'ae\'e5 nh\'b5 "vi h\'b5nh" c\'f1a ch\'f3ng ta ra sao. Ph\'b6i ch\'a8ng l\'b5 ng\'b5i mu\'e8n bi\'d5t d\'a9n Ph\'b8p, d\'ad\'edi quy\'d2n ng\'f9 tr\'de c\'f1a b\'b9n ng\'b5i l\'b5 Al\'d5chx\'a8ng \'ae\'d6 nh\'cat}
{\cs17\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 4{\footnote \pard\plain \s28\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa60\sl-240\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 4) }{
\i\insrsid1378858 Alexandre Millerand}{\insrsid1378858 : T\'e6ng th\'e8ng Ph\'b8p l\'f3c b\'cay gi\'ea. G\'e4i T\'e6ng th\'e8ng Ph\'b8p theo ki\'d3u ch\'d8 vua ch\'f3a: "Al\'d5chx\'a8ng \'ae\'d6 nh\'cat", l\'b5 \'ae\'d3 nh\'can m\'b9nh t\'ddnh h\'b5i h
\'ad\'edc c\'f1a \'aeo\'b9n v\'a8n, \'ae\'e5ng th\'eai l\'b5 \'ae\'d3 n\'aau r\'e2 s\'f9 l\'e7i th\'eai c\'f1a vua ch\'f3a, t\'f8c c\'f2ng l\'b5 \'ae\'d3 ch\'a9m bi\'d5m Kh\'b6i \'a7\'denh chua cay h\'acn.}})}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  c\'e3 \'ae\'ad\'ee
c sung s\'ad\'edng, c\'e3 \'ae\'ad\'eec u\'e8ng nhi\'d2u  
\par }\pard \qj \li0\ri0\sa80\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 r\'ad\'eeu, v\'b5 \'ae\'ad\'eec h\'f3t nhi\'d2u thu\'e8c phi\'d6n b\'bbng d\'a9n Nam, d\'ad\'edi quy\'d2n ng\'f9 tr\'de c\'f1
a ng\'b5i, hay kh\'abng? Ph\'b6i ch\'a8ng ng\'b5i mu\'e8n h\'e4c s\'f6 d\'f4ng (theo ki\'d3u Ph\'b8p) c\'b8i li\'d2m c\'f1a nh\'b5 n\'abng c\'efng c\'b8i b\'f3a c\'f1a th\'b5y th\'ee \'ae\'d3 sau cu\'e9c ngao du, \'aeem v\'d2 ch\'f3t \'cam no m\'b5 \'ae
\'b8m "d\'a9n"}{\cs17\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 1{\footnote \pard\plain \s28\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa60\sl-240\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {
\insrsid1378858 1) Trong nguy\'aan b\'b6n ch\'f7 "d\'a9n" \'ae\'ad\'eec vi\'d5t b\'bbng ch\'f7 Vi\'d6t.}})}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  b\'cat h\'b9nh c\'f1a ng\'b5i t\'edi nay ho\'b5n to\'b5n ch\'bcng bi\'d5t \'ae\'d5n? Hay l\'b5, ch\'b8n c\'b6nh l\'b5m m
\'e9t \'abng vua to, b\'a9y gi\'ea ng\'b5i l\'b9i mu\'e8n n\'d5m th\'f6 cu\'e9c \'ae\'eai c\'f1a c\'b8c c\'cbu c\'abng t\'f6 b\'d0}{\cs17\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 2{\footnote \pard\plain \s28\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa60\sl-240\slmult0
\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 2) }{\i\insrsid1378858 Petits ducs.}{\insrsid1378858  C\'e3 ngh\'dca l\'b5 ti\'d3u c\'abng hay c\'abng t\'ad\'ed
c b\'d0. }{\f38\cf1\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 \'eb}{\f38\insrsid1378858  }{\insrsid1378858 \'ae\'a9y, t\'b8c gi\'b6 gi\'d4u c\'eet r\'cat tinh vi v\'b5 ch\'aci ch\'f7 r\'cat t\'d5 nh\'de: ti\'d5ng Ph\'b8p v\'e8n c\'e3 th\'b5nh ng\'f7 coi nh\'f7ng \'abng ho
\'b5ng Nga m\'b5 t\'ad\'edc hi\'d6u l\'b5 \'ae\'b9i c\'abng }{\i\insrsid1378858 (grand-duc)}{\insrsid1378858  l\'b5 nh\'f7ng tay \'a8n ch\'aci b\'f5a b\'b7i.}})}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 .
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-270\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Th\'d5 n\'b5o th\'d7 th\'d5, \'ddt l\'a9u nay t\'abi \'ae\'b7 tr\'eb th\'b5nh m\'e9t \'ae\'cang Ho\'b5ng th\'ad\'eeng b
\'cat \'ae\'bec d\'dc. B\'cat c\'f8 t\'abi \'aei \'ae\'a9u, l\'b5 c\'e3 ng\'ad\'eai nh\'d7n t\'abi, ganh t\'de t\'abi, m\'d8m c\'ad\'eai v\'edi t\'abi, t\'b8n t\'f4ng t\'abi, \'aei theo t\'abi.
\par C\'ab em th\'a9n m\'d5n, h\'bcn c\'ab b\'b6o t\'abi r\'bbng, th\'d5 l\'b5 c\'b8i b\'b8nh xe v\'ab l\'ad\'eeng n\'e3 \'ae\'b7 quay r\'e5i \'ae\'cay. \'a7\'d5n nay, t\'cat c\'b6 nh\'f7ng ai \'eb \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng c\'e3 m\'b5u da tr\'beng \'ae\'d2u l
\'b5 nh\'f7ng b\'cbc khai ho\'b8, th\'d7 b\'a9y gi\'ea \'ae\'d5n l\'ad\'eet t\'cat c\'b6 nh\'f7ng ai c\'e3 m\'b5u da v\'b5ng \'ae\'d2u tr\'eb th\'b5nh ho\'b5ng \'ae\'d5 \'eb Ph\'b8p.
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-270\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 C\'ab kh\'abng th\'d3 t\'ad\'ebng t\'ad\'eeng \'ae\'ad\'ee
c c\'b6nh \'ae\'e3n ti\'d5p t\'e8t \'ae\'d1p ng\'ad\'eai ta d\'b5nh cho ch\'f3ng t\'abi \'eb \'ae\'a9y. Qu\'c7n ch\'f3ng c\'f8 l\'b5 t\'f9 ph\'b8t m\'b5 bi\'d3u l\'e9 nhi\'d6t t\'d7nh khi v\'f5a tho\'b8ng th\'cay m\'e9t \'ae\'e5ng b\'b5o ta. Nh\'f7ng ti
\'d5ng "h\'ben \'ae\'cay!" hay "xem h\'ben k\'d7a!" l\'b5 nh\'f7ng l\'eai ch\'b5o m\'f5ng k\'ddn \'ae\'b8o v\'b5 k\'ddnh tr\'e4ng m\'b5 ch\'f3ng t\'abi th\'ad\'eang g\'c6p d\'e4c \'ae\'ad\'eang.
\par C\'b8i vui nh\'cat l\'b5 ngay \'ae\'d5n Ch\'ddnh ph\'f1 c\'f2ng ch\'bcng nh\'cbn ra \'ae\'ad\'eec kh\'b8ch th\'cbt c\'f1a m\'d7nh n\'f7a, v\'b5 \'ae\'d3 ch\'bec ch\'ben kh\'e1i th\'cat th\'e8 trong nhi\'d6m v\'f4 ti\'d5p t\'a9n, Ch\'ddnh ph\'f1 b\'ccn 
\'ae\'e8i \'ae\'b7i v\'edi t\'cat c\'b6 m\'e4i ng\'ad\'eai An Nam v\'b5o h\'b5ng vua ch\'f3a v\'b5 ph\'b8i tu\'fa t\'efng \'aei h\'e9 gi\'b8 tu\'e8t! \'a7\'e3 l\'b5 nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai ph\'f4c v\'f4 th\'c7m k\'ddn, r\'f4t r\'cc, v\'ab t\'ad v\'b5 h\'d5
t s\'f8c t\'cbn t\'f4y. C\'b8c v\'de ch\'bcng n\'d2 h\'b5 ch\'f3t c\'abng s\'f8c n\'b5o \'ae\'d3 b\'b6o v\'d6 b\'e4n t\'abi, v\'b5 gi\'b8 c\'ab \'ae\'ad\'eec tr\'abng th\'cay c\'b8c v\'de \'a9n c\'c7n theo d\'e2i t\'abi ch\'bcng kh\'b8c b\'b5 m\'d1 hi\'d2
n r\'d7nh con th\'ac ch\'cbp ch\'f7ng b\'ad\'edc \'aei th\'f8 nh\'cat, th\'d7 h\'bcn c\'ab ph\'b6i ph\'b8t ghen l\'aan \'ae\'ad\'eec v\'d2 n\'e7i ni\'d2m \'a9u y\'d5m c\'f1a c\'b8c v\'de \'ae\'e8i v\'edi t\'abi. C\'e3 th\'d3 n\'e3i l\'b5 c\'b8c v\'de b
\'b8m l\'cay \'ae\'d5 gi\'b5y t\'abi, d\'ddnh ch\'c6t v\'edi t\'abi nh\'ad h\'d7nh v\'edi b\'e3ng. V\'b5 th\'cbt t\'d7nh l\'b5 c\'b8c v\'de cu\'e8ng cu\'e5ng c\'b6 l\'aan n\'d5u m\'cat h\'f3t t\'abi ch\'d8 trong d\'a8m ph\'f3t! C\'ab th\'f6 ngh\'dc, l\'b5
m sao m\'b5 kh\'abng x\'f3c \'ae\'e9ng s\'a9u xa \'ae\'ad\'eec, khi \'ae\'ad\'eec \'ae\'e8i \'ae\'b7i nh\'ad th\'d5?
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Ng\'b5y nay, c\'f8 m\'e7i l\'c7n ra kh\'e1i c\'f6a, th\'cb
t t\'abi kh\'abng sao che gi\'cau n\'e6i ni\'d2m t\'f9 h\'b5o \'ae\'ad\'eec l\'b5 m\'e9t ng\'ad\'eai An Nam v\'b5 s\'f9 ki\'aau h\'b7nh \'ae\'ad\'eec c\'e3 m\'e9t v\'de ho\'b5ng \'ae\'d5.
\par }\pard\plain \s24\qr \fi397\li0\ri567\sb360\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin567\lin0\itap0 \f38\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 nguy\'d4n \'b8i qu\'e8c
