\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-250\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 B\'d0cs\'ab (Guyxtanh), th\'ad\'eeng ngh\'de s\'dc qu\'cb
n Anp\'ac H\'b9, Anp\'ac th\'cap thu\'e9c c\'b8c H\'e9i b\'e1 th\'c7u v\'b5 khai th\'b8c \'eb \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng, H\'e9i qu\'e8c t\'d5 nghi\'aan c\'f8u v\'b5 x\'a9y d\'f9ng \'eb Mar\'e8c v\'b5 H\'e9i b\'e1 th\'c7u \'eb t\'a9y Mar\'e8c.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-250\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Rul\'a8ng (v\'a9ng, c\'e8 nhi\'aan), th\'ad\'eeng ngh\'de
