\par C\'b8c \'abng:
\par }{\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'b8}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 cc\'a8mbray, ngh\'de s\'dc qu\'cbn Exn\'ac, thu\'e9c T\'a9n c\'abng ty Phi ch\'a9u v\'d2 th\'ad\'acng m\'b9i, k\'fc ngh\'d6 v\'b5 canh n\'abng.
\par }{\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'b8}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 ct\'ab, ngh\'de s\'dc qu\'cbn C\'f6a s\'abng R\'abn, Gi\'b8m \'ae\'e8c C\'abng ty Ph\'b8p qu\'e8c c\'f1a T\'a9y Phi, tr\'ad\'ebng ban tr\'de s\'f9 th\'ad\'acng qu\'b8n Ph\'b8p - Mar\'e8c v\'b5 nh
\'f7ng nh\'b5 m\'b8y \'ae\'ad\'eang thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea.
\par Bal\'a8ng\'ae\'ac, ngh\'de s\'dc qu\'cbn Gir\'abng, thu\'e9c U\'fb ban li\'aan bang thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea.
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-250\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 R\'acnaden, ngh\'de s\'dc qu\'cbn Anh\'aer\'ac, thu\'e9c v
\'efng m\'e1 Bu\'b8cpha (Mar\'e8c).
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-250\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Bect\'abl\'abni, ngh\'de s\'dc qu\'cbn Xavoa, L\'b5o, thu
\'e9c C\'abng ty th\'ad\'acng m\'b9i L\'b5o.
\par C\'a8mbrud\'ac, ngh\'de s\'dc qu\'cbn Gir\'abng, thu\'e9c C\'abng ty Ph\'b8p \'eb T\'abg\'ab.
\par Satxenh\'ac G\'abi\'abng, ngh\'de s\'dc qu\'cbn Xen, Ph\'e3 ch\'f1 t\'dech H\'e9i h\'eep nh\'cat Liegi\'ac \'ae\'aa Ham\'a8ng\'aea - Ti\'d3u Kabili.
\par Duybo\'a8ng (Gi\'becke), ngh\'de s\'dc qu\'cbn Xavoa, L\'b5o, thu\'e9c C\'abng ty Mar\'e8c v\'abi, xim\'a8ng, v\'b5 v\'cbt li\'d6u x\'a9y d\'f9ng.
\par Ph\'acd\'a8ng, ngh\'de s\'dc qu\'cbn Xa\'abn v\'b5 Loa, thu\'e9c T\'e6ng c\'abng ty Ph\'b8p v\'b5 \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng v\'d2 l\'f4a.
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 Oen\'aeen (Phr\'a8ngxoa \'ae\'ea), ngh\'de s\'dc qu\'cbn M
\'edc v\'b5 M\'abden, thu\'e9c c\'b8c m\'e1 thi\'d5c v\'b5 v\'abnphram \'eb B\'bec K\'fa.
\par }\pard \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-272\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\insrsid1378858 Gaxparanh, ngh\'de s\'dc \'ae\'b6o R\'aauyni\'abng, thu\'e9c C\'abng ty Ph\'b8p \'eb T\'abg\'ab.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-272\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Gir\'ab (Huybe), ngh\'de s\'dc qu\'cbn C\'f6a s\'abng R
\'abn, Gi\'b8m \'ae\'e8c Ng\'a9n h\'b5ng Xyri v\'b5 C\'abng ty Mar\'e8c.
\par Han\'aa (Anbe), ngh\'de s\'dc qu\'cbn Exn\'ac, thu\'e9c C\'abng ty th\'b6m T\'abn ph\'f1.
\par Gi\'e8tx\'ac (Pr\'abxp\'ac), ngh\'de s\'dc qu\'cbn \'a5r\'ac, thu\'e9c Ph\'b8p qu\'e8c ng\'a9n h\'b5ng ch\'a9u Phi x\'ddch \'ae\'b9o, c\'f1a C\'abng ty Phi v\'b5 C\'abngg\'ab.
\par Lus\'ac, ngh\'de s\'dc qu\'cbn No, thu\'e9c T\'e6ng c\'abng ty c\'b8c x\'dd nghi\'d6p \'eb Mar\'e8c.
\par - Qu\'b6 th\'cbt, t\'abi n\'e3i v\'edi anh b\'b9n, \'ae\'cay \'ae\'f3ng l\'b5 nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai \'ae\'b9i di\'d6n v\'f5a cho quy\'d2n l\'eei th\'cbt s\'f9 c\'f1a c\'f6 tri \'eb Qu\'e8c h\'e9i Ph\'b8p, v\'f5a cho quy\'d2n l\'eei v\'b5 n\'d2n v\'a8n ho
\'b8 Ph\'b8p \'eb thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea. Nh\'adng c\'dfn...
\par - T\'ed bi\'d5t c\'cbu s\'bep n\'e3i g\'d7, X\'abra ng\'bet l\'eai t\'abi, c\'cbu mu\'e8n b\'b6o t\'ed kh\'abng ngh\'dc \'ae\'d5n b\'e4n thu\'e9c r\'ad\'eeu Rum hay thu\'e9c \'ae\'e9c quy\'d2n r\'ad\'eeu, ch\'f8 g\'d7? Nh\'adng danh s\'b8ch \'ae\'b7 d\'b5
i v\'b5 c\'a8n nh\'b5 ch\'f8a s\'cf b\'d0 qu\'b8 kh\'abng \'ae\'f1 cho t\'cat c\'b6 nh\'f7ng con ng\'ad\'eai n\'b5y. V\'edi l\'b9i k\'fa t\'edi t\'ed c\'dfn m\'e9t \'ae\'d2 ngh\'de hay h\'acn nhi\'d2u c\'ac.
\par Kh\'e3i thu\'e8c d\'b5y \'ae\'c6c tho\'b8t ra t\'f5 t\'c8u v\'a9y l\'cay X\'abra nh\'ad h\'ad\'acng th\'acm c\'f1a nh\'f7ng \'abng ch\'e5ng chung thu\'fb bao quanh th\'b8nh Gi\'abd\'d0p. X\'abra ch\'cbm r\'b7i b\'b6o t\'abi: C\'cbu c\'e3 bi\'d5t l\'b5
 Anbe Xar\'ab \'ae\'b7 \'ae\'e6 b\'d3 r\'e5i kh\'abng?
\par - ...
\par - \'a7\'f5ng v\'ea ng\'e8c ngh\'d5ch n\'f7a \'aei n\'b5o! C\'cbu th\'f5a bi\'d5t l\'b5 t\'ed n\'e3i \'ae\'d5n con t\'c7u - con t\'c7u duy nh\'cat c\'f1a H\'b9m \'ae\'e9i \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng - \'cay m\'b5... M\'b5 c\'cbu kh\'abng hi\'d3u g\'d7, th\'d7 
\'ae\'d3 t\'ed k\'d3 cho nghe. Mu\'e8n c\'e3 m\'e9t H\'b9m \'ae\'e9i \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng, th\'d7 ph\'b6i c\'e3 m\'e9t chi\'d5c t\'b5u \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng. Th\'d5 l\'b5 ng\'ad\'eai ta cho \'ae\'e3ng "con t\'c7u". R\'e5i ng\'ad\'eai ta l\'cay t\'aan v
\'de c\'c7m l\'b8i l\'edn \'ae\'c6t t\'aan cho c\'b8i l\'b8i l\'edn. Dung l\'ad\'eeng con t\'c7u ch\'b9y h\'aci n\'ad\'edc n\'b5y, khi ra kh\'e1i x\'ad\'ebng, ch\'d8 l\'b5 3.500 t\'can. M\'cay h\'abm sau, trong b\'b5i di\'d4n v\'a8n c\'f1a v\'de cha \'ae
\'ec \'ae\'c7u l\'f5ng danh c\'f1a n\'e3, n\'e3 c\'e3 dung l\'ad\'eeng 6.000 t\'can. M\'cay th\'b8ng sau, trong b\'b5i \'ae\'a8ng tr\'aan m\'e9t t\'ea b\'b8o l\'edn th\'d7 dung l\'ad\'eeng n\'e3 l\'b5 60.000 t\'can. Ph\'b6i c\'b8i l\'b5 \'ae\'b8ng l\'cf
 ph\'b6i ch\'b9y 12 n\'f3t}{\cs17\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 1{\footnote \pard\plain \s28\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa60\sl-240\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {
\insrsid1378858 1) N\'f3t l\'b5 \'ae\'acn v\'de ch\'d8 t\'e8c \'ae\'e9 h\'b5ng h\'b6i. T\'b5u ch\'b9y m\'ad\'eai n\'f3t l\'b5 ch\'b9y m\'ad\'eai h\'b6i l\'fd/gi\'ea. G\'e4i h\'b6i l\'fd/gi\'ea nh\'ad th\'d5, th\'d7 chuy\'d3n \'ae\'ad\'eec t\'f5 d\'efng ch
\'e7 ch\'aci ch\'f7 n\'b5y, v\'edi noeud coulant = n\'f3t th\'dfng l\'e4ng.}})}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 , th\'d7 tho\'b9t \'ae\'c7u n\'e3 ch\'d8 ch\'b9y c\'e3 6 n\'f3t th\'abi.
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 B\'a9y gi\'ea n\'e3 ch\'d5t gi\'cac.
\par \'a7\'d3 t\'b8n thi\'aan h\'b9, ng\'ad\'eai ta d\'c9n n\'e3 sang ch\'aci Trung Hoa. V\'d7 qu\'aan kh\'abng cho n\'e3 \'aei t\'b5u ho\'b6, \'ae\'d5n Th\'ad\'eeng H\'b6i, c\'b8i c\'f1a \'cay kh\'abng ch\'deu \'aei n\'f7a, n\'e3 h\'e1ng, n\'e3 r\'d8 n\'ad
\'edc, n\'e3 h\'ad s\'f3pde, n\'e3 \'ae\'denh t\'f9 t\'f6, n\'e3 ch\'d8 c\'dfn l\'b5 c\'b8i... n\'f3t th\'dfng l\'e4ng. T\'ad\'ebng ch\'f5ng con t\'b5u kh\'e8n kh\'e6 m\'bec b\'d6nh tim la. Nh\'adng kh\'abng h\'d2 g\'d7, \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng v\'c9n ki
\'aau h\'b7nh c\'e3 h\'b9m \'ae\'e9i c\'f1a m\'d7nh v\'b5 c\'e3 nh\'f7ng Xar\'ab c\'f1a m\'d7nh.
\par - Th\'d5 c\'cbu n\'e3i v\'edi t\'ed l\'b5m g\'d7? T\'ed s\'cf l\'b5 m\'e9t th\'bbng v\'ab \'acn b\'e9i ngh\'dca.
\par - \'a7\'d3 b\'b6o c\'cbu r\'bbng t\'ed s\'cf l\'b5 m\'e9t th\'bbng v\'ab \'acn b\'e9i ngh\'dca n\'d5u kh\'abng \'ae\'ada ng\'b5i th\'ad\'eeng th\'ad thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea c\'f1a ch\'f3ng ta v\'b5o Vi\'d6n h\'b5n... l\'a9m.
\par - V\'edi t\'ad c\'b8ch l\'b5 \'ae\'ab \'ae\'e8c H\'b9m \'ae\'e9i \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng \'b5?
\par - \'a7\'a9u c\'e3. T\'ad c\'b8ch ch\'f1 nhi\'d6m khoa gi\'b6i ph\'c9u.
\par - ...?
\par - Ph\'b6i. Gi\'b6i ph\'c9u. \'a4ng ta \'eb \'ae\'cay l\'b5 h\'eep kh\'ddt. Th\'d5 c\'cbu kh\'abng nghe \'abng ta n\'e3i v\'d2 "b\'b5n gi\'b6i ph\'c9u" \'eb Qu\'b6ng tr\'ad\'eang Ho\'b5 h\'eep}{\cs17\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 2{\footnote \pard\plain 
\s28\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa60\sl-240\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 2) Qu\'b6ng tr\'ad\'eang Concorde l\'b5 m\'e9t qu\'b6ng tr\'ad\'eang lo
\'b9i l\'edn nh\'cat \'eb Pari}{\f38\insrsid1378858 . \'fd}{\insrsid1378858  n\'e3i: di\'d4n v\'a8n tr\'ad\'edc qu\'c7n ch\'f3ng r\'e9ng r\'b7i.}})}{\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858  }{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 sao?
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\expnd0\expndtw-2\insrsid1378858 C\'cbu kh\'abng bi\'d5t l\'b5 c\'b6 tr\'ad
\'eang \'ae\'b9i h\'e4c y khoa nh\'e8n nh\'b8o c\'b6 l\'aan v\'d7 c\'b8i b\'b6n tuy\'aan ng\'abn khoa h\'e4c c\'f1a C\'f4 l\'edn \'b5? "Ng\'b5i y\'aau qu\'fd nhi\'d6m v\'f4 \'ae\'d5n qu\'c6n c\'b6 l\'dfng. Ni\'d2m say \'ae\'bem \'ae\'e8i v\'edi n\'e7i c
\'efng c\'f9c cao c\'b6 g\'ben nh\'f7ng c\'acn s\'e8t n\'e3ng c\'f1a n\'e3 v\'b5o da th\'det ng\'b5i. N\'e3 ho\'b5 l\'f6a c\'f1a n\'e3 v\'b5o m\'b8u ng\'b5i, trong huy\'d5t qu\'b6n ng\'b5i, c\'f2ng nh\'ad v\'b5o \'ae\'ad\'eang g\'a9n ng\'b5i, th\'ed th
\'det ng\'b5i, c\'f8 nh\'ad chi\'d5c \'b8o l\'f6a c\'f1a N\'d0txuy b\'b8m l\'cay h\'abng l\'cay c\'cbt".
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 T\'abi th\'ddch ng\'b5i th\'ad\'eeng th\'ad n\'e3i. T\'ab
i th\'ddch nh\'d7n nh\'f7ng \'ae\'e9i ng\'f2 \'ae\'abng \'ae\'b6o c\'f1a h\'e4... Ti\'d5ng h\'ab l\'f3c n\'b5y th\'e8t ra t\'f5 l\'e5ng ng\'f9c t\'abi... r\'e3t v\'b5i d\'dfng trong huy\'d5t m\'b9ch t\'abi ch\'cat \'ae\'e9c \'b8c nghi\'d6t m\'b5 th\'b8
nh th\'c7n... C\'e3 nh\'f7ng k\'ce m\'c6t t\'e8i t\'a8m kh\'abng bao gi\'ea c\'e3 \'b8nh s\'b8ng lung linh soi \'ae\'d5n. Nh\'f7ng l\'eai x\'ada kia th\'e8t l\'aan t\'f5 tr\'b8i tim v\'dc \'ae\'b9i nh\'cat... v\'a9n v\'a9n... C\'cbu ngh\'dc xem v\'edi nh
\'f7ng b\'bep th\'det, nh\'f7ng \'ae\'ad\'eang g\'a9n, c\'b8i... m\'c6t v\'b5 nh\'f7ng \'ae\'e9i ng\'f2 \'cay, c\'e3 th\'d3 n\'c6n ra \'ae\'ad\'eec m\'e9t v\'de khai ho\'b8 c\'f5 l\'bem ch\'f8, tr\'f5 phi...
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 Nh\'adng th\'abi, ta h\'b7y \'aei u\'e8ng v\'b9i bia, ch
\'f3c s\'f8c kho\'ce Ai C\'cbp Ho\'b5ng \'ae\'d5 ch\'f8?
\par }\pard\plain \s24\qr \fi397\li0\ri567\sb360\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin567\lin0\itap0 \f38\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 Nguy\'d4n \'b8i qu\'e8c
\par }\pard\plain \s26\ql \li0\ri567\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin567\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 B\'b8o}{\i\insrsid1378858  Le Paria}{\insrsid1378858 , s\'e8
 12, th\'b8ng 2-1923
