\par }\pard\plain \s20\qc \li0\ri0\sb1400\sa440\sl-380\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \b\f38\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 CH\'f1 NGH\'dcA QU\'a2N PHI\'d6T TH\'f9C D\'a2N
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-268\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Ch\'f3ng t\'abi \'ae\'b7 n\'e3i r\'bbng, vi\'d6c b\'bet l
\'ddnh r\'b8o ri\'d5t l\'b5 m\'e9t trong nh\'f7ng nguy\'aan nh\'a9n th\'f3c \'ae\'c8y ng\'ad\'eai \'a7ah\'abm\'a9y \'ae\'f8ng l\'aan b\'b9o \'ae\'e9ng.
\par Tr\'ad\'edc h\'d5t, ch\'f3ng ta th\'cay ngay m\'e9t s\'f9 b\'cat b\'d7nh \'ae\'bcng n\'e6i b\'cbt: ng\'ad\'eai Ph\'b8p ch\'d8 ph\'f4c v\'f4 trong qu\'a9n \'ae\'e9i hai n\'a8m, c\'dfn ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8 th\'d7 ph\'b6i ph\'f4c v\'f4 ba n\'a8
m. Sau khi b\'e1 ra 36 th\'b8ng tu\'e6i thanh xu\'a9n t\'ad\'aci \'ae\'d1p c\'f1a m\'d7nh \'ae\'d3 b\'b6o v\'d6 t\'f9 do v\'b5 c\'abng l\'fd (?), ng\'ad\'eai d\'a9n b\'b6n x\'f8 \'ae\'ad\'eec gi\'b6i ng\'f2 l\'b9i ch\'deu s\'f9 t\'b8c \'ae\'e9ng c\'f1a 
\'ae\'b9o lu\'cbt v\'d2 ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8 trong \'ae\'e3 kh\'abng c\'e3 t\'f9 do v\'b5 c\'abng l\'fd! Song s\'f9 b\'cat b\'d7nh \'ae\'bcng \'cay c\'f2ng 
\par c\'e3 c\'b8i t\'e8t: n\'e3 g\'a9y ra cho t\'cat c\'b6 nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8 c\'b8i t\'a9m tr\'b9ng ch\'e8ng ch\'f1 ngh\'dca qu\'a9n phi\'d6t.
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-268\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 S\'f9 t\'b5n \'b8c c\'f1a b\'e4n b\'bet l\'ddnh \'eb c\'b8
c thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea tinh vi t\'edi m\'f8c th\'cbm ch\'dd ng\'ad\'eai Ph\'b8p \'eb ch\'ddnh qu\'e8c c\'f2ng kh\'abng th\'d3 h\'d7nh dung \'ae\'ad\'eec m\'e9t c\'b8i g\'d7 gi\'e8ng nh\'ad th\'d5. Trong th\'eai gian chi\'d5n tranh, nh\'f7ng vi\'aan ch\'d8
 huy mang l\'ddnh \'aei h\'d5t l\'b5ng n\'b5y sang l\'b5ng kh\'b8c bu\'e9c ch\'ddnh quy\'d2n b\'b6n x\'f8 cung c\'cap ngay l\'cbp t\'f8c s\'e8 ng\'ad\'eai c\'c7n thi\'d5t \'ae\'d3 \'ae\'ada v\'b5o qu\'a9n \'ae\'e9i.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-268\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858\charrsid11492876 L\'cf n\'b5o m\'e9t s\'dc quan Ph\'b8p th
\'b8o v\'b8t l\'b9i kh\'abng bi\'d5t tra t\'can nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai cha v\'b5 nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai m\'d1 c\'f1a nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai X\'aan\'aagan tr\'ce tu\'e6i \'aeang l\'c8n tr\'e8n khi \'abng ta xu\'cat hi\'d6n, \'ae\'d3 bu\'e9c h\'e4 ph\'b6
i chui ra kh\'e1i nh\'f7ng n\'aci \'c8n n\'cap c\'f1a h\'e4 v\'b5 kho\'b8c b\'e9 \'b8o l\'ddnh Duav\'ac? L\'cf n\'b5o h\'ben l\'b9i kh\'abng b\'bet c\'b8c \'abng gi\'b5, ph\'f4 n\'f7 c\'e3 mang, thi\'d5u n\'f7, bu\'e9c h\'e4 ph\'b6i c\'ebi tr\'c7n tru\'e5
ng v\'b5 \'ae\'e8t qu\'c7n \'b8o c\'f1a h\'e4 ngay tr\'ad\'edc m\'bet h\'e4. Tr\'c7n tru\'e5ng, b\'de tr\'e3i, nh\'f7ng n\'b9n nh\'a9n b\'cat h\'b9nh bu\'e9c ph\'b6i ch\'b9y kh\'bep l\'b5ng d\'ad\'edi tr\'cbn m\'ada roi \'ae\'d3 l\'b5m}{\insrsid1378858  "
}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858\charrsid11492876 g\'ad\'acng". M\'e9t ng\'ad\'eai ph\'f4 n\'f7 c\'e2n}{\insrsid1378858 g con}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \li0\ri0\sa80\sl-268\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 \'ae\'bbng sau l\'adng bu\'e9c ph\'b6i xin ph\'d0p \'ae\'ad\'ee
c c\'ebi tr\'e3i m\'e9t tay \'ae\'d3 \'ae\'ec l\'cay \'ae\'f8a b\'d0 cho kh\'e1i ng\'b7. Hai c\'f4 gi\'b5 \'ae\'b7 ng\'b7 b\'cat t\'d8nh nh\'a9n s\'f9 trong cu\'e9c ch\'b9y \'cay. Nh\'f7ng em g\'b8i b\'de h\'b5nh h\'b9 nh\'ad th\'d5 \'ae\'b7 h\'b5
nh kinh tr\'ad\'edc tu\'e6i, m\'e9t ph\'f4 n\'f7 c\'e3 mang, \'ae\'f8a con sinh ra \'ae\'b7 b\'de ch\'d5t, m\'e9t ph\'f4 n\'f7 kh\'b8c th\'d7 \'ae\'f8a con sinh ra \'ae\'b7 b\'de m\'ef.
\par }\pard\plain \s24\qr \fi397\li0\ri567\sb360\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin567\lin0\itap0 \f38\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 Nguy\'d4n \'b8i Qu\'e8c
