\'f5 "chinoiserie" trong ti\'d5ng Ph\'b8p, xu\'cat ph\'b8t t\'f5 chinois: Trung Qu\'e8c; chinoiserie (tr\'df T\'b5u), ch\'d8 c\'b8i g\'d7 k\'fa qu\'c6c, v\'d7 ng\'ad\'eai Ph\'b8p tr\'ad\'edc \'ae\'a9y cho r\'bbng c\'b8i g\'d7 \'eb Trung Qu\'e8c c\'f2ng l
\'b5 k\'fa qu\'c6c. C\'f2ng nh\'ad }{\i\insrsid1378858 chinoiserie, Indochinoiserie}{\insrsid1378858  \'ae\'ad\'eec \'ae\'c6t ra \'ae\'d3 ch\'d5 gi\'d4u.}})}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  to \'ae\'efng khi \'ae\'ada Ng\'b5i l\'aan cai tr\'de m\'e9t \'ae\'ca
t n\'ad\'edc m\'b5 Ng\'b5i kh\'abng bi\'d5t g\'d7 v\'d2 n\'e3 c\'b6.
\par Th\'d7, \'ae\'f3ng th\'d5! Nh\'adng \'ae\'e3 l\'b5 c\'b8i m\'e8t m\'b5 m\'e9t b\'b9n \'ae\'e5ng nghi\'d6p, h\'abm n\'e4 cho bi\'d5t \'abng \'ae\'b7 th\'cay ch\'d4m ch\'d6 ng\'e5i \'eb v\'f4 T\'a9y Phi thu\'e9c Ph\'b8p c\'f1a B\'e9 Thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea m\'e9
t c\'f9u c\'abng s\'f8 \'eb \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng. M\'e9t c\'f9u c\'abng s\'f8 kh\'b8c \'eb T\'a9y Phi th\'d7 l\'b9i \'ae\'b6m nhi\'d6m vi\'d6c ch\'a9u Phi x\'ddch \'ae\'b9o. M\'e9t c\'f9u quan ch\'f8c \'eb Xu\'ae\'a8ng}{
