\f37\insrsid1378858\charrsid11492876 Xu\'ae\'a8ng thu\'e9c Ph\'b8p, b\'a9y gi\'ea l\'b5 n\'ad\'edc Mali, kh\'b8c v\'edi Xu\'ae\'a8ng thu\'e9c Anh, b\'a9y gi\'ea l\'b5 n\'ad\'edc Xu\'ae\'a8ng.}})}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  th\'d7 l\'b9i \'ae\'ad\'eec ch
\'e4n \'ae\'d3 ph\'f4 tr\'b8ch c\'b8c v\'can \'ae\'d2 v\'d2 Ma\'aeag\'b8txca, trong khi \'ae\'e3, \'eb H\'e9i ch\'ee thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea, ng\'ad\'eai \'ae\'b9i di\'d6n cho Cam\'acrun l\'b9i l\'b5 m\'e9t quan ch\'f8c ch\'ada h\'d2 \'ae\'c6t ch\'a9n l\'aan n
\'ad\'edc n\'b5y bao gi\'ea.
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-264\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 V\'b6 l\'b9i, c\'c7n qu\'b8i g\'d7, n\'d5u quy\'d2n l\'eei c\'f1a n\'ad\'edc Ph\'b8p c\'e3 b\'de M\'d0clanh qu\'b6n l
\'fd t\'e5i th\'d7 \'ae\'b7 sao, mi\'d4n l\'b5 quy\'d2n l\'eei c\'b8 nh\'a9n c\'f1a \'abng b\'e9 tr\'ad\'ebng \'ae\'ad\'eec ph\'f4c v\'f4 t\'e8t. T\'ea }{\i\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 "Petit Bleu"}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  b\'b5n v\'d2 s\'f9 b\'e6 nhi\'d6
m t\'a9n th\'b8i th\'f3 \'ae\'b7 n\'e3i th\'d5 n\'b5y:
\par "\'a7\'f5ng c\'e3 m\'b5 l\'c7m; kh\'abng ph\'b6i l\'dfng tham c\'f1a \'abng M\'d0clanh \'ae\'b7 l\'b8i \'abng ta m\'b5 l\'b5 l\'dfng tham c\'f1a \'abng Xar\'ab \'ae\'b7 g\'a9y ra m\'e4i tai h\'b9i".
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-264\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 Qu\'b6 v\'cby, \'abng Xar\'ab th\'d7, nh\'ad ch\'f3ng t\'ab
i \'ae\'b7 n\'e3i v\'b5 ch\'b8n v\'b9n ng\'ad\'eai c\'f2ng \'ae\'b7 n\'e3i, mu\'e8n tr\'eb l\'b9i \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng v\'b5 ch\'bec ch\'ben \'abng ta s\'cf l\'b5 ng\'ad\'eai th\'d5 ch\'a9n ngay \'abng L\'abng, n\'d5u kh\'abng c\'e3 cu\'e9c b\'c7u c\'f6
 ngh\'de vi\'d6n s\'bep di\'d4n ra ch\'f5ng m\'ad\'aci th\'b8ng t\'edi. Th\'d5 nh\'adng, tuy c\'e3 th\'ccm mu\'e8n l\'b5m To\'b5n quy\'d2n \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng \'ae\'cay, \'abng Xar\'ab l\'b9i kh\'abng mu\'e8n v\'d7 th\'d5 b\'e1 ch\'f8c v\'f4 \'eb ngh
\'de vi\'d6n. D\'a9n gian c\'e3 c\'a9u t\'f4c ng\'f7: "S\'e8 ph\'cbn ai hay s\'cf th\'d5 n\'b5o". Ngh\'de s\'dc h\'b9 vi\'d6n hay ngh\'de s\'dc th\'ad\'eeng vi\'d6n, th\'d7 bi\'d5t \'ae\'a9u m\'e9t s\'edm kia t\'d8nh d\'cby l\'b9i ch\'b6 th\'cay m\'d7nh l
\'b5 b\'e9 tr\'ad\'ebng, c\'dfn c\'e3 th\'d3 l\'b5 th\'f1 t\'ad\'edng n\'f7a \'cay ch\'f8; c\'dfn n\'d5u ch\'d8 l\'b5 to\'b5n quy\'d2n, ngh\'dca l\'b5 vi\'aan ch\'f8c, th\'d7 kh\'abng l\'b5m b\'e9 tr\'ad\'ebng \'ae\'ad\'eec.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-264\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 V\'cby th\'d7 v\'can \'ae\'d2 l\'b5 h\'b7y \'ae\'c6t \'eb 
\'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng m\'e9t quan ch\'f8c c\'e3 th\'d3 g\'e4i l\'b5 t\'b9m quy\'d2n, \'ae\'d3 \'ae\'d5n m\'efa xu\'a9n sang n\'a8m, sau k\'fa b\'c7u c\'f6 ngh\'de vi\'d6n, th\'d7 \'abng Xar\'ab s\'cf d\'d4 d\'b5ng th\'d5 ch\'a9n. Th\'d5 l\'b5 \'abng ngh
\'dc ngay \'ae\'d5n vi\'d6c ch\'e4n \'abng M\'d0clanh v\'b5o c\'b8i v\'de tr\'dd ch\'b6 th\'f3 v\'de g\'d7 \'cay, b\'ebi v\'d7 \'abng n\'b5y s\'bep m\'b7n h\'b9n l\'b5m vi\'d6c, ch\'b6 bao l\'a9u n\'f7a \'abng \'ae\'b7 \'ae\'f1 quy\'d2n v\'d2 h\'adu.

\par \'a7\'e3, v\'d7 sao \'abng M\'d0clanh s\'bep l\'aan \'ae\'ad\'eang sang \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng, v\'d7 sao bao nhi\'aau c\'abng vi\'d6c h\'f7u \'ddch m\'edi b\'bet \'ae\'c7u \'eb T\'a9y Phi b\'de \'abng x\'d5p x\'e3, v\'d7 sao \'eb Vi\'d4n \'a7\'abng, \'ab
ng s\'cf ch\'bcng l\'b5m vi\'d6c g\'d7 \'ae\'b8ng k\'d3 m\'b5 ch\'bec s\'cf ch\'d8 l\'b5m cho xong vi\'d6c s\'f9 v\'f4 v\'d7 bi\'d5t r\'bbng m\'d7nh c\'f2ng ch\'bcng \'eb bao l\'a9u, v\'b5 v\'d7 sao n\'f7a \'eb c\'b8i "C\'e9ng ho\'b5 C\'c8m m\'b5 l\'b8
ch v\'edi nhau"}{\cs17\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 1{\footnote \pard\plain \s28\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa60\sl-240\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {
\insrsid1378858 1) Th\'b5nh ng\'f7 \'ae\'d3 ch\'d8 m\'e9t c\'e9ng \'ae\'e5ng thi\'aan v\'de n\'d3 nang, m\'e3c ngo\'c6c nhau, kh\'abng coi tr\'e4ng l\'eei \'ddch chung. D\'dech s\'b8t ngh\'dca l\'b5 "C\'e9ng ho\'b5 c\'b8c \'ae\'e5ng ch\'dd", nguy\'aan b
\'b6n vi\'d5t ti\'d5ng Ph\'b8p l\'b5 "}{\i\insrsid1378858 R\'d0publique des Camarades".}})}{\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858  }{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 n\'b5y, t\'cat c\'b6 \'ae\'d2u 
\par }\pard \qj \li0\ri0\sa80\sl-268\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 b\'de b\'e1 qua, t\'cat c\'b6 \'ae\'d2u t\'f4t d\'e8c, t\'cat c\'b6 \'ae\'d2u ng\'b5y c\'b5ng t\'e5i t\'d6, v\'d7 quy\'d2n l
\'eei c\'b8 nh\'a9n c\'f1a \'abng n\'b5y hay \'abng n\'e4 bao gi\'ea c\'f2ng \'ae\'d2u \'ae\'c6t l\'aan tr\'aan quy\'d2n l\'eei chung c\'f1a \'ae\'cat n\'ad\'edc.
\par }\pard\plain \s24\qr \fi397\li0\ri850\sb360\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin850\lin0\itap0 \f38\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 N.
