c l\'b5 quan cai tr\'de t\'d8nh, b\'de l\'aan \'b8n l\'b5 \'a8n h\'e8i l\'e9, l\'b5 c\'ad\'eang h\'b5o v\'b5 \'ae\'b7 g\'a9y ra cu\'e9c n\'e6i d\'cby \'ae\'c9m m\'b8u \'eb Th\'b8i Nguy\'aan, \'ae\'b7 \'ae\'ad\'eec ch\'ddnh ph\'f1 thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea c\'f6
 v\'b5o H\'e9i \'ae\'e5ng th\'b5nh ph\'e8 S\'b5i G\'dfn.
\par \'a4ng T\'aaa, k\'fc s\'ad v\'b5 gi\'b8m \'ae\'e8c m\'e9t h\'b7ng bu\'abn l\'edn, b\'de t\'e8 c\'b8o l\'b5 c\'e3 t\'e9i nh\'f2ng l\'b9m m\'b5 kh\'abng b\'de r\'c7y r\'b5 g\'d7.
\par Gi\'ea \'ae\'d5n l\'ad\'eet Bu\'aein\'ab, vi\'aan quan cai tr\'de n\'b5y b\'de ki\'d6n: \'ae\'b7 \'ae\'f3t t\'f3i s\'e8 ti\'d2n l\'eai m\'e9t cu\'e9c ch\'ee phi\'aan t\'e6 ch\'f8c nh\'a9n d\'dep kh\'b8nh th\'b5nh t\'ad\'eeng \'ae\'b5i t\'f6 s\'dc; \'ae
\'b7 \'ae\'dfi v\'b5 nh\'cbn m\'e9t m\'e3n ti\'d2n "b\'e5i th\'ad\'eang" l\'edn tr\'b6 cho s\'f9 c\'e3 m\'c6t c\'f1a m\'d7nh trong bu\'e6i ch\'abn c\'cat m\'e9t m\'f4 nh\'b5 gi\'b5u b\'b6n x\'f8, \'ae\'b7 \'ae\'dfi nh\'f7ng m\'e3n ti\'d2n l\'edn ch\'cc l
\'b8 khi c\'cap m\'e9t gi\'cay ph\'d0p hay gi\'cay l\'d6nh n\'b5o \'ae\'e3.
\par Cu\'e8i c\'efng, \'ae\'b7 l\'eei d\'f4ng, trong m\'e4i tr\'ad\'eang h\'eep quy\'d2n h\'b5nh quan cai tr\'de (m\'b5 n\'ad\'edc Ph\'b8p c\'e3 ch\'f1 quy\'d2n \'ae\'b7 u\'fb th\'b8c cho) \'ae\'d3 l\'b5m \'ae\'e6 m\'e5 h\'abi s\'abi n\'ad\'edc m\'bet ng\'ad
\'eai b\'de tr\'de v\'b5 \'ae\'d3 cho ph\'d7nh v\'dd ti\'d2n c\'f1a \'abng ta. Nh\'adng l\'eai k\'d5t t\'e9i n\'c6ng nh\'cat l\'b5 th\'d5 n\'b5y: L\'b5ng T\'a9n An (Nam K\'fa) c\'e3 m\'e9t nh\'b5 m\'b8y \'aei\'d6n. Vi\'d6c khai th\'b8c c\'e3 l\'eei v\'b5
 ph\'e8 x\'b8, nh\'b5 c\'f6a trong l\'b5ng c\'e3 \'aei\'d6n s\'b8ng m\'b5 kh\'abng ph\'b6i tr\'b6 ti\'d2n. Quan cai tr\'de Bu\'aein\'ab bu\'e9c l\'b5ng ph\'b6i nh\'ad\'eeng kh\'abng nh\'b5 m\'b8y cho m\'e9t anh th\'c7u kho\'b8n \'ae\'b7 c\'e3 vi thi\'d2
ng cho \'abng ta.
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'dd}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 t l\'a9u sau, l\'b5ng ph\'b6i tr\'b6 ti\'d2n \'aei\'d6n d\'efng ngo\'b5i ph\'e8 v\'b5
 trong nh\'b5. Th\'cay h\'b5ng ngh\'d7n \'aei\'d2u b\'cat l\'eei, h\'e4 m\'edi bi\'d5t m\'d7nh t\'f9 qu\'b6n nh\'b5 m\'b8y th\'d7 l\'eei h\'acn. H\'e4 ph\'b6i b\'e1 ra m\'cay ch\'f4c ng\'b5n \'ae\'e5ng \'ae\'d3 chu\'e9c l\'b9i c\'b8i m\'b5 h\'e4 \'ae\'b7
 ph\'b6i "nh\'ad\'eeng kh\'abng". L\'c7n th\'f8 hai n\'b5y, v\'de quan cai tr\'de \'ae\'f3t t\'f3i th\'aam m\'cay t\'ea b\'b9c l\'edn n\'f7a.
\par B\'de ki\'d6n v\'d7 t\'e9i bu\'abn b\'b8n ng\'ad\'eai ch\'d5t, b\'e3c l\'e9t ng\'ad\'eai s\'e8ng, tham \'ab l\'e9 li\'d4u, quan cai tr\'de Bu\'aein\'ab v\'f5a \'ae\'ad\'eec c\'abng l\'fd Ph\'b8p cho tr\'beng \'b8n. Ng\'b5y mai c\'e3 th\'d3 \'abng ta c\'df
n \'ae\'ad\'eec hu\'a9n ch\'ad\'acng.
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 Bao gi\'ea ng\'ad\'eai ta c\'f2ng v\'d7 uy t\'ddn ch\'f1
ng t\'e9c, m\'b5 x\'b8 t\'e9i cho l\'f2 "v\'ab l\'b9i kh\'b6 \'e8". Bao gi\'ea ng\'ad\'eai ta c\'f2ng nh\'a9n danh nh\'a9n d\'a9n Ph\'b8p m\'b5 b\'bet c\'abng l\'fd l\'b5m \'ae\'dc b\'eem.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 V\'a8n minh l\'b5 nh\'ad th\'d5 \'ae\'e3.
\par }\pard\plain \s24\qr \fi397\li0\ri567\sb360\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin567\lin0\itap0 \f38\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 \~Nguy\'d4n \'b8i Qu\'e8c
\par }\pard\plain \s26\ql \li0\ri567\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin567\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 B\'b8o }{\i\insrsid1378858 Le Paria,}{\insrsid1378858  s\'e8 15,

