\'b5y 7-2, 37 ng\'ad\'eai ch\'d5t, h\'acn 200 ng\'ad\'eai b\'de th\'ad\'acng.}})}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 . H\'e9i coi vi\'d6c gi\'f3p \'ae\'ec c\'abng nh\'a9n n\'b9n nh\'a9n c\'f1a cu\'e9c \'ae\'cau tranh, l\'b5 ngh\'dca v\'f4 c\'f1a m\'d7nh, v\'b9ch tr
\'c7n v\'b5 l\'aan \'b8n tr\'ad\'edc to\'b5n qu\'e8c h\'b5nh \'ae\'e9ng t\'e9i \'b8c c\'f1a ch\'ddnh ph\'f1 v\'b5 b\'cc l\'f2 qu\'a9n phi\'d6t c\'f1a n\'e3 trong th\'eai gian \'ae\'d7nh c\'abng.
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-264\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 Ch\'f3ng ta c\'f2ng n\'e3i th\'aam l\'b5 Li\'aan \'aeo\'b5
