\f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 1) Trong th\'ad kh\'abng c\'e3 t\'aan ng\'ad\'eai nh\'cbn, c\'e3 th\'d3 l\'b5 Nguy\'d4n }{\f38\insrsid1378858 \'b8}{\insrsid1378858 i Qu\'e8c g\'f6i cho m\'e9t \'ae\'e5ng ch\'dd
