\par }{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 T\'abi qu\'aa qu\'b8n \'eb \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng v\'b5 l\'b5 \'ae\'b6ng vi\'aan \'a7\'b6ng C\'e9ng s\'b6n Ph\'b8p. Ch\'ddnh v\'edi t\'ad c\'b8ch \'ae\'e3 m\'b5 t\'abi m\'b9o mu\'e9i c\'b6m \'acn \'ae\'e5ng ch\'dd v\'d2 s\'f9 ch
\'f3 \'fd c\'f1a \'ae\'e5ng ch\'dd \'ae\'d5n v\'can \'ae\'d2 thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea t\'b9i \'a7\'b9i h\'e9i Li\'abng.
\par M\'c6t kh\'b8c, t\'abi s\'cf sung s\'ad\'edng v\'d7 \'ae\'ad\'eec th\'b6o lu\'cbn v\'edi \'ae\'e5ng ch\'dd v\'d2 v\'can \'ae\'d2 thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea n\'d5u \'ae\'e5ng ch\'dd vui l\'dfng cho g\'c6p.
\par }\pard\plain \s22\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f40\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Do m\'f2i v\'b5 c\'b8c ng\'e3n tay b\'de l\'b9nh c
