\'ae\'d2 \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng v\'b5 Th\'b8i B\'d7nh D\'ad\'acng kh\'abng li\'aan quan g\'d7 \'ae\'d5n c\'abng nh\'a9n ch\'a9u \'a2u. Nh\'adng n\'d5u ng\'ad\'eai ta nh\'ed l\'b9i r\'bbng:
\par }{\f37\fs20\expnd0\expndtw-2\insrsid1378858 a) Trong th\'eai k\'fa c\'b8ch m\'b9ng, c\'b8c n\'ad\'edc \'a7\'e5ng minh kh\'abng t\'can c\'abng \'ae\'ad\'eec n\'ad\'edc Nga t\'f5 ph\'dda T\'a9y, \'ae\'b7 t\'d7m c\'b8ch t\'can c\'abng t\'f5 ph\'dda \'a7\'ab
ng. Th\'d5 l\'b5 c\'b8c c\'ad\'eang qu\'e8c \'eb Th\'b8i B\'d7nh D\'ad\'acng, M\'fc v\'b5 Nh\'cbt, \'ae\'b7 cho qu\'a9n \'ae\'e9i \'ae\'e6 b\'e9 l\'aan Vla\'aeiv\'abxt\'e8c, \'ae\'e5ng th\'eai n\'ad\'edc }{\i\f37\fs20\expnd0\expndtw-2\insrsid1378858 Ph
\'b8p}{\f37\fs20\expnd0\expndtw-2\insrsid1378858  c\'f2ng g\'f6i }{\i\f37\fs20\expnd0\expndtw-2\insrsid1378858 nh\'f7ng \'ae\'b9o qu\'a9n ng\'ad\'eai \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng sang Xib\'aari}{\f37\fs20\expnd0\expndtw-2\insrsid1378858  \'ae\'d3 gi\'f3p b\'e4
n b\'b9ch qu\'a9n.
\par }\pard\plain \s22\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f40\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 b) Hi\'d6n nay, t\'cat c\'b6 sinh l\'f9c c\'f1a ch
\'f1 ngh\'dca t\'ad b\'b6n qu\'e8c t\'d5 \'ae\'d2u l\'cay \'eb c\'b8c x\'f8 thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea. \'a7\'e3 l\'b5 n\'aci ch\'f1 ngh\'dca t\'ad b\'b6n l\'cay nguy\'aan li\'d6u cho c\'b8c nh\'b5 m\'b8y c\'f1a n\'e3, n\'aci n\'e3 \'ae\'c7u t\'ad, ti\'aau th\'f4
 h\'b5ng, m\'e9 nh\'a9n c\'abng r\'ce m\'b9t cho \'ae\'b9o qu\'a9n lao \'ae\'e9ng c\'f1a n\'e3, v\'b5 nh\'cat l\'b5 tuy\'d3n nh\'f7ng binh l\'ddnh ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8 cho c\'b8c \'ae\'b9o qu\'a9n ph\'b6n c\'b8ch m\'b9ng c\'f1a n\'e3. Th\'d5 n\'b5o r
\'e5i c\'f2ng c\'e3 ng\'b5y n\'ad\'edc Nga c\'b8ch m\'b9ng ph\'b6i \'ae\'e4 s\'f8c v\'edi ch\'f1 ngh\'dca t\'ad b\'b6n \'ae\'e3. Cho n\'aan c\'b8c \'ae\'e5ng ch\'dd Nga c\'c7n ph\'b6i bi\'d5t r\'e2 t\'cat c\'b6 l\'f9c l\'ad\'eeng v\'b5 t\'cat c\'b6 c\'b8
c m\'b8nh kho\'d0 tr\'f9c ti\'d5p hay gi\'b8n ti\'d5p c\'f1a \'ae\'e8i th\'f1 c\'f1a m\'d7nh.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 c) V\'d7 \'ae\'b7 tr\'eb th\'b5nh m\'e9t trung t\'a9m m
\'b5 b\'e4n \'ae\'d5 qu\'e8c tham lam \'ae\'d2u h\'ad\'edng c\'b6 v\'b5o nh\'dfm ng\'e3, n\'aan Th\'b8i B\'d7nh D\'ad\'acng v\'b5 c\'b8c n\'ad\'edc thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea xung quanh Th\'b8i B\'d7nh D\'ad\'acng, t\'ad\'acng lai c\'e3 th\'d3 tr\'eb th\'b5nh m
\'e9t l\'df l\'f6a c\'f1a chi\'d5n tranh th\'d5 gi\'edi m\'edi m\'b5 giai c\'cap v\'ab s\'b6n s\'cf ph\'b6i nai l\'adng ra g\'b8nh.
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Xem th\'d5 th\'d7 ta th\'cay r\'e2 r\'bbng v\'can \'ae\'d2 Th\'b8i B\'d7nh D\'ad\'acng l\'b5 v\'can \'ae\'d2 m\'b5 t\'ca
t c\'b6 m\'e4i ng\'ad\'eai v\'ab s\'b6n n\'e3i chung }{\i\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'ae\'d2u ph\'b6i quan t\'a9m \'ae\'d5n}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 .
\par }\pard \qc \li0\ri0\sb80\sa80\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 *
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-254\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 \~Mu\'e8n x\'a9y d\'f9ng l\'b9i n\'ad\'edc Ph\'b8p \'ae\'b7 b\'de cu\'e9c chi\'d5n tranh \'ae\'d5 qu\'e8c ch\'f1 ngh\'dc
a t\'b5n ph\'b8, B\'e9 Thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea Ph\'b8p \'ae\'b7 th\'b6o m\'e9t d\'f9 \'b8n khai th\'b8c c\'b8c thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea. D\'f9 \'b8n \'ae\'e3 nh\'bbm khai th\'b8c nh\'f7ng t\'b5i nguy\'aan c\'f1a c\'b8c n\'ad\'edc thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea \'ae\'d3 l\'b5m l
\'eei cho ch\'ddnh qu\'e8c. C\'f2ng d\'f9 \'b8n \'cay n\'e3i r\'bbng \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng ph\'b6i gi\'f3p \'ae\'ec c\'b8c thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea kh\'b8c \'eb Th\'b8i B\'d7nh D\'ad\'acng \'ae\'c8y m\'b9nh s\'b6n xu\'cat c\'f1a h\'e4 l\'aan, \'ae\'d3 l\'b5
m cho c\'b6 c\'b8c thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea \'ae\'e3 c\'f2ng tr\'eb th\'b5nh "c\'e3 \'ddch" cho ch\'ddnh qu\'e8c. N\'d5u d\'f9 \'b8n \'ae\'ad\'eec th\'f9c hi\'d6n, th\'d7 nh\'cat \'ae\'denh l\'b5 \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng s\'cf l\'a9m v\'b5o t\'d7nh tr\'b9ng gi
\'b6m s\'f3t d\'a9n s\'e8 v\'b5 b\'c7n c\'efng.
\par Th\'d5 nh\'adng, m\'edi \'ae\'a9y, m\'c6c d\'c7u b\'de d\'ad lu\'cbn An Nam ph\'b6n kh\'b8ng, H\'e9i \'ae\'e5ng ch\'ddnh ph\'f1 \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng c\'f2ng \'ae\'b7 nh\'cat tr\'dd t\'b8n th\'b5nh d\'f9 \'b8n \'cay. Mu\'e8n hi\'d3u r\'e2 s\'f9 nh\'ca
t tr\'dd \'ae\'e3 c\'e3 gi\'b8 tr\'de \'ae\'d5n \'ae\'a9u, th\'d7 c\'f2ng c\'c7n bi\'d5t r\'bbng H\'e9i \'ae\'e5ng \'ae\'e3 g\'e5m c\'e3 To\'b5n quy\'d2n \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng, T\'ad\'edng t\'e6ng t\'ad l\'d6nh qu\'a9n \'ae\'e9i \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng v
\'b5 \'ae\'e9 ba ch\'f4c vi\'aan ch\'f8c cao c\'cap ng\'ad\'eai Ph\'b8p, c\'e9ng th\'aam n\'a8m vi\'aan quan l\'b9i b\'b6n x\'f8 do vi\'aan To\'b5n quy\'d2n n\'c6n ra. }{\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'ca}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 y th\'d5 m\'b5 t\'cat c\'b6 c
\'b8c ng\'b5i \'cay l\'b9i cho r\'bbng h\'e4 thay m\'c6t cho c\'b6 \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng v\'b5 h\'b5nh \'ae\'e9ng v\'d7 l\'eei \'ddch c\'f1a nh\'a9n d\'a9n An Nam! C\'b8c b\'b9n h\'b7y t\'ad\'ebng t\'ad\'eeng m\'b5 xem, ng\'ad\'eai \'d0txkim\'ab}{
\cs17\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 1{\footnote \pard\plain \s28\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa60\sl-240\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 1) D\'a9n c
\'ad mi\'d2n B\'bec c\'f9c.
\par 2) Nh\'f7ng b\'e9 t\'e9c \'eb mi\'d2n Nam ch\'a9u Phi.}})}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  hay ng\'ad\'eai Dulu}{\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 2)}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  m\'b5 l\'b9i quy\'d5t \'ae\'denh v\'cbn m\'d6nh c\'f1a m\'e9t d\'a9n t\'e9c ch\'a9u 
