\'ad\'acng \'ae\'ad\'acng l\'a9m v\'b5o t\'d7nh tr\'b9ng suy t\'b5n, v\'b5 ch\'d8 s\'e8ng - n\'d5u nh\'ad th\'d5 m\'b5 c\'e3 th\'d3 g\'e4i \'ae\'ad\'eec l\'b5 s\'e8ng - m\'e9t cu\'e9c s\'e8ng c\'b5ng ng\'b5y c\'b5ng l\'f4n b\'b9i \'aei. S\'f9 th\'cbt th
\'d7 trong m\'e9t th\'eai gian ng\'ben, c\'b8c \'ae\'b6o \'ae\'abng 
\par }\pard \qj \li0\ri0\sa80\sl-254\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 d\'a9n c\'ad, \'ae\'b7 ho\'b5n to\'b5n th\'ada h\'bcn \'aei v\'d7 r\'ad\'eeu c\'e5n v\'b5 lao d\'dech. Qu\'c7n \'ae\'b6o M\'b8
ckid\'ac}{\cs17\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 1{\footnote \pard\plain \s28\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa60\sl-220\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 
1) Nh\'f7ng \'ae\'b6o \'eb ch\'a9u }{\f38\insrsid1378858 \'f3}{\insrsid1378858 c thu\'e9c Ph\'b8p.}})}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 , tr\'ad\'edc \'ae\'a9y 50 n\'a8m, \'ae\'abng \'ae\'d5n 20.000 ng\'ad\'eai, m\'b5 b\'a9y gi\'ea ch\'d8 c\'dfn c\'e3 1.500 ng
\'ad\'eai y\'d5u \'aeu\'e8i v\'b5 tho\'b8i ho\'b8. Trong v\'dfng 10 n\'a8m, d\'a9n s\'e8 \'ae\'b6o Tahiti}{\cs17\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 2{\footnote \pard\plain \s28\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa60\sl-220\slmult0
\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 2) Nh\'f7ng \'ae\'b6o \'eb B\'bec ch\'a9u M\'fc thu\'e9c Ph\'b8p.}})}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  gi\'b6m \'ae
i 25%. Trong s\'e8 nh\'f7ng d\'a9n c\'ad \'aeang ch\'d5t d\'c7n ch\'d5t m\'dfn \'aei nh\'ad th\'d5, ch\'f1 ngh\'dca \'ae\'d5 qu\'e8c Ph\'b8p l\'b9i c\'dfn c\'ad\'edp \'aei h\'acn 3.500 ng\'ad\'eai \'ae\'d3 l\'b5m bia \'ae\'ec \'ae\'b9n cho ch\'f3ng. Th
\'cbt kh\'e3 m\'b5 t\'ad\'ebng t\'ad\'eeng \'ae\'ad\'eec t\'d7nh tr\'b9ng t\'b5n l\'f4i c\'f1a m\'e9t gi\'e8ng ng\'ad\'eai l\'b9i nhanh \'ae\'d5n nh\'ad th\'d5. Nh\'adng \'ae\'e3 l\'b9i l\'b5 m\'e9t s\'f9 th\'cbt m\'b5 ng\'ad\'eai ta c\'e3 th\'d3 th\'cay 
\'ae\'ad\'eec \'eb nhi\'d2u thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea. (}{\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'eb}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  c\'b8c mi\'d2n thu\'e9c C\'abngg\'ab, trong v\'dfng 20 n\'a8m, d\'a9n s\'e8 t\'f5 40.000 ng\'ad\'eai \'ae\'b7 gi\'b6m xu\'e8ng ch\'d8 c\'df
n 30.000. \'a7\'b6o Xanh Pie}{\cs17\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 3{\footnote \pard\plain \s28\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa60\sl-220\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 
