\cs17\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 4{\footnote \pard\plain \s30\ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f42\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 4) Nh\'f7ng \'ae\'b6o \'eb B\'bec ch\'a9
u M\'fc thu\'e9c Ph\'b8p.}})}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 , n\'a8m 1902 c\'e3 6.500 d\'a9n, \'ae\'d5n n\'a8m 1922, thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea n\'b5y ch\'d8 c\'dfn c\'e3 3.900 ng\'ad\'eai m\'b5 th\'abi, v.v.).
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa60\sl-252\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\expnd0\expndtw-4\insrsid1378858 H\'c7u h\'d5t c\'b8c \'ae\'b6o \'eb Th\'b8
i B\'d7nh D\'ad\'acng thu\'e9c Ph\'b8p \'ae\'d2u \'ae\'ad\'eec nh\'ad\'eeng cho c\'b8c c\'abng ty khai kh\'c8n \'ae\'e5n \'aei\'d2n. C\'b8c c\'abng ty n\'b5y t\'ad\'edc \'aeo\'b9t ru\'e9ng \'ae\'cat c\'f1a ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8 v\'b5 b\'bet h\'e4 l\'b5
m nh\'ad n\'ab l\'d6 v\'cby. \'a7\'a9y l\'b5 m\'e9t th\'dd d\'f4 ch\'f8ng t\'e1 r\'bbng ng\'ad\'eai ta \'ae\'e8i x\'f6 v\'edi c\'abng nh\'a9n b\'b6n x\'f8 nh\'ad th\'d5 n\'b5o. 200 ng\'ad\'eai chuy\'aan m\'df ng\'e4c trai \'ae\'b7 b\'de c\'b8c h\'b7ng Ph
\'b8p \'eb ch\'a9u }{\f38\expnd0\expndtw-4\insrsid1378858 \'f3}{\expnd0\expndtw-4\insrsid1378858 c b\'bet \'d0p \'ae\'ada \'aei c\'b8c \'ae\'e5n \'aei\'d2n c\'b8ch qu\'aa h\'ad\'acng c\'f1a h\'e4 \'ae\'d5n 800 h\'b6i l\'fd... (Th\'cbt kh\'abng kh\'b8c 
\'ae\'ada th\'ee may \'aei l\'b5m m\'e1). H\'e4 b\'de d\'e5n xu\'e8ng m\'e9t chi\'d5c thuy\'d2n bu\'e5m nh\'e1 ch\'d8 v\'f5a ch\'e7 cho 10 ng\'ad\'eai v\'b5 kh\'abng c\'e3 qua m\'e9t ph\'ad\'acng ti\'d6n n\'b5o ph\'dfng l\'f3c \'ae\'bem thuy\'d2n. H\'e4 b
\'de \'ae\'ada ngay xu\'e8ng thuy\'d2n kh\'abng k\'dep nh\'d7n m\'c6t v\'ee con n\'f7a. Su\'e8t hai n\'a8m r\'dfng, nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai c\'abng nh\'a9n kh\'e8n kh\'e6 \'cay b\'de \'ae\'c7y \'aeo\'b9 trong c\'b8c tr\'b9i c\'f1a c\'abng ty. Nhi\'d2u ng\'ad
\'eai b\'de \'ae\'e8i x\'f6 t\'b5n t\'d6. Nhi\'d2u ng\'ad\'eai \'ae\'b7 v\'d7 th\'d5 m\'b5 ch\'d5t.
\par }{\insrsid1378858 C\'b8c b\'b9n h\'b7y c\'e9ng th\'aam v\'b5o s\'f9 b\'e3c l\'e9t v\'ab nh\'a9n \'ae\'b9o \'cay s\'f9 t\'e5i t\'d6 c\'f1a b\'e4n v\'ab l\'ad\'acng m\'b5 \'ae\'d5 qu\'e8c Ph\'b8p giao cho cai tr\'de c\'b8c \'ae\'b6o \'ae\'e3, th\'d7 c\'b8
c b\'b9n s\'cf th\'cay t\'cat c\'b6 c\'b8i t\'e8t \'ae\'d1p c\'f1a ch\'d5 \'ae\'e9 b\'e3c l\'e9t v\'b5 \'b8p b\'f8c \'aeang \'ae\'ada c\'b8c n\'ad\'edc b\'de chi\'d5m l\'b5m thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea \'eb Th\'b8i B\'d7nh D\'ad\'acng \'ae\'d5n ch\'e7 ch\'d5t v
\'b5 di\'d6t vong.
\par }\pard \s15\qc \li0\ri0\sa80\sl-256\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\insrsid1378858 *
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-244\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Ng\'b5y nay, ch\'f1 ngh\'dca \'ae\'d5 qu\'e8c \'ae\'b7 ti
\'d5n t\'edi m\'e9t tr\'d7nh \'ae\'e9 ho\'b5n b\'de g\'c7n nh\'ad l\'b5 khoa h\'e4c. N\'e3 d\'efng nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai v\'ab s\'b6n da tr\'beng \'ae\'d3 chinh ph\'f4c nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai v\'ab s\'b6n c\'b8c thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea. Sau \'ae\'e3 n\'e3 l\'b9
i tung nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai v\'ab s\'b6n \'eb m\'e9t thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea n\'b5y \'aei \'ae\'b8nh nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai v\'ab s\'b6n \'eb m\'e9t thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea kh\'b8c. Sau h\'d5t, n\'e3 d\'f9a v\'b5o nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai v\'ab s\'b6n \'eb c\'b8c thu\'e9
c \'ae\'dea \'ae\'d3 th\'e8ng tr\'de nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai v\'ab s\'b6n da tr\'beng. Chi\'d5n c\'abng \'ae\'b8ng bu\'e5n c\'f1a ng\'ad\'eai X\'aan\'aagan l\'b5 \'ae\'b7 gi\'f3p b\'e4n qu\'a9n phi\'d6t Ph\'b8p gi\'d5t h\'b9i anh em c\'f1a m\'d7nh \'eb C\'ab
ngg\'ab, Xu\'ae\'a8ng, \'a7ah\'abm\'a9y}{\cs17\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 1{\footnote \pard\plain \s28\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa60\sl-240\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 
\f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 1) Nay l\'b5 n\'ad\'edc C\'e9ng ho\'b5 nh\'a9n d\'a9n B\'aananh.}})}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 , Ma\'aeag\'b8txca. Ng\'ad\'eai Angi\'aari \'ae\'b7 sang \'ae\'b8nh \'a7\'abng D\'ad
\'acng. Ng\'ad\'eai An Nam th\'d7 sang \'ae\'e3ng \'ae\'e5n canh ph\'dfng \'eb ch\'a9u Phi, v\'a9n v\'a9n v\'b5 v\'a9n v\'a9n. Trong cu\'e9c \'ae\'b9i chi\'d5n, h\'acn m\'e9t tri\'d6u n\'abng d\'a9n v\'b5 c\'abng nh\'a9n thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea \'ae\'b7 b\'de 
\'ae\'ada sang ch\'a9u \'a2u \'ae\'d3 ch\'d0m gi\'d5t n\'abng d\'a9n v\'b5 c\'abng nh\'a9n da tr\'beng. V\'f5a r\'e5i, ng\'ad\'eai ta \'ae\'b7 \'aeem l\'ddnh ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8 bao v\'a9y l\'ddnh Ph\'b8p \'eb mi\'d2n Ruya, v\'b5 ph\'b8i l\'ddnh ph
\'b8o th\'f1 thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea \'aei d\'d1p nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai \'a7\'f8c b\'b7i c\'abng. Non m\'e9t n\'f6a qu\'a9n \'ae\'e9i Ph\'b8p l\'b5 ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8, \'ad\'edc ch\'f5ng 300.000 ng\'ad\'eai.
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-244\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 Ngo\'b5i vi\'d6c d\'efng c\'b8c thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea v\'d2 m
\'c6t qu\'a9n s\'f9 nh\'ad v\'cby, ch\'f1 ngh\'dca t\'ad b\'b6n c\'dfn s\'f6 d\'f4ng c\'b8c thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea \'ae\'d3 b\'e3c l\'e9t v\'d2 m\'c6t kinh t\'d5 b\'bbng nh\'f7ng c\'b8ch th\'cbt tinh vi. Ng\'ad\'eai ta th\'ad\'eang th\'cay r\'bbng nh\'f7ng v
\'efng n\'b5o \'eb Ph\'b8p v\'b5 nh\'f7ng ngh\'d2 n\'b5o \'ae\'e3 m\'b5 ti\'d2n c\'abng b\'de h\'b9 xu\'e8ng, th\'d7 tr\'ad\'edc \'ae\'e3 th\'d5 n\'b5o c\'f2ng c\'e3 vi\'d6c t\'a8ng th\'aam nh\'a9n c\'abng thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea. Ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8 \'ae
\'b7 \'ae\'ad\'eec d\'efng \'ae\'d3 ph\'b8 c\'b8c cu\'e9c b\'b7i c\'abng. Hi\'d6n nay ch\'f1 ngh\'dca t\'ad b\'b6n d\'efng m\'e9t thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea n\'b5y l\'b5m c\'abng c\'f4 \'ae\'d3 b\'e3c l\'e9t m\'e9t thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea kh\'b8c, \'ae\'e3 l\'b5 tr
\'ad\'eang h\'eep \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng v\'b5 Th\'b8i B\'d7nh D\'ad\'acng.
\par }\pard\plain \qc \li0\ri0\sb120\sa80\sl-244\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 *
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-244\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 M\'c6c d\'c7u c\'b8c nh\'b5 c\'c7m quy\'d2n khua chi\'aa
ng g\'e2 tr\'e8ng \'ae\'d3 l\'f5a g\'b9t ng\'ad\'eai ta, nh\'adng s\'f9 th\'cbt th\'d7 \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng \'ae\'b7 ki\'d6t qu\'d6 r\'e5i. Su\'e8t trong nh\'f7ng n\'a8m 1914-1918, ng\'ad\'eai ta b\'bet g\'c7n m\'ad\'eai v\'b9n ng\'ad\'eai An Nam (con s
\'e8 c\'f1a nh\'b5 c\'c7m quy\'d2n l\'b5 97.903 ng\'ad\'eai) ph\'b6i b\'e1 ru\'e9ng v\'ad\'ean \'ae\'d3 sang ch\'a9u \'a2u. M\'c6c d\'c7u thi\'d5u ng\'ad\'eai s\'b6n xu\'cat, \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng c\'f2ng \'ae\'b7 bu\'e9c ph\'b6i g\'f6i \'aei 500.000 t
\'can ng\'f2 c\'e8c \'ae\'d3 g\'e3p ph\'c7n b\'b6o v\'d6 nh\'f7ng k\'ce \'b8p b\'f8c m\'d7nh. Nh\'f7ng c\'abng tr\'b8i Chi\'d5n th\'beng \'ae\'b7 b\'dfn r\'f3t \'aei h\'b5ng tr\'a8m tri\'d6u phr\'a8ng. M\'e7i n\'a8m, ng\'ad\'eai An Nam \'ae\'b7 ph\'b6i 
\'ae\'e6 m\'e5 h\'abi s\'abi n\'ad\'edc m\'bet \'ae\'d3 n\'e9p kho\'b6ng ch\'f5ng 450.000.000 phr\'a8ng h\'c7u h\'d5t ch\'d8 \'ae\'d3 
\par }\pard \s15\qj \li0\ri0\sa80\sl-248\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\insrsid1378858 nu\'abi b\'d0o b\'e4n \'a8n b\'b8m. Ngo\'b5i ra, h\'e4 l\'b9i c\'dfn ph\'b6i g\'b8nh nh\'f7ng kho\'b6n chi ti\'aau r\'cat l\'edn v
\'d2 qu\'a9n s\'f9 m\'b5 B\'e9 tr\'ad\'ebng B\'e9 Thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea g\'e4i m\'e9t c\'b8ch v\'a8n ho\'b8 l\'b5 "kho\'b6n \'ae\'b6m ph\'f4 c\'f1a d\'a9n con".
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Ch\'ddnh \'eb c\'b8i x\'f8 \'ae\'b7 b\'de b\'e3p n\'c6n, g
\'c7y c\'dfm tr\'ac c\'b6 x\'ad\'acng ra n\'b5y, b\'a9y gi\'ea ng\'ad\'eai ta l\'b9i c\'dfn s\'bep b\'dfn r\'f3t \'aei h\'b5ng bao nhi\'aau tri\'d6u b\'b9c v\'b5 h\'b5ng bao nhi\'aau v\'b9n ng\'ad\'eai n\'f7a (b\'bet \'ae\'c7u, ng\'ad\'eai ta b\'bet \'ae
i 40.000 ng\'ad\'eai) \'ae\'d3 tho\'b6 m\'b7n t\'f3i tham kh\'abng \'ae\'b8y c\'f1a b\'e4n ch\'f1 \'ae\'e5n \'aei\'d2n v\'b5 tham v\'e4ng c\'b8 nh\'a9n c\'f1a m\'e9t b\'c7y ch\'ddnh kh\'b8ch v\'ab li\'aam s\'d8.
\par L\'b5m \'ae\'e5i tru\'fe t\'cat c\'b6 n\'dfi gi\'e8ng An Nam b\'bbng r\'ad\'eeu v\'b5 thu\'e8c phi\'d6n, ch\'ada \'ae\'f1. M\'e7i n\'a8m b\'bet \'aei h\'b5ng 4 v\'b9n ng\'ad\'eai "t\'d7nh nguy\'d6n \'ae\'c7u qu\'a9n" \'ae\'d3 \'aeem l\'b9
i vinh quang cho ch\'f1 ngh\'dca qu\'a9n phi\'d6t v\'c9n ch\'ada \'ae\'f1. Bi\'d5n m\'e9t d\'a9n t\'e9c 20 tri\'d6u ng\'ad\'eai th\'b5nh m\'e9t c\'b8i kho thu\'d5 l\'edn, c\'f2ng v\'c9n ch\'ada \'ae\'f1. Ng\'ad\'eai ta c\'dfn s\'bep t\'c6ng th\'aam cho ch
\'f3ng t\'abi ch\'d5 \'ae\'e9 n\'ab l\'d6 n\'f7a kia \'ae\'cay.
\par }\pard \qc \li0\ri0\sa80\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 *
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-266\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs16\insrsid1378858 \~}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Nh\'f7ng h\'b5nh \'ae\'e9ng \'ae\'d5 qu\'e8c ch\'f1 ngh\'dca \'cay kh\'abng nh\'f7ng ch\'d8
 nguy cho ri\'aang v\'cbn m\'d6nh c\'f1a giai c\'cap v\'ab s\'b6n \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng v\'b5 Th\'b8i B\'d7nh D\'ad\'acng, n\'e3 c\'dfn nguy cho c\'b6 v\'cbn m\'d6nh c\'f1a giai c\'cap v\'ab s\'b6n qu\'e8c t\'d5 n\'f7a. Nh\'cbt B\'b6n ch\'d8 huy c\'b8
c tr\'b9m \'aei\'d6n b\'b8o \'eb \'ae\'b6o Y\'b8p. M\'fc chi ti\'aau h\'b5ng bao nhi\'aau tri\'d6u \'ae\'abla \'ae\'d3 c\'b6i ti\'d5n c\'b8c \'e6 s\'f3ng \'ae\'b9i b\'b8c tr\'aan c\'b8c t\'b5u chi\'d5n \'eb Th\'b8i B\'d7nh D\'ad\'acng. Anh s\'bep bi\'d5
n Xanhgapo th\'b5nh m\'e9t c\'a8n c\'f8 h\'b6i qu\'a9n. Ph\'b8p th\'cay c\'c7n ph\'b6i thi\'d5t l\'cbp m\'e9t h\'d6 th\'e8ng thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea \'eb Th\'b8i B\'d7nh D\'ad\'acng.
\par Sau H\'e9i ngh\'de Oasinht\'acn}{\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 44}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 , vi\'d6c tranh gi\'b5nh thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea ng\'b5y c\'b5ng tr\'eb n\'aan gay g\'bet h\'acn. B\'e4n \'ae\'d5 qu\'e8c ng\'b5y c\'b5ng tr\'eb n\'aan \'aei\'aan cu
\'e5ng h\'acn; nh\'f7ng cu\'e9c xung \'ae\'e9t ch\'ddnh tr\'de ng\'b5y c\'b5ng tr\'eb n\'aan kh\'abng th\'d3 tr\'b8nh kh\'e1i. Nh\'f7ng cu\'e9c chi\'d5n tranh \'ae\'b7 t\'f5ng n\'e6 ra v\'d7 v\'can \'ae\'d2 }{\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'ca}{
\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 n \'a7\'e9, ch\'a9u Phi v\'b5 Mar\'e8c. Nh\'f7ng cu\'e9c chi\'d5n tranh kh\'b8c s\'cf c\'e3 th\'d3 n\'e6 ra v\'d7 v\'can \'ae\'d2 Th\'b8i B\'d7nh D\'ad\'acng, n\'d5u giai c\'cap v\'ab s\'b6n kh\'abng c\'b6nh gi\'b8c.
\par }\pard\plain \s24\qr \fi397\li0\ri567\sb240\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin567\lin0\itap0 \f38\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 Nguy\'d4n \'b8i Qu\'e8c
\par }\pard\plain \s26\ql \li0\ri567\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin567\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 T\'cbp san }{\i\insrsid1378858 Inprekorr, }{\insrsid1378858 ti\'d5
ng Ph\'b8p,\line s\'e8 18, ng\'b5y 19-3-1924.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\b\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 
