T\'e6NG TH\'a6 K\'fd BAN PH\'a6\'a5NG \'a7\'a4NG
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-286\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f38\insrsid1378858 \'a7\'d2 NGH\'de:
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-286\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\i\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'a7\'e5ng ch\'dd th\'a9n m\'d5n,
\par }{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 H\'abm qua, trong khi d\'f9 cu\'e9c m\'ddt tinh c\'f1a sinh vi\'aan Tr\'ad\'eang \'ae\'b9i h\'e4c c\'e9ng s\'b6n ph\'ad\'acng \'a7\'abng}{\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 45}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 , m\'e9t \'fd ki\'d5n m\'b5 t
\'abi \'ae\'b7 ng\'c9m ngh\'dc t\'f5 l\'a9u, l\'b9i n\'b6y ra trong \'ae\'c7u \'e3c t\'abi. T\'abi t\'f9 th\'cay c\'e3 tr\'b8ch nhi\'d6m ph\'b6i tr\'d7nh b\'b5y v\'edi \'ae\'e5ng ch\'dd.
\par 1) \'a7\'e5ng ch\'dd \'ae\'b7 hi\'d3u r\'e2 nguy\'aan nh\'a9n \'ae\'c7u ti\'aan \'ae\'b7 g\'a9y ra s\'f9 suy y\'d5u c\'f1a c\'b8c d\'a9n t\'e9c ph\'ad\'acng \'a7\'abng, \'ae\'e3 l\'b5 }{\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 S\'f9 BI\'d6T L\'cbP}{
\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 . Kh\'abng gi\'e8ng nh\'ad c\'b8c d\'a9n t\'e9c ph\'ad\'acng T\'a9y, c\'b8c d\'a9n t\'e9c ph\'ad\'acng \'a7\'abng kh\'abng c\'e3 nh\'f7ng quan h\'d6 v\'b5 ti\'d5p x\'f3c gi\'f7a c\'b8c l\'f4c \'ae\'dea v\'edi nhau. H\'e4 ho\'b5
n to\'b5n kh\'abng bi\'d5t \'ae\'d5n nh\'f7ng vi\'d6c x\'b6y ra \'eb c\'b8c n\'ad\'edc l\'b8ng gi\'d2ng g\'c7n g\'f2i nh\'cat c\'f1a h\'e4, do \'ae\'e3 h\'e4 }{\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 THI\'d5U S\'f9 TIN C\'cbY L\'c9N NHAU, S\'f9 PH\'e8I H\'eeP H\'b5NH 
\'a7\'e9NG V\'b5 S\'f9 C\'e6 V\'f2 L\'c9N NHAU}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 .
\par }\pard\plain \s22\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-286\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f40\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 S\'cf r\'cat c\'e3 \'ddch cho ng\'ad\'ea
i An Nam bi\'d5t bao, n\'d5u h\'e4 \'ae\'ad\'eec bi\'d5t nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai anh em }{\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'ca}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 n \'a7\'e9 c\'f1a h\'e4 t\'f9 t\'e6 ch\'f8c nh\'ad th\'d5 n\'b5o \'ae\'d3 \'ae\'cau tranh ch\'e8ng ch\'f1 ngh
\'dca \'ae\'d5 qu\'e8c Anh, ho\'c6c bi\'d5t c\'abng nh\'a9n Nh\'cbt B\'b6n \'aeo\'b5n k\'d5t nhau l\'b9i nh\'ad th\'d5 n\'b5o \'ae\'d3 ch\'e8ng l\'b9i \'b8ch b\'e3c l\'e9t c\'f1a ch\'f1 ngh\'dca t\'ad b\'b6n, ho\'c6c bi\'d5t ng\'ad\'eai Ai C\'cbp \'ae\'b7
 ph\'b6i hy sinh cao c\'b6 nh\'ad th\'d5 n\'b5o \'ae\'d3 \'ae\'dfi l\'b9i quy\'d2n t\'f9 do c\'f1a m\'d7nh? N\'e3i chung th\'d7 c\'b8c d\'a9n t\'e9c ph\'ad\'acng \'a7\'abng \'ae\'d2u gi\'b5u t\'d7nh c\'b6m, v\'b5 \'ae\'e8i v\'edi h\'e4 m\'e9t t\'cam g\'ad
\'acng s\'e8ng c\'dfn c\'e3 gi\'b8 tr\'de h\'acn m\'e9t tr\'a8m b\'b5i di\'d4n v\'a8n tuy\'aan truy\'d2n.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 2) C\'b8c chi\'d5n s\'dc ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8 \'ae\'d2
u b\'de gi\'b8m s\'b8t v\'b5 truy n\'b7 r\'cat r\'b8o ri\'d5t t\'b9i ch\'ddnh n\'ad\'edc h\'e4. Nh\'adng \'eb m\'e9t n\'ad\'edc l\'b8ng gi\'d2ng h\'e4 c\'e3 th\'d3 ho\'b9t \'ae\'e9ng d\'d4 d\'b5ng h\'acn, v\'d7 c\'e3 \'ddt ng\'ad\'eai bi\'d5t h\'e4. S\'cf
 r\'cat thu\'cbn l\'eei, n\'d5u Qu\'e8c t\'d5 c\'e3 th\'d3 c\'f6 nh\'f7ng \'ae\'e5ng ch\'dd ng\'ad\'eai Trung Qu\'e8c ch\'bcng h\'b9n, sang \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng, nh\'f7ng \'ae\'e5ng ch\'dd Th\'e6 Nh\'dc K\'fa sang }{\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'ca}{
\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 n \'a7\'e9 v\'b5 c\'f8 nh\'ad th\'d5. Nh\'adng mu\'e8n l\'b5m tr\'dfn nh\'f7ng s\'f8 m\'b9ng \'cay, nh\'f7ng chi\'d5n s\'dc \'ae\'e3 ph\'b6i hi\'d3u bi\'d5t t\'d7nh h\'d7nh to\'b5n ch\'a9u }{\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'b8}{
\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  v\'b5 ph\'b6i c\'e3 m\'e9t m\'e8i quan h\'d6 m\'cbt thi\'d5t gi\'f7a c\'b8c chi\'d5n s\'dc c\'f1a c\'b8c n\'ad\'edc kh\'b8c nhau. V\'cby m\'b5 hi\'d6n nay ch\'ada c\'e3 s\'f9 hi\'d3u bi\'d5t \'cay v\'b5 m\'e8i quan h\'d6 \'ae\'e3
. Trong nh\'f7ng \'aei\'d2u ki\'d6n nh\'ad v\'cby m\'e4i s\'f9 t\'ad\'acng tr\'ee, m\'e4i s\'f9 \'aeo\'b5n k\'d5t kh\'abng th\'d3 c\'e3 \'ae\'ad\'eec.
\par 3) Tr\'ad\'eang \'ae\'b9i h\'e4c ph\'ad\'acng \'a7\'abng hi\'d6n nay \'aeang dung n\'b9p 62 d\'a9n t\'e9c ph\'ad\'acng \'a7\'abng. Con s\'e8 n\'b5y s\'cf ng\'b5y c\'b5ng t\'a8ng th\'aam t\'efy theo s\'f9 ho\'b9t \'ae\'e9ng v\'b5 c\'abng t\'b8c tuy\'aa
n truy\'d2n c\'f1a Qu\'e8c t\'d5 m\'e7i ng\'b5y m\'e9t m\'eb r\'e9ng. Tr\'ad\'eang \'ae\'b9i h\'e4c n\'b5y l\'b5 m\'e9t c\'b8i l\'df \'ae\'b5o t\'b9o nh\'f7ng c\'b8n b\'e9 tuy\'aan truy\'d2n \'ae\'c7u ti\'aan cho c\'b8c n\'ad\'edc ph\'ad\'acng \'a7\'ab
ng. N\'e3 c\'f2ng ph\'b6i l\'b5 c\'ac s\'eb tr\'aan \'ae\'e3 s\'cf \'ae\'ad\'eec thi\'d5t l\'cbp m\'e9t }{\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 LI\'a3N BANG C\'e9NG S\'b6N PH\'a6\'a5NG \'a7\'a4NG}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 . \'a7\'d3 cho c\'abng t\'b8c \'ae\'ad\'eec d
\'d4 d\'b5ng, ch\'f3ng ta \'ae\'b7 l\'cbp nh\'e3m Latinh, nh\'e3m \'a1nggl\'ab X\'becx\'abng, v.v., v\'cby v\'d7 l\'cf g\'d7 ch\'f3ng ta l\'b9i kh\'abng l\'cbp nh\'e3m ch\'a9u }{\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'b8}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 .
\par V\'cby t\'abi \'ae\'d2 ngh\'de l\'b5 tr\'ad\'edc ng\'b5y c\'b8c sinh vi\'aan t\'e8t nghi\'d6p l\'aan \'ae\'ad\'eang v\'b5 tr\'ad\'edc cu\'e9c \'a7\'b9i h\'e9i th\'d5 gi\'edi, m\'e9t }{\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 TI\'d3U BAN PH\'a6\'a5NG \'a7\'a4NG}{
\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  s\'cf \'ae\'ad\'eec c\'b8c \'ae\'e5ng ch\'dd tri\'d6u t\'cbp \'ae\'d3 chu\'c8n b\'de vi\'d6c th\'b5nh l\'cbp }{\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 NH\'e3M CH\'a2U \'b8}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  \'ae\'e3.
\par }\pard\plain \s22\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f40\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 V\'edi l\'dfng mong m\'e1i \'ae\'e5ng ch\'dd s\'cf
 t\'b8n th\'b5nh khi xem x\'d0t \'ae\'d2 ngh\'de c\'f1a t\'abi, t\'abi xin g\'f6i \'ae\'d5n \'ae\'e5ng ch\'dd th\'a9n m\'d5n l\'eai ch\'b5o c\'e9ng s\'b6n th\'a9n \'b8i.
\par }\pard\plain \s24\qc \li3969\ri425\sb360\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin425\lin3969\itap0 \f38\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 Nguy\'d4n \'b8i Qu\'e8c\line }{
\i\f37\insrsid1378858 thu\'e9c \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng}{\insrsid1378858 
\par }\pard\plain \s26\ql \li0\ri567\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin567\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 Th\'ad \'ae\'b8nh m\'b8y, ti\'d5ng Ph\'b8p,
\par b\'b6n ch\'f4p l\'adu t\'b9i Vi\'d6n H\'e5 Ch\'dd Minh.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 
\par }{\b\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 
\par }\pard\plain \s20\qc \li0\ri0\sb1400\sa440\sl-380\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \b\f38\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 \'a7O\'b5N K\'d5T GIAI C\'caP
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'a7\'c7u n\'a8m 1921, m\'e9t cu\'e9c b\'b7i c\'abng l\'ed
n c\'f1a c\'abng nh\'a9n h\'b5ng h\'b6i \'ae\'a8ng b\'b9}{\cs17\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 1{\footnote \pard\plain \s28\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa60\sl-240\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 
\f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 1) Do y\'aau c\'c7u c\'f1a s\'f9 ki\'d3m so\'b8t qu\'e8c gia v\'b5 qu\'e8c t\'d5, ng\'ad\'eai \'aei bi\'d3n ph\'b6i theo lu\'cbt h\'b5ng h\'b6i qu\'e8c t\'d5, \'ae\'ad\'eec \'ae
\'a8ng k\'fd v\'b5o m\'e9t danh b\'b9 Nh\'b5 n\'ad\'edc. C\'e3 \'ae\'a8ng b\'b9 m\'edi l\'b5 c\'abng nh\'a9n h\'b5ng h\'b6i ch\'ddnh th\'f8c.}})}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  n\'e6 ra \'eb Braxin. M\'e9t chi\'d5c t\'b5u v\'f5a c\'c6p b\'d5n Ri\'ab \'a7\'aa
 Han\'a9yr\'ab. Thu\'fb th\'f1 tr\'aan t\'b5u ch\'ada bi\'d5t r\'bbng b\'b9n c\'f1a m\'d7nh \'eb \'ae\'a9y \'aeang \'ae\'cau tranh ch\'e8ng b\'e4n ch\'f1. M\'e9t ng\'ad\'eai da \'aeen tham gia \'ae\'d7nh c\'abng, H\'abx\'aa L\'aaan\'aer\'ab \'a7
a Xinva, mu\'e8n l\'aan t\'b5u b\'b8o tin cho c\'b8c thu\'fb th\'f1 bi\'d5t. Tr\'aan b\'d5n, H\'abx\'aa g\'c6p m\'e9t t\'aan c\'b6nh s\'b8t ng\'a8n anh l\'b9i.
\par - T\'abi c\'e3 quy\'d2n l\'aan t\'b5u g\'c6p c\'b8c b\'b9n t\'abi, ch\'f8 sao kh\'abng, H\'abx\'aa n\'e3i v\'edi tay \'ae\'b9i di\'d6n tr\'cbt t\'f9 ch\'ddnh quy\'d2n.
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 - Kh\'abng n\'e3i n\'a8ng l\'bbng nh\'bbng! X\'d0o! T\'aa
n n\'b5y c\'f9 l\'b9i.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 H\'abx\'aa c\'e8 n\'b5i.
\par T\'aan c\'b6nh s\'b8t ch\'bcng th\'ccm tr\'b6 l\'eai n\'f7a, r\'f3t s\'f3ng l\'f4c ra b\'ben. H\'abx\'aa nhanh nh\'d1n tr\'b8nh k\'dep, v\'b5, l\'d1 nh\'ad ch\'edp, anh t\'f3m l\'cay th\'bbng \'ae\'e9i, qu\'bcng n\'e3 xu\'e8ng n\'ad\'edc.
\par C\'e3 \'ae\'d5n n\'a8m ch\'f4c t\'aan c\'b6nh s\'b8t c\'e3 v\'f2 kh\'dd \'ae\'e6 x\'ab \'ae\'d5n \'ae\'b8nh H\'abx\'aa. Anh ch\'e8ng c\'f9 l\'b9i. S\'bdn con dao \'aei bi\'d3n, anh \'ae\'a9m ch\'d5t m\'cay t\'aan v\'b5 l\'b5m b\'de th\'ad\'acng nhi\'d2u t
\'aan kh\'b8c. Cu\'e8i c\'efng anh kh\'abng ch\'deu n\'e6i s\'e8 \'ae\'abng, ng\'b7 xu\'e8ng, coi nh\'ad ch\'d5t, v\'edi 18 vi\'aan \'ae\'b9n trong m\'d7nh.
\par Tuy v\'cby anh v\'c9n c\'dfn \'ae\'f1 s\'f8c \'ae\'d3 l\'c8m nh\'c8m b\'b5i }{\i\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Qu\'e8c t\'d5 ca}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  khi \'ae\'ad\'eec khi\'aang \'ae\'d5n nh\'b5 th\'ad\'acng. R\'e5i sau ch\'f3ng l\'abi anh ra to\'b5. }{
\i\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Anh b\'de k\'d5t \'b8n 30 n\'a8m kh\'e6 sai.
\par }{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 V\'f5a \'ae\'ad\'eec tin x\'f6, anh em c\'abng nh\'a9n c\'b8ch m\'b9ng l\'cbp ngay m\'e9t U\'fb ban b\'b6o v\'d6. M\'e9t m\'c6t, h\'e4 m\'ad\'edn nhi\'d2u tr\'b9ng s\'ad c\'b7i cho b\'b9n; m\'c6t kh\'b8c, h\'e4 t\'e6 ch\'f8c nh
\'f7ng cu\'e9c bi\'d3u t\'d7nh ph\'b6n \'ae\'e8i trong c\'b6 n\'ad\'edc. M\'e9t chi\'d5n d\'dech v\'cbn \'ae\'e9ng \'ae\'cau tranh \'f1ng h\'e9 H\'abx\'aa \'ae\'ad\'eec ti\'d5n h\'b5nh m\'b9nh m\'cf su\'e8t ba n\'a8m. D\'ad lu\'cbn qu\'c7n ch\'f3ng c\'ab
ng ph\'c9n \'ae\'d5n m\'f8c nh\'b5 ch\'f8c tr\'b8ch ph\'b6i mang v\'f4 \'b8n ra x\'d0t l\'b9i.
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 Ng\'b5y m\'e5ng 8 th\'b8ng 2, H\'abx\'aa ra to\'b5 x\'f6 l
\'b9i \'b8n. M\'e9t v\'b9n r\'ad\'ebi c\'abng nh\'a9n d\'f9 phi\'aan to\'b5 k\'d0o d\'b5i su\'e8t \'ae\'aam. B\'e4n ch\'f1 kh\'abng ch\'deu nh\'b6 m\'e5i ra, v\'b5 bi\'d6n l\'fd ph\'b6i m\'cat 5 ti\'d5ng \'ae\'e5ng h\'e5 m\'edi \'ae\'e4c xong b\'b6n c\'b8
o tr\'b9ng d\'b5i.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'a7\'e5ng ch\'dd Paol\'ab \'a7\'aa Lax\'d0cda v\'b5 c\'b8
c b\'b9n \'ae\'e5ng nghi\'d6p \'ae\'b7 h\'efng bi\'d6n b\'b8c b\'e1 m\'e9t c\'b8ch th\'beng l\'eei m\'e4i l\'fd l\'cf c\'f1a bi\'d6n l\'fd.
\par Phi\'aan to\'b5 \'ae\'d5n 4 gi\'ea r\'ad\'eci s\'b8ng m\'edi k\'d5t th\'f3c.
\par To\'b5 x\'f6 tr\'beng \'b8n.
\par B\'b6n tuy\'aan \'b8n \'ae\'ad\'eec hoan ngh\'aanh b\'bbng nh\'f7ng ti\'d5ng v\'e7 tay vang nh\'ad s\'cam. V\'b5 H\'abx\'aa, anh chi\'d5n s\'dc b\'b7i c\'abng da \'aeen ng\'b6 m\'d7nh trong c\'b8nh tay c\'b8c \'ae\'e5ng ch\'dd v\'b5 c\'b8c ng\'ad\'eai b
\'b6o v\'d6 anh, nh\'f7ng \'ae\'b9i bi\'d3u c\'f1a c\'abng nh\'a9n da tr\'beng.
\par V\'cby l\'b5, d\'ef m\'b5u da c\'e3 kh\'b8c nhau, tr\'aan \'ae\'eai n\'b5y ch\'d8 c\'e3 hai gi\'e8ng ng\'ad\'eai: gi\'e8ng ng\'ad\'eai b\'e3c l\'e9t v\'b5 gi\'e8ng ng\'ad\'eai b\'de b\'e3c l\'e9t. M\'b5 c\'f2ng ch\'d8 c\'e3 m\'e9t m\'e8i t\'d7nh h\'f7u 
\'b8i l\'b5 th\'cbt m\'b5 th\'abi: t\'d7nh h\'f7u \'b8i v\'ab s\'b6n.
\par }\pard\plain \s24\qr \fi397\li0\ri567\sb360\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin567\lin0\itap0 \f38\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 \~NGUY\'d4N \'b8I QU\'e8C
\par }\pard\plain \s26\ql \li0\ri567\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin567\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 T\'b5i li\'d6u \'ae\'b8nh m\'b8y, ti\'d5ng Ph\'b8p,
\par b\'b6n ch\'f4p l\'adu t\'b9i Vi\'d6n H\'e5 Ch\'dd Minh.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 
\par }\pard\plain \s21\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \b\f39\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 
\par 
\par 
\par }\pard\plain \s20\qc \li0\ri0\sb1400\sa440\sl-380\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \b\f38\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 PH\'f4 N\'f7 PH\'a6\'a5NG \'a7\'a4NG
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-266\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Ph\'f4 n\'f7 Th\'e6 Nh\'dc K\'fa tham gia b\'b6o v\'d6 
\'ae\'cat n\'ad\'edc ch\'e8ng s\'f9 x\'a9m l\'ad\'eec c\'f1a ch\'f1 ngh\'dca \'ae\'d5 qu\'e8c ph\'ad\'acng T\'a9y.
\par Ph\'f4 n\'f7 }{\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'ca}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 n \'a7\'e9 v\'efng l\'aan ch\'e8ng s\'f9 \'ae\'ab h\'e9 c\'f1a Anh. Ph\'f4 n\'f7 Trung Qu\'e8c tham gia cu\'e9c c\'b8ch m\'b9ng n\'a8m 1912. Ph\'f4 n\'f7 Tri\'d2u Ti\'aan \'ae\'b7 v
\'b5 \'aeang \'ae\'cau tranh v\'d7 \'ae\'e9c l\'cbp c\'f1a T\'e6 qu\'e8c. Ph\'f4 n\'f7 Nh\'cbt B\'b6n \'ae\'b7 bu\'e9c Ch\'ddnh ph\'f1 ph\'b6i hu\'fb b\'e1 \'ae\'b9o lu\'cbt c\'cam ph\'f4 n\'f7 tham gia \'ae\'eai s\'e8ng ch\'ddnh tr\'de v\'b5 v.v..
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-266\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 Trong \'ae\'eai s\'e8ng kinh t\'d5 nh\'f7ng "b\'abng h\'e5
ng" c\'f1a ph\'ad\'acng \'a7\'abng b\'bet \'ae\'c7u t\'e1 cho ch\'f1 ngh\'dca t\'ad b\'b6n th\'cay \'eb h\'e4 c\'e3 nh\'f7ng chi\'d5c gai nh\'e4n. Nh\'f7ng cu\'e9c b\'b7i c\'abng c\'f1a n\'f7 c\'abng nh\'a9n \'eb c\'b8c nh\'b5 m\'b8y v\'b5 x\'ad\'ebng d
\'d6t l\'f4a kh\'abng c\'dfn l\'b5 hi\'d6n t\'ad\'eeng hi\'d5m n\'f7a.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-266\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Trong c\'b8c t\'e6 ch\'f8c c\'abng \'aeo\'b5n Nh\'cbt B
\'b6n, ph\'f4 n\'f7 chi\'d5m m\'e9t t\'fb l\'d6 \'ae\'b8ng k\'d3. \'a7o\'b5n Thanh ni\'aan c\'e9ng s\'b6n Trung Qu\'e8c m\'edi th\'b5nh l\'cbp \'ae\'ad\'eec ba n\'a8m \'ae\'b7 c\'e3 trong h\'b5ng ng\'f2 c\'f1a m\'d7nh h\'acn 150 n\'f7 c\'abng nh\'a9n v
\'b5 n\'f7 sinh vi\'aan.
\par T\'f5 khi \'ae\'e5ng ch\'dd L\'aanin m\'cat, c\'b8c t\'e6 ch\'f8c ch\'ddnh tr\'de, v\'a8n ho\'b8 v\'b5 c\'b8c t\'e6 ch\'f8c kh\'b8c c\'f1a h\'e4c sinh c\'b8c n\'ad\'edc ph\'ad\'acng \'a7\'abng t\'e6 ch\'f8c nhi\'d2u cu\'e9c m\'ddt tinh v\'b5 h\'e9i h\'e4
p.
\par D\'ad\'edi \'ae\'a9y l\'b5 l\'eai k\'aau g\'e4i c\'f1a m\'e9t n\'f7 sinh vi\'aan \'ae\'a8ng tr\'aan }{\i\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 B\'b8o Ph\'f4 n\'f7 }{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'eb Th\'ad\'eeng H\'b6i (Trung Qu\'e8c):
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-266\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 "H\'eci c\'b8c ch\'de em!
\par }\pard\plain \s22\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f40\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 T\'f5 khi c\'e3 ch\'f1 ngh\'dca t\'ad b\'b6n, to
\'b5n b\'e9 c\'ac th\'d3 x\'b7 h\'e9i \'ae\'d2u b\'de \'b6nh h\'ad\'ebng tai h\'b9i c\'f1a n\'e3. C\'b8c v\'cbt ph\'c8m do t\'cat c\'b6 m\'e4i ng\'ad\'eai s\'b6n xu\'cat ra, \'ae\'b8ng l\'cf ph\'b6i thu\'e9c v\'d2 t\'cat c\'b6 m\'e4i ng\'ad\'eai th\'d7 l
\'b9i thu\'e9c \'ae\'c6c quy\'d2n c\'f1a m\'e9t v\'b5i ng\'ad\'eai! }{\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'b8}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 ch \'b8p b\'f8c kinh t\'d5 \'ae\'b7 n\'ab d\'dech con ng\'ad\'eai, c\'f2ng \'b8ch \'b8p b\'f8c \'cay \'ae\'b7 bi\'d5n ph\'f4 n
\'f7 th\'b5nh nh\'f7ng \'ae\'e5 v\'cbt tu\'fa thu\'e9c quy\'d2n s\'f6 d\'f4ng c\'f1a nam gi\'edi!
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 T\'f5 bao th\'d5 k\'fb nay, bao nhi\'aau tri\'d6u con ng
\'ad\'eai \'ae\'b7 b\'de xi\'d2ng x\'ddch nh\'ad th\'d5 ? Bao nhi\'aau tri\'d6u \'ae\'b5n b\'b5 \'ae\'b7 b\'de hy sinh?
\par Trong l\'f3c cu\'e9c chi\'d5n tranh th\'d5 gi\'edi \'aeang di\'d4n ra \'b8c li\'d6t, trong l\'f3c h\'b5ng tri\'d6u ng\'ad\'eai kh\'abng l\'b5m h\'b9i \'ae\'d5n ai, \'aeang mu\'e8n s\'e8ng, nh\'adng l\'b9i b\'de \'ae\'ada v\'b5o ch\'e7 ch\'d5t, L\'aanin 
\'ae\'b7 \'ae\'b9p b\'bbng gian kh\'e6 v\'b5 kh\'e3 kh\'a8n, \'ae\'b7 th\'f8c t\'d8nh giai c\'cap v\'ab s\'b6n Nga n\'e6i d\'cby, \'ae\'b7 t\'e6 ch\'f8c c\'b8c x\'abvi\'d5t.
\par L\'aanin kh\'abng nh\'f7ng ch\'d8 gi\'b6i ph\'e3ng nam gi\'edi v\'b5 n\'f7 gi\'edi tr\'aan \'ae\'cat n\'ad\'edc Ti\'aan sinh, m\'b5 c\'dfn ch\'d8 \'ae\'ad\'eang cho t\'cat c\'b6 nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai ngh\'cco kh\'e6 tr\'aan th\'d5 gi\'edi. V\'b5 b\'cat ch
\'cap b\'e4n b\'b9ch v\'d6 t\'can c\'abng \'eb b\'aan trong, b\'e4n t\'ad b\'b6n bao v\'a9y \'eb b\'aan ngo\'b5i, \'fd ch\'dd ki\'aan c\'ad\'eang c\'f1a L\'aanin \'ae\'b7 c\'f8u \'ae\'e5ng b\'b5o c\'f1a Ti\'aan sinh ra kh\'e1i c\'b6nh \'aeau kh\'e6 v\'b5
 l\'c7m than, v\'b5 \'ae\'b7 n\'aau cao ng\'e4n c\'ea c\'f1a Qu\'e8c t\'d5 cho t\'cat c\'b6 nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai b\'de \'b8p b\'f8c.
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 \'a7i\'d2u \'ae\'e3 h\'b8 ch\'bcng \'ae\'b8ng \'ae\'d3 ta k
\'ddnh c\'c8n m\'c6c ni\'d6m tr\'ad\'edc anh linh v\'dc \'ae\'b9i c\'f1a Ti\'aan sinh hay sao ?
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Ng\'b5y 21 th\'b8ng 1 h\'b8 ch\'bcng m\'b7i m\'b7i l\'b5 m
\'e9t ng\'b5y tang cho t\'cat c\'b6 nh\'f7ng nam n\'f7 \'aeang ch\'deu kh\'e6 c\'f9c hay sao?
\par N\'ad\'edc Nga \'aeang \'ae\'d5n ph\'e5n vinh. Nh\'adng mu\'e8n c\'e3 \'ae\'ad\'eec m\'e9t n\'d2n ho\'b5 b\'d7nh th\'f9c s\'f9 th\'d7 c\'dfn ph\'b6i ti\'d5n l\'aan h\'acn n\'f7a v\'b5 c\'dfn ph\'b6i l\'b5m nhi\'d2u vi\'d6c n\'f7a. Lo\'b5i ng\'ad\'eai \'ae
ang th\'f8c t\'d8nh, nh\'adng mu\'e8n t\'f9 gi\'b6i ph\'e3ng ho\'b5n to\'b5n th\'d7 c\'dfn ph\'b6i \'ae\'cau tranh}{\cs17\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 1{\footnote \pard\plain \s28\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa60\sl-240\slmult0
\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 1) L\'eai k\'aau g\'e4i n\'b5y c\'e3 \'ae\'e8i chi\'d5u v\'edi b\'b6n ti\'d5ng Ph\'b8p.}})}{
\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 ".
\par L\'eai k\'aau g\'e4i tr\'aan \'ae\'a9y n\'e3i l\'aan r\'bbng \'ae\'b7 c\'e3 m\'e9t b\'ad\'edc ngo\'c6t l\'edn \'eb c\'b8c n\'ad\'edc ph\'ad\'acng \'a7\'abng t\'f5 khi ng\'e4n c\'ea \'ae\'e1 in h\'d7nh b\'f3a li\'d2m tung bay tr\'aan n\'ad\'edc Nga sa ho
\'b5ng.
\par }\pard\plain \s24\qr \fi397\li0\ri567\sb100\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin567\lin0\itap0 \f38\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 \~NGUY\'d4N \'b8I QU\'e8C
\par }\pard\plain \s26\ql \li0\ri567\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin567\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 T\'b9p ch\'dd }{\i\insrsid1378858 Rab\'e3tnhitxa}{\insrsid1378858 
, ti\'d5ng Nga, s\'e8 9,
\par th\'b8ng 5-1924.
\par }\pard\plain \s21\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \b\f39\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 
\par }\pard\plain \s20\qc \li0\ri0\sb1400\sa440\sl-380\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \b\f38\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 NH\'f7NG C\'b8I T\'e8T \'a7\'d1P\line C\'f1A N\'d2N V
\'a1N MINH PH\'b8P
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-288\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Trong cu\'e9c th\'b6o lu\'cbn v\'d2 v\'can \'ae\'d2 \'ae
\'b9i di\'d6n c\'f1a d\'a9n b\'b6n x\'f8 c\'b8c thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea t\'b9i Qu\'e8c h\'e9i Ph\'b8p, \'abng P\'abn T\'b8pponni\'aa \'ae\'b7 ph\'b8t bi\'d3u \'fd ki\'d5n \'eb H\'b9 ngh\'de vi\'d6n nh\'ad sau:
\par "N\'ad\'edc Ph\'b8p v\'e8n h\'b5o hi\'d6p v\'b5 \'ae\'f8c khoan nh\'a9n c\'f1a n\'ad\'edc Ph\'b8p \'ae\'ad\'eec bi\'d3u hi\'d6n trong m\'e4i tr\'ad\'eang h\'eep. }{\i\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Kh\'abng c\'e3 g\'d7 c\'e3 th\'d3 s\'b8nh t\'c7y n\'d2n v\'a8
n minh Ph\'b8p}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 " . Ch\'f3ng t\'abi th\'b5nh th\'cbt c\'b6m \'acn \'abng ngh\'de \'cay \'ae\'b7 cho ch\'f3ng t\'abi d\'dep t\'e8t k\'d3 ra \'ae\'a9y m\'e9t s\'e8 \'ae\'f8c t\'ddnh b\'cat h\'f1 c\'f1a n\'ad\'edc Ph\'b8p - ngo\'b5
i c\'b8i \'ae\'f8c t\'ddnh r\'cat c\'ad\'acng quy\'d5t khai ho\'b8 d\'a9n b\'b6n x\'f8 b\'bbng \'ae\'b9i b\'b8c v\'b5 l\'ad\'eci l\'aa.
\par }{\b\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 L\'d4 \'ae\'e9}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 . - Khu\'abn ph\'d0p th\'f9c d\'a9n mu\'e8n r\'bbng b\'cat c\'f8 ng\'ad\'eai d\'a9n b\'b6n x\'f8 n\'b5o - d\'ef \'ae\'dea v\'de, tu\'e6i t\'b8c ra sao, d\'ef nam hay n\'f7 - \'ae\'d2
u ph\'b6i c\'f3i \'ae\'c7u k\'ddnh c\'c8n ch\'b5o ng\'ad\'eai \'a2u. Ng\'ad\'eai ta t\'f5ng th\'cay \'eb \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng, \'eb Ma\'aeag\'b8txca nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai d\'a9n b\'b6n x\'f8 b\'de ng\'ad\'eec \'ae\'b7i, \'ae\'b8nh \'ae\'cbp v\'b5 b\'de b
\'e1 t\'ef, ch\'d8 v\'d7 }{\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'a7\'b7 QU\'a3N T\'e1 D\'caU T\'a4N K\'ddNH \'a7\'e3 TR\'a6\'edC \'a7\'f8C UY NGHI\'a3M C\'f1A C\'b8C V\'de \'a7I KHAI Ho\'b8}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 . M\'edi \'ae\'a9y th\'abi, m\'e9t v\'de
 quan cai tr\'de \'eb M\'d0tgiana (Angi\'aari) \'ae\'b7 ra l\'d6nh b\'bet nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai d\'a9n b\'b6n x\'f8 trong v\'efng cai tr\'de c\'f1a m\'d7nh, v\'d7 m\'b6i l\'b5m kh\'abng tr\'abng th\'cay quan l\'edn \'aei d\'b9o ch\'aci qua, n\'aan \'ae\'b7
 d\'b8m kh\'abng ch\'b5o ng\'b5i.
\par }\pard\plain \s22\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-288\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f40\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\b\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 R\'e9ng l\'ad\'eeng.}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 
 - }{\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'eb }{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng, th\'ad\'eang nh\'a9n d\'dep \'aei ch\'aci c\'f1a m\'e9t \'abng Gi\'e8pphr\'ac hay sinh nh\'cbt m\'e9t \'abng Cl\'aam\'a8ngx\'ab ch\'bcng h\'b9n, ho\'c6c kh\'b8nh th\'b5
nh m\'e9t \'ae\'b5i "li\'d6t s\'dc ch\'d5t v\'d7 T\'e6 qu\'e8c" ho\'c6c ti\'d5p \'ae\'e3n m\'e9t ph\'b8i vi\'aan c\'f1a n\'d2n c\'e9ng ho\'b5, th\'d7 c\'b8c quan cai tr\'de \'ae\'d2u c\'e3 m\'eb "l\'b9c quy\'aan". C\'b8c quan \'ae\'b7 d\'efng c\'b8ch nh
\'ad sau: Quan l\'edn cai tr\'de c\'f8 vi\'d6c d\'f9a theo d\'a9n s\'e8 v\'b5 thu\'d5 b\'b9 c\'f1a t\'d8nh m\'b5 quy \'ae\'denh s\'e8 ti\'d2n c\'c7n thi\'d5t cho cu\'e9c l\'d4, nh\'a9n s\'e8 ti\'d2n \'ae\'e3 l\'aan g\'cap 3, g\'cap 4 hay g\'cap 5, \'ae
\'denh ng\'b5y n\'e9p, r\'e5i \'ae\'dfi c\'b8c k\'fa h\'b5o h\'ad\'acng l\'fd \'ae\'d5n v\'b5 n\'e3i v\'edi h\'e4: "Quan l\'edn c\'c7n ti\'d2n, \'ae\'a9y l\'b5 s\'e8 ti\'d2n quan l\'edn mu\'e8n c\'e3, \'ae\'a9y l\'b5 k\'fa h\'b9n quan l\'edn \'ae\'de
nh cho c\'b8c ng\'ad\'eai \'ae\'d3 n\'e9p cho quan l\'edn. H\'b7y li\'d6u l\'cay \'ae\'cay. N\'d5u kh\'abng th\'d7...". \'a7\'d3 kh\'e1i ng\'e5i t\'ef, c\'b8c k\'fa h\'b5o h\'ad\'acng l\'fd c\'f8 vi\'d6c m\'b5 "li\'d6u". S\'e8 ti\'d2n b\'de nh\'a9n l\'aa
n c\'f1a cu\'e9c l\'b9c quy\'aan \'d0p bu\'e9c th\'d7 d\'efng \'ae\'d3 "t\'e1 l\'dfng t\'abn k\'ddnh c\'b8c b\'cbc \'ae\'b9i nh\'a9n", c\'dfn s\'e8 th\'b5nh c\'f1a b\'b5i t\'ddnh nh\'a9n th\'d7 chui v\'b5o t\'f3i c\'f1a quan l\'edn cai tr\'de. N\'abng d
\'a9n c\'f8 \'cc c\'e6 \'ae\'e3ng c\'b8c th\'f8 ph\'f4 thu lu\'abn lu\'abn nh\'ad th\'d5.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\b\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 L\'dfng h\'b5o hi\'d6p}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 . - Ti
\'d5p theo ch\'a9m ng\'abn "\'a7\'b7 c\'e3 n\'ad\'edc \'a7\'f8c tr\'b6" l\'b5 c\'a9u ch\'a9m ng\'abn "\'a7\'b7 c\'e3 c\'b8c thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea tr\'b6". N\'ad\'edc m\'d1 \'ae\'dfi h\'e1i c\'b8c thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea ph\'b6i \'ae\'ada }{
\i\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 t\'cat c\'b6}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  s\'f8c l\'f9c c\'f1a m\'d7nh, }{\i\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 t\'cat c\'b6}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  kh\'b6 n\'a8ng c\'f1a m\'d7nh, }{\i\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 t\'cat c\'b6}{
\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  \'fd ch\'dd c\'f1a m\'d7nh, }{\i\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 t\'cat c\'b6}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  t\'b5i nguy\'aan c\'f1a m\'d7nh \'ae\'d3 gi\'f3p v\'b5o vi\'d6c ph\'f4c h\'adng kinh t\'d5 c\'f1a n\'ad\'edc m\'d1, trong khi \'ae
\'e3 th\'d7 n\'ad\'edc m\'d1 l\'b9i 
\par v\'f5a c\'cam xu\'cat kh\'c8u p\'abt\'b8t c\'f1a And\'b8tx\'ac sang thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea, }{\i\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'ae\'d3 ho\'b5n to\'b5n d\'b5nh ri\'aang s\'b6n ph\'c8m \'ae\'e3 cho n\'abng nghi\'d6p Ph\'b8p.
\par }\pard \qj \li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\b\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 B\'d7nh \'ae\'bcng}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 . - C\'b8c c\'abng d\'a9n Ph\'b8p ph\'b6i l\'b5m qu\'a9n d\'dech m\'ad\'eai t
\'b8m th\'b8ng; d\'a9n b\'b6n x\'f8 c\'b8c thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea th\'d7 bu\'e9c ph\'b6i ph\'f4c v\'f4 ba, b\'e8n n\'a8m d\'ad\'edi ng\'e4n c\'ea m\'b5... m\'b5... m\'b5 r\'e8t cu\'e9c ng\'ad\'eai ta \'ae\'b7 nh\'a9n danh n\'e3 \'ae\'d3 nh\'cbp v\'b5o n\'ad
\'edc h\'e4 r\'ad\'eeu c\'e5n, thu\'e8c phi\'d6n, ch\'d5 \'ae\'e9 lao d\'dech, ch\'d5 \'ae\'e9 b\'e8c v\'b8c n\'c6ng n\'d2, ch\'d5 \'ae\'e9 d\'a9n b\'b6n x\'f8 v\'b5 s\'f9 c\'ad\'edp \'aeo\'b9t. Trong l\'f3c ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8 b\'de t\'ef \'ae\'b5
y v\'d7 nh\'f7ng duy\'aan c\'ed vu v\'ac, th\'d7 b\'e4n th\'f9c d\'a9n v\'b5 b\'e4n quan cai tr\'de ph\'b9m t\'e9i gi\'d5t ng\'ad\'eai, h\'e8i l\'e9, mua b\'b8n ch\'f8c t\'ad\'edc, \'a8n c\'bep, v\'c9n nh\'d1 b\'ad\'edc thang m\'a9y. T\'abi kh\'abng n\'e3
i \'ae\'d5n ng\'b5i \'a7\'b8cl\'ac, u\'fb vi\'aan H\'e9i \'ae\'e5ng qu\'e8c gia t\'ad v\'can Nam K\'fa, hay ng\'b5i B\'ab\'aeoanh, to\'b5n quy\'d2n \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng; chuy\'d6n c\'f1a c\'b8c v\'de \'cay \'ae\'b7 qua ba n\'a8m nay r\'e5i. T\'abi mu
\'e8n n\'e3i \'ae\'d5n hai vi\'aan ch\'f8c \'eb Angi\'aari h\'e5i th\'b8ng 4 v\'f5a r\'e5i, \'ae\'b7 b\'de t\'e8 c\'b8o c\'abng khai v\'d2 t\'e9i d\'efng gi\'cay t\'ea gi\'b6 m\'b9o, v\'d2 t\'e9i th\'f4t ti\'d2n c\'abng qu\'fc c\'efng c\'b8c t\'e9i n\'c6
ng kh\'b8c, nh\'adng l\'b9i \'ae\'ad\'eec }{\i\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 tha b\'e6ng}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 . T\'abi c\'f2ng
\par }\pard\plain \s22\qj \li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f40\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 mu\'e8n n\'e3i \'ae\'d5n m\'cay v\'de u\'fb vi\'aan H
