u \'fd Qu\'e8c t\'d5 C\'e9ng s\'b6n \'ae\'d5n m\'e9t s\'f9 th\'cbt l\'b5: Thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea v\'c9n \'aeang t\'e5n t\'b9i, v\'b5 v\'b9ch ra \'ae\'d3 Qu\'e8c t\'d5 C\'e9ng s\'b6n th\'cay r\'bbng: C\'b8ch m\'b9ng, ngo\'b5i v\'can \'ae\'d2 t\'ad\'acng lai c
\'f1a c\'b8c thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea c\'dfn c\'e3 c\'b6 nguy c\'ac c\'f1a c\'b8c thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea. Song, t\'abi th\'cay r\'bbng h\'d7nh nh\'ad, c\'b8c \'ae\'e5ng ch\'dd ch\'ada ho\'b5n to\'b5n th\'cam nhu\'c7n t\'ad t\'ad\'ebng cho r\'bbng v\'cbn m\'d6nh c
\'f1a giai c\'cap v\'ab s\'b6n th\'d5 gi\'edi v\'b5 \'ae\'c6c bi\'d6t l\'b5 v\'cbn m\'d6nh c\'f1a giai c\'cap v\'ab s\'b6n \'eb c\'b8c n\'ad\'edc \'aei x\'a9m l\'ad\'eec thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea g\'ben ch\'c6t v\'edi v\'cbn m\'d6nh c\'f1a giai c\'cap b\'de \'b8
p b\'f8c \'eb c\'b8c thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea. V\'d7 v\'cby, t\'abi s\'cf t\'cbn d\'f4ng m\'e4i c\'ac h\'e9i c\'e3 \'ae\'ad\'eec, s\'cf g\'eei ra nh\'f7ng v\'can \'ae\'d2 v\'b5 n\'d5u c\'c7n t\'abi s\'cf th\'f8c t\'d8nh c\'b8c \'ae\'e5ng ch\'dd v\'d2 v\'can 
\'ae\'d2 thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea.
\par }{\expnd0\expndtw-2\insrsid1378858 H\'abm nay, t\'abi c\'c7n nh\'bec l\'b9i l\'eai ph\'b8t bi\'d3u t\'b9i \'ae\'a9y c\'f1a \'ae\'e5ng ch\'dd R\'abi, ch\'d8 xin \'ae\'e6i nh\'f7ng t\'aan ri\'aang, ngh\'dca l\'b5 \'ae\'acn gi\'b6n thay th\'d5 t\'f5 n\'ad
\'edc Anh b\'bbng c\'b8c t\'f5 Ph\'b8p, B\'d8, M\'fc, Nh\'cbt ... Song, v\'d7 t\'abi l\'b5 ng\'ad\'eai x\'f8 thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea Ph\'b8p v\'b5 v\'d7 t\'abi mu\'e8n n\'e3i ng\'ben, n\'aan t\'abi ch\'d8 n\'e3i v\'d2 ch\'f1 ngh\'dca \'ae\'d5 qu\'e8c Ph\'b8
p, v\'d2 \'a7\'b6ng Ph\'b8p c\'f1a ch\'f3ng t\'abi v\'b5 v\'d2 c\'b8c \'ae\'b6ng t\'b9i c\'b8c thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea Ph\'b8p, gi\'e8ng nh\'ad \'ae\'e5ng ch\'dd R\'abi \'ae\'b7 n\'e3i v\'d2 n\'ad\'edc Anh, v\'d2 \'ae\'b6ng anh em c\'f1a ch\'f3ng ta v\'b5 v
\'d2 c\'b8c \'ae\'b6ng \'eb c\'b8c thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea c\'f1a n\'ad\'edc Anh.
