 sung nh\'f7ng \'fd ki\'d5n ph\'aa b\'d7nh c\'f1a \'ae\'e5ng ch\'dd Manuinxki v\'d2 ch\'ddnh s\'b8ch c\'f1a ch\'f3ng ta trong v\'can \'ae\'d2 thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea. Nh\'adng tr\'ad\'edc khi \'aei v\'b5o th\'f9c ch\'cat c\'f1a v\'can \'ae\'d2, t\'abi th\'ca
y n\'aan \'ae\'ada ra m\'e9t v\'b5i con s\'e8 th\'e8ng k\'aa v\'d2 thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea. \'a7i\'d2u n\'b5y s\'cf gi\'f3p ch\'f3ng ta th\'cay r\'e2 h\'acn t\'cat c\'b6 t\'c7m quan tr\'e4ng c\'f1a v\'can \'ae\'d2 thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea.
