c t\'d5 N\'abng d\'a9n g\'f6i nh\'a9n d\'a9n c\'b8c n\'ad\'edc thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea, do Qu\'e8c t\'d5 C\'e9ng s\'b6n g\'f6i \'ae\'d5n \'ae\'d3 \'ae\'a8ng tr\'aan b\'b8o. Tr\'ad\'edc \'a7\'b9i h\'e9i Li\'abng}{\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 47}{
\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  trong m\'f4c \'ae\'a8ng c\'b8c b\'b5i tranh lu\'cbn, \'ae\'b7 \'ae\'a8ng h\'d5t m\'e4i lu\'cbn c\'ad\'acng, tr\'f5 lu\'cbn c\'ad\'acng v\'d2 v\'can \'ae\'d2 thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea. B\'b8o }{\i\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 L'Humanit\'d0 }{
