\par 1. M\'eb tr\'aan b\'b8o }{\i\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 L'Humanit\'d0 }{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 m\'e9t m\'f4c \'ae\'d3 \'ae\'a8ng \'ae\'d2u \'ae\'c6n h\'bbng tu\'c7n \'ddt nh\'cat hai c\'e9t c\'b8c b\'b5i v\'d2 v\'can \'ae\'d2 thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea.
\par 2. T\'a8ng c\'ad\'eang tuy\'aan truy\'d2n v\'b5 tuy\'d3n l\'f9a \'ae\'b6ng vi\'aan c\'f1a \'a7\'b6ng trong nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8 \'eb nh\'f7ng n\'ad\'edc thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea \'ae\'b7 c\'e3 ph\'a9n b\'e9 c\'e9ng s\'b6n.
\par 3. G\'f6i nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8 v\'b5o Tr\'ad\'eang \'ae\'b9i h\'e4c c\'e9ng s\'b6n c\'f1a nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai lao \'ae\'e9ng ph\'ad\'acng \'a7\'abng \'eb M\'b8txc\'acva.
\par 4. Tho\'b6 thu\'cbn v\'edi T\'e6ng Li\'aan \'aeo\'b5n lao \'ae\'e9ng th\'e8ng nh\'cat}{\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 49}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  \'ae\'d3 t\'e6 ch\'f8c nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai lao \'ae\'e9ng c\'f1a c\'b8c thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea l\'b5m vi\'d6c 
\'eb Ph\'b8p.
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-290\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 5. \'a7\'c6t nhi\'d6m v\'f4 cho c\'b8c \'ae\'b6ng vi\'aan c
\'f1a \'a7\'b6ng ph\'b6i quan t\'a9m h\'acn n\'f7a \'ae\'d5n v\'can \'ae\'d2 thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea.
\par Theo t\'abi, nh\'f7ng \'ae\'d2 ngh\'de n\'b5y l\'b5 h\'eep l\'fd v\'b5 n\'d5u Qu\'e8c t\'d5 C\'e9ng s\'b6n v\'b5 c\'b8c \'ae\'b9i bi\'d3u c\'f1a \'a7\'b6ng ch\'f3ng t\'abi t\'b8n th\'b5nh th\'d7 t\'abi tin r\'bbng \'ae\'d5n \'a7\'b9i h\'e9i l\'c7n th\'f8
 VI, \'a7\'b6ng C\'e9ng s\'b6n Ph\'b8p ch\'f3ng t\'abi s\'cf c\'e3 th\'d3 n\'e3i r\'bbng m\'c6t tr\'cbn th\'e8ng nh\'cat c\'f1a nh\'a9n d\'a9n ch\'ddnh qu\'e8c v\'b5 thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea \'ae\'b7 tr\'eb th\'b5nh s\'f9 th\'cbt.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Th\'ada c\'b8c \'ae\'e5ng ch\'dd, v\'d7 ch\'f3ng ta t\'f9
 coi m\'d7nh l\'b5 h\'e4c tr\'df c\'f1a L\'aanin, cho n\'aan ch\'f3ng ta c\'c7n ph\'b6i t\'cbp trung t\'cat c\'b6 s\'f8c l\'f9c v\'b5 ngh\'de l\'f9c \'ae\'d3 th\'f9c hi\'d6n tr\'aan th\'f9c t\'d5 nh\'f7ng l\'eai di hu\'can qu\'fd b\'b8u c\'f1a L\'aanin 
\'ae\'e8i v\'edi ch\'f3ng ta v\'d2 v\'can \'ae\'d2 thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea c\'f2ng nh\'ad c\'b8c v\'can \'ae\'d2 kh\'b8c.
\par 
\par }\pard\plain \s26\ql \li0\ri567\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin567\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 In trong s\'b8ch }{\i\insrsid1378858 \'a7\'b9i h\'e9i to\'b5n th
\'d5 gi\'edi\line l\'c7n th\'f8 V Qu\'e8c t\'d5 C\'e9ng s\'b6n,}{\insrsid1378858  b\'b6n t\'e8c\line k\'fd, ti\'d5ng Nga, ph\'c7n I, Nxb. Ch\'ddnh tr\'de\line qu\'e8c gia, M\'b8txc\'acva, 1925, tr.653-657.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 
