\'a7\'b9I H\'e9I L\'c7N TH\'f8 V QU\'e8C T\'d5 C\'e9NG S\'b6N
\par }\pard\plain \qr \fi397\li0\ri425\sa240\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin425\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 \~Ng\'b5y 3-7-1924
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-270\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 C\'b8c thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea Ph\'b8p chi\'d5m m\'e9t di\'d6n t\'ddch r\'e9ng 10.211.510 km}{\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 
2}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  v\'edi s\'e8 d\'a9n l\'b5 55.571.000 ng\'ad\'eai \'eb r\'b6i kh\'bep b\'e8n l\'f4c \'ae\'dea. D\'ef c\'e3 s\'f9 kh\'b8c nhau v\'d2 ch\'f1ng t\'e9c, kh\'dd h\'cbu, t\'cbp qu\'b8n, truy\'d2n th\'e8ng, v\'d2 tr\'d7nh \'ae\'e9 ph
\'b8t tri\'d3n kinh t\'d5 v\'b5 x\'b7 h\'e9i, song c\'e3 hai \'aei\'d3m chung l\'b5m cho c\'b8c n\'ad\'edc thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea gi\'e8ng nhau v\'b5 sau n\'b5y c\'e3 th\'d3 \'aei t\'edi th\'e8ng nh\'cat \'ae\'d3 c\'efng \'ae\'cau tranh:
\par 1. }{\i\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 T\'d7nh h\'d7nh kinh t\'d5}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 : trong t\'cat c\'b6 c\'b8c thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea Ph\'b8p, c\'abng nghi\'d6p v\'b5 th\'ad\'acng nghi\'d6p ph\'b8t tri\'d3n r\'cat y\'d5u \'edt v\'b5 nh\'a9n d\'a9n h\'c7u h
\'d5t l\'b5m ngh\'d2 n\'abng, 95% s\'e8 d\'a9n b\'b6n x\'f8 l\'b5 n\'abng d\'a9n.
\par 2. }{\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'eb}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  t\'cat c\'b6 c\'b8c n\'ad\'edc thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea, nh\'a9n d\'a9n b\'b6n x\'f8 \'ae\'d2u b\'de t\'ad b\'b6n \'ae\'d5 qu\'e8c ch\'f1 ngh\'dca Ph\'b8p b\'e3c l\'e9t kh\'abng ng\'f5ng.
\par T\'abi kh\'abng c\'e3 th\'d7 gi\'ea ph\'a9n t\'ddch k\'fc l\'ad\'ecng v\'d2 t\'d7nh h\'d7nh n\'abng d\'a9n t\'f5ng n\'ad\'edc thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea. V\'d7 v\'cby, t\'abi ch\'d8 l\'cay m\'e9t v\'b5i th\'dd d\'f4 \'aei\'d3n h\'d7nh \'ae\'d3 ch\'f3ng ta c\'e3 m
\'e9t \'fd ni\'d6m v\'d2 t\'d7nh c\'b6nh n\'abng d\'a9n c\'b8c n\'ad\'edc thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea.
\par T\'abi xin b\'bet \'ae\'c7u t\'f5 n\'ad\'edc t\'abi, \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng l\'b5 n\'ad\'edc t\'abi bi\'d5t r\'e2 h\'acn c\'b6.
\par Khi Ph\'b8p \'ae\'b8nh chi\'d5m thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea n\'b5y, chi\'d5n tranh \'ae\'b7 l\'b5m cho n\'abng d\'a9n ph\'b6i r\'eai b\'e1 l\'b5ng m\'b9c c\'f1a h\'e4. Sau \'ae\'e3, khi h\'e4 tr\'eb v\'d2 th\'d7 \'ae\'b7 th\'cay ru\'e9ng \'ae\'cat c\'f1a h\'e4 b
\'de b\'e4n ch\'f1 \'ae\'e5n \'aei\'d2n, theo sau qu\'a9n \'ae\'e9i chi\'d5n th\'beng, chi\'d5m m\'cat. Th\'cbm ch\'dd ch\'f3ng \'ae\'b7 chia nhau c\'b6 nh\'f7ng \'ae\'cat \'aeai m\'b5 n\'abng d\'a9n b\'b6n x\'f8 \'ae\'b7 c\'b5y c\'cay t\'f5 bao \'ae\'ea
i nay. Nh\'ad v\'cby l\'b5 n\'abng d\'a9n An Nam \'ae\'b7 bi\'d5n th\'b5nh n\'abng n\'ab v\'b5 bu\'e9c ph\'b6i c\'b5y c\'cay ru\'e9ng \'ae\'cat c\'f1a ch\'ddnh m\'d7nh cho b\'e4n ch\'f1 n\'ad\'edc ngo\'b5i.
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sl-268\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 Nhi\'d2u ng\'ad\'eai trong nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai x\'cau s\'e8 n
\'b5y v\'d7 kh\'abng ch\'deu s\'e8ng trong nh\'f7ng \'aei\'d2u ki\'d6n v\'ab c\'efng kh\'bec nghi\'d6t do nh\'f7ng k\'ce chi\'d5m \'aeo\'b9t \'ae\'ada ra, n\'aan \'ae\'b7 b\'e1 ru\'e9ng \'ae\'cat c\'f1a m\'d7nh v\'b5 lang thang nay \'ae\'a9y mai \'ae\'e3
 kh\'bep n\'ad\'edc; ng\'ad\'eai Ph\'b8p g\'e4i h\'e4 l\'b5 "gi\'c6c c\'ad\'edp" v\'b5 t\'d7m \'ae\'f1 m\'e4i c\'b8ch truy n\'b7 h\'e4.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sl-268\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Ru\'e9ng \'ae\'cat c\'ad\'edp \'ae\'ad\'eec b\'bbng c\'b8ch 
\'cay \'ae\'b7 \'ae\'ad\'eec \'aeem chia cho b\'e4n ch\'f1 \'ae\'e5n \'aei\'d2n. Ch\'d8 c\'c7n xin m\'e9t ti\'d5ng l\'b5 b\'e4n ch\'f3ng c\'e3 th\'d3 \'ae\'ad\'eec h\'ad\'ebng nh\'f7ng kho\'b6nh \'ae\'cat c\'e3 khi tr\'aan 2 v\'b9n v\'b5 2,5 v\'b9n ha.

\par Nh\'f7ng t\'aan ch\'f1 \'ae\'e5n \'aei\'d2n n\'b5y kh\'abng nh\'f7ng chi\'d5m kh\'abng ru\'e9ng \'ae\'cat m\'b5 c\'dfn chi\'d5m kh\'abng c\'b6 m\'e4i th\'f8 c\'c7n thi\'d5t \'ae\'d3 khai th\'b8c s\'e8 ru\'e9ng \'ae\'cat \'ae\'e3, k\'d3 c\'b6 s\'f8c lao 
\'ae\'e9ng.
\par Ch\'ddnh quy\'d2n cho ph\'d0p ch\'f3ng s\'f6 d\'f4ng m\'e9t s\'e8 t\'ef kh\'e6 sai l\'b5m kh\'abng c\'abng, ho\'c6c b\'bet c\'b8c x\'b7 ph\'b6i cung c\'cap nh\'a9n l\'f9c cho c\'b8c ch\'f1 
\par }\pard \qj \li0\ri0\sa80\sl-268\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'ae\'e5n \'aei\'d2n.
\par }{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858\charrsid7755815 B\'aan c\'b9nh ch\'ddnh quy\'d2n lang s\'e3i \'ae\'e3, c\'c7n ph\'b6i n\'e3i t\'edi Nh\'b5 chung. Ch\'d8 ri\'aang gi\'b8o h\'e9i Thi\'aan Ch\'f3a \'ae\'b7 chi\'d5m 1/4 di\'d6n t\'ddch }{
\i\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858\charrsid7755815 c\'b5y c\'cay}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858\charrsid7755815  \'eb Nam K\'fa. \'a7\'d3 chi\'d5m s\'e8 ru\'e9ng \'ae\'cat \'ae\'e3, Nh\'b5 chung \'ae\'b7 d\'efng nh\'f7ng ph\'ad\'acng ph\'b8p kh\'abng th\'d3 t\'ad\'eb
ng t\'ad\'eeng \'ae\'ad\'eec l\'b5 mua chu\'e9c, l\'f5a \'ae\'b6o v\'b5 c\'ad\'ecng b\'f8c. \'a7\'a9y l\'b5 m\'e9t v\'b5i th\'dd d\'f4. L\'eei d\'f4ng l\'f3c m\'cat m\'efa, Nh\'b5 chung cho n\'abng d\'a9n vay ti\'d2n nh\'adng b\'bet bu\'e9c h\'e4 ph\'b6
i c\'c7m ru\'e9ng. Ti\'d2n l\'b7i qu\'b8 cao l\'b5m cho n\'abng d\'a9n kh\'abng sao tr\'b6 h\'d5t n\'ee, n\'aan bu\'e9c ph\'b6i b\'b8n \'ae\'f8t s\'e8 ru\'e9ng c\'c7m tr\'ad\'edc cho Nh\'b5 chung. B\'bbng m\'e4i th\'f1 \'aeo\'b9n t\'b5n \'b8c, Nh\'b5
 chung c\'e8 t\'d7m ra \'ae\'f1 m\'e4i th\'f8 t\'b5i li\'d6u m\'cbt c\'e3 th\'d3 g\'a9y nguy h\'b9i cho nh\'f7ng nh\'b5 c\'c7m quy\'d2n. L\'eei d\'f4ng nh\'f7ng gi\'cay t\'ea \'ae\'e3 l\'b5m c\'abng c\'f4 \'aee do\'b9, Nh\'b5 chung \'ae\'b9t \'ae\'ad\'ee
c t\'cat c\'b6 nh\'f7ng g\'d7 h\'e4 mu\'e8n. Nh\'b5 chung l\'cbp h\'e9i v\'edi b\'e4n t\'ad b\'b6n l\'edn \'ae\'d3 khai kh\'c8n nh\'f7ng \'ae\'e5n \'aei\'d2n chi\'d5m kh\'abng v\'b5 nh\'f7ng ru\'e9ng \'ae\'cat c\'ad\'edp \'ae\'ad\'eec c\'f1a n\'abng d\'a9
n. B\'e4n tay ch\'a9n c\'f1a Nh\'b5 chung gi\'f7 nh\'f7ng ch\'f8c cao trong ch\'ddnh ph\'f1. Nh\'b5 chung c\'f2ng b\'e3c l\'e9t "con chi\'aan" m\'e9t c\'b8ch t\'b5n nh\'c9n kh\'abng k\'d0m ch\'f1 \'ae\'e5n \'aei\'d2n. M\'e9t th\'f1 \'aeo\'b9n kh\'b8c c
\'f1a Nh\'b5 chung l\'b5 t\'cbp h\'eep nh\'f7ng
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \li0\ri0\sa80\sl-268\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 ng\'ad\'eai \'a8n xin, b\'bet h\'e4 khai kh\'c8n \'ae\'cat m\'ed
i v\'b5 h\'f8a l\'b5 sau khi khai kh\'c8n xong s\'cf chia cho h\'e4. Nh\'adng khi ru\'e9ng \'ae\'cat m\'edi v\'f5a khai kh\'c8n xong v\'b5 s\'bep \'ae\'ad\'eec g\'c6t, th\'d7 Nh\'b5 chung tuy\'aan b\'e8 l\'b5 ru\'e9ng \'ae\'cat n\'b5y thu\'e9c v\'d2 Nh
\'b5 chung v\'b5 \'aeu\'e6i nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai \'ae\'b7 d\'efng s\'f8c lao \'ae\'e9ng c\'f1a m\'d7nh l\'b5m cho ru\'e9ng \'ae\'cat \'cay \'ae\'ad\'eec ph\'d7 nhi\'aau. B\'de nh\'f7ng k\'ce "b\'b6o h\'e9" h\'e4 (\'eb trong t\'abn gi\'b8o hay \'eb ngo\'b5
i t\'abn gi\'b8o) c\'ad\'edp b\'e3c, n\'abng d\'a9n An Nam th\'cbm ch\'dd kh\'abng th\'d3 y\'aan \'e6n l\'b5m \'a8n tr\'aan ph\'c7n ru\'e9ng \'ae\'cat \'ddt \'e1i c\'dfn l\'b9i c\'f1a m\'d7nh. Ng\'ad\'eai ta b\'bet nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai \'aeo \'ae\'b9c ph
\'b6i \'aeo ru\'e9ng \'ae\'cat c\'f1a n\'abng d\'a9n kh\'abng \'ae\'f3ng \'ae\'d3 b\'bet h\'e4 ph\'b6i \'ae\'e3ng thu\'d5 kh\'e8ng. Thu\'d5 ru\'e9ng \'ae\'cat m\'e7i n\'a8m m\'e9t t\'a8ng. M\'edi \'ae\'a9y, khi chi\'d5m h\'b5ng ngh\'d7n h\'d0cta c\'f1a ng
\'ad\'eai An Nam \'eb mi\'d2n ng\'ad\'eec \'ae\'d3 giao cho b\'e4n \'ae\'c7u c\'ac, c\'b8c nh\'b5 c\'c7m quy\'d2n \'ae\'b7 ph\'b8i m\'b8y bay \'ae\'d5n \'ae\'d3 nh\'f7ng n\'b9n nh\'a9n b\'de c\'ad\'edp b\'e3c \'eb \'ae\'cay kh\'abng d\'b8m ngh\'dc \'ae
\'d5n n\'e6i lo\'b9n.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai n\'abng d\'a9n b\'de c\'ad\'edp b\'e3
c, ph\'b8 s\'b6n v\'b5 b\'de \'aeu\'e6i \'aei n\'aci kh\'b8c l\'b9i t\'d7m c\'b8ch khai kh\'c8n \'ae\'cat \'ae\'d3 l\'b5m ru\'e9ng. Nh\'adng khi \'ae\'cat m\'edi v\'f5a khai kh\'c8n xong th\'d7 ch\'ddnh quy\'d2n l\'b9i chi\'d5m l\'cay v\'b5 bu\'e9c n\'ab
ng d\'a9n ph\'b6i mua l\'b9i theo gi\'b8 do ch\'ddnh quy\'d2n \'ae\'denh. Ai kh\'abng \'ae\'f1 s\'f8c mua th\'d7 b\'de \'aeu\'e6i \'aei m\'e9t c\'b8ch t\'b5n nh\'c9n.
\par N\'a8m ngo\'b8i, m\'c6c d\'ef \'ae\'cat n\'ad\'edc b\'de n\'b9n l\'f4t t\'b5n ph\'b8, th\'d5 m\'b5 thu\'d5 ru\'e9ng \'ae\'cat v\'c9n t\'a8ng ngay m\'e9t l\'f3c l\'aan 30%.
\par Ngo\'b5i nh\'f7ng th\'f8 thu\'d5 b\'cat c\'abng l\'b5m cho n\'abng d\'a9n b\'de ph\'b8 s\'b6n, n\'abng d\'a9n c\'dfn ph\'b6i \'aei phu, \'ae\'e3ng thu\'d5 th\'a9n, thu\'d5 mu\'e8i, \'ae\'e3ng c\'abng tr\'b8i c\'ad\'ecng b\'f8c, l\'b9c quy\'aan v\'b5 v.v..

\par Ch\'f1 ngh\'dca t\'ad b\'b6n Ph\'b8p c\'f2ng th\'f9c hi\'d6n ch\'ddnh s\'b8ch \'a8n c\'ad\'edp v\'b5 b\'e3c l\'e9t nh\'ad v\'cby \'eb Angi\'aari, Tuynidi, Mar\'e8c. T\'cat c\'b6 nh\'f7ng ru\'e9ng \'ae\'cat t\'e8t v\'b5 \'ae\'ad\'eec t\'ad\'edi n\'ad\'ed
c th\'d7 ph\'b6i \'ae\'d3 cho b\'e4n th\'f9c d\'a9n di c\'ad t\'edi chi\'d5m. D\'a9n b\'b6n x\'f8 b\'de \'aeu\'e6i \'aei, h\'e4 ph\'b6i t\'d7m n\'aci n\'ad\'acng t\'f9a \'eb nh\'f7ng v\'efng ven n\'f3i hay nh\'f7ng n\'aci ru\'e9ng \'ae\'cat kh\'e3 l\'b5m 
\'a8n. C\'b8c c\'abng ty t\'b5i ch\'ddnh, b\'e4n \'ae\'c7u c\'ac v\'b5 quan l\'b9i cao c\'cap chia nhau ru\'e9ng \'ae\'cat c\'f1a c\'b8c thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea.
\par Do nh\'f7ng ho\'b9t \'ae\'e9ng tr\'f9c ti\'d5p v\'b5 gi\'b8n ti\'d5p, c\'b8c ng\'a9n h\'b5ng Angi\'aari v\'b5 Tuynidi n\'a8m 1914 \'ae\'b7 thu \'ae\'ad\'eec 12.258.000 phr\'a8ng ti\'d2n l\'eai v\'edi s\'e8 v\'e8n l\'b5 25 tri\'d6u phr\'a8ng.
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-264\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Ng\'a9n h\'b5ng Mar\'e8c v\'edi s\'e8 v\'e8n l\'b5 15.400.000 phr\'a8ng, n\'a8m 1921 \'ae\'b7 thu \'ae\'ad\'ee
c 1.753.000 phr\'a8ng ti\'d2n l\'eai.
\par C\'abng ty Ph\'b8p - Angi\'aari chi\'d5m 324.000 ha ru\'e9ng \'ae\'cat t\'e8t nh\'cat.
\par T\'e6ng c\'abng ty Angi\'aari chi\'d5m 10 v\'b9n h\'d0cta.
\par M\'e9t c\'abng ty t\'ad nh\'a9n \'ae\'b7 chi\'d5m kho\'b6ng 5 v\'b9n h\'d0cta r\'f5ng, c\'dfn c\'abng ty ph\'e8t ph\'b8t v\'b5 \'ae\'ad\'eang s\'bet C\'b8pde th\'d7 \'ae\'b7 chi\'d5m 5 v\'b9n h\'d0cta c\'e3 nhi\'d2u m\'e1 qu\'c6ng v\'b5 l\'b9i c\'e3 quy
\'d2n \'adu ti\'aan \'ae\'e8i v\'edi 2 v\'b9n ha chung quanh khu v\'f9c n\'b5y.
\par M\'e9t c\'f9u ngh\'de s\'dc Ph\'b8p \'ae\'b7 chi\'d5m m\'e9t \'ae\'e5n \'aei\'d2n 1.125 ha c\'e3 qu\'c6ng m\'e1, tr\'de gi\'b8 l\'b5 10 tri\'d6u phr\'a8ng, thu nh\'cbp h\'bbng n\'a8m l\'b5 4 tri\'d6u phr\'a8ng. D\'a9n b\'b6n x\'f8, ng\'ad\'eai ch\'f1 c
\'f1a nh\'f7ng m\'e1 qu\'c6ng n\'b5y, m\'e7i n\'a8m ch\'d8 thu ho\'b9ch \'ae\'ad\'eec 1% phr\'a8ng m\'e7i h\'d0cta.
\par Ch\'ddnh s\'b8ch th\'f9c d\'a9n c\'f1a Ph\'b8p \'ae\'b7 th\'f1 ti\'aau quy\'d2n chi\'d5m h\'f7u c\'abng c\'e9ng v\'b5 thay th\'d5 b\'bbng quy\'d2n chi\'d5m h\'f7u t\'ad nh\'a9n. N\'e3 c\'f2ng th\'f1 ti\'aau quy\'d2n chi\'d5m h\'f7u nh\'e1, l\'b5m l\'ee
i cho quy\'d2n chi\'d5m h\'f7u \'ae\'e5n \'aei\'d2n l\'edn. N\'e3 \'ae\'b7 l\'b5m cho n\'abng d\'a9n b\'b6n x\'f8 m\'cat h\'acn 5 tri\'d6u ha ru\'e9ng \'ae\'cat t\'e8t nh\'cat.
\par Trong 15 n\'a8m, n\'abng d\'a9n \'eb Cabili b\'de c\'ad\'edp m\'cat 192.090 ha.
\par T\'f5 n\'a8m 1913, m\'e7i n\'a8m n\'abng d\'a9n Mar\'e8c b\'de c\'ad\'edp m\'cat 12.500 ha ru\'e9ng \'ae\'cat c\'b5y c\'cay. T\'f5 khi Ph\'b8p th\'beng trong cu\'e9c chi\'d5n tranh "v\'d7 c\'abng l\'fd", con s\'e8 \'ae\'e3 t\'a8ng l\'aan t\'edi 14.540 ha.

\par Hi\'d6n nay \'eb Mar\'e8c ch\'d8 c\'e3 1.070 ng\'ad\'eai Ph\'b8p m\'b5 chi\'d5m t\'edi 500.000 ha ru\'e9ng \'ae\'cat.
\par C\'f2ng nh\'ad nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai anh em c\'f1a h\'e4 l\'b5 n\'abng d\'a9n An Nam, n\'abng d\'a9n ch\'a9u Phi ph\'b6i ch\'deu c\'b6nh c\'ac c\'f9c kh\'abng th\'d3 ch\'deu n\'e6i, ph\'b6i lao d\'dech li\'aan mi\'aan v\'b5 ph\'b6i g\'b8nh nh\'f7ng th\'f8
 thu\'d5 m\'b8 n\'c6ng n\'d2. S\'f9 c\'efng kh\'e6 c\'f1a h\'e4 kh\'abng sao t\'b6 xi\'d5t. Thi\'d5u l\'ad\'acng th\'f9c n\'aan h\'e4 ph\'b6i \'a8n nh\'f7ng th\'f8 rau c\'e1 d\'b9i hay th\'e3c g\'b9o m\'f4c n\'b8t, v\'d7 th\'d5 m\'b5 b\'d6nh s\'e8t, th
\'ad\'acng h\'b5n, b\'d6nh lao ho\'b5nh h\'b5nh trong nh\'a9n d\'a9n. Ngay nh\'f7ng n\'a8m \'ae\'ad\'eec m\'efa c\'f2ng th\'cay c\'e3 n\'abng d\'a9n \'aei b\'edi nh\'f7ng \'ae\'e8ng r\'b8c \'eb th\'b5nh th\'de, tranh th\'f8c \'a8n th\'f5a v\'edi ch\'e3. C
\'dfn khi m\'cat m\'efa th\'d7 x\'b8c ch\'d5t n\'abng d\'a9n ng\'e6n ngang ngo\'b5i \'ae\'e5ng v\'b5 tr\'aan \'ae\'ad\'eang.
\par T\'d7nh c\'b6nh c\'f1a n\'abng d\'a9n \'eb mi\'d2n T\'a9y ch\'a9u Phi v\'b5 ch\'a9u Phi x\'ddch \'ae\'b9o thu\'e9c Ph\'b8p c\'dfn kh\'f1ng khi\'d5p h\'acn n\'f7a.
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-264\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 G\'c7n 40 c\'abng ty chi\'d5m nh\'f7ng thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea n
\'b5y. H\'e4 chi\'d5m t\'cat c\'b6: ru\'e9ng \'ae\'cat, t\'b5i nguy\'aan thi\'aan nhi\'aan, c\'b6 sinh m\'b9ng c\'f1a d\'a9n b\'b6n x\'f8 n\'f7a. Nh\'a9n d\'a9n b\'b6n x\'f8 th\'cbm ch\'dd kh\'abng c\'e3 quy\'d2n l\'b5m vi\'d6c cho m\'d7nh. H\'e4 bu\'e9
c ph\'b6i l\'b5m vi\'d6c cho c\'b8c c\'abng ty, bao gi\'ea c\'f2ng th\'d5 v\'b5 ch\'d8 \'ae\'ad\'eec l\'b5m vi\'d6c cho c\'b8c c\'abng ty m\'b5 th\'abi. \'a7\'d3 b\'bet h\'e4 ph\'b6i l\'b5m kh\'abng c\'abng, c\'b8c c\'abng ty \'ae\'b7 d\'efng th\'f1 \'aeo
\'b9n c\'ad\'ecng b\'f8c v\'ad\'eet qu\'b8 s\'f8c t\'ad\'ebng t\'ad\'eeng. T\'cat c\'b6 ru\'e9ng \'ae\'cat \'ae\'d2u b\'de t\'dech thu h\'d5t. Ch\'d8 c\'e3 ng\'ad\'eai n\'b5o ch\'deu l\'b5m c\'abng vi\'d6c do c\'b8c c\'abng ty \'cay \'ae\'dfi h\'e1i th
\'d7 m\'edi \'ae\'ad\'eec m\'e9t ph\'c7n ru\'e9ng nh\'e1. \'a1n u\'e8ng thi\'d5u th\'e8n \'ae\'b7 l\'b5m cho h\'e4 m\'bec \'ae\'f1 th\'f8 b\'d6nh t\'cbt v\'b5 ch\'d5t r\'cat nhi\'d2u, nh\'cat l\'b5 tr\'ce con.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-264\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 M\'e9t ph\'ad\'acng ph\'b8p kh\'b8c l\'b5 b\'bet \'abng gi
\'b5, ph\'f4 n\'f7 v\'b5 tr\'ce con l\'b5m con tin. Ch\'f3ng gi\'f7 nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai n\'b5y trong nh\'f7ng c\'a8n nh\'b5 ch\'cbt ch\'e9i, \'ae\'e8i x\'f6 t\'b5n t\'d6, h\'b5nh h\'b9 h\'e4, b\'bet nh\'den \'ae\'e3i v\'b5 nhi\'d2u khi gi\'d5t h\'e4 n
\'f7a. }{\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'eb }{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 m\'e9t v\'b5i \'ae\'dea ph\'ad\'acng, s\'e8 ng\'ad\'eai b\'de b\'bet l\'b5m con tin th\'ad\'eang xuy\'aan l\'b9i nhi\'d2u b\'bbng s\'e8 ng\'ad\'eai l\'b5m vi\'d6c \'ae\'d3 \'ae\'d2 ph\'df
ng m\'e4i m\'adu toan c\'f1a nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai l\'b5m vi\'d6c t\'d7m c\'b8ch ch\'b9y tr\'e8n. \'a7\'d3 c\'abng vi\'d6c \'eb c\'b8c \'ae\'e5n \'aei\'d2n kh\'e1i b\'de \'ae\'d7nh tr\'d6, ng\'ad\'eai ta c\'cam d\'a9n b\'b6n x\'f8 kh\'abng \'ae\'ad\'eec c
\'b5y c\'cay ru\'e9ng c\'f1a m\'d7nh k\'dep th\'eai. Do \'ae\'e3, n\'b9n \'ae\'e3i v\'b5 b\'d6nh d\'dech th\'ad\'eang x\'b6y ra, t\'b5n ph\'b8 c\'b8c thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea.
\par N\'d5u m\'e9t v\'b5i b\'e9 l\'b9c tr\'e8n v\'b5o r\'f5ng v\'b5 tr\'b8nh \'ae\'ad\'eec \'b8ch b\'e3c l\'e9t c\'f1a b\'e4n ch\'f1 \'ae\'e5n \'aei\'d2n th\'d7 h\'e4 ph\'b6i s\'e8ng ch\'bcng kh\'b8c g\'d7 th\'f3 v\'cbt, h\'e4 \'a8n r\'d4 c\'f1 v\'b5 l\'b8 c
\'a9y, ch\'d5t v\'d7 s\'e8t r\'d0t, v\'d7 kh\'dd h\'cbu. Trong l\'f3c \'cay th\'d7 b\'e4n ch\'f1 da tr\'beng t\'b5n ph\'b8 \'ae\'e5ng ru\'e9ng v\'b5 l\'b5ng m\'b9c c\'f1a h\'e4 \'ae\'d3 kh\'f1ng b\'e8. Sau \'ae\'a9y l\'b5 m\'e9t \'aeo\'b9n trong cu\'e8n s
\'e6 tay c\'abng v\'f4 c\'f1a m\'e9t s\'dc quan t\'b6 m\'e9t c\'b8ch v\'ben t\'bet, r\'e2 r\'b5ng v\'b5 th\'aa th\'b6m s\'f9 \'ae\'b5n \'b8p n\'abng d\'a9n b\'b6n x\'f8:
\par H\'b5nh binh c\'b5n qu\'d0t l\'b5ng C\'abevan.
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-264\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 H\'b5nh binh c\'b5n qu\'d0t l\'b5ng Phan\'e8p Cun\'ab, l
\'b5ng v\'b5 v\'ad\'ean tr\'b9i b\'de t\'b5n ph\'b8.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-264\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 H\'b5nh binh c\'b5n qu\'d0t l\'b5ng B\'aacannix\'ac, l\'b5
ng b\'de \'ae\'e8t tr\'f4i, 3.000 c\'a9y chu\'e8i b\'de ch\'c6t.
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 H\'b5nh binh c\'b5n qu\'d0t l\'b5ng Cua, l\'b5ng b\'de ph\'b8, v\'ad\'ean tr\'b9i ho\'b5n to\'b5n b\'de ph\'b8 tr\'f4i.

\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 H\'b5nh binh c\'b5n qu\'d0t l\'b5ng Abimaphan, t\'cat c\'b6
 nh\'b5 c\'f6a \'ae\'d2u b\'de \'ae\'e8t, v\'ad\'ean tr\'b9i b\'de ph\'b8.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 H\'b5nh binh c\'b5n qu\'d0t l\'b5ng Examphami, l\'b5ng b
\'de ph\'b8.
\par C\'b8c l\'b5ng ven s\'abng B\'abm \'ae\'d2u b\'de \'ae\'e8t.
\par T\'b9i nh\'f7ng mi\'d2n ch\'a9u Phi thu\'e9c }{\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'fd}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 , T\'a9y Ban Nha, Anh v\'b5 B\'e5 \'a7\'b5o Nha c\'f2ng c\'e3 m\'e9t ch\'d5 \'ae\'e9 c\'ad\'edp b\'e3c, l\'b5m ph\'b8 s\'b6n, gi\'d5t ch\'e3c v\'b5 t
\'b5n ph\'b8 m\'e9t c\'b8ch kh\'f1ng khi\'d5p nh\'ad v\'cby.
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'eb}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  C\'abngg\'ab thu\'e9c B\'d8, n\'a8m 1891 d\'a9n s\'e8 l\'b5 25 tri\'d6u, th\'d5 m\'b5 \'ae
\'d5n n\'a8m 1911 ch\'d8 c\'dfn c\'e3 8,5 tri\'d6u. Nh\'f7ng b\'e9 l\'b9c Herer\'ab v\'b5 Cama \'eb thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea c\'f2 c\'f1a \'a7\'f8c t\'b9i ch\'a9u Phi \'ae\'b7 ho\'b5n to\'b5n b\'de ti\'aau di\'d6t, 8 v\'b9n ng\'ad\'eai b\'de gi\'d5t trong th
\'eai gian \'a7\'f8c chi\'d5m \'ae\'e3ng v\'b5 15.000 ng\'ad\'eai b\'de gi\'d5t trong th\'eai k\'fa "b\'d7nh \'ae\'denh" n\'a8m 1914. C\'abngg\'ab thu\'e9c Ph\'b8p n\'a8m 
\par 1894 c\'e3 20.000 d\'a9n, th\'d5 m\'b5 \'ae\'d5n 1911 ch\'d8 c\'dfn c\'e3 9.700 ng\'ad\'eai. Trong m\'e9t v\'efng, n\'a8m 1910 c\'e3 10.000 d\'a9n, sau \'ae\'e3 8 n\'a8m ch\'d8 c\'dfn \'ae\'ad\'eec 1.080 ng\'ad\'eai. Trong m\'e9t v\'efng kh\'b8c v\'ed
i 4 v\'b9n d\'a9n da \'aeen, ch\'d8 trong 2 n\'a8m \'ae\'b7 c\'e3 2 v\'b9n ng\'ad\'eai b\'de gi\'d5t, n\'f6a n\'a8m sau 6.000 ng\'ad\'eai n\'f7a l\'b9i b\'de gi\'d5t v\'b5 b\'de th\'ad\'acng t\'cbt.
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 Nh\'f7ng v\'efng ven s\'abng tr\'ef ph\'f3 v\'b5 \'ae\'abng \'ae
\'f3c d\'a9n c\'ad, ch\'d8 sau 15 n\'a8m \'ae\'b7 bi\'d5n th\'b5nh nh\'f7ng mi\'d2n hoang vu. Nh\'f7ng m\'b6nh x\'ad\'acng t\'b5n \'ae\'b7 r\'b6i r\'b8c tr\'beng kh\'bep c\'b8c \'e8c \'ae\'b6o v\'b5 l\'b5ng m\'b9c b\'de t\'b5n ph\'b8.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 T\'d7nh c\'b6nh nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai c\'dfn s\'e8ng s\'e3t th
\'cbt kh\'f1ng khi\'d5p: n\'abng d\'a9n b\'de c\'ad\'edp m\'cat ph\'c7n ru\'e9ng b\'d0 nh\'e1 "\'ae\'d3 d\'b5nh" c\'f1a m\'d7nh, th\'ee th\'f1 c\'abng m\'cat ngh\'d2, c\'dfn ng\'ad\'eai ch\'a8n nu\'abi th\'d7 m\'cat s\'f3c v\'cbt. D\'a9n Matab\'aale l\'b5
 d\'a9n ch\'a8n nu\'abi nhi\'d2u s\'f3c v\'cbt tr\'ad\'edc khi ng\'ad\'eai Anh \'ae\'d5n, h\'e4 c\'e3 t\'edi 20 v\'b9n s\'f3c v\'cbt c\'e3 s\'f5ng. Hai n\'a8m sau ch\'d8 c\'dfn 40.900 con. D\'a9n Herer\'ab c\'e3 9 v\'b9n s\'f3c v\'cbt, trong v\'dfng 12 n
\'a8m b\'e4n th\'f9c d\'a9n \'a7\'f8c \'ae\'b7 c\'ad\'edp m\'cat m\'e9t n\'f6a. Nh\'f7ng tr\'ad\'eang h\'eep t\'ad\'acng t\'f9 nh\'ad v\'cby, x\'b6y ra r\'cat nhi\'d2u trong t\'cat c\'b6 c\'b8c n\'ad\'edc da \'aeen \'ae\'b7 ti\'d5p x\'f3c v\'edi v\'a8
n minh c\'f1a ng\'ad\'eai da tr\'beng.
\par }\pard \qj \li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'a7\'d3 k\'d5t lu\'cbn, t\'abi xin l\'cay m\'e9t d\'c9n ch\'f8ng c\'f1a m\'e9t ng\'ad\'eai da \'aeen l\'b5 R\'acn\'aa Mar\'a8
ng, t\'b8c gi\'b6 cu\'e8n }{\i\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Batuala}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 . \'a4ng ta n\'e3i: "Ch\'a9u Phi v\'efng x\'ddch \'ae\'b9o l\'b5 n\'aci d\'a9n c\'ad \'ae\'abng \'ae\'f3c, gi\'b5u cao su, \'eb \'ae\'a9y c\'e3 \'ae\'f1 c\'b8c lo\'b9
i v\'ad\'ean tr\'b9i tr\'e5ng c\'a9y, g\'b5 v\'b5 d\'aa r\'cat nhi\'d2u. Ch\'d8 sau 7 n\'a8m m\'e4i c\'b8i \'ae\'d2u b\'de ph\'b8 ho\'b9i. L\'b5ng m\'b9c tan t\'b5nh, v\'ad\'ean tr\'b9i hoang t\'b5n, g\'b5 v\'b5 d\'aa b\'de gi\'d5t. Nh\'a9n d\'a9n b\'b6
n x\'f8 ki\'d6t s\'f8c v\'d7 ph\'b6i l\'b5m vi\'d6c n\'c6ng nh\'e4c li\'aan mi\'aan v\'b5 kh\'abng c\'abng n\'aan kh\'abng \'ae\'f1 s\'f8c v\'b5 kh\'abng c\'dfn th\'eai gian, d\'ef l\'b5 r\'cat \'ddt, \'ae\'d3 c\'b5y c\'cay ru\'e9ng \'ae\'cat. B\'d6nh t
\'cbt ph\'b8t sinh, n\'b9n \'ae\'e3i ho\'b5nh h\'b5nh, s\'e8 ng\'ad\'eai ch\'d5t c\'b5ng nhi\'d2u... N\'aan bi\'d5t r\'bbng h\'e4 l\'b5 con ch\'b8u c\'f1a m\'e9t b\'e9 l\'b9c kho\'ce m\'b9nh, thi\'d6n chi\'d5n, d\'ceo dai v\'b5 \'ae\'b7 \'ae\'ad\'eec t
\'abi luy\'d6n. }{\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'eb }{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'ae\'a9y, n\'d2n v\'a8n minh \'ae\'b7 ti\'aau tan...".
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 \'a7\'d3 b\'e6 sung b\'f8c tranh bi th\'b6m n\'b5y, t\'ab
i xin th\'aam m\'e9t \'aei\'d3m l\'b5 ch\'f1 ngh\'dca t\'ad b\'b6n Ph\'b8p kh\'abng h\'d2 ng\'c7n ng\'b9i \'ae\'c8y c\'b6 m\'e9t khu v\'f9c v\'b5o c\'b6nh \'ae\'e3i k\'d0m, n\'d5u vi\'d6c \'ae\'e3 c\'e3 l\'eei cho n\'e3. Trong nhi\'d2u n\'ad\'edc thu\'e9
c \'ae\'dea, v\'dd d\'f4 nh\'ad R\'aauyni\'abng, Angi\'aari, Ma\'aeag\'b8txca, v.v., ng\'ad\'eai ta kh\'abng tr\'e5ng ng\'f2 c\'e8c n\'f7a, m\'b5 l\'b9i ph\'b6i tr\'e5ng nh\'f7ng th\'f8 kh\'b8c c\'c7n cho n\'d2n c\'abng nghi\'d6p c\'f1a Ph\'b8p. Nh\'f7
ng th\'f8 n\'b5y c\'e3 l\'eei h\'acn cho ch\'f1 \'ae\'e5n \'aei\'d2n. \'a7i\'d2u \'ae\'e3 l\'b5m cho \'ae\'eai s\'e8ng \'eb thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea r\'cat \'ae\'bet \'ae\'e1 v\'b5 lu\'abn lu\'abn x\'b6y ra n\'b9n \'ae\'e3i.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Trong t\'cat c\'b6 c\'b8c thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea c\'f1a Ph\'b8
p, n\'b9n ngh\'cco \'ae\'e3i \'ae\'d2u t\'a8ng, s\'f9 ph\'c9n u\'cat ng\'b5y c\'b5ng l\'aan cao. S\'f9 n\'e6i d\'cby c\'f1a n\'abng d\'a9n b\'b6n x\'f8 \'ae\'b7 ch\'ddn mu\'e5i. Trong nhi\'d2u n\'ad\'edc thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea, h\'e4 \'ae\'b7 v\'b5i l\'c7n n
\'e6i d\'cby, nh\'adng l\'c7n n\'b5o c\'f2ng b\'de d\'d7m trong m\'b8u. N\'d5u hi\'d6n nay n\'abng d\'a9n v\'c9n c\'dfn \'eb trong t\'d7nh tr\'b9ng ti\'aau c\'f9c, th\'d7 nguy\'aan nh\'a9n l\'b5 v\'d7 h\'e4 c\'dfn thi\'d5u t\'e6 ch\'f8c, thi\'d5u ng\'ad
\'eai l\'b7nh \'ae\'b9o. Qu\'e8c t\'d5 C\'e9ng s\'b6n c\'c7n ph\'b6i gi\'f3p \'ae\'ec h\'e4 t\'e6 ch\'f8c l\'b9i, c\'c7n ph\'b6i cung c\'cap c\'b8n b\'e9 l\'b7nh \'ae\'b9o cho h\'e4 v\'b5 ch\'d8 cho h\'e4 con \'ae\'ad\'eang \'aei t\'edi c\'b8ch m\'b9ng v
\'b5 gi\'b6i ph\'e3ng.
\par 
\par }\pard\plain \s26\ql \li0\ri567\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin567\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 In trong s\'b8ch }{\i\insrsid1378858 \'a7\'b9i h\'e9i to\'b5n th
\'d5 gi\'edi l\'c7n th\'f8 V
\par Qu\'e8c t\'d5 C\'e9ng s\'b6n}{\insrsid1378858 , b\'b6n t\'e8c k\'fd,
\par ti\'d5ng Nga, ph\'c7n I, Nxb. Ch\'ddnh tr\'de\line Qu\'e8c gia, M\'b8txc\'acva, 1925, tr.758-762.
\par }\pard\plain \s21\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \b\f39\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 
\par }\pard\plain \s20\qc \li0\ri0\sb1400\sa440\sl-380\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \b\f38\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 THAM LU\'cbN T\'b9I \'a7\'b9I H\'e9I L\'c7N TH\'f8 III
