\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Ch\'f1 ngh\'dca t\'ad b\'b6n l\'b5 m\'e9t con \'ae\'d8a c
\'e3 m\'e9t c\'b8i v\'dfi b\'b8m v\'b5o giai c\'cap v\'ab s\'b6n \'eb ch\'ddnh qu\'e8c v\'b5 m\'e9t c\'b8i v\'dfi kh\'b8c b\'b8m v\'b5o giai c\'cap v\'ab s\'b6n \'eb c\'b8c thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea. N\'d5u ng\'ad\'eai ta mu\'e8n gi\'d5t con v\'cbt \'cay, ng\'ad
\'eai ta ph\'b6i \'ae\'e5ng th\'eai c\'bet c\'b6 hai v\'dfi. N\'d5u ng\'ad\'eai ta ch\'d8 c\'bet m\'e9t v\'dfi th\'abi, th\'d7 c\'b8i v\'dfi kia v\'c9n ti\'d5p t\'f4c h\'f3t m\'b8u c\'f1a giai c\'cap v\'ab s\'b6n; con v\'cbt v\'c9n ti\'d5p t\'f4c s\'e8
ng v\'b5 c\'b8i v\'dfi b\'de c\'bet \'ae\'f8t l\'b9i s\'cf m\'e4c ra. C\'b8ch m\'b9ng Nga r\'cat 
\par }\pard \qj \li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 hi\'d3u r\'e2 \'aei\'d2u \'ae\'e3. V\'d7 th\'d5 n\'e3 kh\'abng v\'f5a l\'dfng v\'edi vi\'d6c \'ae\'e4c nh\'f7ng b\'b5i di\'d4
n v\'a8n r\'e7ng tu\'d5ch v\'b5 vi\'d5t ra nh\'f7ng quy\'d5t \'ae\'denh "nh\'a9n \'ae\'b9o" \'ae\'e8i v\'edi c\'b8c d\'a9n t\'e9c b\'de \'b8p b\'f8c, m\'b5 c\'b8ch m\'b9ng Nga d\'b9y cho h\'e4 \'ae\'cau tranh, gi\'f3p \'ae\'ec h\'e4 b\'bbng tinh th\'c7n v
\'b5 v\'cbt ch\'cat nh\'ad L\'aanin \'ae\'b7 tuy\'aan b\'e8 trong lu\'cbn c\'ad\'acng c\'f1a Ng\'ad\'eai v\'d2 v\'can \'ae\'d2 thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea. C\'b8ch m\'b9ng Nga \'ae\'b7 tri\'d6u t\'cbp \'a7\'b9i h\'e9i Bacu}{\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 51}{
\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 ; hai m\'ad\'aci m\'e8t d\'a9n t\'e9c ph\'ad\'acng \'a7\'abng \'ae\'b7 ph\'b8i \'ae\'b9i bi\'d3u t\'edi d\'f9 \'a7\'b9i h\'e9i \'ae\'e3. Nh\'f7ng \'ae\'b9i bi\'d3u c\'f1a c\'b8c \'ae\'b6ng c\'abng nh\'a9n ph\'ad\'acng T\'a9y c\'f2
ng tham gia c\'abng vi\'d6c c\'f1a \'a7\'b9i h\'e9i. \'a7\'e3 l\'b5 l\'c7n \'ae\'c7u ti\'aan trong l\'dech s\'f6, giai c\'cap v\'ab s\'b6n \'eb c\'b8c n\'ad\'edc ph\'ad\'acng T\'a9y \'aei x\'a9m chi\'d5m v\'b5 giai c\'cap v\'ab s\'b6n c\'b8c n\'ad\'edc b
\'de x\'a9m chi\'d5m \'eb ph\'ad\'acng \'a7\'abng \'ae\'b7 th\'a9n m\'cbt n\'bem tay nhau v\'b5 c\'efng nhau t\'d7m c\'b8ch \'ae\'cau tranh c\'e3 hi\'d6u qu\'b6 ch\'e8ng ch\'f1 ngh\'dca t\'ad b\'b6n l\'b5 k\'ce th\'ef chung c\'f1a h\'e4.
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Sau cu\'e9c \'a7\'b9i h\'e9i l\'dech s\'f6 \'cay, m\'c6c d\'c7u \'aeang v\'cap ph\'b6i nh\'f7ng kh\'e3 kh\'a8n trong n
\'ad\'edc v\'b5 ngo\'b5i n\'ad\'edc, n\'ad\'edc Nga c\'b8ch m\'b9ng kh\'abng h\'d2 m\'e9t ch\'f3t do d\'f9 trong vi\'d6c gi\'f3p \'ae\'ec c\'b8c d\'a9n t\'e9c m\'b5 n\'e3 \'ae\'b7 th\'f8c t\'d8nh b\'bbng cu\'e9c c\'b8ch m\'b9ng anh d\'f2ng v\'b5 th\'be
ng l\'eei. M\'e9t trong nh\'f7ng vi\'d6c quan
\par }\pard\plain \s25\qj \li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f38\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\insrsid1378858 tr\'e4ng \'ae\'c7u ti\'aan c\'f1a n\'e3 l\'b5 th\'b5nh l\'cb
p Tr\'ad\'eang \'ae\'b9i h\'e4c ph\'ad\'acng \'a7\'abng.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-274\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Tr\'ad\'eang \'ae\'b9i h\'e4c ph\'ad\'acng \'a7\'abng hi
\'d6n nay g\'e5m c\'e3 1.025 sinh vi\'aan, trong \'ae\'e3 c\'e3 151 n\'f7 sinh. Trong s\'e8 sinh vi\'aan \'cay, c\'e3 865 \'ae\'b6ng vi\'aan c\'e9ng s\'b6n. Th\'b5nh ph\'c7n x\'b7 h\'e9i c\'f1a h\'e4c sinh nh\'ad sau: 547 n\'abng d\'a9n, 265 c\'abng nh
\'a9n, 210 tr\'dd th\'f8c v\'ab s\'b6n. N\'d5u ng\'ad\'eai ta ch\'f3 \'fd r\'bbng c\'b8c n\'ad\'edc ph\'ad\'acng \'a7\'abng \'ae\'d2u l\'b5 nh\'f7ng n\'ad\'edc h\'c7u nh\'ad ho\'b5n to\'b5n n\'abng nghi\'d6p th\'d7 s\'cf d\'d4 hi\'d3u v\'d7 sao s\'e8
 sinh vi\'aan n\'abng d\'a9n chi\'d5m t\'fb l\'d6 cao h\'acn. }{\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'eb \'ca}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 n \'a7\'e9, \'eb Nh\'cbt, \'eb Trung Qu\'e8c - nh\'cat l\'b5 \'eb Trung Qu\'e8c, ph\'c7n nhi\'d2u l\'b5 c\'b8c tr\'dd th\'f8
c trung th\'b5nh v\'edi s\'f9 nghi\'d6p c\'f1a giai c\'cap c\'abng nh\'a9n \'aeang l\'b7nh \'ae\'b9o giai c\'cap n\'b5y trong cu\'e9c \'ae\'cau tranh, \'aei\'d2u \'ae\'e3 gi\'b6i th\'ddch v\'d7 sao s\'e8 tr\'dd th\'f8c chi\'d5m t\'fb l\'d6 m\'e9t thi\'d3
u s\'e8 t\'ad\'acng \'ae\'e8i quan tr\'e4ng; v\'b5 t\'fb l\'d6 c\'abng nh\'a9n \'ddt l\'b5 do c\'abng nghi\'d6p v\'b5 th\'ad\'acng nghi\'d6p t\'ad\'acng \'ae\'e8i k\'d0m ph\'b8t tri\'d3n trong c\'b8c v\'efng ph\'ad\'acng \'a7\'abng, tr\'f5 n\'ad\'edc Nh
\'cbt. Ngo\'b5i ra, c\'dfn c\'e3 75 h\'e4c sinh thi\'d5u ni\'aan, t\'f5 10 \'ae\'d5n 16 tu\'e6i.
\par 150 gi\'b8o s\'ad ph\'f4 tr\'b8ch gi\'b6ng d\'b9y v\'d2 khoa h\'e4c x\'b7 h\'e9i, v\'d2 to\'b8n h\'e4c, v\'d2 duy v\'cbt l\'dech s\'f6, v\'d2 l\'dech s\'f6 phong tr\'b5o c\'abng nh\'a9n, v\'d2 khoa h\'e4c t\'f9 nhi\'aan, v\'d2 l\'dech s\'f6 c\'b8c cu\'e9
c c\'b8ch m\'b9ng, v\'d2 khoa kinh t\'d5 ch\'ddnh tr\'de, v.v.. Trong l\'edp h\'e4c, thanh ni\'aan c\'f1a 62 ch\'f1ng t\'e9c kh\'b8c nhau c\'efng th\'a9n m\'cbt s\'b8t c\'b8nh b\'aan nhau.
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-274\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 Tr\'ad\'eang \'ae\'b9i h\'e4c ph\'ad\'acng \'a7\'abng c\'e3
 10 ng\'abi nh\'b5 to \'ae\'d3 cho sinh vi\'aan d\'efng. Tr\'ad\'eang c\'e3 m\'e9t r\'b9p chi\'d5u b\'e3ng cho sinh vi\'aan xem kh\'abng m\'cat ti\'d2n v\'b5o ng\'b5y th\'f8 n\'a8m v\'b5 ng\'b5y ch\'f1 nh\'cbt; c\'dfn nh\'f7ng ng\'b5y kh\'b8c trong tu\'c7
n l\'d4 th\'d7 \'ae\'d3 cho m\'e9t ng\'ad\'eai th\'c7u. C\'e3 hai t\'f1 s\'b8ch v\'edi 47.000 quy\'d3n s\'b8ch gi\'f3p cho c\'b8c nh\'b5 c\'b8ch m\'b9ng tr\'ce tu\'e6i \'aei s\'a9u v\'b5o vi\'d6c nghi\'aan c\'f8u c\'f1a m\'d7nh v\'b5 b\'e5i d\'ad\'ecng th
\'aam t\'ad t\'ad\'ebng. M\'e7i d\'a9n t\'e9c hay "nh\'e3m", c\'e3 m\'e9t t\'f1 s\'b8ch ri\'aang, g\'e5m s\'b8ch b\'b8o b\'bbng ti\'d5ng m\'d1 \'ae\'ce c\'f1a h\'e4. Ph\'dfng \'ae\'e4c s\'b8ch \'ae\'ad\'eec sinh vi\'aan trang tr\'dd m\'e9t c\'b8ch c\'e3
 ngh\'d6 thu\'cbt v\'b5 c\'e3 \'ae\'c7y \'ae\'f1 b\'b8o ch\'dd. C\'b8c h\'e4c sinh c\'f2ng cho ra m\'e9t t\'ea b\'b8o ch\'d8 c\'e3 m\'e9t b\'b6n duy nh\'cat d\'b8n v\'b5o c\'b8i b\'b6ng to \'ae\'c6t tr\'ad\'edc c\'f6a ph\'dfng \'ae\'e4c s\'b8ch. Nh\'f7
ng ng\'ad\'eai \'aeau \'e8m \'ae\'ad\'eec v\'b5o ch\'f7a trong b\'d6nh vi\'d6n c\'f1a nh\'b5 tr\'ad\'eang. M\'e9t tr\'b9i \'aei\'d2u d\'ad\'ecng \'eb Crim\'aa d\'b5nh ri\'aang cho sinh vi\'aan c\'c7n \'ae\'ad\'eec d\'ad\'ecng s\'f8c. Ch\'ddnh ph\'f1 X\'ab
vi\'d5t \'ae\'b7 t\'c6ng cho Tr\'ad\'eang \'ae\'b9i h\'e4c hai tr\'b9i h\'cc m\'e7i tr\'b9i c\'e3 9 ng\'abi nh\'b5. M\'e7i tr\'b9i h\'cc c\'e3 m\'e9t ch\'e7 cho sinh vi\'aan h\'e4c ch\'a8n nu\'abi. Ng\'ad\'eai "b\'dd th\'ad n\'abng nghi\'d6p" c\'f1a Tr
\'ad\'eang \'ae\'b9i h\'e4c \'ae\'b7 t\'f9 h\'b5o n\'e3i v\'edi t\'abi: "Ch\'f3ng t\'abi \'ae\'b7 c\'e3 30 con b\'df c\'b8i v\'b5 50 con l\'een". M\'e9t tr\'a8m h\'d0cta ru\'e9ng \'ae\'cat c\'cap cho c\'b8c tr\'b9i h\'cc \'cay l\'b5 do sinh vi\'aan t\'f9
 c\'b5y c\'cay l\'cay. Trong k\'fa ngh\'d8 h\'cc v\'b5 sau gi\'ea l\'b5m vi\'d6c v\'b5 t\'cbp luy\'d6n, sinh vi\'aan \'aei gi\'f3p \'ae\'ec n\'abng d\'a9n. Nh\'a9n \'ae\'a9y c\'f2ng n\'e3i qua r\'bbng m\'e9t trong nh\'f7ng tr\'b9i h\'cc \'cay tr\'ad\'ed
c kia l\'b5 th\'b8i \'cap c\'f1a m\'e9t qu\'cbn c\'abng. Th\'cbt l\'b5 m\'e9t c\'b6nh \'ae\'b8ng ghi nh\'ed khi tr\'abng th\'cay l\'b8 c\'ea \'ae\'e1 tung bay ki\'aau h\'b7nh tr\'aan ng\'e4n th\'b8p c\'e3 mang t\'ad\'edc huy qu\'cbn c\'abng, v\'b5 th\'ca
y nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai n\'abng d\'a9n tr\'ce tu\'e6i Tri\'d2u Ti\'aan hay }{\f38\insrsid1378858 \'b8}{\insrsid1378858 cm\'aani vui \'ae\'efa trong l\'d4 \'aei\'d6n c\'f1a qu\'cbn c\'abng kh\'abng ki\'aang n\'d3 g\'d7 c\'b6.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-288\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Sinh vi\'aan \'a8n, \'eb v\'b5 m\'c6c kh\'abng ph\'b6i m
\'cat ti\'d2n. M\'e7i th\'b8ng m\'e7i sinh vi\'aan c\'dfn \'ae\'ad\'eec l\'dcnh 5 \'ae\'e5ng r\'f3p v\'b5ng \'ae\'d3 ti\'aau v\'c6t.
\par \'a7\'d3 h\'e4c sinh c\'e3 m\'e9t quan ni\'d6m \'ae\'f3ng \'ae\'ben v\'d2 vi\'d6c gi\'b8o d\'f4c tr\'ce em, Tr\'ad\'eang \'ae\'b9i h\'e4c c\'e3 m\'e9t nh\'b5 nu\'abi tr\'ce v\'b5 m\'e9t nh\'b5 g\'f6i tr\'ce r\'cat ki\'d3u m\'c9u g\'e5m 60 em nh\'e1.

\par M\'e7i n\'a8m Tr\'ad\'eang \'ae\'b9i h\'e4c chi ti\'aau \'ae\'d5n 516.000 \'ae\'e5ng r\'f3p v\'b5ng.
\par C\'b8c \'ae\'b9i bi\'d3u c\'f1a 62 ch\'f1ng t\'e9c trong Tr\'ad\'eang \'ae\'b9i h\'e4c l\'cbp th\'b5nh m\'e9t "C\'abng x\'b7". Ch\'f1 t\'dech v\'b5 c\'b8c c\'b8n s\'f9 c\'f1a C\'abng x\'b7 do ph\'e6 th\'abng \'ae\'c7u phi\'d5u b\'c7u ra ba th\'b8ng m\'e9
t l\'c7n.
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-288\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 M\'e9t \'ae\'b9i bi\'d3u sinh vi\'aan tham gia vi\'d6c qu
\'b6n tr\'de kinh t\'d5 v\'b5 h\'b5nh ch\'ddnh c\'f1a Tr\'ad\'eang \'ae\'b9i h\'e4c. T\'cat c\'b6 c\'b8c sinh vi\'aan \'ae\'d2u ph\'b6i thay phi\'aan nhau l\'c7n l\'ad\'eet l\'b5m c\'abng vi\'d6c nh\'b5 b\'d5p, th\'ad vi\'d6n, c\'a9u l\'b9c b\'e9, v.v.. T
\'cat c\'b6 m\'e4i v\'f4 "ph\'b9m ph\'b8p" ho\'c6c tranh ch\'cap \'ae\'d2u do m\'e9t to\'b5 \'b8n \'ae\'ad\'eec b\'c7u ra x\'d0t x\'f6 tr\'ad\'edc m\'c6t to\'b5n th\'d3 c\'b8c \'ae\'e5ng ch\'dd. C\'abng x\'b7 h\'e4p m\'e7i tu\'c7n m\'e9t l\'c7n \'ae\'d3
 th\'b6o lu\'cbn t\'d7nh h\'d7nh ch\'ddnh tr\'de v\'b5 kinh t\'d5 qu\'e8c t\'d5. Th\'d8nh tho\'b6ng ng\'ad\'eai ta t\'e6 ch\'f8c nh\'f7ng cu\'e9c h\'e9i h\'e4p v\'b5 nh\'f7ng bu\'e6i d\'b9 h\'e9i trong \'ae\'e3 nh\'f7ng sinh vi\'aan c\'e3 khi\'d5u v\'d2
 ngh\'d6 thu\'cbt tr\'d7nh b\'b5y ngh\'d6 thu\'cbt v\'b5 v\'a8n h\'e4c c\'f1a kh\'bep c\'b8c mi\'d2n \'eb ph\'ad\'acng \'a7\'abng.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-288\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 M\'e9t \'aei\'d3m \'ae\'c6c bi\'d6t nh\'cat bi\'d3u hi\'d6
n s\'f9 "d\'b7 man" c\'f1a nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai b\'abns\'aav\'ddch l\'b5 kh\'abng nh\'f7ng h\'e4 coi "nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai d\'a9n thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea th\'cap k\'d0m" \'cay nh\'ad anh em, m\'b5 c\'dfn t\'e6 ch\'f8c cho h\'e4 tham gia \'ae\'eai s\'e8ng ch
\'ddnh tr\'de c\'f1a n\'ad\'edc Nga n\'f7a. Trong k\'fa b\'c7u c\'f6 c\'b8c X\'abvi\'d5t, nh\'f7ng sinh vi\'aan m\'b5 khi c\'dfn \'eb trong n\'ad\'edc c\'f1a h\'e4 th\'d7 ch\'d8 l\'b5 nh\'f7ng "k\'ce d\'a9n l\'b5nh", nh\'f7ng "ng\'ad\'eai \'ae\'ad\'eec b
\'b6o h\'e9", ngh\'dca l\'b5 nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai kh\'abng c\'e3 quy\'d2n g\'d7 kh\'b8c h\'acn l\'b5 quy\'d2n n\'e9p thu\'d5, nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai kh\'abng h\'d2 c\'e3 quy\'d2n \'f8ng c\'f6 v\'b5 b\'c7u c\'f6 \'eb n\'ad\'edc h\'e4, nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai kh
\'abng \'ae\'ad\'eec ph\'d0p b\'b5n b\'b9c ch\'ddnh tr\'de, th\'d7 nay \'eb n\'ad\'edc Nga X\'abvi\'d5t nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai \'ae\'e3 \'ae\'ad\'eec tham gia b\'c7u c\'f6 v\'b5 c\'f6 \'ae\'b9i bi\'d3u c\'f1a h\'e4 v\'b5o X\'abvi\'d5t. Mong r\'bbng nh\'f7
ng anh em c\'f1a t\'abi \'eb c\'b8c thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea \'aeang c\'c7u xin \'ae\'e6i qu\'e8c t\'dech m\'b7i m\'b5 kh\'abng \'ae\'ad\'eec, h\'b7y th\'f6 so s\'b8nh n\'d2n d\'a9n ch\'f1 t\'ad s\'b6n v\'edi n\'d2n d\'a9n ch\'f1 v\'ab s\'b6n.
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\expnd0\expndtw-2\insrsid1378858 T\'cat c\'b6 nh\'f7ng sinh vi\'aan \'cay 
\'ae\'d2u \'ae\'b7 t\'f5ng \'aeau kh\'e6 v\'b5 \'ae\'b7 th\'cay ng\'ad\'eai kh\'b8c \'aeau kh\'e6. T\'cat c\'b6 \'ae\'d2u \'ae\'b7 s\'e8ng d\'ad\'edi "n\'d2n v\'a8n minh khai ho\'b8 cao c\'b6" v\'b5 d\'ad\'edi \'b8ch b\'e3c l\'e9t v\'b5 \'b8p b\'f8c c\'f1
a ch\'f1 ngh\'dca t\'ad b\'b6n n\'ad\'edc ngo\'b5i. V\'d7 th\'d5 t\'cat c\'b6 \'ae\'d2u ham m\'aa v\'b5 khao kh\'b8t h\'e4c t\'cbp v\'b5 hi\'d3u bi\'d5t. H\'e4 v\'f5a h\'a8ng h\'b8i v\'f5a nghi\'aam t\'f3c. H\'e4 kh\'abng h\'d2 ch\'aci b\'eai ph\'e3ng t
\'f3ng nh\'ad nh\'f7ng thanh ni\'aan ph\'ad\'acng \'a7\'abng \'eb Pari, \'eb \'a4xpho, \'eb B\'d0clin. Ng\'ad\'eai ta c\'e3 th\'d3 n\'e3i kh\'abng ngoa r\'bbng Tr\'ad\'eang \'ae\'b9i h\'e4c ph\'ad\'acng \'a7\'abng \'abm \'cap d\'ad\'edi m\'b8i tr\'ad\'ea
ng m\'d7nh t\'cat c\'b6 t\'ad\'acng lai c\'f1a c\'b8c d\'a9n t\'e9c thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Mi\'d2n C\'cbn \'a7\'abng v\'b5 mi\'d2n Vi\'d4n \'a7\'ab
ng, t\'f5 Xyri \'ae\'d5n Tri\'d2u Ti\'aan - ch\'f3ng t\'abi ch\'d8 n\'e3i \'ae\'d5n nh\'f7ng n\'ad\'edc thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea v\'b5 n\'f6a thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea c\'e3 m\'e9t di\'d6n t\'ddch r\'e9ng h\'acn 15 tri\'d6u km}{\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 2}{
\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 , v\'edi s\'e8 d\'a9n h\'acn 1.200 tri\'d6u ng\'ad\'eai, t\'cat c\'b6 nh\'f7ng n\'ad\'edc r\'e9ng l\'edn \'cay ng\'b5y nay \'ae\'d2u \'aeang \'eb d\'ad\'edi \'b8ch c\'f1a ch\'f1 ngh\'dca t\'ad b\'b6n v\'b5 ch\'f1 ngh\'dca \'ae\'d5
 qu\'e8c. V\'b5 m\'c6c d\'ef s\'e8 l\'ad\'eeng c\'f1a h\'e4 \'ae\'b8ng l\'cf ph\'b6i l\'b5m cho h\'e4 c\'e3 s\'f8c m\'b9nh, c\'b8c d\'a9n t\'e9c b\'de \'b8p b\'f8c \'ae\'e3 v\'c9n ch\'ada th\'f9c s\'f9 m\'adu \'ae\'e5 t\'f9 gi\'b6i ph\'e3ng kh\'e1i \'b8
ch \'ae\'e3, v\'b5 v\'d7 h\'e4 ch\'ada hi\'d3u gi\'b8 tr\'de c\'f1a s\'f9 \'aeo\'b5n k\'d5t qu\'e8c t\'d5, n\'aan h\'e4 ch\'ada bi\'d5t \'aeo\'b5n k\'d5t nhau l\'b9i \'ae\'d3 \'ae\'cau tranh. H\'e4 ch\'ada c\'e3 nh\'f7ng s\'f9 li\'aan h\'d6 gi\'f7a c\'b8
c n\'ad\'edc h\'e4 v\'edi nhau, nh\'ad c\'b8c d\'a9n t\'e9c ch\'a9u \'a2u v\'b5 ch\'a9u M\'fc. H\'e4 c\'e3 s\'bdn m\'e9t s\'f8c m\'b9nh to l\'edn m\'b5 h\'e4 ch\'ada bi\'d5t! Vi\'d6c th\'b5nh l\'cbp Tr\'ad\'eang \'ae\'b9i h\'e4c ph\'ad\'acng \'a7\'abng, t
\'cbp h\'eep nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai l\'b7nh \'ae\'b9o tr\'ce tu\'e6i t\'ddch c\'f9c, th\'abng minh c\'f1a c\'b8c n\'ad\'edc thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea, \'ae\'b7 l\'b5m \'ae\'ad\'eec m\'e9t c\'abng cu\'e9c to l\'edn l\'b5:
\par a) Tr\'ad\'eang \'ae\'b7 hu\'can luy\'d6n cho c\'b8c chi\'d5n s\'dc ti\'aan phong t\'ad\'acng lai \'cay nguy\'aan l\'fd \'ae\'cau tranh giai c\'cap, nguy\'aan l\'fd m\'b5 m\'e9t m\'c6t c\'b8c cu\'e9c \'ae\'cau tranh ch\'f1ng t\'e9c v\'b5 m\'c6t kh\'b8c c
\'b8c t\'cbp t\'f4c c\'f1a ch\'d5 \'ae\'e9 gia tr\'ad\'ebng \'ae\'b7 l\'b5m l\'c9n l\'e9n trong \'ae\'c7u \'e3c h\'e4.
\par b) Tr\'ad\'eang \'ae\'b7 l\'b5m cho \'ae\'e9i ti\'aan phong c\'f1a giai c\'cap v\'ab s\'b6n c\'b8c n\'ad\'edc thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea ti\'d5p x\'f3c m\'cbt thi\'d5t v\'edi giai c\'cap v\'ab s\'b6n ph\'ad\'acng T\'a9y \'ae\'d3 d\'e4n \'ae\'ad\'eang cho m\'e9t s
\'f9 h\'eep t\'b8c th\'cbt s\'f9 sau n\'b5y, ch\'d8 c\'e3 s\'f9 h\'eep t\'b8c \'ae\'e3 m\'edi c\'e3 th\'d3 b\'b6o \'ae\'b6m cho giai c\'cap c\'abng nh\'a9n qu\'e8c t\'d5 gi\'b5nh \'ae\'ad\'eec th\'beng l\'eei cu\'e8i c\'efng.
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 c) Tr\'ad\'eang \'ae\'b7 l\'b5m cho c\'b8c d\'a9n t\'e9
c thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea - t\'f5 tr\'ad\'edc \'ae\'d5n nay r\'eai r\'b9c v\'edi nhau - hi\'d3u bi\'d5t nhau, v\'b5 \'aeo\'b5n k\'d5t v\'edi nhau, do \'ae\'e3 \'ae\'c6t c\'ac s\'eb cho m\'e9t kh\'e8i li\'aan h\'eep t\'ad\'acng lai gi\'f7a c\'b8c n\'ad\'edc ph
\'ad\'acng \'a7\'abng, kh\'e8i li\'aan h\'eep \'ae\'e3 l\'b5 m\'e9t trong nh\'f7ng c\'b8i c\'b8nh c\'f1a c\'b8ch m\'b9ng v\'ab s\'b6n.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 d) Tr\'ad\'eang \'ae\'b7 n\'aau l\'aan cho giai c\'cap v
\'ab s\'b6n c\'b8c n\'ad\'edc m\'b5 giai c\'cap t\'ad s\'b6n c\'e3 thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea, m\'e9t t\'cam g\'ad\'acng v\'d2 nh\'f7ng \'aei\'d2u h\'e4 c\'e3 th\'d3 v\'b5 ph\'b6i l\'b5m cho nh\'f7ng anh em c\'f1a h\'e4 \'aeang b\'de \'b8p b\'f8c.
\par }\pard\plain \s24\qr \fi397\li0\ri567\sb360\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin567\lin0\itap0 \f38\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 \~Nguy\'d4n \'b8i Qu\'e8c
