\par }{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 T\'abi \'ae\'b7 \'ae\'d5n M\'b8txc\'acva v\'b5o th\'b8ng 7-1923. T\'abi s\'cf ra \'aei sau 3 th\'b8ng l\'adu l\'b9i \'eb \'ae\'a9y. V\'d7 l\'fd do n\'b5y hay l\'fd do kh\'b8c, vi\'d6c l\'aan \'ae\'ad\'eang c\'f1a t\'abi \'ae\'b7
 b\'de ho\'b7n h\'d5t tu\'c7n n\'b5y sang tu\'c7n kh\'b8c, r\'e5i h\'d5t th\'b8ng n\'b5y sang th\'b8ng kh\'b8c.
\par Sau \'a7\'b9i h\'e9i l\'c7n th\'f8 V, Ban ph\'ad\'acng \'a7\'abng \'ae\'b7 n\'e3i v\'edi t\'abi r\'bbng:
\par 1/ Ban s\'cf gi\'edi thi\'d6u t\'abi v\'edi Qu\'e8c d\'a9n \'ae\'b6ng \'ae\'d3 t\'abi l\'b5m vi\'d6c \'eb \'ae\'cay v\'d7 ngo\'b5i l\'e9 ph\'dd, Ban kh\'abng th\'d3 gi\'f3p t\'abi v\'d2 t\'b5i ch\'ddnh. 2/ T\'abi s\'cf \'eb ch\'e7 \'ae\'e3 v\'edi t\'ad c
\'b8ch c\'b8 nh\'a9n ch\'f8 kh\'abng ph\'b6i v\'edi t\'ad c\'b8ch l\'b5 c\'b8n b\'e9 c\'f1a Qu\'e8c t\'d5 C\'e9ng s\'b6n. 3/ T\'abi s\'cf kh\'abng c\'e3 nh\'f7ng quan h\'d6 v\'edi \'a7\'b6ng ch\'f3ng t\'abi \'eb Trung Qu\'e8c.
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 D\'ef t\'cat c\'b6 nh\'f7ng \'aei\'d2u ki\'d6n \'ae\'e3 
\'ae\'e8i v\'edi t\'abi l\'b5 kh\'e3, nh\'adng t\'abi v\'c9n ch\'cap nh\'cbn n\'e3 \'ae\'d3 c\'e3 th\'d3 \'aei \'ae\'ad\'eec. \'a7\'d3 c\'f8u v\'b7n c\'b8c \'aei\'d2u ki\'d6n 2 v\'b5 3, t\'abi y\'aau c\'c7u \'a7\'b6ng t\'abi cho t\'abi m\'e9t gi\'cay u
\'fb nhi\'d6m, v\'b5 g\'f6i cho \'a7\'b6ng Trung Qu\'e8c m\'e9t b\'f8c th\'ad y\'aau c\'c7u gi\'f3p \'ae\'ec t\'abi trong c\'abng t\'b8c. V\'cby l\'b5 v\'can \'ae\'d2 \'ae\'b7 \'ae\'ad\'eec gi\'b6i quy\'d5t.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Nh\'adng l\'f3c n\'b5y n\'e9i chi\'d5n \'aeang n\'e6 ra 
\'eb Trung Qu\'e8c, Qu\'e8c d\'a9n \'ae\'b6ng kh\'abng tr\'b6 l\'eai b\'f8c th\'ad c\'f1a Ban ph\'ad\'acng \'a7\'abng. V\'b5 vi\'d6c l\'aan \'ae\'ad\'eang c\'f1a t\'abi m\'e9t l\'c7n n\'f7a l\'b9i ph\'b6i ho\'b7n l\'b9i v\'ab th\'eai h\'b9n.
\par Nh\'ad v\'cby, tr\'ad\'edc l\'b5 v\'d7 \'a7\'b6ng t\'abi kh\'abng tr\'b6 l\'eai. Nay l\'b5 v\'d7 nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai Trung Qu\'e8c \'ae\'b8nh nhau. V\'cby ng\'b5y mai s\'cf l\'b5 v\'d7 chuy\'d6n g\'d7 kh\'b8c n\'f7a. Nh\'adng t\'cat c\'b6 nh\'f7ng kh\'e3
 kh\'a8n s\'cf kh\'abng c\'dfn, n\'d5u nh\'ad v\'can \'ae\'d2 t\'b5i ch\'ddnh kh\'abng \'ae\'c6t ra. \'a7\'d3 v\'can \'ae\'d2 kh\'abng \'ae\'c6t ra khi t\'abi ho\'b9t \'ae\'e9ng \'eb b\'aan \'cay, t\'abi ch\'d8 y\'aau c\'c7u c\'b8c \'ae\'e5ng ch\'dd
 cung c\'cap cho t\'abi nh\'f7ng g\'d7 m\'b5 c\'b8c \'ae\'e5ng ch\'dd \'aeang cung c\'cap \'ae\'d3 t\'abi ch\'ea \'ae\'eei, trong th\'eai gian t\'abi kh\'abng l\'b5m g\'d7 \'eb \'ae\'a9y c\'b6.
\par Xin g\'f6i l\'eai ch\'b5o c\'e9ng s\'b6n.
\par }\pard\plain \s24\qr \fi397\li0\ri567\sb360\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin567\lin0\itap0 \f38\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 \~NGUY\'d4N \'b8I QU\'e8C
