\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Ban ph\'ad\'acng \'a7\'abng \'ae\'b7 b\'b8o tin cho t\'abi r\'bbng: Ban s\'cf chi ti\'d2n \'aei \'ae\'ad\'eang cho t\'ab
i t\'edi Qu\'b6ng Ch\'a9u, nh\'adng khi \'ae\'d5n \'ae\'e3 th\'d7 t\'abi ph\'b6i t\'f9 xoay x\'eb t\'d7m l\'cay c\'abng vi\'d6c.
\par H\'bcn l\'b5 l\'b5m vi\'d6c \'ae\'d3 ki\'d5m s\'e8ng kh\'abng ph\'b6i l\'b5 \'aei\'d2u kh\'e3, th\'cbm ch\'dd ngay c\'b6 \'eb m\'e9t \'ae\'cat n\'ad\'edc m\'b5 t\'abi ch\'d8 bi\'d5t vi\'d5t ch\'f8 kh\'abng bi\'d5t n\'e3i th\'f8 ti\'d5ng \'eb \'ae\'e3
. Tuy nhi\'aan, trong tr\'ad\'eang h\'eep c\'f1a t\'abi, \'aei\'d2u \'ae\'e3 c\'f2ng c\'e3 nh\'f7ng c\'b8i b\'cat ti\'d6n:
\par 1/ T\'abi ph\'b6i s\'e8ng g\'c7n nh\'ad b\'cat h\'eep ph\'b8p \'eb Qu\'b6ng Ch\'a9u, n\'aci nhung nh\'f3c nh\'f7ng m\'cbt th\'b8m Ph\'b8p.
\par 2/ N\'d5u t\'abi nh\'cbn l\'b5m m\'e9t c\'abng vi\'d6c n\'b5o \'ae\'e3, th\'d7 to\'b5n b\'e9 th\'eai gi\'ea c\'f1a t\'abi s\'cf b\'de cho\'b8n h\'d5t. M\'b5 t\'abi th\'d7 ph\'b6i \'ae\'ad\'eec ho\'b5n to\'b5n t\'f9 do \'ae\'d3 l\'b5m vi\'d6c theo \'fd mu
\'e8n, t\'f8c l\'b5 nghi\'aan c\'f8u ho\'b5n c\'b6nh, xem x\'d0t qu\'c7n ch\'f3ng v\'b5 t\'e6 ch\'f8c c\'b8i g\'d7 \'ae\'e3.
\par B\'ebi v\'d7 \'a7\'b6ng ch\'f3ng t\'abi v\'b5 Ban ph\'ad\'acng \'a7\'abng kh\'abng th\'d3 gi\'f3p t\'abi v\'d2 t\'b5i ch\'ddnh, n\'aan t\'abi \'ae\'d2 ngh\'de \'ae\'e5ng ch\'dd tr\'d7nh b\'b5y tr\'ad\'eang h\'eep c\'f1a t\'abi tr\'ad\'edc Ban ch\'cap h
\'b5nh v\'b5 xin cho quy\'d5t \'ae\'denh.
\par Xin g\'f6i \'ae\'e5ng ch\'dd l\'eai ch\'b5o c\'e9ng s\'b6n anh em.
\par }\pard\plain \s24\qr \fi397\li0\ri567\sb200\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin567\lin0\itap0 \f38\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 \~NGUY\'d4N \'b8I QU\'e8C
