n ti\'d5ng \'a7\'f8c, s\'e8 114, ng\'b5y 29-8-1924, tr. 1484, vi\'d5t: "200 ng\'ad\'eai".}})}{\f37\fs20\expnd0\expndtw-4\insrsid1378858 ,... c\'e3 nhi\'d2u \'ae\'b5n b\'b5 v\'b5 tr\'ce em \'ae\'b7 tham d\'f9 v\'f4 thi\'aau... Sau khi ng\'ad\'eai da \'ae
en b\'de tr\'e3i tr\'ad\'edc ph\'b8p tr\'ad\'eang, ng\'ad\'eai ta li\'d2n \'ae\'e8t m\'e9t \'ae\'e8ng l\'f6a. C\'b8ch \'ae\'e3 m\'e9t qu\'b7ng, m\'e9t \'ae\'e8ng l\'f6a kh\'b8c c\'f2ng \'ae\'ad\'eec \'ae\'e8t l\'aan \'ae\'d3 nung m\'e9t thanh s\'be
t. Khi thanh s\'bet \'ae\'b7 \'ae\'e1 r\'f9c, m\'e9t ng\'ad\'eai c\'c7m l\'cay v\'b5 g\'dd v\'b5o ng\'ad\'eai da \'aeen. Ng\'ad\'eai n\'b5y ho\'b6ng l\'aan, v\'e9i n\'bem l\'cay thanh s\'bet. Th\'d5 l\'b5 kh\'abng kh\'dd s\'c6c s\'f4a m\'efi th\'det ch
\'b8y kh\'d0t... Thanh s\'bet \'ae\'e1 \'ae\'ad\'eec g\'dd v\'b5o nhi\'d2u n\'aci tr\'aan m\'d7nh ng\'ad\'eai da \'aeen, ti\'d5ng k\'aau la v\'b5 r\'aan r\'d8 c\'f1a ng\'ad\'eai \'ae\'e3 d\'e9i v\'b5o t\'cbn trong th\'b5nh ph\'e8. H\'b5nh t\'e9i m\'e9t h
\'e5i l\'a9u, nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai \'aeeo m\'c6t n\'b9 t\'ad\'edi x\'a8ng v\'b5o ng\'ad\'eai da \'aeen v\'b5 \'ae\'e8t \'ae\'e8ng c\'f1i l\'aan. Ng\'e4n l\'f6a b\'e8c cao v\'b5 li\'d5m quanh ng\'ad\'eai da \'aeen \'aeang van xin ng\'ad\'eai ta l\'b5m ph
\'f3c cho n\'e3 m\'e9t ph\'b8t \'ae\'b9n. Nh\'f7ng l\'eai n\'a8n n\'d8 c\'f1a n\'e3 l\'b5m cho ng\'ad\'eai ta l\'edn ti\'d5ng ch\'d5 nh\'b9o" - B\'b8o }{\i\f37\fs20\expnd0\expndtw-4\insrsid1378858 Chatanocca Times}{
\f37\fs20\expnd0\expndtw-4\insrsid1378858 , ng\'b5y 13 - 2 - 1918.
\par }{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 "M\'ad\'eai l\'a8m ng\'b5n ng\'ad\'eai v\'f5a \'ae\'b5n \'abng, \'ae\'b5n b\'b5 v\'b5 tr\'ce con h\'df reo nh\'ad s\'cam khi ng\'ad\'eai ta gi\'e9i gad\'ablin}{\cs17\f37\fs20\super\insrsid1378858 2{\footnote \pard\plain 
\s30\ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f42\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 2) }{\i\insrsid1378858 Gazoline.}{\insrsid1378858  X\'a8ng nh\'d1, c\'cat t\'f5 d\'c7u ho\'b6.}})}{
\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  l\'aan ng\'ad\'eai t\'aan da \'aeen v\'b5 ch\'a9m l\'f6a. H\'e4 \'ae\'cam \'ae\'b8 nhau, la h\'d0t, v\'b5 x\'ab \'ae\'c8y nhau \'ae\'d3 \'ae\'ad\'eec \'ae\'f8ng g\'c7n t\'aan da \'aeen h\'acn. Hai ng\'ad\'eai trong b\'e4n h\'e4 c
\'bet tai t\'aan da \'aeen trong khi ng\'e4n l\'f6a b\'bet \'ae\'c7u thui n\'e3.
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 M\'e9t ng\'ad\'eai kh\'b8c \'ae\'denh c\'bet g\'e3t t\'aan da \'aeen... \'a7\'b8m \'ae\'abng nh\'cap nh\'ab v\'b5
 di chuy\'d3n \'ae\'d3 ai n\'cay \'ae\'d2u \'ae\'ad\'eec nh\'d7n th\'cay t\'aan da \'aeen b\'de \'ae\'e8t ch\'b8y. Khi th\'det b\'de ch\'b8y h\'d5t, c\'dfn tr\'ac x\'ad\'acng ra v\'b5 khi c\'b8i th\'a9n h\'d7nh tr\'ad\'edc kia ch\'d8 c\'dfn l\'b5 m\'e9t c
\'b8i x\'b8c r\'b8ch n\'b8t b\'e8c kh\'e3i, kh\'abng ra h\'d7nh th\'ef g\'d7 n\'f7a, ch\'cbp ch\'ean trong ng\'e4n l\'f6a, m\'e4i ng\'ad\'eai c\'f2ng v\'c9n c\'dfn m\'aa m\'b6i \'ae\'f8ng xem..." - B\'b8o }{\i\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Mymphis Press}{
\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 , ng\'b5y 22-5-1917.
\par "... \'ae\'b5n \'abng thu\'e9c \'ae\'f1 m\'e4i h\'b9ng, \'ae\'b5n b\'b5, tr\'ce con \'ae\'d2u k\'d0o \'ae\'d5n xem. Nhi\'d2u b\'b5 trong gi\'edi th\'ad\'eeng l\'adu \'aei theo \'ae\'b8m \'ae\'abng t\'f5 c\'f6a nh\'b5 t\'ef \'ae\'d5n \'ae\'cay, nh\'f7ng b
\'b5 kh\'b8c c\'f2ng t\'f5 c\'b8c ng\'b6 g\'c7n \'ae\'cay k\'d0o \'ae\'d5n... Khi x\'b8c t\'aan da \'aeen r\'aci xu\'e8ng, ng\'ad\'eai ta h\'a8ng h\'b8i tranh nhau nh\'f7ng m\'c8u d\'a9y th\'f5ng" - B\'b8o }{\i\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 
Vicksburg Evening Post,}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  ng\'b5y 4-5-1919.
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 "... m\'e9t ng\'ad\'eai c\'bet tai n\'e3, m\'e9t ng\'ad\'ea
i kh\'b8c x\'ceo b\'e9 ph\'cbn sinh d\'f4c c\'f1a n\'e3... N\'e3 t\'d7m c\'b8ch b\'b8m l\'cay d\'a9y th\'f5ng, ng\'ad\'eai ta li\'d2n ch\'c6t ph\'a8ng c\'b8c ng\'e3n tay \'aei. Trong khi ng\'ad\'eai ta treo n\'e3 l\'aan c\'a9y, m\'e9t g\'b7 to nh\'ad h
\'e9 ph\'b8p l\'cay dao ch\'d0m v\'b5o c\'e6 n\'e3: \'ddt nh\'cat n\'e3 c\'f2ng b\'de t\'edi 25 v\'d5t th\'ad\'acng... N\'e3 b\'de k\'d0o l\'aan r\'e5i h\'b9 xu\'e8ng \'ae\'b8m l\'f6a h\'e5ng, r\'e5i l\'b9i b\'de k\'d0o l\'aan v\'b5 h\'b9 xu\'e8ng, c\'f8
 th\'d5 m\'b7i... Cu\'e8i c\'efng, m\'e9t ng\'ad\'eai n\'d0m d\'a9y th\'dfng l\'e4ng tr\'dfng v\'b5o ng\'ad\'eai n\'e3, \'ae\'c7u kia th\'d7 bu\'e9c v\'b5o m\'e9t con ng\'f9a \'ae\'d3 l\'abi c\'b8i x\'b8c ch\'b9y kh\'bep c\'b8c ph\'e8 Oac\'ab. C\'b8i c
\'a9y treo x\'b8c t\'aan da \'aeen l\'b9i \'eb ngay d\'ad\'edi c\'f6a s\'e6 nh\'b5 vi\'aan th\'de tr\'ad\'ebng. \'a4ng n\'b5y th\'b6n nhi\'aan nh\'d7n \'ae\'b8m \'ae\'abng h\'b5nh h\'d7nh. Tr\'aan su\'e8t ch\'c6ng \'ae\'ad\'eang, t\'cat c\'b6 m\'e4i ng
\'ad\'eai \'ae\'d2u tham gia b\'a8m v\'bbm t\'aan da \'aeen. Nhi\'d2u ng\'ad\'eai \'ae\'cbp n\'e3 b\'bbng x\'ceng, cu\'e8c, g\'b9ch, g\'cby g\'e9c. Kh\'bep m\'d7nh n\'e3, t\'f5 \'ae\'c7u \'ae\'d5n ch\'a9n, ch\'e7 n\'b5o c\'f2ng \'ae\'c7y th\'ad\'acng t
\'ddch. H\'b5ng ngh\'d7n ng\'ad\'eai c\'efng reo vui vang d\'e9i, khi ng\'e4n l\'f6a \'ae\'ad\'eec ch\'a9m l\'aan... M\'e9t l\'f3c sau, c\'b8i x\'b8c \'ae\'ad\'eec k\'d0o l\'aan cao, \'ae\'d3 ai n\'cay \'ae\'d2u c\'e3 th\'d3 ng\'bem nh\'d7n \'ae\'ad\'ee
c, n\'aan ng\'ad\'eai ta v\'e7 tay nh\'ad s\'cam d\'cby..." - B\'b8o }{\i\insrsid1378858 Crisis}{\insrsid1378858 , th\'b8ng 7-1916.
\par }\pard\plain \s25\qj \li0\ri0\sb200\sa120\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f38\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 NH\'f7NG NG\'a6\'eaI DA TR\'beNG L\'b5 N\'b9N NH\'a2N C
\'f1A H\'b5NH H\'d7NH KI\'d3U LINS\'a5
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 Ch\'bcng c\'f8 g\'d7 ng\'ad\'eai da \'aeen m\'b5 c\'b6 nh
\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai da tr\'beng n\'b5o d\'b8m b\'aanh v\'f9c ng\'ad\'eai da \'aeen c\'f2ng b\'de \'ae\'e8i x\'f6 t\'b5n nh\'c9n, nh\'ad b\'b5 Hari\'d0t Bich\'ac Stao, t\'b8c gi\'b6 cu\'e8n "}{\i\insrsid1378858 C\'b8i l\'d2u c\'f1a ch\'f3 T\'abm}{
\insrsid1378858 " ch\'bcng h\'b9n. Eligi\'b8t L\'abvagi\'abi b\'de gi\'d5t. Gi\'abn Brao b\'de treo c\'e6, T\'abm\'b8t B\'ddts\'ac v\'b5 Xt\'aaphen Ph\'abxt\'ac b\'de ng\'ad\'eec \'ae\'b7i, b\'de \'ae\'b8nh \'ae\'cbp v\'b5 b\'de b\'e1 t\'ef. Trong nh\'b5
 t\'ef, Ph\'abxt\'ac \'ae\'b7 vi\'d5t nh\'ad sau: "Khi t\'abi nh\'d7n tay ch\'a9n t\'abi b\'de \'ae\'b8nh n\'b8t nh\'f5, t\'abi ngh\'dc r\'bbng, \'ae\'d3 giam gi\'f7 t\'abi, nh\'b5 t\'ef s\'cf ch\'bcng c\'dfn c\'c7n thi\'d5t bao l\'a9u n\'f7a... 15 th\'b8
ng v\'f5a qua, nh\'b5 t\'ef \'ae\'b7 4 l\'c7n m\'eb c\'f6a x\'b5lim \'ae\'e3n t\'abi, \'ae\'e5ng b\'b5o t\'abi \'ae\'b7 24 l\'c7n l\'abi t\'abi ra kh\'e1i nh\'b5 th\'ea c\'f1a h\'e4, h\'e4 \'ae\'b7 hai l\'c7n n\'d0m t\'abi t\'f5 t\'c7ng g\'b8c th\'f8
 hai xu\'e8ng, m\'e9t l\'c7n \'ae\'b8nh t\'abi \'ae\'d5n s\'f4n l\'adng, m\'e9t l\'c7n kh\'b8c h\'e4 \'ae\'denh c\'efm k\'d1p t\'abi, hai l\'c7n h\'e4 ph\'b9t ti\'d2n t\'abi. C\'e3 l\'c7n, 1 v\'b9n ng\'ad\'eai \'ae\'denh \'ae\'ada t\'abi ra h\'b5nh h\'d7
nh ki\'d3u Lins\'ac, v\'b5 t\'abi \'ae\'b7 b\'de \'ae\'b8nh b\'de th\'ad\'acng 20 ch\'e7, \'eb \'ae\'c7u, c\'b8nh tay, c\'e6...".
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Trong 30 n\'a8m, \'ae\'b7 c\'e3 708 ng\'ad\'eai da tr\'be
ng, trong \'ae\'e3 c\'e3 11 ph\'f4 n\'f7, b\'de h\'b5nh h\'d7nh ki\'d3u Lins\'ac, ng\'ad\'eai th\'d7 v\'d7 \'ae\'b7 t\'e6 ch\'f8c b\'b7i c\'abng, ng\'ad\'eai th\'d7 v\'d7 \'ae\'b7 \'ae\'e5ng t\'d7nh v\'edi cu\'e9c \'ae\'cau tranh c\'f1a ng\'ad\'eai da 
\'aeen.
\par H\'b5nh h\'d7nh ki\'d3u Lins\'ac th\'cbt \'ae\'b8ng chi\'d5m m\'e9t v\'de tr\'dd vinh d\'f9 trong b\'e9 s\'adu t\'cbp to\'b5n b\'e9 nh\'f7ng t\'e9i \'b8c c\'f1a n\'d2n "v\'a8n minh" M\'fc.
\par }\pard\plain \s24\qr \fi397\li0\ri567\sb360\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin567\lin0\itap0 \f38\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 \~NGUY\'d4N \'b8I QU\'e8C
\par }\pard\plain \s26\ql \li0\ri567\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin567\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 T\'cbp san }{\i\insrsid1378858 Inprekorr}{\insrsid1378858 , ti\'d5
ng Ph\'b8p,
\par s\'e8 59, n\'a8m 1924.
\par 
\par 
\par 
\par 
\par 
\par 
\par 
\par 
\par 
\par 
\par 
\par 
\par 
\par }\pard\plain \s21\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \b\f39\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 
\par }\pard\plain \s20\qc \li0\ri0\sb1560\sa440\sl-380\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \b\f38\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 GI\'b8O D\'f4C QU\'e8C D\'a2N
\par }\pard\plain \s25\qc \li0\ri0\sa120\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f38\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 "C\'b8I D\'b7 MAN" B\'a4NS\'acV\'ddCH
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-290\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Ch\'ddnh ph\'f1 X\'abvi\'d5t \'ae\'b7 cho th\'f9c hi\'d6
n ch\'ad\'acng tr\'d7nh sau \'ae\'a9y:
\par A) Gi\'b8o d\'f4c kh\'abng m\'cat ti\'d2n v\'b5 b\'bet bu\'e9c; gi\'b8o d\'f4c ph\'e6 th\'abng v\'b5 b\'b8ch khoa \'ae\'e8i v\'edi c\'b8c tr\'ce em nam n\'f7 cho \'ae\'d5n 17 tu\'e6i; t\'f5 17 tu\'e6i tr\'eb l\'aan th\'d7 gi\'b8o d\'f4c chuy\'aan m\'abn v
\'b5 chuy\'aan nghi\'d6p.
\par B) Nh\'b5 n\'ad\'edc ch\'deu ph\'dd t\'e6n cho t\'cat c\'b6 h\'e4c sinh v\'d2 \'a8n u\'e8ng, qu\'c7n \'b8o, gi\'c7y d\'d0p v\'b5 nh\'f7ng th\'f8 c\'c7n d\'efng cho h\'e4c sinh.
\par C) Thi\'d5t l\'cbp m\'e9t h\'d6 th\'e8ng c\'b8c tr\'ad\'eang m\'c9u gi\'b8o v\'b5 v\'ec l\'dfng, nh\'b5 gi\'f7 tr\'ce, v\'ad\'ean tr\'ce, nh\'b5 nu\'abi tr\'ce, v.v. nh\'bbm m\'f4c \'ae\'ddch c\'b6i thi\'d6n vi\'d6c gi\'b8o d\'f4c c\'f1a x\'b7 h\'e9i, gi
\'b6i ph\'e3ng ng\'ad\'eai ph\'f4 n\'f7.
\par D) Nh\'a9n d\'a9n lao \'ae\'e9ng t\'ddch c\'f9c tham gia vi\'d6c gi\'b8o d\'f4c qu\'e8c d\'a9n; ph\'b8t tri\'d3n c\'b8c "H\'e9i \'ae\'e5ng gi\'b8o d\'f4c qu\'e8c d\'a9n"; t\'cat c\'b6 nh\'f7ng c\'abng d\'a9n c\'e3 tr\'d7nh \'ae\'e9 gi\'b8o d\'f4c ph\'e6
 th\'abng, \'ae\'d2u thu\'e9c quy\'d2n s\'f6 d\'f4ng c\'f1a Nh\'b5 n\'ad\'edc, v.v..
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-290\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 E) Trong ng\'b5nh \'ae\'b9i h\'e4c, c\'b8c sinh vi\'aan ngh
\'cco v\'b5 nh\'cat l\'b5 c\'abng nh\'a9n v\'b5 n\'abng d\'a9n \'ae\'ad\'eec c\'cap h\'e4c b\'e6ng v\'b5 nh\'f7ng \'adu ti\'aan kh\'b8c \'ae\'d3 h\'e4 c\'e3 ph\'ad\'acng ti\'d6n v\'cbt ch\'cat theo h\'e4c ngay c\'b6 c\'b8c tr\'ad\'eang \'ae\'b9i h\'e4c.

\par }\pard\plain \s25\qc \li0\ri0\sb200\sa120\sl-290\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f38\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 "N\'d2N V\'a1N MINH" PH\'b8P
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-290\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'a7\'d3 truy\'d2n b\'b8 \'b8nh s\'b8ng t\'e8t l\'b5nh c
\'f1a n\'d2n v\'a8n minh cao qu\'fd v\'b5o c\'b8c n\'ad\'edc \'ae\'ad\'eec n\'ad\'edc m\'d1 b\'b6o h\'e9, n\'ad\'edc Ph\'b8p \'ae\'b7 \'ae\'ada l\'b9i cho 40.000.000 "ng\'ad\'eai Ph\'b8p h\'b6i ngo\'b9i" 8.007 tr\'ad\'eang h\'e4c. T\'abi kh\'abng n\'e3
i qu\'b8 \'ae\'a9u. D\'ad\'edi \'ae\'a9y l\'b5 con s\'e8 th\'e8ng k\'aa ch\'ddnh th\'f8c.
\par }\trowd \ts11\trleft0\trftsWidth1 \clvertalt\clbrdrt\brdrtbl \clbrdrl\brdrtbl \clbrdrb\brdrtbl \clbrdrr\brdrtbl \cltxlrtb\clftsWidth3\clwWidth2127\clshdrawnil \cellx2127\clvertalt\clbrdrt\brdrtbl \clbrdrl\brdrtbl \clbrdrb\brdrtbl \clbrdrr\brdrtbl 
