\f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 Trong x\'f8 Goa\'ae\'acl\'f3p, 10.000 tr\'ce em kh\'abng c\'e3 tr\'ad\'eang h\'e4c. T\'b9i Angi\'aari thu\'e9c Ph\'b8p, t\'f5 su\'e8t 94 n\'a8m nay, trong s\'e8 5.000.000 d\'a9
n ch\'d8 c\'e3 35.000 h\'e4c sinh l\'b5 \'ae\'ad\'eec h\'ad\'ebng th\'f4 m\'e9t n\'d2n gi\'b8o d\'f4c nh\'e1 gi\'e4t, c\'dfn 695.000 tr\'ce em b\'b6n x\'f8 th\'d7 ph\'b6i ch\'deu d\'e8t n\'b8t. T\'b9i Cao Mi\'aan: 60 tr\'ad\'eang cho 2.000.000 d\'a9n! T
\'b9i Nam K\'fa (thu\'e9c Ph\'b8p t\'f5 h\'acn n\'f6a th\'d5 k\'fb nay): trong s\'e8 2.500.000 ng\'ad\'eai d\'a9n, ch\'d8 c\'e3 51.000 h\'e4c sinh.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 May m\'ben thay, tuy ch\'f3ng ta thi\'d5u tr\'ad\'eang h
\'e4c, nh\'adng n\'ad\'edc Ph\'b8p \'ae\'b7 ban cho ch\'f3ng ta r\'cat nhi\'d2u nh\'b5 th\'e6, ti\'d6m h\'f3t thu\'e8c phi\'d6n v\'b5 ty r\'ad\'eeu.
\par }\pard\plain \s24\qr \fi397\li0\ri567\sb240\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin567\lin0\itap0 \f38\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 NGUY\'d4N \'b8I QU\'e8C
