i hi\'d5n ch\'ad\'acng c\'f1a giai c\'cap t\'ad s\'b6n Ph\'b8p l\'b5 c\'e3 t\'ddnh ch\'cat ph\'b8 ho\'b9i v\'b5 nguy hi\'d3m. 
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sb240\sa80\sl-276\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\i\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 H\'e9i Nh\'a9n quy\'d2n v\'b5 C\'abng d\'a9
n quy\'d2n}{\f37\fs20\super\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 55}{\i\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858  }{\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 (t\'f5 n\'a8m 1924...) \'ae\'b7 c\'e3 c\'b8i ch\'f1 tr\'ad\'acng kh\'ea d\'b9i l\'b5 cho ni\'aam y\'d5t t\'b9i c\'b8c tr\'ad\'eang h
\'e4c v\'b5 c\'abng s\'eb x\'f8 Mar\'e8c thu\'e9c Ph\'b8p b\'b6n Tuy\'aan ng\'abn Nh\'a9n quy\'d2n v\'b5 C\'abng d\'a9n quy\'d2n n\'a8m 1789. Th\'e8ng ch\'d5 Li\'abt\'a9y - ng\'ad\'eai c\'e3 tr\'e4ng tr\'b8ch gi\'f7 v\'f7ng Nh\'a9n quy\'d2n v\'b5 C\'ab
ng d\'a9n quy\'d2n t\'b9i Mar\'e8c, \'ae\'b7 c\'cam ng\'c6t vi\'d6c ni\'aam y\'d5t b\'b6n Tuy\'aan ng\'abn qu\'b8 nguy h\'b9i \'ae\'e3. Kh\'abng may cho ng\'ad\'eai Mar\'e8c v\'b5 may thay cho nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai Ph\'b8p c\'b8ch \'ae\'a9y 135 n\'a8m, l
\'b5 v\'de Th\'e8ng ch\'d5 vinh quang c\'f1a ch\'f3ng ta \'ae\'b7 sinh ra kho\'b6ng 75 hay 80 n\'a8m sau cu\'e9c \'ae\'b9i C\'b8ch m\'b9ng; ch\'f8 kh\'abng th\'d7... Nh\'adng th\'abi, kh\'abng \'ae\'efa n\'f7a, ch\'f3ng ta h\'b7y n\'e3i th\'bcng v\'b5o vi
\'d6c.
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-276\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 Trong b\'f8c th\'ad g\'f6i cho Th\'f1 t\'ad\'edng N\'e9i c\'b8c, Th\'e8ng ch\'d5 c\'bet ngh\'dca l\'d6nh c\'cam 
\'ae\'e3 nh\'ad sau:
\par }{\i\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 "Trong l\'f3c n\'b5y}{\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858  }{\i\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 v\'b5 trong nhi\'d2u n\'a8m v\'d2}{\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858  }{\i\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 sau n\'f7a, \'ae\'e8i}{
\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858  }{\i\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 v\'edi d\'a9n b\'b6n x\'f8, n\'ad\'edc Ph\'b8p c\'e3 m\'e9t nhi\'d6m v\'f4 tr\'ad\'edc nh\'cat ph\'b6i l\'b5m tr\'dfn l\'b5: d\'b9y cho h\'e4 bi\'d5t gi\'f7 b\'e6n ph\'cbn c\'f1a m\'d7
nh. Ch\'d8 khi n\'b5o h\'e4 hi\'d3u b\'e6n ph\'cbn c\'f1a h\'e4 th\'d7 m\'edi c\'e3 th\'d3 n\'e3i \'ae\'d5n vi\'d6c ban b\'e8}{\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858  }{\i\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 cho h\'e4 nh\'f7ng quy\'d2n l\'eei m\'b5 ho\'b5n c\'b6nh x
\'b7 h\'e9i v\'b5 tr\'d7nh \'ae\'e9}{\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858  }{\i\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 hi\'d3u bi\'d5t c\'f1a h\'e4 c\'e3 th\'d3 cho ph\'d0p h\'e4 \'ae\'ad\'eec h\'ad\'ebng.}{\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-268\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 "Trong l\'f3c n\'b5y, }{\i\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 kh\'abng th\'d3}{
\cs17\i\f37\fs20\super\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 *{\footnote \pard\plain \s28\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa60\sl-240\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {
\cs17\super\insrsid1378858 *}{\cgrid0\insrsid1378858  T\'abi g\'b9ch d\'ad\'edi - N.A.Q}}}{\f37\fs20\super\cgrid0\insrsid1378858  }{\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 \'ae\'ada ra cho nh\'f7ng k\'ce m\'b5 ch\'f3ng ta \'aeang b\'b6o h\'e9 c\'b8c quy\'d2n l
\'eei \'ae\'ad\'eec thi h\'b5nh \'eb Ph\'b8p cho c\'abng d\'a9n Ph\'b8p, }{\i\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 nh\'cat l\'b5 }{\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 \'aei\'d3m: "Nguy\'aan t\'bec ch\'f1 quy\'d2n l\'b5 \'eb trong qu\'e8c d\'a9n, v\'b5 lu\'cbt ph
\'b8p l\'b5 bi\'d3u hi\'d6n c\'f1a \'fd ch\'dd"...
\par "V\'cby ni\'aam y\'d5t nh\'f7ng nguy\'aan t\'bec \'ae\'e3 \'eb c\'b8c ch\'e7 c\'abng c\'e9ng l\'b5 r\'cat }{\i\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 nguy hi\'d3m.}{\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 
\par }{\f37\fs20\expnd0\expndtw4\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 "B\'cat \'ae\'bec d\'dc l\'bem, ta ch\'d8 c\'e3 th\'d3 l\'b5m tho\'b6 m\'b7n \'ae\'ad\'eec H\'e9i nh\'a9n quy\'d2n trong nh\'f7ng tr\'f4 s\'eb }{\i\f37\fs20\expnd0\expndtw4\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 ch\'d8 ri
\'aang }{\f37\fs20\expnd0\expndtw4\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 c\'e3 ng\'ad\'eai Ph\'b8p lui t\'edi m\'b5 th\'abi; nh\'adng tr\'aan th\'f9c t\'d5, \'eb Mar\'e8c hi\'d6n kh\'abng c\'e3 nh\'f7ng tr\'f4 s\'eb nh\'ad th\'d5 v.v.".
\par }{\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 M\'c6c cho Li\'abt\'a9y c\'f8 vi\'d6c coi b\'b6n Tuy\'aan ng\'abn... \'ae\'b7 \'ae\'ada l\'b9i s\'f9 t\'f9 h\'b5o cho n\'d2n C\'e9ng ho\'b5 c\'f1a \'abng ta v\'b5 vinh d\'f9 cho cha \'abng c\'f1a \'abng ta, nh\'ad m\'e9
t m\'b6nh gi\'cay l\'e9n t\'e5i t\'b5n; m\'c6c cho \'abng ta c\'f8 vi\'d6c ng\'b9o ngh\'d4 khinh th\'ad\'eang m\'e9t t\'e6 ch\'f8c c\'e3 ti\'d5ng t\'a8m c\'f1a n\'d2n d\'a9n ch\'f1 t\'ad s\'b6n v\'b5 c\'f1a nh\'f7ng nguy\'aan l\'fd l\'edn th\'eai C\'b8
ch m\'b9ng 1789-1793, ch\'f3ng ta c\'f2ng c\'e3c c...\'c7n v\'b5 ng\'ad\'eai Mar\'e8c c\'f2ng v\'cby. Nh\'adng ch\'f3ng ta ph\'b6i nh\'bec l\'b9i cho nh\'f7ng anh em x\'f8 Mar\'e8c ch\'f3ng ta \'aei\'d2u n\'b5y: 
\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-268\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 Trong cu\'e9c chi\'d5n tranh v\'d7 "c\'abng l\'fd
" - kh\'abng ph\'b6i c\'abng l\'fd cho Con ng\'ad\'eai v\'b5 cho C\'abng d\'a9n, m\'b5 c\'abng l\'fd cho b\'e4n Di\'d2u h\'a9u v\'b5 C\'b8 m\'cbp - th\'d7 trong s\'e8 53.000 ng\'ad\'eai Mar\'e8c \'ae\'b7 l\'b5m "b\'e6n ph\'cbn c\'f1a h\'e4" (40.000 ng\'ad
\'eai l\'b5m lao \'ae\'e9ng v\'b5 13.000 l\'b5m l\'ddnh), c\'e3 10.000 \'ae\'b7 l\'b5m tr\'dfn b\'e6n ph\'cbn m\'d7nh \'ae\'d5n n\'e7i \'ae\'b7 b\'e1 x\'ad\'acng tr\'aan c\'b8c b\'b7i chi\'d5n tr\'ad\'eang. C\'e3 nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai Mar\'e8c kh\'b8c c
\'f2ng \'ae\'b7 l\'b5m "b\'e6n ph\'cbn" m\'d7nh b\'bbng c\'b8ch cung c\'cap cho n\'ad\'edc m\'d1 \'aeang l\'a9m chi\'d5n h\'b5ng v\'b9n t\'can h\'b5ng ho\'b8, h\'b5ng tr\'a8m tri\'d6u phr\'a8ng trong c\'b8c cu\'e9c c\'abng tr\'b8i b\'bet bu\'e9c, \'ae\'ad
\'eec g\'e4i l\'b5 c\'abng tr\'b8i "Chi\'d5n th\'beng" v\'b5 cho c\'b8c cu\'e9c l\'b9c quy\'aan b\'bet bu\'e9c, \'ae\'d3 gi\'f3p c\'b8c v\'efng b\'de qu\'a9n "b\'abs\'ac d\'b7 man" x\'a9m chi\'d5m, \'ae\'b7 l\'b5m trong th\'eai k\'fa 1914-1918 \'ae\'f3
ng nh\'f7ng \'aei\'d2u m\'b5 nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai Ph\'b8p v\'a8n minh \'ae\'b7 l\'b5m c\'b8ch \'ae\'a9y 20 n\'a8m \'eb Mar\'e8c v\'b5 hi\'d6n \'aeang l\'b5m h\'bbng ng\'b5y \'eb \'ae\'e3. \'a7\'d3 \'ae\'d2n \'ae\'b8p l\'b9i nh\'f7ng bom \'ae\'b9n v\'b5 nh
\'f7ng c\'abng \'acn c\'f1a N\'ad\'edc b\'b6o h\'e9, n\'abng d\'a9n Mar\'e8c trong kho\'b6ng m\'ad\'eai l\'a8m n\'a8m \'ae\'b7 ph\'b6i "nh\'ad\'eang l\'b9i" h\'b5ng ch\'f4c v\'b9n h\'d0cta ru\'e9ng \'ae\'cat t\'e8t nh\'cat c\'f1a m\'d7nh, c\'dfn m\'d7nh t
h\'d7 l\'aan n\'f3i v\'b5 nh\'f7ng cao nguy\'aan tr\'ac tr\'f4i \'ae\'d3 ch\'d5t \'ae\'e3i. V\'d7 n\'d2n "th\'b8i b\'d7nh c\'f1a n\'ad\'edc Ph\'b8p", h\'e4 \'ae\'b7 ph\'b6i \'ae\'e3ng s\'adu thu\'d5 n\'c6ng n\'d2 c\'f8 h\'bbng n\'a8m l\'b9i t\'a8ng l\'aa
n. Thu\'d5 m\'b8 t\'f5 ch\'e7 109.499.000 phr\'a8ng h\'e5i n\'a8m 1918, n\'a8m 1922 \'ae\'b7 l\'aan t\'edi 171.953.000. Trong s\'e8 m\'cay tr\'a8m tri\'d6u thu\'d5 do ng\'ad\'eai Mar\'e8c \'ae\'b7 \'ae\'e6 m\'e5 h\'abi ra \'ae\'e3ng \'ae\'e3, th\'d7
 96.000.000, ngh\'dca l\'b5 m\'e9t ph\'c7n ba, d\'efng \'ae\'d3 nu\'abi b\'d0o nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai nh\'ad Li\'abt\'a9y v\'b5 \'ae\'e5ng b\'e4n (ch\'d8 ri\'aang nh\'f7ng kho\'b6n chi ph\'dd cho Ph\'f1 To\'b5n quy\'d2n c\'f2ng \'ae\'b7 l\'aan t\'ed
i 25.000.000 phr\'a8ng).
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 Th\'d5 l\'b5 ng\'ad\'eai Mar\'e8c \'ae\'b7 l\'b5
m tr\'dfn "b\'e6n ph\'cbn" c\'f1a m\'d7nh, b\'e6n ph\'cbn ng\'ad\'eai n\'ab l\'d6. Nh\'adng \'ae\'d3 x\'f8ng \'ae\'b8ng v\'edi quy\'d2n Con ng\'ad\'eai v\'b5 quy\'d2n C\'abng d\'a9n, h\'e4 c\'dfn ph\'b6i l\'b5m b\'e6n ph\'cbn c\'f1a h\'e4 l\'b5 nh\'f7
ng Con ng\'ad\'eai v\'b5 nh\'f7ng C\'abng d\'a9n n\'f7a, ngh\'dca l\'b5 ph\'b6i t\'e6 ch\'f8c nhau l\'b9i v\'b5 \'ae\'cau tranh \'ae\'d3 gi\'b5nh l\'cay c\'b8c quy\'d2n \'ae\'e3, nh\'ad ng\'ad\'eai Ph\'b8p t\'f5ng l\'b5m h\'e5i 1789}{
\f37\fs20\super\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 56}{\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858  v\'b5 nh\'ad giai c\'cap v\'ab s\'b6n c\'b8ch m\'b9ng ng\'b5y nay \'aeang l\'b5m. B\'e6n ph\'cbn \'ae\'e3, nh\'f7ng anh em ch\'f3ng ta \'eb Mar\'e8c ch\'ada hi\'d3u. Cho n\'aan Li
\'abt\'a9y \'ae\'b7 c\'e3 l\'fd \'ae\'d3 cho r\'bbng r\'ad\'eeu c\'e5n, thu\'e8c phi\'d6n v\'b5 nh\'b5 th\'e6 (nh\'f7ng ti\'d6m r\'ad\'eeu v\'b5 nh\'b5 th\'e6 \'eb Mar\'e8c c\'f8 5 n\'a8m l\'b9i t\'a8ng 280%) c\'e3 gi\'b8 tr\'de "khai ho\'b8" nhi\'d2u h
\'acn v\'b5 c\'e3 \'ddch cho s\'f9 nghi\'d6p th\'f9c d\'a9n nhi\'d2u h\'acn l\'b5 b\'b6n Tuy\'aan ng\'abn Nh\'a9n quy\'d2n v\'b5 C\'abng d\'a9n quy\'d2n nh\'b9t nh\'cfo v\'cby.
\par }\pard\plain \s24\qr \fi397\li0\ri567\sb360\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin567\lin0\itap0 \f38\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 NGUY\'d4N \'b8I QU\'e8C 
\par }\pard\plain \s26\ql \li0\ri567\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin567\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 T\'cbp san }{\i\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 Inprekorr, }{
\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 ti\'d5ng Ph\'b8p,
\par s\'e8 71, ng\'b5y 17-10-1924.
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 
