\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-267\slmult0\nowidctlpar\tx7513\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 H\'e5i t\'abi \'ae\'d5n B\'bec K\'fa \'aei tr\'aan con t\'b5u c\'f1a m\'e9t nh\'b5 th\'b8m hi\'d3m c\'e3
 ti\'d5ng, c\'b8c anh c\'e3 bi\'d5t \'ae\'eai m\'e9t ng\'ad\'eai An Nam l\'f3c b\'cay gi\'ea \'ae\'b8ng gi\'b8 bao nhi\'aau kh\'abng? Kh\'abng \'ae\'b8ng m\'e9t \'ae\'e5ng trinh! Th\'cbt \'ae\'cay. T\'abi c\'dfn
\par }\pard\plain \s25\qj \li0\ri0\sa80\sl-267\slmult0\nowidctlpar\tx7513\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f38\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 nh\'ed nh\'ad th\'d5 n\'b5y: Ch\'f3ng t\'abi 
\'aeang \'aei ng\'ad\'eec d\'dfng s\'abng H\'e5ng, th\'d7 tr\'aan t\'b5u thu\'fb ng\'ad\'eai ta \'aeem r\'ad\'eeu \'ae\'b8nh cu\'e9c v\'edi nhau, xem ai ng\'e5i d\'ad\'edi t\'b5u b\'ben 10 ph\'b8t s\'f3ng tr\'ad\'eang m\'b5 "h\'b9" \'ae\'ad\'eec nhi\'d2
u ng\'ad\'eai An Nam nh\'cat \'eb tr\'aan b\'ea. M\'e9t v\'b5i ng\'ad\'eai kh\'b8c d\'efng s\'f3ng l\'f4c \'aei b\'bet ng\'ad\'eai v\'b5 b\'bet thuy\'d2n \'ae\'d3 \'ae\'dfi ti\'d2n chu\'e9c.
\par }\pard\plain \qc \li0\ri0\sb120\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\tx7513\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 *
\par }\pard \qc \li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\tx-2268\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 *    *
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-264\slmult0\nowidctlpar\tx7513\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 Ng\'ad\'eai ta s\'cf n\'e3i, \'ae\'e3 l\'b5 nh\'f7ng vi\'d6c \'ae\'b8ng ti\'d5c nh\'adng kh\'e3 tr\'b8
nh kh\'e1i trong nh\'f7ng cu\'e9c x\'a9m l\'ad\'eec v\'b5 chi\'d5n tranh. Th\'d5 c\'f2ng \'ae\'ad\'eec! Nh\'adng ng\'ad\'eai ta \'ae\'f5ng c\'e3 n\'e3i v\'edi ch\'f3ng t\'abi n\'f7a r\'bbng \'ae\'e3 l\'b5 vinh d\'f9, l\'b5 quy\'d2n h\'b9n c\'f1a chi\'d5
n tranh, v\'b5 c\'f2ng \'ae\'f5ng n\'e3i r\'bbng trong cu\'e9c t\'b5n s\'b8t h\'b5ng lo\'b9t n\'b5y, nh\'f7ng nh\'b5 qu\'a9n s\'f9 Ph\'b8p \'ae\'d2u t\'e1 ra h\'b5o hi\'d6p v\'b5 nh\'a9n \'ae\'b9o. \'a7o\'b9n v\'a8n sau \'ae\'a9y, tr\'ddch \'eb b\'f8c th
\'ad c\'f1a m\'e9t vi\'aan trung u\'fd tr\'ce tu\'e6i g\'f6i v\'d2 nh\'b5 ch\'f8ng t\'e1 nh\'f7ng t\'aan \'a8n th\'det ng\'ad\'eai \'cay th\'cbt v\'f5a nh\'a9n \'ae\'b9o l\'b9i v\'f5a h\'b5o hi\'d6p nh\'ad th\'d5 n\'b5o:
\par "Ch\'f3ng t\'abi t\'can c\'abng b\'e8n l\'c7n trong m\'e9t bu\'e6i nh\'adng l\'f3c n\'b5o c\'f2ng ch\'d8 th\'cay trong th\'b5nh c\'e3 v\'b5i t\'aan cu\'e5ng t\'ddn kh\'e8n kh\'e6 ch\'deu ch\'d5t m\'e9t c\'b8ch d\'f2ng c\'b6m, v\'b5 t\'abi c\'f2ng kh\'ab
ng c\'c7n n\'e3i th\'aam r\'bbng b\'cat c\'f8 t\'aan n\'b5o r\'aci v\'b5o tay ch\'f3ng ta, b\'de th\'ad\'acng hay kh\'abng, \'ae\'d2u b\'de \'aeem b\'ben t\'f8c kh\'bec t\'b9i ch\'e7".
\par V\'b5 trong m\'e9t \'aeo\'b9n kh\'b8c, b\'f8c th\'ad vi\'d5t: Tr\'aan m\'e9t con \'ae\'ad\'eang m\'dfn ch\'f3ng t\'abi g\'c6p m\'e9t ng\'ad\'eai da v\'b5ng tr\'aan vai g\'b8nh hai th\'f3ng l\'b9c. Khi ch\'f3ng t\'abi t\'edi anh ta kh\'abng b\'e1 ch\'b9
y. Ng\'ad\'eai ta b\'ccn gi\'f7 anh ta l\'b9i v\'b5 bu\'e6i chi\'d2u \'aeem ra b\'ben.
\par }\pard \qc \li0\ri0\sb120\sl-264\slmult0\nowidctlpar\tx7513\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 *
\par }\pard \qc \li0\ri0\sa80\sl-264\slmult0\nowidctlpar\tx7513\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 *    *
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-264\slmult0\nowidctlpar\tx7513\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 Chi\'d5n tranh k\'d5t th\'f3c, ng\'ad\'eai ta b\'bet \'ae\'c7u c\'abng vi\'d6c b\'d7nh \'ae\'denh. B\'e4
n qu\'a9n phi\'d6t Ph\'b8p hi\'d3u "b\'d7nh \'ae\'denh" nh\'ad th\'d5 n\'b5y \'ae\'a9y:
\par M\'e9t s\'dc quan tr\'ce tu\'e6i v\'f5a \'eb Ph\'b8p sang. M\'e9t h\'abm \'ae\'d5n m\'e9t l\'b5ng n\'e4, h\'ben th\'cay nh\'b5 c\'f6a v\'beng v\'ce, c\'dfn d\'a9n ch\'f3ng th\'d7 t\'f4 t\'cbp trong s\'a9n \'ae\'d7nh. H\'ben t\'ad\'ebng l\'b9c v\'b5o m\'e9
t \'e6 ph\'f4c k\'ddch n\'aan r\'f3t s\'f3ng b\'ben x\'b6 v\'b5o \'ae\'b8m ng\'ad\'eai v\'ab t\'e9i. Th\'cbt ra th\'d7 h\'e4 \'aeang l\'b5m l\'d4 t\'d5 th\'c7n. Th\'cay b\'de b\'ben, h\'e4 h\'e8t ho\'b6ng ch\'b9y t\'b8n lo\'b9n. T\'aan s\'dc quan v\'f5a 
\'aeu\'e6i, v\'f5a t\'b5n s\'b8t.
\par }\pard \qc \li0\ri0\sb120\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\tx7513\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 *
\par }\pard \qc \li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\tx7513\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 *    *
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-290\slmult0\nowidctlpar\tx7513\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 T\'abi ph\'b6i nh\'bec \'ae\'d3 c\'b8c b\'b9n nh\'ed r\'bbng t\'cat c\'b6 nh\'f7ng c\'a9u chuy\'d6n n\'b5
y, c\'f2ng nh\'ad nh\'f7ng chuy\'d6n t\'abi s\'cf k\'d3 th\'aam, \'ae\'d2u do ng\'ad\'eai Ph\'b8p \'ae\'b7 m\'bet th\'cay tai nghe, vi\'d5t ra. Khi h\'e4 vi\'d5t, c\'e3 l\'cf h\'e4 kh\'abng ngh\'dc r\'bbng, m\'e9t ng\'b5y kia s\'cf c\'e3 m\'e9t ng\'ad\'ea
i An Nam \'ae\'e4c nh\'f7ng chuy\'d6n \'ae\'e3; n\'d5u bi\'d5t r\'bbng t\'abi \'ae\'b7 s\'f6 d\'f4ng nh\'f7ng t\'b5i li\'d6u h\'e4 vi\'d5t, ch\'bec ch\'ben l\'b5 nh\'f7ng nh\'b5 v\'a8n \'ae\'e3 s\'cf h\'e8i h\'cbn v\'d7 \'ae\'b7 n\'e3i h\'d5t s\'f9 th\'cb
t. N\'e3i r\'e2 nh\'ad v\'cby r\'e5i, t\'abi xin ti\'d5p t\'f4c: M\'e9t \'ae\'b9i \'ae\'e9i h\'b6i qu\'a9n \'ae\'d5n V\'dcnh Long (Nam K\'fa). Vi\'aan quan t\'d8nh \'ae\'ada l\'ddnh t\'cbp \'aei \'ae\'e3n kh\'b8ch th\'cbt long tr\'e4ng. T\'aan ch\'d8 huy 
\'ae\'e9i tu\'c7n ti\'d4u ra l\'d6nh b\'ben v\'b5o nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai \'aei \'ae\'e3n h\'e4 v\'b5 gi\'d5t ch\'d5t m\'cat nhi\'d2u ng\'ad\'eai m\'e9t c\'b8ch th\'cbt v\'ce vang.
\par }\pard \qc \li0\ri0\sb120\sl-290\slmult0\nowidctlpar\tx7513\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 *
\par }\pard \qc \li0\ri0\sa80\sl-290\slmult0\nowidctlpar\tx7513\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 *    *
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-290\slmult0\nowidctlpar\tx7513\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 Kh\'abng th\'d3 tr\'f5 \'ae\'ad\'eec m\'e9t ng\'ad\'eai phi\'d5n lo\'b9n, ng\'ad\'eai ta b\'ccn \'ae\'e8
t v\'b5 tri\'d6t h\'b9 l\'b5ng m\'b9c, ng\'ad\'eai ta ph\'b8 ho\'b9i c\'b6 nh\'f7ng v\'efng l\'a9n c\'cbn kh\'b8c.
\par }\pard \qc \li0\ri0\sb120\sl-290\slmult0\nowidctlpar\tx7513\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 *
\par }\pard \qc \li0\ri0\sa80\sl-290\slmult0\nowidctlpar\tx7513\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 *    *
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-290\slmult0\nowidctlpar\tx7513\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 Ng\'ad\'eai ta l\'b5m \'ae\'f1 c\'b8ch \'ae\'ada kh\'dd gi\'edi cho ng\'ad\'eai An Nam ch\'d0m gi\'d5t l
\'c9n nhau v\'b5 xui gi\'f4c h\'e4 ph\'b6n b\'e9i nhau.
\par Ng\'ad\'eai ta b\'bet c\'b8c l\'b5ng ph\'b6i ch\'deu tr\'b8ch nhi\'d6m v\'d2 nh\'f7ng v\'f4 ph\'b8 r\'e8i tr\'de an x\'b6y ra trong \'ae\'dea h\'b9t c\'f1a m\'d7nh. Ng\'ad\'eai An Nam ph\'b6i d\'c9n \'ae\'ad\'eang cho qu\'a9n \'ae\'e9i v\'b5 b\'bet n\'e9
p nh\'f7ng k\'ce b\'b9o \'ae\'e9ng. N\'d5u ai kh\'abng tu\'a9n l\'d6nh th\'d7 ch\'f3ng cho l\'b5 c\'e3 t\'e9i. L\'b5ng n\'b5o \'ae\'d3 cho m\'e9t ng\'ad\'eai y\'aau n\'ad\'edc \'c8n n\'b8u th\'d7 b\'de k\'d5t \'b8n. Ph\'ad\'acng ph\'b8p duy nh\'cat \'ae
\'d3 truy t\'c7m th\'cbt l\'b5 \'ae\'acn gi\'b6n: ng\'ad\'eai ta tra h\'e1i l\'fd tr\'ad\'ebng v\'b5 h\'ad\'acng ch\'f8c, ai kh\'abng cung x\'adng li\'d2n b\'de b\'ben ngay. }{\i\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 Trong hai tu\'c7n l\'d4, m\'e9t t\'aan gi\'b8
m binh \'ae\'b7 gi\'d5t m\'cat 75}{\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858  }{\i\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 k\'fa h\'b5o.}{\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\tx7513\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 Kh\'abng khi n\'b5o ng\'ad\'eai ta ngh\'dc \'ae\'d5n ph\'a9n bi\'d6t nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai y\'aau n\'ad\'ed
c \'aeang chi\'d5n \'ae\'cau tuy\'d6t v\'e4ng v\'edi b\'e4n du \'ae\'b7ng c\'abn \'ae\'e5 \'eb th\'b5nh ph\'e8. \'a7\'d3 \'ae\'cbp tan s\'f9 kh\'b8ng c\'f9 c\'f1a nh\'a9n d\'a9n, ng\'ad\'eai ta kh\'abng c\'e3 c\'b8ch n\'b5o h\'acn l\'b5 giao c\'abng vi
\'d6c "b\'d7nh \'ae\'denh" cho nh\'f7ng t\'aan ph\'b6n b\'e9i \'ae\'b7 b\'b8n h\'d5t l\'ad\'acng t\'a9m v\'b5 t\'e6 ch\'f8c \'eb \'ae\'e5ng b\'bbng B\'bec K\'fa, B\'d7nh Thu\'cbn v\'b5 Ngh\'d6 - T\'dcnh nh\'f7ng cu\'e9c t\'b5n s\'b8t \'ae\'c9m m\'b8u, l
\'adu l\'b9i \'ae\'eai \'ae\'eai m\'e9t k\'fb ni\'d6m kinh kh\'f1ng trong k\'fd \'f8c m\'e4i ng\'ad\'eai.
\par }\pard \qc \li0\ri0\sb120\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\tx7513\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 *
\par }\pard \qc \li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\tx7513\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 *    *
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\tx7513\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 Kh\'abng ch\'d8 c\'e3 ng\'ad\'eai s\'e8ng m\'edi l\'b5 n\'b9n nh\'a9n c\'f1a ch\'d5 \'ae\'e9 th\'f9c d\'a9
n man r\'ee \'cay. Bi\'d5t ng\'ad\'eai An Nam r\'cat s\'efng b\'b8i t\'e6 ti\'aan, b\'e4n ng\'ad\'eai Ph\'b8p c\'dfn c\'e3 nh\'f7ng h\'b5nh \'ae\'e9ng \'ae\'e9c \'b8c \'ae\'e8i v\'edi c\'b6 ng\'ad\'eai ch\'d5t; ch\'f3ng gi\'b5y x\'d0o thi th\'d3 cha m\'d1
 ng\'ad\'eai ta \'ae\'d3 cho con c\'b8i ph\'b6i \'aeau x\'e3t, ho\'c6c h\'b5nh h\'b9 x\'b8c k\'ce th\'ef \'ae\'b7 b\'de thua v\'b5 \'ae\'b7 b\'de gi\'d5t ch\'d5t, \'ae\'d3 cho h\'b6 l\'dfng c\'a8m t\'f8c v\'b5 r\'f6a ti\'d5ng b\'cat l\'f9c kh\'abng \'ae
\'b8nh b\'b9i \'ae\'ad\'eec ng\'ad\'eai \'ae\'e3 khi h\'e4 c\'dfn s\'e8ng. Nh\'ad \'a7\'e9i V\'a8n l\'b5 m\'e9t ng\'ad\'eai y\'aau n\'ad\'edc \'ae\'b7 chi\'d5n \'ae\'cau nhi\'d2u n\'a8m tr\'eai, ch\'e8ng l\'b9i n\'d2n cai tr\'de Ph\'b8p, \'ae\'b7 b\'de ch
\'d0m \'eb H\'b5 N\'e9i, \'ae\'c7u \'aeem b\'aau \'eb B\'bec Ninh, x\'b8c n\'d0m xu\'e8ng s\'abng H\'e5ng.
\par T\'e8ng Duy T\'a9n sau m\'ad\'eai n\'a8m chi\'d5n \'ae\'cau tuy\'d6t v\'e4ng c\'f2ng b\'de b\'bet v\'b5 b\'de ch\'d0m. Thi th\'d3 c\'f1a \'abng b\'de \'aeem b\'aau \'eb ph\'e8.
\par Phan \'a7\'d7nh Ph\'efng, m\'e9t v\'de quan to v\'b5 l\'b5 m\'e9t nh\'b5 v\'a8n th\'a9n danh ti\'d5ng, ch\'e8ng Ph\'b8p m\'ad\'eai n\'a8m tr\'eai r\'e5i ch\'d5t trong r\'f5ng s\'a9u. \'a4ng ch\'d5t r\'e5i nh\'adng b\'e4n Ph\'b8p v\'c9n ch\'ada tha: ng\'ad
\'eai ta qu\'cbt m\'e9 \'abng l\'aan, \'ae\'e8t x\'b8c v\'b5 \'aeem tro v\'f8t \'aei. Ng\'ad\'eai ta b\'b8o th\'ef c\'b6 ng\'ad\'eai \'ae\'b7 n\'bbm y\'aan d\'ad\'edi m\'e9.
\par B\'cat l\'f9c kh\'abng \'ae\'b8nh n\'e6i \'abng \'a7\'d2 Th\'b8m, kh\'abng sao gi\'d5t \'ae\'ad\'eec \'abng b\'bbng thu\'e8c \'ae\'e9c c\'f2ng kh\'abng tr\'f5 \'ae\'ad\'eec \'abng b\'bbng c\'e8t m\'d7n, ng\'ad\'eai ta b\'ccn \'ae\'b5o m\'b6 cha m\'d1 \'ab
ng, \'aeem h\'b5i c\'e8t v\'f8t xu\'e8ng s\'abng.
\par Sau nh\'f7ng cu\'e9c bi\'d3u t\'d7nh \'eb mi\'d2n Nam Trung K\'fa, nhi\'d2u nh\'b5 v\'a8n th\'a9n \'ae\'b7 b\'de x\'f6 t\'f6 v\'b5 b\'de \'ae\'c7y bi\'d6t x\'f8. Trong s\'e8 \'ae\'e3 c\'e3 \'abng Ngh\'cc Tr\'c7n Qu\'fd C\'b8p, m\'e9t nh\'b5
 nho thanh cao ai c\'f2ng m\'d5n ph\'f4c. }{\f38\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 \'ab}{\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 ng C\'b8p b\'de b\'bet trong khi c\'dfn d\'b9y h\'e4c; kh\'abng x\'d0t h\'e1i g\'d7 c\'b6, ng\'ad\'eai ta \'aeem ch\'d0m \'abng hai m\'ad\'ac
i b\'e8n gi\'ea sau khi b\'de b\'bet. Ch\'ddnh ph\'f1 gi\'d5t ch\'d5t \'abng ch\'ada \'ae\'f1, c\'dfn h\'b5nh h\'b9 m\'b7i, kh\'abng ch\'deu giao tr\'b6 thi h\'b5i \'abng cho gia \'ae\'d7nh. 
\par }\pard \qc \li0\ri0\sb120\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\tx7513\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 *
\par }\pard \qc \li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\tx-2268\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 *    *
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sl-276\slmult0\nowidctlpar\tx7513\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 Khi h\'b5nh h\'d7nh nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai l\'ddnh kh\'e8 \'ae\'e1 \'eb H\'b5 N\'e9i}{
\f37\fs20\super\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 57}{\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 , Ch\'ddnh ph\'f1 cho b\'bet gi\'b6i cha m\'d1, v\'ee con h\'e4 \'ae\'d5n v\'b5 b\'bet h\'e4 m\'f4c k\'ddch cu\'e9c t\'b5n s\'b8t r\'efng r\'een nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai th\'a9n y\'aa
u ru\'e9t th\'det c\'f1a m\'d7nh. \'a7\'d3 g\'a9y m\'e9t \'can t\'ad\'eeng l\'a9u d\'b5i v\'b5 \'ae\'d3 "d\'b9y d\'a9n ch\'f3ng", ng\'ad\'eai ta l\'b5m l\'b9i c\'b8i vi\'d6c \'ae\'b7 l\'b5m \'eb Anh h\'e5i th\'d5 k\'fb th\'f8 XVIII t\'f8c l\'b5 x\'e3c 
\'ae\'c7u l\'a9u nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai Giac\'abbanh}{\cs17\f37\fs20\super\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 1{\footnote \pard\plain \s28\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa60\sl-240\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 
\f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 1) }{\i\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 Jacobits}{\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 , t\'aan g\'e4i nh\'f7ng th\'b5nh vi\'aan c\'f1a \'ae\'b6ng ch\'ddnh th\'e8ng Anh.}})}{
\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858  b\'b9i tr\'cbn l\'aan m\'f2i gi\'b8o r\'e5i \'aeem c\'bem d\'e4c ph\'e8 Xiti v\'b5 d\'e4c c\'c7u Lu\'a9n \'a7\'abn. }{\i\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 H\'b5ng tu\'c7n }{\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 l\'d4 }{
\i\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 ng\'ad\'eai ta c\'dfn th\'cay \'ae\'c7u l\'a9u nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai l\'ddnh, n\'b9n nh\'a9n c\'f1a n\'d2n v\'a8n minh Ph\'b8p, cau m\'b5y nh\'a8n m\'c6t tr\'aan c\'b8c c\'e4c tre tr\'aan c\'b8c \'ae\'ad\'eang ph\'e8 ch
\'ddnh \'eb H\'b5 N\'e9i.}{\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 
\par B\'a9y gi\'ea n\'ad\'edc An Nam \'ae\'b7 "\'ae\'ad\'eec b\'d7nh \'ae\'denh", ng\'ad\'eai ta ra s\'f8c s\'a8n b\'bet nh\'f7ng "t\'aan c\'ad\'edp" An Nam. Nh\'f7ng t\'aan c\'ad\'edp \'cay l\'b5 ai? M\'e9t vi\'aan s\'dc quan gi\'b6i th\'ddch:
\par C\'f2ng c\'e3 m\'e9t \'e3c t\'ad\'ebng t\'ad\'eeng nh\'ad nhau - \'abng ta n\'e3i - ng\'ad\'eai Anh xem nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai B\'abe quy\'d5t t\'a9m ch\'e8ng l\'b9i h\'e4 nh\'ad l\'b5 phi\'d5n lo\'b9n ngo\'b5i v\'dfng ph\'b8p lu\'cbt th\'d7 ng\'ad\'eai Ph
\'b8p ch\'f3ng ta c\'f2ng coi nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai An Nam y\'aau n\'ad\'edc nh\'ad k\'ce c\'ad\'edp.
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-276\slmult0\nowidctlpar\tx7513\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 M\'e9t ng\'ad\'eai Ph\'b8p kh\'b8c n\'e3i: B\'de c\'ad\'edp h\'d5t c\'f1a c\'b6i, d\'a9n ch\'f3ng nhi\'d2
u l\'b5ng \'ae\'b7 tr\'eb th\'b5nh "k\'ce c\'ad\'edp" t\'cat c\'b6; nh\'adng h\'e4 ch\'d8 l\'b5 nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai n\'e6i d\'cby ch\'e8ng s\'f9 c\'ad\'edp \'aeo\'b9t b\'cat c\'abng m\'b5 th\'abi.
\par T\'d7m ra nh\'f7ng t\'aan "c\'ad\'edp" \'cay kh\'abng ph\'b6i khi n\'b5o c\'f2ng d\'d4 d\'b5ng, b\'bet \'ae\'ad\'eec h\'e4 c\'b5ng kh\'e3 h\'acn. Nh\'f7ng vi\'aan ch\'f8c ph\'b8i \'aei l\'efng b\'bet h\'e4, \'ae\'b7 ch\'d0m gi\'d5t ng\'ad\'eai v\'ab t\'e9
i \'ae\'d3 kh\'e1i tr\'eb v\'d2 tay kh\'abng. \'a7\'a9y l\'b5 m\'e9t b\'bbng ch\'f8ng l\'cay c\'f1a m\'e9t ng\'ad\'eai Ph\'b8p m\'b5 t\'abi \'ae\'b7 tr\'ddch d\'c9n nhi\'d2u chuy\'d6n: 
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\tx7513\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 B\'b6y ng\'ad\'eai An Nam x\'cau s\'e8 \'aeang b\'aci m\'e9t chi\'d5c xu\'e5ng d\'b5i v\'b5 m\'e1ng manh. 
\'a7i xu\'abi d\'dfng n\'ad\'edc, l\'b9i c\'e3 b\'b6y tay ch\'cco, xu\'e5ng \'aei v\'efn v\'f4t nh\'ad m\'e9t chi\'d5c xu\'e5ng m\'b8y. Thuy\'d2n c\'f1a nh\'a9n vi\'aan nh\'b5 \'aeoan khu\'cat sau \'ae\'b8m c\'a9y \'ae\'ad\'edc, c\'e3 qu\'e8c k\'fa Ph\'b8
p ph\'cap ph\'edi sau l\'b8i, v\'f5a \'eb trong l\'b9ch b\'aci ra. M\'e9t thu\'fb th\'f1 g\'e4i xu\'e5ng d\'f5ng l\'b9i. Ng\'ad\'eai tr\'aan xu\'e5ng kh\'abng hi\'d3u c\'f8 vi\'d6c b\'aci \'aei. Thuy\'d2n nh\'b5 \'aeoan b\'aci kh\'abng k\'dep. T\'aan t
\'a9y \'aeoan c\'c7m l\'cay s\'f3ng b\'ben. H\'e4 b\'aci l\'b9i c\'b5ng nhanh. T\'aan \'aeoan b\'ben v\'b5o h\'e4. M\'e9t ng\'ad\'eai \'aeang ch\'cco th\'d0t l\'aan m\'e9t ti\'d5ng r\'e5i ng\'b7 g\'f4c xu\'e8ng. Xu\'e5ng d\'f5ng l\'b9i, c\'b8c b\'b9
n trong xu\'e5ng b\'ccn \'abm l\'cay ng\'ad\'eai ng\'b7. C\'e3 ti\'d5ng h\'ab to: D\'f5ng l\'b9i? H\'e4 nh\'b6y t\'edi n\'bem l\'cay tay ch\'cco v\'f3t \'aei. \'a7o\'b5ng! M\'e9t ng\'ad\'eai n\'f7a ng\'b7. M\'e9t \'ddt kh\'e3i bay l\'aan, m\'e9t ti\'d5ng 
th\'d0t. M\'e9t ng\'ad\'eai Ph\'b8p \'aei thuy\'d2n l\'b6ng v\'b6ng qua \'ae\'e3 nghe th\'cay b\'ccn l\'c8n ch\'ea "nh\'f7ng t\'aan c\'ad\'edp" \'eb m\'e9t ch\'e7 ngo\'c6t. \'a7o\'b5ng! \'a7o\'b5ng! \'a7o\'b5ng! Qu\'b6 l\'b5 m\'e9t tay s\'f3ng c\'f5
. Ba vi\'aan \'ae\'b9n, ba ng\'ad\'eai ng\'b7 theo. Chi\'d5c xu\'e5ng ch\'d8 c\'dfn hai ng\'ad\'eai b\'aci \'aei ch\'cbm ch\'b9p v\'b5 ch\'d7m l\'d8m trong con l\'b9ch.
\par M\'e9t vi\'aan ch\'f8c nh\'b5 \'aeoan kh\'b8c, \'aei v\'edi s\'b8u t\'aan l\'ddnh c\'e3 \'ae\'c7y \'ae\'f1 v\'f2 kh\'dd, b\'bet g\'c6p m\'e9t ng\'ad\'eai \'aeang tr\'e8n d\'ad\'edi ao. Anh n\'b5y d\'can m\'d7nh d\'ad\'edi b\'efn, th\'eb b\'bbng m\'e9t c
\'b8i \'e8ng, ng\'cbm v\'b5o mi\'d6ng; l\'b8 sen k\'d0o che k\'ddn m\'c6t n\'ad\'edc th\'cbt kh\'d0o l\'d0o. T\'aan \'aeoan b\'ccn ch\'c6t \'ae\'c7u "t\'aan c\'ad\'edp" \'aeem v\'d2 to\'b5 s\'f8. Th\'cbt ra anh ta ch\'d8 l\'b5 m\'e9t ng\'ad\'eai nh\'b5 qu
\'aa b\'d7nh th\'ad\'eang ph\'b6i \'c8n tr\'e8n v\'d7 qu\'b8 s\'ee h\'b7i th\'cay c\'e3 nhi\'d2u ng\'ad\'eai l\'b9 v\'b5o l\'b5ng, ai c\'f2ng m\'c6t m\'f2i hung t\'een, m\'d7nh \'aeeo \'ae\'c7y s\'f3ng l\'f4c, t\'f3i \'ae\'b9n v\'b5 l\'a8m l\'a8m m\'e9
t kh\'c8u s\'f3ng trong tay.
\par 
\par 
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 
\par }\pard\plain \s23\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\tx7513\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \b\f37\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 \column 
