i. Ng\'ad\'eai Ph\'b8p kh\'abng d\'b8m b\'e1 v\'b5o \'ae\'e3 m\'e9t s\'e8 v\'e8n l\'edn, v\'b5 h\'e4 ch\'d8 v\'ac v\'d0t nh\'f7ng c\'b8i g\'d7 d\'d4 v\'ac v\'d0t, nh\'ad m\'e9t k\'ce v\'e9i kho\'beng s\'b9ch nh\'f7ng c\'b8i g\'d7 ti\'d6n tay \'ae\'d3 chu
\'e5n \'aei cho nhanh.
\par N\'ad\'edc ch\'f3ng t\'abi c\'f2ng gi\'b5u n\'abng l\'a9m s\'b6n. S\'b6n ph\'c8m ch\'ddnh l\'b5 l\'f3a g\'b9o. H\'bbng n\'a8m, \'ae\'e5ng ru\'e9ng c\'f1a ch\'f3ng t\'abi s\'b6n xu\'cat \'ae\'ad\'eec h\'acn 6 tri\'d6u t\'can l\'f3a.
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa60\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\tx7513\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 N\'a8m 1923, ng\'ad\'eai ta \'ae\'b7 xu\'cat c\'b6ng:
