\par L\'cbp t\'f8c Ng\'b5i \'ae\'ad\'eec th\'a8ng ch\'f8c; Ng\'b5i \'ae\'ad\'eec khen th\'ad\'ebng n\'f7a.
\par }{\f37\fs20\expnd0\expndtw-4\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 \'a4ng \'a7\'ea C. kh\'bcng \'ae\'denh r\'bbng m\'e9t vi\'aan c\'abng s\'f8 kh\'b8c \'ae\'b7 \'ae\'ada \'abng xem m\'e9t b\'f8c th\'ad c\'f1a c\'cap tr\'aan, trong \'ae\'e3 n\'e3i: "S\'e8 r\'ad\'eeu ti
\'aau th\'f4 \'eb ph\'f1 X. t\'ddnh b\'d7nh qu\'a9n theo s\'e8 \'ae\'b7 \'ae\'denh cho d\'a9n, \'ae\'b7 t\'f4t xu\'e8ng k\'d0m m\'f8c Z r\'e5i. \'a4ng c\'e3 ngh\'dc r\'bbng c\'c7n ph\'b6i l\'b5m g\'ad\'acng cho c\'b8c n\'aci kh\'b8c hay}{
\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858  kh\'abng?".
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-274\slmult0\nowidctlpar\tx7513\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 Vi\'aan c\'abng s\'f8 b\'de khi\'d3n tr\'b8ch nh\'ad th\'d5 li\'d2n h\'e4p h\'b5o l\'fd l\'b9i, gi\'b6i th
\'ddch cho h\'e4 nghe l\'b5 s\'eb d\'dc h\'e4 ti\'aau th\'f4 \'ddt r\'ad\'eeu th\'d5 l\'b5 v\'d7 h\'e4 c\'e3 n\'cau r\'ad\'eeu l\'cbu. \'a7\'d3 \'ae\'ad\'eec y\'aan th\'a9n, c\'b8c l\'b5ng li\'d2n mua ngay \'ae\'f1 s\'e8 r\'ad\'eeu c\'f1a Nh\'b5 n\'ad\'ed
c m\'b5 c\'b8c ph\'dfng gi\'cay \'ae\'b7 quy \'ae\'denh cho h\'e4 t\'ddnh theo d\'a9n s\'e8.
\par Tuy kh\'abng ph\'b6i b\'bbng c\'b8ch h\'eep ph\'b8p, nh\'adng th\'f9c t\'d5 ng\'ad\'eai ta \'ae\'b7 quy \'ae\'denh cho m\'e7i ng\'ad\'eai d\'a9n b\'b6n x\'f8 h\'bbng n\'a8m ph\'b6i ti\'aau th\'f4 bao nhi\'aau r\'ad\'eeu, v\'b5 khi ng\'ad\'eai ta \'ae\'b7
 n\'e3i }{\f38\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 M\'e7I NG\'a6\'eaI D\'a2N B\'b6N X\'f8}{\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 , th\'d7 ch\'ed c\'e3 t\'ad\'ebng r\'bbng ng\'ad\'eai ta ch\'d8 t\'ddnh nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai l\'edn m\'b5 th\'abi, m\'b5 ng\'ad\'eai ta t\'dd
nh }{\f38\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 TO\'b5N B\'e9 D\'a2N S\'e8,}{\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858  t\'f5 ng\'ad\'eai gi\'b5, \'ae\'b5n b\'b5, tr\'ce em, \'ae\'d5n c\'b6 nh\'f7ng \'ae\'f8a c\'dfn \'aeang b\'f3 m\'d1; ng\'ad\'eai ta bu\'e9c h\'e4 h\'b5ng th
\'a9n thu\'e9c u\'e8ng thay cho nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai n\'b5y, m\'b5 u\'e8ng thay ch\'bcng nh\'f7ng m\'e9t l\'ddt m\'b5 \'ae\'d5n hai ba l\'ddt kia.
\par D\'a9n m\'e9t l\'b5ng thu\'e9c B\'bec K\'fa, v\'d7 b\'de \'aee do\'b9, bu\'e9c ph\'b6i u\'e8ng r\'ad\'eeu, \'ae\'b7 \'ae\'d5n k\'aau v\'edi quan c\'f1a h\'e4: "Ch\'f3ng t\'abi bi\'d5t l\'b5m th\'d5 n\'b5o? Ch\'f3ng t\'abi kh\'abng c\'e3 ti\'d2n \'ae\'d3 
\'a8n cho \'ae\'f1 no n\'f7a l\'b5...". Quan c\'f1a h\'e4 \'ae\'b8p: "Ch\'f3ng m\'b5y th\'ad\'eang \'a8n m\'e7i ng\'b5y ba b\'f7a; }{\i\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 ch\'f3ng m\'b5y ch\'d8 b\'edt \'aei m\'e9t b\'f7a, hay n\'d5u c\'c7n th\'d7 b\'edt \'ae
i m\'e9t}{\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858  }{\i\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 b\'f7a r\'ad\'eci, }{\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 l\'b5 c\'e3 th\'d3 mua r\'ad\'eeu c\'f1a Nh\'b5 n\'ad\'edc \'ae\'ad\'eec ch\'f8 g\'d7".
\par \'a7\'cay, \'abng Ph.\'ae\'ac Pr\'d0ts\'a8ngs\'aa n\'e3i chuy\'d6n tr\'ad\'edc ngh\'de vi\'d6n nh\'ad v\'cby \'ae\'cay.
\par Ng\'ad\'eai ta c\'e3 m\'e9t kho h\'d7nh ph\'b9t \'ae\'c7y \'ae\'f1 gh\'aa g\'edm \'ae\'d3 gi\'b8ng xu\'e8ng \'ae\'c7u nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai d\'a9n b\'b6n x\'f8 c\'f8ng \'ae\'c7u c\'f8ng c\'e6. C\'e3 nh\'f7ng kho\'b6n ph\'b9t ti\'d2n t\'f5 200 \'ae\'d5
n 3.000 \'ae\'e5ng. C\'e3 nh\'f7ng \'b8n ph\'b9t t\'ef l\'aan t\'edi ba n\'a8m. L\'b9i c\'dfn c\'e3 \'aei\'d2u lu\'cbt m\'edi m\'ce n\'b5y n\'f7a \'ae\'denh r\'bbng m\'e7i l\'c7n b\'de tuy\'aan \'b8n ph\'b9t ti\'d2n, th\'d7 ng\'ad\'eai b\'de ph\'b9t l\'b9
i ph\'b6i ch\'deu m\'e9t kho\'b6n b\'e5i th\'ad\'eang cho c\'abng ty r\'ad\'eeu b\'bbng s\'e8 ti\'d2n ph\'b9t!
\par Kh\'abng ph\'b6i l\'b5 quan to\'b5n quy\'d2n kh\'abng bi\'d5t r\'bbng ng\'ad\'eai An Nam ch\'bcng bao gi\'ea \'ae\'e3ng n\'e6i nh\'f7ng m\'e3n ti\'d2n to \'ae\'d5n th\'d5. Nh\'adng ng\'b5i v\'c9n mu\'e8n c\'f8 l\'b5m ti\'d2n cho k\'fa \'ae\'ad\'eec, n\'aa
n con ng\'ad\'eai kh\'abn ngoan kh\'d0o l\'d0o \'cay \'ae\'b7 d\'f9 ki\'d5n r\'bbng l\'b5ng x\'b7 c\'e3 th\'d3 ph\'b6i li\'aan \'ae\'edi ch\'deu tr\'b8ch nhi\'d6m v\'edi ng\'ad\'eai can ph\'b9m (\'aei\'d2u 4).
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\tx7513\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 B\'b9n c\'e3 th\'d3 b\'b6o: Mu\'e8n k\'d5t \'b8n c\'b6 l\'b5ng x\'b7, th\'d7 d\'ef sao c\'f2ng ph\'b6i x
\'b8c \'ae\'denh r\'bbng l\'b5ng x\'b7 \'cay c\'e3 \'ae\'e5ng l\'e2a \'ae\'b7 ch\'f8.
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-290\slmult0\nowidctlpar\tx7513\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 Kh\'abng \'ae\'a9u. V\'edi \'aei\'d2u 4 th\'d7 ch\'bcng c\'c7n ph\'b6i l\'b5 nh\'ad th\'d5. L\'b5ng n\'b5
o kh\'abng ki\'d5m c\'b8ch ng\'a8n gi\'f7 cho ng\'ad\'eai ta kh\'e1i ph\'b9m ph\'b8p, th\'d7 khi Nh\'b5 n\'ad\'edc b\'bet \'ae\'ad\'eec, l\'b5ng \'cay ph\'b6i ch\'deu tr\'b8ch nhi\'d6m v\'d2 kho\'b6n ti\'d2n ph\'b9t c\'f1a k\'ce ph\'b9m t\'e9i.
\par Th\'cbt l\'b5 qu\'fb qu\'b8i hi\'d3m \'ae\'e9c, v\'d7 ch\'d8 c\'c7n nh\'f7ng tay sai c\'f1a b\'e4n ch\'f1 tr\'adng thu\'d5, - ch\'f3ng n\'e3 \'ae\'ad\'eec thu\'aa ti\'d2n \'ae\'d3 ph\'b8t gi\'b8c ra cho \'ae\'ad\'eec th\'cbt nhi\'d2u v\'f4 ph\'b9m ph\'b8
p, - khai ra l\'b5 l\'b5ng \'ae\'e3 ch\'bcng l\'b5m g\'d7 \'ae\'d3 ng\'a8n ng\'f5a c\'b8c v\'f4 \'cay, th\'d5 l\'b5 \'ae\'f1 \'ae\'d3 bu\'e9c t\'e9i cho c\'b6 l\'b5ng r\'e5i.
\par Ti\'d5t 3 trong \'aei\'d2u lu\'cbt \'ae\'b7 quy \'ae\'denh c\'b8ch th\'f8c l\'cbp bi\'aan b\'b6n v\'d2 nh\'f7ng v\'f4 ph\'b9m ph\'b8p m\'b5 b\'e4n tay sai c\'f1a ch\'f1 tr\'adng thu\'d5 c\'e3 quy\'d2n l\'b5m.
\par Nh\'adng kho\'b6n n\'b5y c\'e3 tr\'eb ng\'b9i. V\'d7 nh\'f7ng t\'aan tay sai \'cay d\'e8t n\'b8t th\'ad}{\f37\fs20\expnd0\expndtw2\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 \'eang l\'b5m bi\'aan b\'b6n kh\'abng h\'eep l\'d6. Ng\'ad\'eai ta kh\'bec ph\'f4c kh\'e3 kh\'a8n \'ca
y b\'bbng c\'b8ch cho vi\'aan ch\'f8c nh\'b5 \'aeoan \'eb t\'d8nh l\'fe l\'b5m bi\'aan b\'b6n, c\'a8n c\'f8 tr\'aan b\'b8o c\'b8o c\'f1a b\'e4n tay sai c\'f1a ch\'f1 tr\'adng thu\'d5. B\'e4n n\'b5y b\'bet \'ae\'ad\'eec m\'e9t v\'f4 ph\'b9m ph\'b8p c\'b8
ch xa t\'d8nh l\'fe 15 hay 50 kil\'abm\'d0t, ch\'f3ng l\'b5m b\'b8o c\'b8o. M\'e9t nh\'a9n vi\'aan nh\'b5 \'aeoan, \'eb H\'b5 N\'e9i ch\'bcng h\'b9n, m\'bet kh\'abng \'ae\'ad\'eec ch\'f8ng ki\'d5n s\'f9 vi\'d6c x\'b6y ra, l\'cbp bi\'aan b\'b6n l\'b5m c
\'ac s\'eb cho vi\'d6c x\'f6 \'b8n. Th\'cbt kh\'e3 m\'b5 t\'ad\'ebng t\'ad\'eeng \'ae\'ad\'eec r\'bbng l\'b9i c\'e3 s\'f9 vi ph\'b9m t\'cat c\'b6 h\'d7nh lu\'cbt c\'f1a n\'ad\'edc Ph\'b8p, truy t\'e8 ng\'ad\'eai ta d\'f9a tr\'aan bi\'aan b\'b6n c\'f1a m
\'e9t nh\'a9n vi\'aan m\'bet kh\'abng \'ae\'ad\'eec ch\'f8ng ki\'d5n s\'f9 vi\'d6c v\'b5 ch\'bcng c\'e3 ch\'f3t tr\'b8ch nhi\'d6m g\'d7, ch\'bcng c\'e3 m\'e9t b\'b6o \'ae\'b6m g\'d7 v\'d2 m\'c6t ph\'b8p l\'fd cho b\'de c\'b8o.}{
\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 
\par Khi b\'de x\'d0t th\'cay l\'b5 ph\'b9m ph\'b8p, ng\'ad\'eai An Nam b\'de b\'bet v\'b5 gi\'b6i v\'d2 H\'b5 N\'e9i hay H\'b6i Ph\'dfng, nh\'f7ng th\'b5nh ph\'e8 c\'b8ch xa bi\'aan gi\'edi Trung Qu\'e8c t\'f5 200 \'ae\'d5n 250 kil\'abm\'d0t, \'ae\'d3 x\'d0t 
x\'f6 \'eb \'ae\'e3, ngh\'dca l\'b5 \'ae\'d3 b\'de k\'d5t \'b8n.
\par Kh\'abng c\'e3 t\'e6 ch\'f8c g\'d7 \'ae\'d3 ng\'ad\'eai b\'de c\'b8o c\'e3 th\'d3 t\'f9 b\'b5o ch\'f7a cho m\'d7nh c\'b6.
\par B\'b8o ch\'dd B\'bec K\'fa th\'ad\'eang thu\'cbt l\'b9i t\'d7nh c\'b6nh nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai kh\'e8n kh\'e6 \'cay - c\'e3 l\'f3c \'ae\'d5n tr\'a8m ng\'ad\'eai, - b\'de \'aei\'d6u \'aei l\'aan to\'b5 \'b8n H\'b5 N\'e9i hay H\'b6i Ph\'dfng v\'d7 ph\'b9m t
\'e9i bu\'abn l\'cbu (th\'ad\'eang m\'edi ch\'d8 b\'de t\'d7nh nghi bu\'abn l\'cbu). C\'e3 m\'e9t t\'ea b\'b8o vi\'d5t: "Ch\'f3ng t\'abi l\'cay l\'b5m ng\'b9c nhi\'aan - m\'b5 k\'d3 c\'f2ng \'ae\'b8ng ng\'b9c nhi\'aan th\'cbt khi th\'cay c\'b6nh binh gi
\'b6i v\'d2 H\'b5 N\'e9i hay H\'b6i Ph\'dfng, t\'f5ng \'aeo\'b5n d\'b5i \'abng gi\'b5, \'ae\'b5n b\'b5 }{\i\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 c\'e3 mang, }{\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 tr\'ce con, c\'f8 hai ng\'ad\'eai m\'e9t tr\'e3i v\'b5o v\'edi nhau, 
\'ae\'d3 tr\'b6 l\'eai v\'d2 t\'e9i vi ph\'b9m thu\'d5 th\'ad\'acng ch\'ddnh".
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-268\slmult0\nowidctlpar\tx7513\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 Nh\'adng th\'d5 c\'f2ng ch\'ada th\'cam v\'b5o \'ae\'a9u so v\'edi c\'b8c t\'d8nh, nh\'cat l\'b5 c\'b8c t
\'d8nh Trung K\'fa, \'eb \'ae\'a9y vi\'aan c\'abng s\'f8 k\'d5t \'b8n v\'b5 b\'e1 t\'ef h\'b5ng lo\'b9t, gi\'b5 c\'e3, tr\'ce c\'e3.
\par V\'b5 m\'e9t \'aeo\'b9n kh\'b8c n\'e3i: "Ng\'ad\'eai An Nam th\'f5a hi\'d3u r\'bbng ng\'ad\'eai Ph\'b8p l\'b5 nh\'f7ng k\'ce m\'b9nh h\'acn, nh\'adng kh\'abng ph\'b6i l\'b5 nh\'f7ng k\'ce c\'abng b\'bbng, \'ae\'b9o \'ae\'f8c h\'acn".
\par C\'f2ng t\'ea b\'b8o \'cay, trong m\'e9t s\'e8 kh\'b8c, n\'e3i m\'e9t c\'b8ch c\'b6m \'ae\'e9ng v\'b5 bu\'e5n r\'c7u v\'d2 nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai b\'b5 con th\'a9n thu\'e9c kh\'e6 n\'b7o, l\'cbt \'ae\'cbt theo sau \'ae\'b8m t\'ef nh\'ad sau:
\par "\'a4ng gi\'b5, \'ae\'b5n b\'b5, tr\'ce con, t\'cat c\'b6 \'ae\'b8m ng\'ad\'eai \'cay \'ae\'d2u b\'c8n th\'d8u, r\'b8ch r\'ad\'edi, m\'c6t h\'e8c h\'b8c, m\'bet \'ae\'e1 ng\'c7u v\'d7 \'aeang l\'aan c\'acn s\'e8t, tr\'ce con b\'de l\'abi theo v\'d7 b\'ad
\'edc kh\'abng k\'dep. T\'cat c\'b6 nh\'f7ng con ng\'ad\'eai \'ae\'b7 ki\'d6t s\'f8c \'cay, mang theo \'ae\'f1 m\'e4i th\'f8, n\'b5o n\'e3n, n\'b5o qu\'c7n \'b8o r\'b8ch, c\'acm n\'bem, th\'f8c \'a8n \'ae\'f1 th\'f8, \'ae\'d3 l\'d0n l\'f3t \'ae\'ad
a cho ng\'ad\'eai b\'de c\'b8o l\'b5 cha, l\'b5 ch\'e5ng, l\'b5 ng\'ad\'eai nu\'abi s\'e8ng gia \'ae\'d7nh, h\'c7u h\'d5t l\'b5 ch\'f1 gia \'ae\'d7nh".
\par \'a7au x\'e3t h\'acn n\'f7a l\'b5 th\'cay c\'b8c v\'f4 \'cay \'ae\'d2u b\'de x\'f6 b\'cat c\'abng v\'b5 k\'d5t \'b8n m\'e9t c\'b8ch t\'b5n nh\'c9n.
\par \'a4ng Combane, m\'b5 t\'abi \'ae\'b7 n\'e3i \'ae\'d5n \'eb tr\'aan, b\'b6o r\'bbng: Nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai n\'abng d\'a9n b\'de t\'d7nh nghi kh\'abng k\'d3 l\'b5 oan hay \'ae\'f3ng \'ae\'b7 n\'cau r\'ad\'eeu l\'cbu hay bu\'abn r\'ad\'eeu l\'cbu c\'e3 l\'cf
 ph\'b6i th\'ccm c\'b8i s\'e8 ph\'cbn nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai Nga b\'de c\'b6nh binh Nga ho\'b5ng l\'efng b\'bet v\'d7 b\'de cho l\'b5 nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai \'aei kh\'f1ng b\'e8. \'a4ng c\'dfn n\'e3i ti\'d5p:
\par B\'de x\'f3c ph\'b9m v\'d2 t\'ddn ng\'ad\'ecng v\'b5 quy\'d2n l\'eei, b\'de \'d0p ph\'b6i u\'e8ng m\'e9t th\'f8 r\'ad\'eeu kh\'e8n n\'b9n l\'b5m b\'bbng t\'cam g\'b9o m\'f4c, n\'d5u kh\'abng c\'b6 l\'b5ng b\'de kh\'f1ng b\'e8..., c\'dfn \'ae\'eei g\'d7 n
\'f7a m\'b5 ng\'ad\'eai ta kh\'abng n\'e6i d\'cby ch\'e8ng l\'b9i.
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\tx7513\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 D\'ef c\'e3 di\'d4n t\'b6 th\'d5 n\'b5o \'aei n\'f7a v\'c9n ch\'ada n\'e3i h\'d5t \'ae\'ad\'eec s\'f9 th
\'cbt m\'e9t nh\'b5 v\'a8n \'eb thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea, b\'a9y gi\'ea \'ae\'b7 l\'b9c h\'cbu, \'ae\'b7 ph\'b6i k\'aau l\'aan nh\'ad th\'d5. Ch\'ada c\'e3 bao gi\'ea \'eb m\'e9t th\'eai \'ae\'b9i n\'b5o, \'eb m\'e9t n\'ad\'edc n\'b5o, ng\'ad\'eai ta l\'b9
i vi ph\'b9m m\'e4i quy\'d2n l\'b5m ng\'ad\'eai m\'e9t c\'b8ch \'ae\'e9c \'b8c tr\'ac tr\'b8o \'ae\'d5n th\'d5.
\par V\'d2 v\'can \'ae\'d2 n\'b5y, \'abng M\'ddtximi, ngh\'de s\'dc v\'b5 c\'f9u b\'e9 tr\'ad\'ebng, \'ae\'b7 vi\'d5t: C\'abng ch\'f8c v\'b5 nh\'a9n vi\'aan nh\'b5 \'aeoan, khi \'aeu\'e6i theo ng\'ad\'eai bu\'abn l\'cbu, c\'e3 quy\'d2n \'aei qua c\'b6 \'ae\'ca
t \'aeai nh\'b5 t\'ad c\'f1a ng\'ad\'eai ta. M\'e9t bi\'aan b\'b6n, b\'bet \'ae\'c7u l\'cbp l\'f3c c\'dfn ban ng\'b5y, v\'c9n c\'e3 th\'d3 ti\'d5p t\'f4c l\'b5m ban \'ae\'aam \'eb ngay nh\'b5 ng\'ad\'eai b\'de c\'b8o, ngh\'dca l\'b5 b\'cat c\'f8 \'eb \'ae
\'a9u, b\'cat c\'f8 l\'f3c n\'b5o, ng\'b5y c\'f2ng nh\'ad \'ae\'aam, nh\'b5 \'aeoan mu\'e8n l\'b5m kh\'e6 ng\'ad\'eai An Nam c\'f2ng \'ae\'ad\'eec c\'b6.
\par Kh\'abng ph\'b6i ch\'d8 c\'e3 nh\'f7ng cu\'e9c kh\'b8m nh\'b5 th\'ad\'eang xuy\'aan m\'b5 c\'dfn c\'e3 nh\'f7ng cu\'e9c kh\'b8m x\'d0t th\'a9n th\'d3 ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8 \'eb b\'cat k\'fa ch\'e7 n\'b5o, b\'cat k\'fa l\'b5 nam hay n\'f7 n\'f7a. Nh\'a9
n nh\'f7ng cu\'e9c kh\'b8m x\'d0t th\'a9n th\'d3, ng\'ad\'eai ta \'ae\'b7 l\'b9m d\'f4ng gh\'aa g\'edm bi\'d5t ch\'f5ng n\'b5o! Nh\'a9n vi\'aan nh\'b5 \'aeoan v\'b5o nh\'b5 ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8, th\'cay c\'e3 \'ae\'b5n b\'b5 v\'b5 con g\'b8i, }{
\i\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 b\'bet h\'e4 l\'e9t h\'d5t qu\'c7n \'b8o tr\'ad\'edc m\'c6t ch\'f3ng, }{\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 v\'b5 khi h\'e4 \'ae\'b7 tr\'c7n tru\'e5ng nh\'ad nh\'e9ng th\'d7 ch\'f3ng gi\'eb tr\'df tinh ngh\'dech \'ae\'d5n n
\'e7i \'aeem c\'b6 con d\'cau nh\'b5 \'aeoan }{\i\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 \'ae\'e3ng l\'aan ng\'ad\'eai h\'e4!.}{\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 
\par \'a4ng \'a7\'ea C. k\'d3 chuy\'d6n r\'bbng \'abng \'ae\'b7 \'ae\'ad\'eec g\'c6p \'eb mi\'d2n B\'bec Trung K\'fa m\'e9t vi\'aan qu\'b6n \'aeoan say s\'ada nh\'ad \'aei\'aan cu\'e5ng v\'edi vi\'d6c \'ae\'b5n \'b8p nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai An Nam l\'cbu thu\'d5
. H\'ben n\'e3i v\'d2 c\'b8c cu\'e9c h\'b5nh tr\'d7nh x\'abng x\'b8o \'eb c\'b8c l\'b5ng m\'b9c v\'edi v\'ce th\'ddch th\'f3 v\'ab c\'efng m\'e4i r\'ee; ngh\'dc \'ae\'d5n l\'f3c \'aei bao v\'a9y c\'b8c t\'f3p l\'d2u tranh khi c\'dfn m\'ea s\'b8ng, h\'be
n l\'cay l\'b5m kho\'b8i tr\'b8. T\'cat c\'b6 l\'fd l\'cf c\'f1a h\'ben ch\'d8 c\'dfn l\'b5 c\'b8i d\'efi cui m\'b5 h\'ben vung l\'aan. Nh\'f7ng nh\'a9n vi\'aan nh\'ad th\'d5 ch\'bec h\'bcn ph\'b6i l\'b5m cho \'ae\'eai s\'e8ng c\'f1a nh\'a9n d\'a9n \'ae
\'ad\'eec \'cam \'aam l\'bem \'ae\'cay, nh\'cat l\'b5 l\'f3c ch\'f3ng v\'b5o nh\'b5 h\'e4 s\'f4c s\'b9o, \'ae\'b6o l\'e9n ng\'ad\'eec xu\'abi m\'e4i th\'f8 l\'aan, l\'f4c so\'b8t c\'b6 \'ae\'d5n b\'b5n th\'ea t\'e6 ti\'aan.
\par }{\f38\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 \'eb}{\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858  Ph\'b8p, ng\'ad\'eai ta ch\'d8 d\'efng nh\'f7ng bi\'d6n ph\'b8p th\'cbt ch\'ddnh \'ae\'b8ng v\'b5 th\'cbt \'abn ho\'b5 \'ae\'e8i v\'edi nh\'f7ng v\'f4 gian l\'cbu, v\'b5 d\'a9n c\'e3
 quy\'d2n n\'cau r\'ad\'eeu n\'d5u ch\'d8 d\'efng nh\'f7ng nguy\'aan li\'d6u do m\'d7nh s\'b6n xu\'cat l\'cay, \'cay th\'d5 m\'b5 c\'f2ng c\'e3 nhi\'d2u v\'f4 ph\'b6n \'ae\'e8i d\'f7 d\'e9i x\'b6y ra. }{\f38\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 \'eb }{
\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 b\'aan Ph\'b8p n\'d5u c\'f2ng \'b8p d\'f4ng m\'e9t ch\'ddnh s\'b8ch gi\'e8ng nh\'ad \'eb \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng th\'d7 nh\'cat \'ae\'denh kh\'abng tr\'b8nh kh\'e1i \'ae\'e6 m\'b8u. D\'a9n t\'e9c An Nam ph\'b6i l\'b5 nh\'c9
n nh\'f4c v\'b5 \'aei\'d2m t\'dcnh qu\'b8 \'ae\'b8ng m\'edi kh\'abng n\'e6i lo\'b9n.
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-268\slmult0\nowidctlpar\tx7513\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f38\fs20\expnd0\expndtw-2\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 \'eb}{\f37\fs20\expnd0\expndtw-2\cgrid0\insrsid1378858  kh\'bep c\'b8c n\'ad\'edc v\'a8
n minh, ng\'ad\'eai ta c\'cam d\'efng thu\'e8c phi\'d6n, th\'d5 m\'b5 \'eb \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng, nh\'b5 n\'ad\'edc l\'b9i n\'cau, chuy\'aan ch\'eb v\'b5 b\'b8n thu\'e8c phi\'d6n.
\par }{\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 Nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai th\'b5nh th\'b9o trong vi\'d6c n\'cau thu\'e8c phi\'d6n s\'e8ng, trong vi\'d6c ch\'d5 bi\'d5n nhi\'d2u l\'c7n, qu\'b6 quy\'d5t r\'bbng c\'abng ty tr\'adng th\'c7u thu\'e8c phi\'d6n \'ae\'b7 d\'efng n
\'ad\'edc l\'b7 thay cho r\'ad\'eeu c\'e5n tinh khi\'d5t, r\'bbng ng\'ad\'eai ta c\'f8 \'ae\'d3 nguy\'aan trong thu\'e8c phi\'d6n c\'b8c ch\'cat \'ae\'e9c \'ae\'b8ng l\'cf ph\'b6i l\'e4c ra, r\'bbng ng\'ad\'eai ta r\'bec c\'b6 v\'b5o thu\'e8c phi\'d6n m
\'e9t th\'f8 b\'f4i kim lo\'b9i \'ae\'c6c bi\'d6t l\'b5m cho n\'e3 n\'c6ng c\'a9n l\'aan.
\par B\'b5i x\'ddch thu\'e8c phi\'d6n v\'d2 ph\'ad\'acng di\'d6n v\'d6 sinh, nh\'adng ng\'ad\'eai Ph\'b8p l\'b9i h\'d5t s\'f8c l\'b5m cho vi\'d6c h\'f3t thu\'e8c \'cay lan tr\'b5n ra kh\'bep n\'aci \'ae\'d3 c\'abng qu\'fc \'ae\'ad\'eec th\'a8ng b\'bb
ng. Trong l\'f3c b\'b7o l\'f4t t\'b5n ph\'b8 \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng, gi\'f7a l\'f3c \'ae\'e3i k\'d0m, Nh\'b5 n\'ad\'edc ch\'d8 c\'e3 m\'e9t m\'f4c \'ae\'ddch: }{\i\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 b\'b8n m\'b9nh }{\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 th\'aam }{
\i\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 thu\'e8c phi\'d6n v\'b5 r\'ad\'eeu}{\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 . Ng\'ad\'eai ta \'ae\'b8nh gi\'b8 c\'b8c quan cai tr\'de kh\'abng ph\'b6i b\'bbng t\'b5i cai tr\'de kh\'abn kh\'d0o, m\'b5 b\'bbng vi\'d6c }{
\i\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 b\'dfn r\'f3t}{\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858  }{\i\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8... }{\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 \'a7\'e3 l\'b5 t\'cat c\'b6 c\'abng \'acn c\'f1a n\'d2n v\'a8n minh gi\'b6
 nh\'a9n gi\'b6 ngh\'dca, n\'e3 \'ae\'b7 \'ae\'c8y ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8 v\'b5o m\'e4i th\'f8 b\'aa tha c\'e3 l\'eei cho n\'e3, m\'b5 ng\'ad\'eai \'ae\'eai ai c\'f2ng ph\'d8 nh\'e6.
\par \'a7\'d3 k\'d5t lu\'cbn, t\'abi th\'cay c\'c7n ph\'b6i tr\'ddch d\'c9n b\'b6n th\'abng t\'ad c\'f1a \'abng Anbe Xar\'ab, khi \'abng l\'b5m to\'b5n quy\'d2n \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng, g\'f6i cho t\'cat c\'b6 c\'b8c vi\'aan c\'abng s\'f8 nh\'ad sau:
\par "K\'ddnh g\'f6i \'abng c\'abng s\'f8,
\par "T\'abi tr\'a9n tr\'e4ng y\'aau c\'c7u \'abng h\'d5t s\'f8c gi\'f3p \'ae\'ec Nha th\'ad\'acng ch\'ddnh }{\i\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 \'ae\'c6t th\'aam}{\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858  }{\i\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 \'ae\'b9i l\'fd thu\'e8c phi
\'d6n v\'b5 r\'ad\'eeu, }{\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 theo ch\'d8 th\'de c\'f1a \'abng t\'e6ng gi\'b8m \'ae\'e8c Nha th\'ad\'acng ch\'ddnh \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng. 
\par "\'a7\'d3 c\'abng vi\'d6c ti\'d5n h\'b5nh c\'e3 k\'d5t qu\'b6, t\'abi xin g\'f6i \'abng m\'e9t b\'b6n danh s\'b8ch nh\'f7ng \'ae\'b9i l\'fd c\'c7n \'ae\'c6t trong c\'b8c x\'b7 \'ae\'b7 k\'aa t\'aan; t\'edi nay ph\'c7n \'ae\'abng c\'b8c x\'b7 n\'b5y v\'c9
n ho\'b5n to\'b5n ch\'ada c\'e3 r\'ad\'eeu v\'b5 thu\'e8c phi\'d6n.
\par "Th\'abng qua c\'b8c quan v\'b5 c\'b8c x\'b7 tr\'ad\'ebng Cao Mi\'aan, \'abng c\'e3 th\'d3 d\'efng \'b6nh h\'ad\'ebng l\'edn c\'f1a \'abng \'ae\'d3 l\'b5m cho m\'e9t s\'e8 ti\'d3u th\'ad\'acng ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8 th\'cay r\'bbng bu\'abn th\'aam r\'ad
\'eeu v\'b5 thu\'e8c phi\'d6n l\'b5 r\'cat c\'e3 l\'eei.
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-272\slmult0\nowidctlpar\tx7513\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 "V\'d2 ph\'c7n ch\'f3ng t\'abi th\'d7 nh\'f7ng vi\'aan ch\'f8c l\'adu \'ae\'e9ng trong l\'f3c \'aei kinh l
\'fd c\'f2ng t\'d7m c\'b8ch \'ae\'c6t \'ae\'b9i l\'fd, tr\'f5 khi n\'d5u \'abng c\'abng s\'f8 mu\'e8n h\'e4 ch\'ea \'abng v\'cbn \'ae\'e9ng c\'b8c quan ch\'f8c \'ae\'dea ph\'ad\'acng tr\'ad\'edc \'ae\'b7, th\'d7 h\'e4 ph\'b6i ch\'ea. Trong tr\'ad\'eang h
\'eep \'cay, t\'abi xin \'abng vui l\'dfng b\'b8o c\'b8o cho t\'abi bi\'d5t.
\par "Ch\'f3ng ta ch\'d8 c\'e3 th\'d3 \'ae\'b9t \'ae\'ad\'eec k\'d5t qu\'b6 m\'fc m\'b7n, n\'d5u ch\'f3ng ta \'ae\'e5ng l\'dfng ph\'e8i h\'eep ch\'c6t ch\'cf v\'b5 li\'aan t\'f4c, v\'d7 l\'eei \'ddch t\'e8i \'aea c\'f1a c\'abng kh\'e8.
\par }\pard \qc \li1985\ri0\sb120\sa200\sl-300\slmult0\nowidctlpar\tx7513\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin1985\itap0 {\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 K\'fd t\'aan: Anbe Xar\'ab\line }{\i\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 To\'b5n quy\'d2n \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'ac
ng}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-272\slmult0\nowidctlpar\tx7513\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 N\'aan ch\'f3 \'fd r\'bbng l\'f3c \'ae\'e3, trong 1.000 l\'b5ng \'ae\'b7 c\'e3 1.500 \'ae\'b9i l\'fd r\'ad
\'eeu v\'b5 thu\'e8c phi\'d6n, m\'b5 tr\'ad\'eang h\'e4c th\'d7 v\'cen v\'d1n c\'e3 10 c\'b8i; m\'e7i n\'a8m, ng\'ad\'eai ta \'ae\'c7u \'ae\'e9c d\'a9n b\'b6n x\'f8, c\'b6 \'ae\'b5n b\'b5 l\'c9n tr\'ce con, b\'bbng 23 t\'edi 24 tri\'d6u l\'ddt r\'ad\'ee
u v\'b5 h\'acn 100.000 kil\'abgam thu\'e8c phi\'d6n! B\'b8n nh\'f7ng th\'f8 thu\'e8c \'ae\'e9c \'cay m\'e7i n\'a8m l\'eai g\'c7n 130 tri\'d6u phr\'a8ng.
\par C\'f2ng trong th\'eai k\'fa \'cay, ng\'ad\'eai ta ch\'d8 ti\'aau cho ng\'b5nh y t\'d5 kh\'abng \'ae\'c7y 400.000 phr\'a8ng v\'b5 ch\'d8 c\'e3 1 tri\'d6u phr\'a8ng cho ng\'b5nh gi\'b8o d\'f4c, ngh\'dca l\'b5 cho c\'abng vi\'d6c x\'b7 h\'e9i m\'e9t ph\'c7
n tr\'a8m s\'e8 thu nh\'cbp c\'f1a vi\'d6c \'ae\'c7u \'ae\'e9c, th\'d5 kh\'abng ph\'b6i l\'b5 m\'e9t ch\'d5 \'ae\'e9 k\'fa di\'d6u l\'bem sao!
\par Mu\'e8i l\'b5 v\'cbt ph\'c8m t\'e8i c\'c7n cho d\'a9n ch\'b5i l\'ad\'edi, th\'d5 m\'b5 d\'a9n An Nam \'ae\'b7 ph\'b6i \'ae\'c6c bi\'d6t x\'e3t xa v\'d7 mu\'e8i!
\par L\'f3c \'ae\'c7u thu\'d5 mu\'e8i ch\'d8 c\'e3 5 xu, r\'e5i \'ae\'d5n 3 h\'b5o, l\'aan d\'c7n \'ae\'d5n 5 h\'b5o, \'ae\'d5n 1 \'ae\'e5ng, r\'e5i \'ae\'d5n 1 \'ae\'e5ng s\'b8u. Trong v\'dfng kh\'abng \'ae\'c7y b\'b6y n\'a8m, thu\'d5 mu\'e8i \'ae\'b7 t\'a8
ng l\'aan g\'cap m\'ad\'eai l\'c7n. B\'a9y gi\'ea h\'e4 b\'bet ng\'ad\'eai l\'b5m mu\'e8i An Nam ph\'b6i cung c\'cap mu\'e8i cho Nh\'b5 n\'ad\'edc theo gi\'b8 17 xu m\'e9t t\'b9. Nh\'b5 n\'ad\'edc b\'b8n l\'b9i cho nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai ti\'aau th\'f4 b
\'b6n x\'f8 1 \'ae\'e5ng 7.
\par K\'d5t qu\'b6 cho An Nam l\'b5 ngh\'d2 \'ae\'b8nh c\'b8 b\'de ph\'b8 s\'b6n. Cho \'ae\'d5n nay \'eb nhi\'d2u n\'aci, d\'a9n \'ae\'b8nh c\'b8 v\'b5 d\'a9n l\'b5m mu\'e8i h\'eep t\'b8c v\'edi nhau th\'b5nh ph\'ad\'eang, nh\'ea \'ae\'e3 h\'e4 l\'b5m n\'ad
\'edc m\'bem kh\'abng c\'c7n ph\'b6i v\'e8n. Nh\'b5 n\'ad\'edc \'ae\'e9c quy\'d2n gi\'b6i t\'b8n nh\'f7ng ph\'ad\'eang \'cay ch\'bcng ch\'f3t b\'e5i th\'ad\'eang. M\'c6t kh\'b8c, gi\'b8 mu\'e8i t\'a8ng l\'aan qu\'b8 qu\'bet l\'b5m cho ng\'ad\'eai \'ae\'b8
nh c\'b8 kh\'abng s\'bdn v\'e8n kh\'abng th\'d3 mua tr\'f7 \'ae\'ad\'eec \'ae\'f1 s\'e8 mu\'e8i c\'c7n thi\'d5t cho m\'e9t chuy\'d5n \'aei c\'b8. V\'d7 th\'d5, ph\'c7n l\'edn nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai l\'b5m c\'b8 \'ae\'b7 ph\'b6i b\'e1 ngh\'d2.
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-274\slmult0\nowidctlpar\tx7513\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 Ngh\'d2 l\'b5m mu\'e8i tr\'ad\'edc kia l\'b5 m\'e9t c\'abng nghi\'d6p ph\'b8t \'ae\'b9t nh\'cat \'eb \'a7
\'abng D\'ad\'acng; ng\'ad\'eai ta \'ae\'b7 c\'e8 t\'d7nh l\'b5m cho n\'e3 suy \'ae\'e5i, ch\'d8 \'ae\'d3 l\'b9i s\'e8 ru\'e9ng mu\'e8i c\'c7n thi\'d5t cho vi\'d6c \'a8n u\'e8ng. Vi\'d6c xu\'cat c\'b6ng mu\'e8i b\'de \'ae\'d7nh ch\'d8 h\'bcn. Su\'e8
t trong th\'eai k\'fa chi\'d5n tranh, n\'ad\'edc Nh\'cbt xin mua mu\'e8i ch\'bcng \'ae\'ad\'eec.
\par T\'d6 h\'acn n\'f7a, v\'d7 ng\'ad\'eai ta kh\'abng th\'d3 t\'ddnh \'ae\'ad\'eec s\'e8 ru\'e9ng mu\'e8i c\'c7n thi\'d5t cho vi\'d6c \'a8n u\'e8ng, th\'b5nh ra h\'bbng n\'a8m nh\'b5 \'aeoan l\'b9i ph\'b6i mua mu\'e8i c\'f1a Trung Qu\'e8c. Tr\'ad\'ed
c kia, An Nam xu\'cat c\'b6ng mu\'e8i (l00.000 t\'can trong n\'a8m 1896), b\'a9y gi\'ea l\'b9i ph\'b6i nh\'cbp c\'b6ng \'ae\'d3 ti\'aau d\'efng.
\par X\'ada kia, \'eb v\'efng \'ae\'e5ng b\'bbng B\'bec K\'fa, kh\'abng c\'e3 n\'a8m n\'b5o l\'b5 ho\'b5n to\'b5n m\'cat m\'efa. Khi n\'ad\'edc l\'f4t tr\'b5n ng\'cbp \'ae\'e5ng ru\'e9ng, th\'d7 c\'b8 theo n\'ad\'edc v\'b5o nhi\'d2u; ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8 l
\'b9i l\'b5m m\'efa c\'b8. B\'a9y gi\'ea th\'d7 kh\'abng th\'d3 \'ae\'ad\'eec, v\'d7 kh\'abng c\'e3 mu\'e8i. M\'c6t kh\'b8c, d\'a9n ch\'f3ng tr\'ad\'edc th\'d7 \'a8n quen m\'e9t th\'f8 mu\'e8i th\'abi, b\'a9y gi\'ea th\'d7 b\'cat c\'f8 th\'f8 n\'b5o, h
\'e4 c\'f2ng ph\'b6i nh\'cbn v\'cby. C\'b8c b\'b9n th\'f6 t\'ad\'ebng t\'ad\'eeng xem ng\'ad\'eai quen \'a8n mu\'e8i nh\'e1 tr\'beng b\'a9y 
\par }\pard \qj \li0\ri0\sa80\sl-274\slmult0\nowidctlpar\tx7513\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 gi\'ea ph\'b6i \'a8n mu\'e8i \'aeen kh\'e3 ch\'deu nh\'ad th\'d5 n\'b5o. H\'acn n\'f7a mu\'e8i chuy\'aan ch\'eb
 t\'f5 Nam K\'fa ra B\'bec K\'fa ph\'b6i ch\'deu ti\'d2n v\'cbn t\'b6i kh\'b8 \'ae\'bet, nh\'b5 \'aeoan li\'d2n t\'a8ng gi\'b8 mu\'e8i b\'b8n cho c\'abng ch\'f3ng. Ng\'ad\'eai \'a8n ph\'b6i tr\'b6 \'ae\'bet h\'acn t\'f5 20 \'ae\'d5n 25% cho m\'e9t th\'f8
 mu\'e8i m\'d7nh ch\'bcng \'ada ch\'f3t n\'b5o.
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-274\slmult0\nowidctlpar\tx7513\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 Kho mu\'e8i r\'cat \'ddt m\'b5 l\'b9i \'eb c\'b8ch qu\'b7ng r\'cat xa nhau, n\'aan ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x
\'f8 \'eb c\'b8c l\'b5ng ph\'b6i nh\'ea ng\'ad\'eai Hoa chuy\'aan ch\'eb v\'d2 cho v\'b5 nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai n\'b5y l\'b9i l\'eei d\'f4ng t\'f9 ti\'d6n t\'a8ng gi\'b8 mu\'e8i l\'aan, nhi\'d2u \'ddt tu\'fa ch\'e7 xa g\'c7n.
\par Khi \'ae\'c6t ra thu\'d5 mu\'e8i, ng\'ad\'eai ta quy\'d5t \'ae\'denh t\'ad nh\'a9n kh\'abng \'ae\'ad\'eec t\'ddch tr\'f7 qu\'b8 15 kil\'abgam. \'a7\'d3 ki\'d3m so\'b8t, nh\'a9n vi\'aan nh\'b5 \'aeoan ph\'b6i kh\'b8m x\'d0t, m\'b5 h\'e4 kh\'b8m x\'d0t tu
\'fa theo s\'eb th\'ddch c\'f1a h\'e4. Ch\'d8 c\'c7n c\'e3 k\'ce t\'e8 c\'b8o l\'b5 h\'e4 kh\'b8m x\'d0t \'ae\'b6o l\'e9n c\'b6 nh\'b5 ng\'ad\'eai ta l\'aan.
\par D\'a9n ch\'f3ng khi\'d5p s\'ee nh\'a9n vi\'aan nh\'b5 \'aeoan \'ae\'d5n n\'e7i khi v\'f5a \'ae\'ad\'eec tin c\'b8c ng\'b5i t\'edi, h\'e4 li\'d2n b\'e1 c\'f6a b\'e1 nh\'b5 ra \'aei, m\'c6c cho c\'b8c ng\'b5i mu\'e8n l\'b5m g\'d7 th\'d7 l\'b5m. Th\'cay \'ae
\'b5n b\'b5 con g\'b8i \'eb nh\'b5, c\'b8c ng\'b5i li\'d2n x\'f6 s\'f9 theo th\'e3i c\'f1a k\'ce chi\'d5n th\'beng tr\'aan \'ae\'cat n\'ad\'edc chi\'d5n b\'b9i. (\'a7\'b9i t\'b8 B\'d0cna).
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\tx7513\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 Ch\'ddnh s\'b8ch \'ae\'e9c quy\'d2n mu\'e8i nh\'bec ng\'ad\'eai ta h\'e5i t\'ad\'ebng \'ae\'d5n m\'e9t ch
\'ddnh s\'b8ch b\'de nguy\'d2n r\'f1a nh\'cat c\'f1a ch\'d5 \'ae\'e9 c\'f2 \'eb n\'ad\'edc Ph\'b8p: thu\'d5 mu\'e8i. Nh\'adng c\'b8i thu\'d5 mu\'e8i \'eb \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng n\'b5y kh\'abng ph\'b6i nh\'ad thu\'d5 mu\'e8i \'ae\'e3ng g\'e3p cho qu\'e8
c gia \'eb Ph\'b8p, m\'b5 l\'b5 m\'e9t th\'f8 thu\'d5 mu\'e8i do nh\'f7ng con ng\'ad\'eai kh\'abng bi\'d5t c\'b6 ti\'d5ng n\'e3i n\'ad\'edc m\'d7nh b\'bet m\'d7nh ph\'b6i \'ae\'e3ng g\'e3p cho m\'e9t \'abng ch\'f1 ng\'ad\'eai ngo\'b9i qu\'e8c.
\par M\'e9t b\'c7y \'a8n c\'ad\'edp \'ae\'b7 l\'b5m cho c\'b6 m\'e9t d\'a9n t\'e9c \'ae\'e3i kh\'b8t kh\'e8n c\'efng, \'ae\'b7 l\'b5m cho c\'b6 m\'e9t c\'abng ngh\'d6 qu\'e8c gia b\'de ph\'b8 s\'b6n nh\'ad th\'d5 \'ae\'cay.
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 
\par }\pard\plain \s21\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \b\f39\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 \column 
\par }\pard\plain \s20\qc \li0\ri0\sb1400\sa440\sl-380\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \b\f38\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 S\'f9 NH\'a6\'eeNG QUY\'d2N\line V\'b5 NH\'f7NG K\'ce 
\'a7\'a6\'eeC NH\'a6\'eeNG QUY\'d2N
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-268\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 \~Sau khi b\'de binh l\'ddnh b\'ben ph\'b8 v\'b5 ch\'d0
m gi\'d5t, \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng l\'b9i b\'de b\'e4n c\'b8 m\'cbp th\'f9c d\'a9n c\'ad\'edp b\'e3c \'ae\'d5n t\'cbn x\'ad\'acng tu\'fb. Vi\'d6c c\'ad\'edp b\'e3c \'ae\'aa ti\'d6n \'cay g\'e4i theo ti\'d5ng th\'f9c d\'a9n l\'b5 \'ae\'e5n \'aei\'d2n.

\par Trong cu\'e9c chi\'d5n tranh x\'a9m l\'ad\'eec l\'a9u d\'b5i, d\'a9n ch\'f3ng ph\'b6i b\'e1 \'ae\'cat \'aeai \'aei l\'b8nh n\'b9n, ch\'ea cho qua ng\'b5y kh\'e3i l\'f6a. Tr\'ad\'edc h\'d5t, ng\'ad\'eai ta mang \'ae\'cat \'aeai c\'f1a h\'e4 nh\'ad\'ee
ng cho k\'ce kh\'b8c. Khi \'ae\'b7 y\'aan \'e6n r\'e5i, nh\'f7ng 
\par }\pard \qj \li0\ri0\sa80\sl-268\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 ch\'f1 c\'f2 v\'d2 l\'b5ng th\'d7 th\'cay ru\'e9ng \'ae\'cat c\'f1a m\'d7nh \'ae\'b7 b\'de chi\'d5m m\'cat; mu\'e8n v\'d2 l
\'b9i ch\'e7 c\'f2 l\'b5m \'a8n, h\'e4 ph\'b6i nh\'cbn nh\'f7ng \'aei\'d2u ki\'d6n c\'f1a ng\'ad\'eai m\'edi \'ae\'d5n: c\'b5y c\'cay ch\'ddnh \'ae\'e5ng ru\'e9ng c\'f1a m\'d7nh cho m\'e9t anh ch\'f1 ng\'ad\'eai ngo\'b9i qu\'e8c.
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-268\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Nhi\'d2u khi ng\'ad\'eai ta nh\'ad\'eeng c\'b6 nh\'f7ng \'ae\'cat \'aeai \'ae\'b7 c\'e3 ng\'ad\'eai \'eb v\'b5 c\'b5y c
\'cay v\'edi c\'b6 l\'b5ng m\'b9c \'eb \'ae\'e3.
\par Nhi\'d2u n\'aci, c\'b6 l\'b5ng b\'de t\'ad\'edc \'aeo\'b9t h\'d5t \'ae\'cat \'aeai nh\'ad v\'cby, ph\'b6i tr\'eb th\'b5nh nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai m\'b5 ng\'ad\'eai ta g\'e4i l\'b5 "k\'ce c\'ad\'edp"; th\'cbt ra h\'e4 ch\'d8 l\'b5 nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai n\'e6
i d\'cby ch\'e8ng vi\'d6c c\'ad\'edp \'aeo\'b9t b\'cat c\'abng.
\par Nh\'f7ng t\'aan c\'ad\'edp b\'cat c\'abng \'cay l\'b9i \'ae\'ad\'eec Ch\'ddnh ph\'f1 thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea n\'a9ng \'ae\'ec.
\par M\'e9t t\'aan to\'b5n quy\'d2n \'ae\'b7 nh\'ad\'eeng m\'e9t \'ae\'e5n \'aei\'d2n l\'edn cho m\'e9t c\'abng ty tr\'e5ng ch\'cc \'eb \'a7\'b5 N\'bdng - nh\'adng c\'abng ty ch\'bcng ph\'b8t \'ae\'b9t g\'d7 l\'bem -, \'ae\'b7 mang \'ae\'cat \'aeai c\'f1a nh
\'b5 vua An Nam nh\'ad\'eeng cho k\'ce kh\'b8c, ng\'ad\'eai ta c\'f2ng ch\'ada l\'cay l\'b5m v\'f5a l\'dfng, ng\'ad\'eai ta c\'dfn b\'bet c\'b6 nh\'b5 vua ph\'b6i cho c\'abng ty vay 30 v\'b9n b\'b9c n\'f7a. Ngo\'b5i ra c\'abng ty c\'dfn \'ae\'ad\'eec th
\'c7u cung
\par }\pard\plain \s25\qj \li0\ri0\sa80\sl-268\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f38\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\insrsid1378858 c\'cap ch\'cc cho binh l\'ddnh. Nh\'adng ng\'ad\'ea
i An Nam kh\'abng th\'ddch u\'e8ng th\'f8 ch\'cc x\'cau \'cay, n\'aan ch\'cc cung c\'cap \'ae\'d3 m\'e8c trong kho.
\par }\pard\plain \qc \li0\ri0\sb120\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\tx7513\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 *\line *    *
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f38\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 \'eb}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  ngo\'b9i th\'b5nh, nhi\'d2u ng\'ad\'eai \'a2u kh\'abng ph\'b6i \'ae\'e3ng thu\'d5
 \'aei\'d2n th\'e6, v\'d7 Nh\'b5 n\'ad\'edc cho r\'bbng b\'bet ch\'f1 \'ae\'e5n \'aei\'d2n ph\'b6i \'ae\'e3ng thu\'d5 \'aei\'d2n th\'e6 l\'b5 l\'b5m h\'b9i cho s\'f9 ph\'b8t tri\'d3n c\'f1a n\'d2n n\'abng nghi\'d6p.
\par Gi\'b6m nh\'d1 thu\'d5 cho ng\'ad\'eai \'a2u, d\'ef l\'b5 ng\'ad\'eai \'a2u gi\'b5u c\'e3, l\'b5 vi\'d6c th\'ad\'eang; \'ae\'c6c bi\'d6t \'eb Cao Mi\'aan, nhi\'d2u ng\'ad\'eai \'ae\'ad\'eec gi\'b6m thu\'d5, v\'b5 th\'ad\'eang th\'ad\'eang h\'e4 l\'b5 nh
\'f7ng vi\'aan ch\'f8c ng\'ad\'eai \'a2u.
\par }\pard \qc \li0\ri0\sb120\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\tx7513\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 *\line *    *
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-276\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Ng\'ad\'eai An Nam, d\'ef c\'e3 s\'bdn ti\'d2n c\'c7n thi\'d5t, c\'f2ng kh\'abng xin \'ae\'ad\'eec nh\'ad\'eeng \'ae\'d5
n }{\i\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 n\'a8m h\'d0cta, }{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 nh\'adng \'ae\'e8i v\'edi th\'f9c d\'a9n th\'d7 di\'d6n t\'ddch xin }{\i\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 kh\'abng b\'de h\'b9n ch\'d5.}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  Nhi\'d2u ng\'ad\'eai \'a2
u c\'e3 \'ae\'e5n \'aei\'d2n r\'e9ng tr\'aan 25.000 h\'d0cta.
\par }{\f37\fs20\expnd0\expndtw-2\insrsid1378858 Ng\'ad\'eai ta \'ae\'b7 nh\'ad\'eeng nh\'f7ng \'ae\'e5n \'aei\'d2n r\'e9ng t\'f5 10 \'ae\'d5n 20 ng\'b5n h\'d0cta cho nh\'f7ng k\'ce ch\'bcng hi\'d3u bi\'d5t ch\'f3t g\'d7 v\'d2 n\'abng nghi\'d6p; b\'e4n n\'b5
y ch\'d8 c\'e3 m\'e9t \'fd ngh\'dc: l\'cbp l\'b9i \'eb \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng m\'e9t ch\'d5 \'ae\'e9 phong ki\'d5n c\'e3 l\'eei cho h\'e4 b\'bbng c\'b8ch coi ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8 nh\'ad nh\'f7ng n\'abng n\'ab th\'f9c s\'f9.
\par }{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 C\'e3 hai vi\'aan c\'abng ch\'f8c \'ae\'b7 \'ae\'ad\'eec nh\'ad\'eeng l\'b5m \'ae\'e5n \'aei\'d2n 30 ng\'b5n h\'d0cta r\'f5ng v\'edi gi\'b8 5 phr\'a8ng m\'e9t h\'d0cta. H\'acn n\'f7a h\'e4 c\'dfn ghi r\'e2 r\'bbng 30 ng\'b5n h
\'d0cta \'cay \'ae\'ad\'eec mi\'d4n thu\'d5 trong su\'e8t th\'eai k\'fa c\'abng ty kinh doanh, ngh\'dca l\'b5 su\'e8t 80 n\'a8m.
\par }{\f37\fs20\expnd0\expndtw-2\insrsid1378858 M\'e9t l\'c7n kh\'b8c, khi v\'b5o s\'e6 tr\'ad\'edc b\'b9 c\'b8i v\'a8n t\'f9 b\'b8n 30 ng\'b5n h\'d0cta \'ae\'cat v\'edi gi\'b8 150 ng\'b5n phr\'a8ng, vi\'aan ch\'f1 s\'f9 tr\'ad\'edc b\'b9 ghi d\'ad\'edi v\'a8
n t\'f9 nh\'ad sau: }{\i\f37\fs20\expnd0\expndtw-2\insrsid1378858 "\'ae\'b7 thu 10 phr\'a8ng thu\'d5 theo l\'d6nh c\'f1a quan to\'b5n quy\'d2n".}{\f37\fs20\expnd0\expndtw-2\insrsid1378858  Ch\'d8 10 phr\'a8ng thu\'d5 \'ae\'d3 chi\'d5m l\'b5m c\'f1a ri\'aa
ng \'ae\'ad\'eec 30 ng\'b5n h\'d0cta \'ae\'cat!
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 V\'f5a r\'e5i, ng\'ad\'eai ta cho b\'e4n \'ae\'c7u c\'ac 8 ng\'b5n, 10 ng\'b5n v\'b5 20 ng\'b5n h\'d0cta r\'f5ng c\'abng v
\'b5 ru\'e9ng \'ae\'cat c\'f1a ng\'ad\'eai An Nam \'eb th\'ad\'eeng du. B\'de c\'ad\'edp \'aeo\'b9t nh\'ad th\'d5, nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai n\'b5y t\'e1 ra b\'cat b\'d7nh. Th\'d5 l\'b5, Ch\'ddnh ph\'f1 \'ae\'ada ngay m\'b8y bay ch\'eb bom l\'aan, l\'b5m cho h
\'e4 y\'aan \'aei.
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sl-268\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 B\'a9y gi\'ea ch\'f3ng ta x\'d0t sang b\'e4n \'a8n c\'ad\'edp m\'e9t ki\'d3u kh\'b8c \'ae\'b7 tr\'e6 h\'d5t t\'b5i kh\'d0o l
\'d0o l\'f5a c\'b6 Nh\'b5 n\'ad\'edc l\'c9n d\'a9n b\'b6n x\'f8. Qu\'a9n c\'ad\'edp n\'b5y g\'e4i l\'b5 ng\'ad\'eai cho th\'c7u, ng\'ad\'eai b\'e1 th\'c7u hay th\'c7u kho\'b8n.
\par H\'b7y k\'d3 v\'b5i v\'dd d\'f4:
\par Ng\'ad\'eai ta cho b\'e1 th\'c7u c\'abng vi\'d6c v\'cbn t\'b6i \'ae\'ad\'eang thu\'fb l\'b5m hai l\'ab, m\'e9t l\'ab v\'cbn t\'b6i \'ae\'ad\'eang s\'abng v\'b5 m\'e9t l\'ab v\'cbn t\'b6i \'ae\'ad\'eang bi\'d3n. B\'b6n h\'eep \'ae\'e5ng \'ae\'denh r\'bb
ng khi c\'b6 hai l\'ab \'ae\'b7 cho b\'e1 th\'c7u xong, th\'d7 m\'e9t trong s\'e8 ng\'ad\'eai b\'e1 th\'c7u c\'e3 th\'d3 nh\'cbn th\'c7u chung c\'b6 hai l\'ab.
\par L\'ab th\'f8 nh\'cat \'ae\'ad\'eec \'aeem ra \'ae\'cau gi\'b8. \'a4ng R. xin 6 phr\'a8ng r\'ad\'eci m\'e9t h\'b6i l\'fd. V\'d7 kh\'abng h\'eep l\'d6, \'abng R. b\'de lo\'b9i ra ngo\'b5i. L\'ab th\'f8 nh\'cat \'ae\'ad\'eec th\'c7u 9 phr\'a8ng m\'e9t h\'b6
i l\'fd v\'b5 l\'ab th\'f8 hai 18 phr\'a8ng.
\par Xong r\'e5i ng\'ad\'eai ta \'aeem cho \'ae\'cau gi\'b8 chung c\'b6 hai l\'ab g\'e9p l\'b9i. Ch\'d8 nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai \'ae\'b7 \'ae\'cau gi\'b8 tr\'f3ng ri\'aang t\'f5ng l\'ab m\'edi \'ae\'ad\'eec \'ae\'cau gi\'b8 chung c\'b6 hai l\'ab. \'a4ng R. \'ae
\'b7 b\'de lo\'b9i l\'c7n \'ae\'c7u, \'ae\'b8ng l\'cf kh\'abng \'ae\'ad\'eec 
\par }\pard \qj \li0\ri0\sl-268\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 tham gia l\'c7n \'ae\'cau gi\'b8 chung n\'b5y. Tuy v\'cby, trong th\'eai gian t\'f5 l\'c7n \'ae\'c7u \'ae\'d5n l\'c7n n\'b5y, h\'e4
 \'ae\'b7 th\'abng \'ae\'e5ng v\'edi nhau. Hai nh\'b5 tr\'f3ng th\'c7u l\'c7n tr\'ad\'edc kh\'abng ch\'deu \'ae\'cau gi\'b8 c\'b6 hai l\'ab g\'e9p l\'b9i. V\'cby \'abng R. l\'b9i \'ae\'ad\'eec ph\'d0p b\'e1 th\'c7u, v\'b5 \'abng R. tr\'ad\'edc xin c\'e3
 6 phr\'a8ng r\'ad\'eci, nay l\'b9i \'ae\'dfi 9 phr\'a8ng kia.
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-268\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 S\'b8u phr\'a8ng r\'ad\'eci xin kh\'abng \'ae\'b9t, m\'b5 nay l\'b9i \'ae\'ad\'eec nh\'f7ng ch\'ddn phr\'a8ng!
\par C\'abng ty \'ae\'ad\'eec th\'c7u c\'e3 l\'b7i r\'cat nhi\'d2u, thi\'d6t h\'b9i cho x\'f8 thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea. Khi m\'edi th\'b5nh l\'cbp, c\'abng ty ch\'d8 c\'e3 500.000 phr\'a8ng l\'b5m v\'e8n. Trong 30 n\'a8m, s\'e8 v\'e8n \'cay \'ae\'b7 th\'b5
nh 11.000.000 phr\'a8ng.
\par M\'e9t th\'b5nh ph\'e8 \'eb Nam K\'fa m\'eb m\'e9t nh\'b5 m\'b8y \'aei\'d6n. C\'abng vi\'d6c kinh doanh ph\'b8t \'ae\'b9t l\'bem. Vi\'aan c\'abng s\'f8 b\'bet h\'b5ng t\'d8nh ph\'b6i nh\'ad\'eeng kh\'abng nh\'b5 m\'b8y cho m\'e9t ng\'ad\'eai b\'b9n c\'f1
a \'abng ta. }{\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'dd}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 t l\'a9u sau, v\'d7 nh\'b5 m\'b8y kh\'abng ph\'b8t t\'b5i \'ae\'ad\'eec nh\'adng \'ae\'b7 l\'b5 c\'f1a t\'ad nh\'a9n, n\'aan h\'b5ng t\'d8nh b\'de c\'ad\'edp \'aeo\'b9t tr\'ad\'ed
c kia l\'b9i ph\'b6i mua l\'b9i r\'cat \'ae\'bet c\'b8i m\'b5 h\'e4 \'ae\'b7 ph\'b6i cho kh\'abng.
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-272\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'a7\'d3 lo\'cc \'ae\'eai, ng\'ad\'eai ta \'ae\'b7 b\'e1 ra h\'b5ng ng\'b5n b\'b9c \'ae\'d3 \'ae\'c6t m\'e9t \'ae\'b5i v
\'ab tuy\'d5n \'aei\'d6n \'eb S\'b5i G\'dfn. C\'abng vi\'d6c v\'f5a ho\'b5n th\'b5nh th\'d7 c\'b6 nh\'b5 c\'f6a l\'c9n m\'b8y m\'e3c \'ae\'b7 l\'e4t v\'b5o tay m\'e9t c\'abng ty c\'f1a t\'ad nh\'a9n. Nh\'adng vi\'d6c kinh doanh l\'e7 m\'e7i ng\'b5y m\'ca
t m\'e9t ng\'b5n b\'b9c, c\'abng ty d\'b5n x\'d5p \'ae\'d3 ch\'ddnh x\'f8 thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea, ngh\'dca l\'b5 nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai d\'a9n \'ae\'e3ng thu\'d5, ph\'b6i g\'b8nh s\'f9 thua l\'e7 \'cay.
\par M\'e9t c\'abng ty kh\'b8ch s\'b9n \'ae\'ad\'eec th\'b5nh l\'cbp v\'edi s\'e8 v\'e8n l\'b5 25.000 \'ae\'e5ng. L\'cay c\'ed \'ae\'d3 khuy\'d5n kh\'ddch vi\'d6c du l\'dech, Ch\'ddnh ph\'f1 g\'e3p ph\'c7n v\'b5o 1.200.000 \'ae\'e5ng \'ae\'d3 x\'a9y d\'f9ng nh
\'b5 c\'f6a. Ngo\'b5i ra, h\'e4 c\'dfn \'ae\'denh r\'e2 r\'bbng n\'d5u cho th\'c7u kh\'abng h\'d5t s\'e8 ti\'d2n \'cay th\'d7 s\'e8 ti\'d2n ti\'d5t ki\'d6m \'ae\'ad\'eec s\'cf }{\i\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 chia cho c\'abng ty }{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 v
\'b5 Nh\'b5 n\'ad\'edc. Kh\'b8ch s\'b9n s\'cf c\'e3 t\'cat c\'b6 12 bu\'e5ng. Th\'d5 l\'b5 d\'a9n An Nam ph\'b6i tr\'b6 100.000 \'ae\'e5ng hay 1.000.000 phr\'a8ng m\'e7i bu\'e5ng \'ae\'d3 m\'e9t ng\'b5y kia v\'b5i \'abng da tr\'beng \'a8n b\'b8m v\'b5 l
\'ad\'eai bi\'d5ng \'ae\'d5n ngh\'d8 tay ch\'a9n r\'e7i r\'b7i c\'f1a c\'b8c \'abng!
\par }{\f37\fs20\expnd0\expndtw-2\insrsid1378858 M\'e9t anh ch\'f1 th\'c7u c\'e8ng r\'b7nh n\'b5o \'ae\'e3 giao \'e8ng n\'ad\'edc l\'b5m b\'bbng v\'abi thay cho \'e8ng xim\'a8ng, \'e8ng kh\'abng \'ae\'c7y m\'e9t m\'d0t l\'b9i khai l\'b5 d\'b5i ba m\'d0t, r\'e5
i chia nhau v\'edi c\'b8c \'abng h\'e9i \'ae\'e5ng th\'b5nh ph\'e8 ng\'ad\'eai \'a2u 1.600.000 phr\'a8ng. M\'e9t \'abng k\'fc s\'ad kh\'b8c, \'ae\'e5ng th\'eai ki\'aam c\'b6 nhi\'d6m v\'f4 ph\'e3 \'ae\'e8c l\'fd, bi\'d3n th\'f1 300.000 phr\'a8ng trong vi
\'d6c x\'a9y c\'e8ng r\'b7nh v\'b5 s\'f6a sang l\'b9i c\'e3 m\'e9t \'ae\'ad\'eang ph\'e8. M\'e9t \'abng k\'fc s\'ad \'ae\'dea ch\'ddnh v\'b5 h\'e9i \'ae\'e5ng thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea n\'b5o \'ae\'e3 \'ae\'f3t t\'f3i h\'acn 900.000 phr\'a8ng ti\'d2n c\'abng 
\'aeo \'ae\'b9c \'ae\'d3 l\'cbp b\'b6n \'ae\'e5 \'ae\'cat \'aeai \'eb ba t\'e6ng. V\'b5, v\'d7 th\'cay ng\'b5i "thanh li\'aam" l\'bem v\'b5 c\'e3 ch\'a9n trong c\'abng ty \'ae\'e9c quy\'d2n h\'b6i c\'b6ng S\'b5i G\'dfn, n\'aan Ch\'ddnh ph\'f1 v\'f5a m\'ed
i giao cho ng\'b5i l\'b5m lu\'abn c\'b6 c\'b8c c\'abng vi\'d6c \'ae\'b9c \'aei\'d2n \'eb nhi\'d2u t\'d8nh kh\'b8c.
\par }{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'a7\'b9i b\'eem nh\'cat trong s\'e8 k\'ce c\'ad\'edp \'cay l\'b5 "T\'e6ng c\'abng ty thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea" v\'f5a m\'edi \'ae\'ad\'eec nh\'ad\'eeng h\'b6i c\'b6ng S\'b5i G\'dfn - Ch\'ee L\'edn (Nam K\'fa). Cho h\'ad\'ebng \'ae
\'e9c quy\'d2n t\'f8c l\'b5 cho c\'abng ty \'cay h\'b6i c\'b6ng v\'edi c\'b6 \'ae\'cat \'aeai nh\'b5 c\'f6a, d\'f4ng c\'f4 m\'b8y m\'e3c c\'c7n thi\'d5t \'ae\'d3 kinh doanh, cho quy\'d2n thu thu\'d5 v\'b5 \'ae\'e9c quy\'d2n v\'cbn t\'b6i \'ae\'d3 xu\'ca
t c\'b6ng.
\par Nh\'ad th\'d5 l\'b5, n\'abng d\'a9n, ti\'d3u th\'ad\'acng, c\'abng nh\'a9n khu\'a9n v\'b8c \'eb c\'b6ng, ch\'f1 thuy\'d2n \'eb Nam K\'fa, t\'cat c\'b6 m\'e4i ng\'ad\'eai \'ae\'d2u b\'de ph\'e3 m\'c6c trong tay m\'e9t c\'abng ty \'ae\'e9c quy\'d2n \'a8n c
\'ad\'edp mu\'e8n l\'b5m g\'d7 th\'d7 l\'b5m, m\'b5 \'ae\'b9i bi\'d3u l\'b5 m\'e9t t\'aan k\'fc s\'ad v\'b5 ... l\'b5 ngh\'de vi\'aan h\'e9i \'ae\'e5ng thu\'e9c \'ae\'dea.
\par }\pard\plain \s21\qj \li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \b\f39\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\b0\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 
\par }\pard\plain \s20\qc \li0\ri0\sb1400\sa440\sl-380\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \b\f38\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 C\'a4NG CH\'ddNH
\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-294\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Th\'f9c d\'a9n Ph\'b8p \'ae\'b8nh gi\'b8 c\'abng \'ac
n khai ho\'b8 c\'f1a h\'e4 \'eb \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng b\'bbng nh\'f7ng kil\'abm\'d0t \'ae\'ad\'eang c\'b8i m\'b5 h\'e4 \'ae\'b7 \'ae\'bep b\'bbng ti\'d2n v\'b5 c\'abng s\'f8c c\'f1a ng\'ad\'eai An Nam. Song ng\'ad\'eai Ph\'b8p c\'f2ng ch\'d8 \'ae\'c6t 
\'ae\'ad\'eang xe l\'f6a \'eb nh\'f7ng n\'aci h\'e4 c\'c7n d\'efng \'ae\'d3 chuy\'aan ch\'eb h\'b5ng ho\'b8 hay qu\'a9n \'ae\'e9i \'ae\'d3 \'ae\'b5n \'b8p d\'a9n ch\'f3ng; v\'b5 \'ae\'ad\'eang s\'b8 \'ae\'bep kh\'abng ph\'b6i \'ae\'d3 cho ng\'ad\'eai b
\'b6n x\'f8 \'aei, v\'d7 nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai n\'b5y kh\'abng c\'e3 quy\'d2n t\'f9 do \'aei l\'b9i ngay c\'b6 \'aei t\'f5 t\'d8nh n\'b5y sang t\'d8nh kh\'b8c, m\'b5 l\'b5 \'ae\'d3 ph\'f4c v\'f4 cho ng\'ad\'eai \'a2u.
\par C\'e3 khi h\'e4 c\'f2ng h\'cap t\'cap x\'a9y d\'f9ng nh\'f7ng c\'abng tr\'d7nh xa hoa l\'e9ng l\'c9y, nh\'adng kh\'abng ph\'b6i \'ae\'d3 cho nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai \'ae\'b7 b\'e1 ti\'d2n ra, kh\'abng ph\'b6i \'ae\'d3 cho ng\'ad\'eai An Nam \'ae\'ad\'eec h
\'ad\'ebng.
\par }{\f37\fs20\expnd0\expndtw2\insrsid1378858 Tai v\'b9 l\'b5 \'eb ch\'e7 ph\'c7n l\'edn nh\'f7ng m\'e3n ti\'d2n s\'bdn c\'e3 l\'b9i th\'ad\'eang \'aeem d\'efng v\'b5o nh\'f7ng vi\'d6c ph\'ef phi\'d5m (c\'b8c quan s\'f8 \'aei ch\'aci, \'ae
i thanh tra, v.v.) c\'dfn \'ae\'ad\'eang s\'b8 c\'c7n thi\'d5t cho vi\'d6c khai kh\'c8n v\'b5 th\'abng th\'ad\'acng trong x\'f8 th\'d7 ch\'d8 l\'b5 nh\'f7ng v\'f2ng n\'ad\'edc \'ae\'e4ng l\'c7y l\'e9i, l\'f3n s\'f4t, kh\'abng th\'d3 \'aei \'ae\'ad\'eec, d
\'ef cho tr\'a9u r\'f5ng c\'f2ng ch\'deu. \'a7\'ad\'eang c\'b8i, ch\'d8 \'ae\'d1p \'ae\'cf \'eb xung quanh t\'d8nh v\'b5 c\'b8c to\'b5 s\'f8 c\'dfn ngo\'b5i ra th\'d7 \'ddt \'e1i, l\'b9i \'ae\'bep v\'b5 r\'b6i \'ae\'b8 r\'cat t\'e5i. Kh\'abng c\'e3 l\'ca
y m\'e9t con \'ae\'ad\'eang \'aei xe \'ae\'ad\'eec v\'b5o c\'b8c v\'efng \'ae\'e5ng ru\'e9ng c\'b5y c\'cay.
\par }{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 M\'e9t con \'ae\'ad\'eang, \'ae\'d3 n\'e8i li\'d2n hai t\'d8nh Nam K\'fa, d\'b5i c\'e3 34 kil\'abm\'d0t, nh\'adng \'ae\'b7 ba m\'ad\'aci n\'a8m nay, h\'e4 m\'edi \'ae\'e6 \'ae\'ad\'eec \'ddt \'ae\'cat v\'b5 c\'b8t m\'b5 \'ae\'b7
 ng\'e8n h\'d5t m\'e9t s\'e8 ti\'d2n kh\'b8 l\'edn, \'ae\'f1 \'ae\'d3 l\'b8t \'ae\'ad\'eec su\'e8t con \'ae\'ad\'eang \'ae\'e3, t\'f5 \'ae\'c7u \'ae\'d5n cu\'e8i, m\'e9t l\'edp b\'b9c d\'b5y.
\par }\pard \qj \li0\ri0\sa80\sl-274\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'eb}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  Hu\'d5, ng\'ad\'eai ta c\'e3 \'ae\'bep m\'e9t \'ae\'b9i l\'e9 r\'e9ng 20 m\'d0t - th\'cbt ra l
\'b5 v\'ab \'ddch - ch\'b9y th\'bcng t\'f5 th\'b5nh \'ae\'d5n \'ae\'b5n Nam giao. Con \'ae\'ad\'eang \'cay m\'eb qua hai l\'b5ng v\'b5 m\'e9t ngh\'dca trang, khi l\'b5m ph\'b6i ph\'b8 hay di chuy\'d3n m\'cat s\'b8u ng\'b5n ng\'abi m\'e9. Ng\'ad\'eai ta ch
\'bcng ch\'deu b\'e5i th\'ad\'eang hay gi\'f3p \'ae\'ec g\'d7 cho c\'b8c gia \'ae\'d7nh c\'e3 nh\'b5 ph\'b6i ph\'b8, c\'e3 c\'a9y ph\'b6i ch\'c6t, c\'e3 m\'e5 m\'b6 ph\'b6i khai qu\'cbt l\'aan.
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-274\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'eb}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858  B\'bec K\'fa, vi\'d6c s\'f6a sang t\'ab \'aei\'d3m th\'b5nh ph\'e8 l\'b5m ch\'bcng h\'d5
t m\'cay \'ae\'e5ng ti\'d2n, nh\'adng thi\'d6t h\'b9i l\'edn cho ng\'ad\'eai An Nam.
\par M\'e9t vi\'aan \'ae\'e8c l\'fd ng\'ad\'eai Ph\'b8p ch\'d8 \'ae\'acn gi\'b6n ra m\'e9t ngh\'de \'ae\'denh, b\'bet \'ae\'bep m\'e9t \'ae\'ad\'eang ph\'e8 cho d\'b5i th\'aam, l\'b5m cho nh\'b5 c\'f6a th\'bcng h\'b5ng, ph\'b8 nh\'f7ng l\'d2u tranh v\'b5 ph
\'b6i l\'b5m l\'b9i b\'bbng g\'b9ch. Nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai ngh\'cco kh\'e6 kh\'abng c\'e3 \'ae\'f1 ti\'d2n \'ae\'d3 tu\'a9n l\'d6nh ph\'b6i b\'e1 th\'b5nh ph\'e8 ra \'aei.
\par Ng\'ad\'eai An Nam \'eb g\'c7n doanh tr\'b9i b\'de \'aeu\'e6i \'aei. H\'e4 \'ae\'ad\'eec b\'e5i th\'ad\'eang b\'bbng nh\'f7ng mi\'d5ng \'ae\'cat \'eb ph\'e8 kh\'b8c \'ae\'d3 d\'f9ng l\'b9i nh\'f7ng t\'f3p l\'d2u tranh c\'f1a h\'e4.
\par }{\f38\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'dd}{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 t l\'a9u sau, ng\'ad\'eai ta h\'b9 l\'d6nh cho h\'e4 ph\'b6i x\'a9y nh\'b5 g\'b9ch. Nhi\'d2u ng\'ad\'eai kh\'abng c\'e3 gi\'cay ch\'f8ng nh\'cbn quy\'d2n s\'eb h\'f7u v\'d7 tr\'ad\'edc kia s\'ac su
\'cat kh\'abng xin n\'aan ph\'b6i b\'e1 nh\'b5 c\'f6a. Th\'d5 l\'b5 th\'b5nh ph\'e8 l\'cay l\'b9i \'ae\'cat v\'b5 b\'b8n l\'cay ti\'d2n b\'e1 qu\'fc.
\par Trong ph\'c7n nhi\'d2u c\'b8c th\'b5nh ph\'e8 l\'edn, m\'e9t h\'e9i \'ae\'e5ng th\'b5nh ph\'e8 g\'e5m to\'b5n nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai \'a2u, tu\'fa \'fd s\'f6 d\'f4ng c\'abng qu\'fc do ng\'ad\'eai b\'b6n x\'f8 \'ae\'e3ng g\'e3p m\'b5 ch\'bcng \'ae\'d5m x\'d8
a g\'d7 \'ae\'d5n nguy\'d6n v\'e4ng v\'b5 nhu c\'c7u c\'f1a nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai An Nam kh\'e8n kh\'e6 n\'b5y.
\par }\pard \qc \li0\ri0\sb120\sa80\sl-274\slmult0\nowidctlpar\tx7513\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 *\line *    *
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-274\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\expnd0\expndtw-4\insrsid1378858 M\'e9t ng\'ad\'eai Ph\'b8p t\'f9 h\'e1i: C\'e3 n\'ad\'edc n\'b5o tr\'aan th\'d5 gi\'edi d\'b8m khoe nh
\'ad \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng c\'e3 nguy\'aan li\'d6u v\'b5 nh\'a9n c\'abng r\'ce m\'b9t m\'b5 l\'b5m m\'e9t \'ae\'ad\'eang xe l\'f6a ph\'b6i t\'e8n ph\'dd t\'f5 16 \'ae\'d5n 20 phr\'a8ng m\'e9t x\'a8ngtim\'d0t kh\'abng ?
\par }{\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 Khi l\'b5m \'ae\'ad\'eang h\'c7m \'eb \'ae\'cco H\'b6i V\'a9n, mu\'e8n cho c\'abng vi\'d6c mau ch\'e3ng, ng\'ad\'eai ta \'ae\'f4c c\'b6 hai \'ae\'c7u v\'b5o m\'e9t l\'f3c. Hai \'aeo\'b9n \'ae\'f4c \'eb hai \'ae\'c7u v\'b5o kh
\'abng \'a8n kh\'edp v\'edi nhau, th\'b5nh th\'f6 ra m\'e7i \'aeo\'b9n \'ae\'b7 th\'b5nh ri\'aang bi\'d6t m\'e9t \'ae\'ad\'eang h\'c7m ho\'b5n to\'b5n. H\'c7m \'ae\'f4c ngay gi\'f7a n\'f3i \'ae\'b8, th\'d5 m\'b5 ng\'ad\'eai ta c\'f8 ph\'b6i x\'a9y th\'aa
m m\'e9t l\'edp \'ae\'b8 n\'f7a \'eb ngo\'b5i, tr\'b8t th\'cbt k\'fc l\'ad\'ecng l\'b5m hao t\'e8n bao nhi\'aau c\'f1a.
\par }\pard \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 \'a7\'ad\'eang L\'b9ng S\'acn, \'ae\'bep \'ae\'d3 d\'efng v\'b5o vi\'d6c b\'d7nh \'ae\'denh v\'efng \'cay, d\'f9 tr\'ef
 h\'d5t c\'e3 4 tri\'d6u, nh\'adng l\'b5m xong t\'e8n \'ae\'d5n 38 tri\'d6u.
\par Ch\'ada c\'bem \'ae\'ad\'eec m\'e9t c\'b8i m\'e8c n\'b5o tr\'aan \'aeo\'b9n \'ae\'ad\'eang d\'f9 \'ae\'denh l\'b5m, ng\'ad\'eai ta \'ae\'b7 cho tr\'adng th\'c7u cung c\'cap r\'cat nhi\'d2u \'ae\'ad\'eang ray v\'b5 nhi\'d2u v\'cbt li\'d6u kh\'b8c. Khi vi
\'aan thanh tra g\'c7n t\'edi, ng\'ad\'eai ta \'aeem ch\'abn bi\'d5n nh\'f7ng \'ae\'ad\'eang ray \'ae\'b8ng l\'cf c\'dfn l\'a9u l\'bem m\'edi ph\'b6i mua \'cay, xu\'e8ng nh\'f7ng h\'e8 d\'b5i m\'cay kil\'abm\'d0t.
\par K\'fc s\'ad tr\'ef t\'ddnh h\'d5t 94 tri\'d6u, nh\'adng khi chi ti\'aau l\'b9i m\'cat \'ae\'d5n 165 tri\'d6u.
\par \'a4ng Combane, nh\'b5 th\'b8m hi\'d3m k\'d3 tr\'aan, c\'dfn n\'e3i th\'aam r\'bbng: Ch\'d8 vi\'d6c nghi\'aan c\'f8u \'ae\'d3 \'ae\'c6t \'ae\'ad\'eang xe l\'f6a \'eb \'a7\'abng D\'ad\'acng c\'f2ng \'ae\'b7 t\'e8n h\'d5t s\'e8 ti\'d2n l\'edn c\'e3 th\'d3 
\'ae\'f1 \'ae\'d3 l\'b5m c\'b6 qu\'b7ng \'ae\'ad\'eang \'cay.
\par 
\par 
\par }\pard\plain \s21\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-280\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \b\f39\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\insrsid1378858 
