\cs17\super\insrsid1378858 1{\footnote \pard\plain \s28\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa60\sl-240\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid1378858 1) Th\'ad n\'b5y \'ae
