\par }}\pard\plain \s25\qj \li0\ri0\sa80\sl-270\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f38\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 cho vi\'d6c \'ae\'e3, \'ae\'b7 c\'e3 nh\'f7ng \'b8n t
\'f6 h\'d7nh v\'b5 h\'b5ng tr\'a8m ng\'ad\'eai \'ae\'b7 b\'de m\'cat \'ae\'c7u.
\par }\pard\plain \s18\qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f37\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\fs20\insrsid1378858 - Ng\'ad\'eai d\'a9n An Nam kh\'abng c\'e3 linh m\'f4
c, kh\'abng c\'e3 t\'abn gi\'b8o, theo c\'b8ch ngh\'dc c\'f1a ch\'a9u \'a2u. Vi\'d6c c\'f3ng b\'b8i t\'e6 ti\'aan ho\'b5n to\'b5n l\'b5 m\'e9t hi\'d6n t\'ad\'eeng x\'b7 h\'e9i. Ch\'f3ng t\'abi kh\'abng c\'e3 nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai t\'ad t\'d5 n\'b5o. Nh\'f7
ng ng\'ad\'eai gi\'b5 trong gia \'ae\'d7nh hay c\'b8c gi\'b5 b\'b6n l\'b5 ng\'ad\'eai th\'f9c hi\'d6n nh\'f7ng nghi l\'d4 t\'ad\'ebng ni\'d6m. Ch\'f3ng t\'abi kh\'abng bi\'d5t uy t\'ddn c\'f1a ng\'ad\'eai th\'c7y c\'f3ng, c\'f1a linh m\'f4c l\'b5 g\'d7.

\par }\pard\plain \qj \fi397\li0\ri0\sa80\sl-260\slmult0\nowidctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 - V\'a9ng, th\'cbt th\'f3 v\'de l\'b5 ch\'ddnh quy
\'d2n Ph\'b8p \'ae\'b7 d\'b9y cho nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai n\'abng d\'a9n ch\'f3ng t\'abi bi\'d5t nh\'f7ng t\'f5 "b\'abns\'aav\'ddch" v\'b5 "L\'aanin". Ch\'f3ng l\'efng b\'bet nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai c\'e9ng s\'b6n trong d\'a9n ch\'f3ng, trong khi ch\'bcng c\'e3
 ng\'ad\'eai c\'e9ng s\'b6n n\'b5o, ho\'b5n to\'b5n kh\'abng c\'e3 ngay c\'b6 trong \'fd ni\'d6m, v\'b5 nh\'ad v\'cby ch\'ddnh ch\'f3ng \'ae\'b7 tuy\'aan truy\'d2n cho ch\'f1 ngh\'dca b\'abns\'aav\'ddch v\'b5 L\'aanin.
\par D\'a9n An Nam l\'b5 m\'e9t d\'a9n t\'e9c gi\'b6n d\'de v\'b5 l\'dech thi\'d6p. Qua phong th\'b8i thanh cao, trong gi\'e4ng n\'e3i tr\'c7m \'cam c\'f1a Nguy\'d4n }{\f38\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 \'b8}{\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 i Qu\'e8c, ch\'f3
ng ta nh\'ad nghe th\'cay ng\'b5y mai, nh\'ad th\'cay s\'f9 y\'aan t\'dcnh m\'aanh m\'abng c\'f1a t\'d7nh h\'f7u \'b8i to\'b5n th\'d5 gi\'edi.
\par Tr\'aan b\'b5n c\'e3 m\'e9t t\'cbp b\'b6n th\'b6o, m\'e9t b\'b6n b\'b8o c\'b8o c\'abng t\'b8c r\'e2 r\'b5ng, mang phong c\'b8ch truy\'d2n tin c\'f1a ph\'e3ng vi\'aan. Anh \'aeang t\'ad\'ebng t\'ad\'eeng \'ae\'d5n \'ae\'d2 t\'b5i: \'a7\'b9i h\'e9i Qu\'e8
c t\'d5 C\'e9ng s\'b6n n\'a8m 1947. Anh nh\'ad \'aeang nh\'d7n th\'cay, nghe th\'cay di\'d4n bi\'d5n c\'f1a h\'e9i ngh\'de, m\'b5 \'eb \'ae\'e3 anh s\'cf \'aei\'d2u khi\'d3n ch\'ad\'acng tr\'d7nh ngh\'de s\'f9.
\par L\'f3c chia tay, Nguy\'d4n }{\f38\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 \'b8}{\f37\fs20\cgrid0\insrsid1378858 i Qu\'e8c nh\'ad nh\'ed \'aei\'d2u g\'d7.
\par - V\'a9ng, ch\'f3ng t\'abi c\'dfn c\'e3 m\'e9t cu\'e9c "n\'e6i d\'cby" n\'f7a do vua An Nam tr\'ce tu\'e6i Duy T\'a9n ph\'b8t \'ae\'e9ng, ch\'e8ng l\'b9i vi\'d6c \'ae\'ada nh\'f7ng ng\'ad\'eai n\'abng d\'a9n c\'f1a ch\'f3ng t\'abi \'ae\'d5n chi\'d5n tr
\'ad\'eang c\'f1a Ph\'b8p. Vua Duy T\'a9n \'ae\'b7 ch\'b9y, b\'a9y gi\'ea \'abng \'cay \'aeang s\'e8ng l\'adu vong. H\'b7y k\'d3 v\'d2 \'abng \'cay n\'f7a. 
